# <a name="required-diagnostic-data-for-office"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-103">Nepieciešamie Office diagnostikas dati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-103">Required diagnostic data for Office</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-104">Office produktu, uz kuriem attiecas šī konfidencialitātes informācija, saraksts ir pieejams [Konfidencialitātes kontroles līdzekļi Office produktiem](products-versions-privacy-controls.md).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-104">For a list of Office products covered by this privacy information, see [Privacy controls available for Office products](products-versions-privacy-controls.md).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-105">Diagnostikas dati tiek izmantoti, lai uzturētu Office drošu un atjauninātu, noteiktu, diagnosticētu un novērstu problēmas, kā arī uzlabotu produktu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-105">Diagnostic data is used to keep Office secure and up-to-date, detect, diagnose and fix problems, and also make product improvements.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-106">Šie dati neietver lietotāja vārdu vai e-pasta adresi, failu saturu vai informāciju par programmām, kas nav saistītas ar Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-106">This data does not include a user's name or email address, the content of the user's files, or information about apps unrelated to Office.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-107">Šie diagnostikas dati tiek apkopoti un nosūtīti korporācijai Microsoft par Office klienta programmatūru, kas tiek lietota datoros, kuros darbojas operētājsistēma Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-107">This diagnostic data is collected and sent to Microsoft about Office client software being used on computers running Windows.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-108">Daži diagnostikas dati ir nepieciešami, bet daži diagnostikas dati ir neobligāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-108">Some diagnostic data is required, while some diagnostic data is optional.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-109">Piedāvājam jums iespēju izvēlēties, vai sūtīt mums nepieciešamos vai neobligātos diagnostikas datus, izmantojot tādus konfidencialitātes kontroles līdzekļus kā organizācijas politikas iestatījumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-109">We give you the ability to choose whether to send us required or optional diagnostic data through the use of privacy controls, such as policy settings for organizations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-110">Mums sūtāmos diagnostikas datus varat skatīt, izmantojot diagnostikas datu skatītāju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-110">You can see the diagnostic data being sent to us by using the Diagnostic Data Viewer.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-111">***Nepieciešamie diagnostikas dati*** ir minimālie dati, kas nepieciešami, lai Office uzturētu drošu, atjauninātu un ar paredzēto veiktspēju atbilstošajā ierīcē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-111">***Required diagnostic data*** is the minimum data necessary to help keep Office secure, up-to-date, and performing as expected on the device it's installed on.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-112">Nepieciešamie diagnostikas dati palīdz noteikt ar Office saistītas problēmas, kuru cēlonis var būt saistīts ar ierīces vai programmatūras konfigurāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-112">Required diagnostic data helps to identify problems with Office that may be related to a device or software configuration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-113">Piemēram, tie var palīdzēt noteikt, vai Office līdzeklis biežāk avarē noteiktā operētājsistēmas versijā, kopā ar nesen ieviestiem līdzekļiem vai tad, kad ir atspējoti konkrēti Office līdzekļi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-113">For example, it can help determine if an Office feature crashes more frequently on a particular operating system version, with newly introduced features, or when certain Office features are disabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-114">Nepieciešamie diagnostikas dati palīdz mums ātrāk noteikt, diagnosticēt un novērst problēmas, lai mazinātu ietekmi uz lietotājiem vai organizācijām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-114">Required diagnostic data helps us detect, diagnose, and fix these problems more quickly so the impact to users or organizations is reduced.</span></span>

- [<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-116">Neobligātie Office diagnostikas dati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-116">Optional diagnostic data for Office</span></span>](optional-diagnostic-data.md)

## <a name="categories-and-data-fields-that-are-common-for-all-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-167">Kategorijas un datu lauki, kas ir kopīgi visiem notikumiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-167">Categories and data fields that are common for all events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-168">Neatkarīgi no kategorijas vai datu apakštipa pastāv informācija par notikumiem, kas attiecas uz visiem notikumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-168">There is some information about events that is common to all events, regardless of category or data subtype.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-169">Šī kopīgā informācija, ko dažkārt dēvē par *datu līgumiem*, ir sakārtota kategorijās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-169">This common information, which is sometimes referred to as *data contracts*, is organized into categories.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-170">Katrā kategorijā ir lauki, un šie lauki ir atsevišķa notikuma metadati un rekvizīti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-170">Each category contains fields, and these fields are the metadata and properties of an individual event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-171">Šo informāciju varat skatīt, izmantojot diagnostikas datu skatītāju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-171">You can view this information by using the Diagnostic Data Viewer.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-172">Kategorijas, kurās ir apkopota informācija par notikumiem, var iedalīt divās grupās:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-172">The categories of information that is collected about events can be divided into two groups:</span></span>

  - [<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-173">Informācija, kas ir kopīga visiem notikumiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-173">Information common to all events</span></span>](#information-common-to-all-events)
  - [<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-174">Informācija, kas īpaši atbalsta diagnostikas datu apkopošanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-174">Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection</span></span>](#information-that-specifically-supports-diagnostic-data-collection)

### <a name="information-common-to-all-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-175">*Informācija, kas ir kopīga visiem notikumiem*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-175">*Information common to all events*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-176">Informācija, kas ir kopīga visiem notikumiem, tiek apkopota tālāk norādītajās kategorijās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-176">Information common to all events is collected in the following categories.</span></span>

#### <a name="app"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-177">Programma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-177">App</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-178">Informācija par lietojumprogrammu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-178">Information about the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-179">Visi lauki ir konstanti visām attiecīgās lietojumprogrammas versijas sesijām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-179">All fields are constant for all sessions of a given application version.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-180">Šajā kategorijā ir šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-180">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-181">**Branch** — zars, no kura nāk attiecīgā būvējuma versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-181">**Branch** - The branch that the given build came from.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-182">Ļauj mums noteikt, no kāda zara tipa nāk attiecīgais būvējums, lai mēs varētu pareizi piemērot labojumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-182">Allows us to determine what type of branch a given build came from so that we can correctly target fixes.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-183">**InstallType** — skaitītājs, kas norāda, kā lietotājs ir instalējis lietojumprogrammu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-183">**InstallType** - An enumerator that identifies how the user installed the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-184">Ļauj mums noteikt, vai konkrēti instalēšanas mehānismi rada problēmas, kas nav sastopamas citos instalēšanas mehānismos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-184">Allows us to determine if specific install mechanisms are creating issues that are not seen in other installation mechanisms.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-189">**Version** — lietojumprogrammas versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-189">**Version** - The version of the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-190">Ļauj mums noteikt, kurās produkta versijās ir radusies problēma, lai mēs varētu pareizi noteikt tās prioritāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-190">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>

#### <a name="session"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-249">Sesija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-249">Session</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-250">Informācija par procesa sesiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-250">Information about the process session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-251">Visi šīs sesijas lauki ir konstanti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-251">All fields are constant for this session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-252">Šajā kategorijā ir šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-252">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-253">**ABConfigs** — norāda testējamo variantu kopu, kas darbojas konkrētajā sesijā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-253">**ABConfigs** - Identifies the set of flights that are running in a given session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-254">Ļauj mums noteikt, kuri konkrētie testējamie varianti darbojas sesijā, lai mēs varētu noteikt, vai testējamā versija ir tās problēmas cēlonis, kas ietekmē lietotājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-254">Allows us to identify which individual flights are running on a session so that we can determine if a flight is the source of an issue impacting users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-255">**EcsETag** — indikators no testējamo variantu sistēmas, kas apzīmē mašīnai nosūtītos testējamos variantus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-255">**EcsETag** - An indicator from the flighting system that represents the flights sent to the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-256">Ļauj mums noteikt, kuri testējamie varianti, iespējams, ietekmē attiecīgo sesiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-256">Allows us to identify what flights might be impacting a given session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-257">**Flags** — karodziņi, kas izseko bitmasku un attiecas uz visu sesiju. Pašlaik galvenā uzmanība tiek pievērsta iztveršanai un diagnostikas datu opcijām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-257">**Flags** - Bitmask tracking flags applicable to an entire session, currently primarily focused on sampling and diagnostic data options.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-258">Ļauj mums kontrolēt attiecīgās sesijas darbību saistībā ar sesijas ģenerētajiem diagnostikas datiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-258">Allows us to control how a given session behaves in relation to the diagnostic data that the session generates.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-259">**Id** — unikāli identificē attiecīgo datu sesiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-259">**Id** - Uniquely identifies a given session of data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-260">Ļauj mums noteikt problēmu ietekmi, izvērtējot ietekmēto sesiju skaitu un nosakot, vai šīm sesijām ir kopīgi līdzekļi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-260">Allows us to identify the impact of issues by evaluating the number of sessions that are impacted and if there are common features of those sessions.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-263">**MeasuresEnabled** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai pašreizējie sesijas dati tiek iztverti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-263">**MeasuresEnabled** - Flag indicating if the current sessions data is sampled or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-264">Ļauj mums noteikt, kā statistiski izvērtēt datus, kas tiek apkopoti no attiecīgās sesijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-264">Allows us to determine how to statistically evaluate the data that is gathered from the given session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-265">**SamplingClientIdValue** — klienta ID, kas tiek izmantots, lai noteiktu, vai tas ir daļa no iztveršanas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-265">**SamplingClientIdValue** - The id of the client used to determine if it is part of sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-266">Ļauj mums noteikt, kāpēc konkrēta sesija tika iekļauta vai neiekļauta iztveršanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-266">Allows us to determine why an individual session was included or excluded from sampling.</span></span>
  
 - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-267">**SubAppName** — Office mobilo programmai šis lauks apzīmē pamatā esošo programmu, kas tiek lietota, lai atvērtu dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-267">**SubAppName** - For Office Mobile app, this field represents the underlying application being used to open a document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-268">Piemēram, ja Office atverat Word dokumentu, šajā laukā tiek parādīta "Word" vērtība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-268">For example, if you open a Word document in Office app, this field will report the value of “Word”.</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-269">**VirtualizationType** — virtualizācijas tips, ja Office darbojas tajā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-269">**VirtualizationType** - Type of virtualization if Office is running in one.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-270">Iespējamās vērtības:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-270">The possible values are:</span></span> 
    - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-271">0 = Neviens</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-271">0 = None</span></span>

#### <a name="user"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-275">Lietotājs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-275">User</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-276">Sniedz komerciālās programmatūras SKU informāciju par nomnieku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-276">Provides tenant information for commercial software SKUs.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-278">**PrimaryIdentityHash** — identifikatora pseidonīms, kas apzīmē pašreizējo lietotāju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-278">**PrimaryIdentityHash** – A pseudonymous identifier that represents the current user.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-279">**PrimaryIdentitySpace** — tās identitātes tips, kas atrodas šeit: PrimaryIdentityHash.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-279">**PrimaryIdentitySpace** – The type of identity contained in the PrimaryIdentityHash.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-280">Kāds no MASCID, OrgIdCID vai UserObjectId.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-280">One of MASCID, OrgIdCID or UserObjectId.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-281">**TenantGroup** — tā nomnieka tips, kam pieder abonements.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-281">**TenantGroup** - The type of the tenant that the subscription belongs to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-282">Ļauj mums klasificēt problēmas un noteikt, vai problēma ir plaši izplatīta vai izolēta lietotāju kopā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-282">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-283">**TenantId** — nomnieks, ar kuru ir saistīts lietotāja abonements.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-283">**TenantId** - The tenant that a user's subscription is tied to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-284">Ļauj mums klasificēt problēmas un noteikt, vai problēma ir plaši izplatīta vai izolēta konkrēta nomnieka lietotāju kopā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-284">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users or a specific tenant.</span></span>

### <a name="information-that-specifically-supports-diagnostic-data-collection"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-285">*Informācija, kas īpaši atbalsta diagnostikas datu apkopošanu*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-285">*Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-286">Informācija, kas īpaši atbalsta diagnostikas datu apkopošanu, tiek apkopota tālāk norādītajās kategorijās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-286">Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection is collected in the following categories.</span></span>

#### <a name="activity"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-287">Darbība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-287">Activity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-288">Informācija, lai izprastu paša pasākuma apkopošanas panākumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-288">Information to understand the success of the collection event itself.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-289">Šajā kategorijā ir šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-289">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-290">**AggMode** — nosaka, kā sistēmai jāapkopo darbības rezultāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-290">**AggMode** - Tells the system how to aggregate activity results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-291">Ļauj mums samazināt no lietotāja mašīnas augšupielādētās informācijas apjomu, apkopojot darbības rezultātus vienā notikumā, kas tiek periodiski nosūtīts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-291">Allows us to reduce the amount of information uploaded from a user's machine by aggregating activity results into a single event that gets sent periodically.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-292">**Count** — notikušās darbības reižu skaits, ja skaits ir no apkopotā notikuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-292">**Count** - The number of times the activity happened if the count is from an aggregated event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-293">Ļauj mums noteikt, cik bieži darbība izdevās vai neizdevās, pamatojoties uz darbības apkopošanas režīmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-293">Allows us to determine how often an activity succeeded or failed based on the aggregation mode of the activity.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-294">**CV** — vērtība, kas norāda relāciju starp darbībām un pakārtotajām darbībām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-294">**CV** - A value that identifies the relationship between activities and sub-activities.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-295">Ļauj mums atjaunot relāciju starp ligzdotajām darbībām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-295">Allows us to rebuild the relationship between nested activities.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-296">**Duration** — darbības izpildei nepieciešamais laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-296">**Duration** - The length of time the activity took to execute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-297">Ļauj mums noteikt veiktspējas problēmas, kas negatīvi ietekmē lietotāju pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-297">Allows us to identify performance issues that are negatively impacting the user's experience.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-298">**Result**.**Code** — programmas definēts kods, lai identificētu noteiktu rezultātu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-298">**Result**.**Code** - An application defined code to identify a given result.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-299">Ļauj mums noteikt specifiskāku informāciju par konkrēto kļūmi, piemēram, kļūmes kodu, ko var izmantot, lai klasificētu un novērstu problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-299">Allows us to determine more specific details of a given failure such as a failure code that can be used to classify and fix issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-300">**Result.Tag** — vesela skaitļa tags, kas nosaka atrašanās vietu kodā, kurā tika ģenerēts rezultāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-300">**Result.Tag** - An integer tag that identifies the location in code where the result was generated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-301">Ļauj mums skaidri noteikt atrašanās vietu kodā, kurā tika ģenerēts rezultāts, kas iespējo kļūmju klasifikāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-301">Allows us to distinctly identify the location in code where a result was generated which enables classification of failures.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-302">**Result**.**Type** — rezultāta koda tips.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-302">**Result**.**Type** - The type of the result code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-303">Norāda nosūtītā rezultātu koda tipu, lai varētu pareizi interpretēt vērtību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-303">Identifies what type of result code was sent so that the value can be correctly interpreted.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-304">**Success** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai darbība izdevās vai neizdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-304">**Success** - A flag indicating if the activity succeeded or failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-305">Ļauj mums noteikt, vai lietotāja veiktās darbības produktā ir sekmīgas vai nesekmīgas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-305">Allows us to determine if actions the user takes in the product are succeeding or failing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-306">Ļauj mums noteikt problēmas, kas ietekmē lietotāju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-306">This allows us to identify issues that are impacting the user.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-314">**DistributionChannel** — kanāls, kurā ir izvietota programma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-314">**DistributionChannel** - The channel where the app was deployed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-315">Ļauj mums sadalīt ienākošos datus, lai mēs varētu noteikt, vai problēmas ietekmē auditoriju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-315">Allows us to partition incoming data so we can determine if issues are impacting audiences.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-316">**InstallMethod** — vai pašreizējais Office būvējums tika jaunināts, atritināts vai instalēts no jauna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-316">**InstallMethod** - Whether the current build of Office was upgraded from an older build, rolled back to an older build, or a fresh install.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-317">**IsClickToRunInstall** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai tika veikta Click-To-Run instalācija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-317">**IsClickToRunInstall** - Flag indicating if install was a click to run install.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-318">Ļauj mums noteikt problēmas, kas varētu būt specifiskas Click-To-Run instalēšanas mehānismam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-318">Allows us to identify issues that might be specific to the Click-To-Run install mechanism.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-319">**IsDebug** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai Office būvējums ir atkļūdošanas būvējums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-319">**IsDebug** - Flag indicating if the Office build is a Debug build.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-320">Ļauj mums noteikt, vai problēmas rodas no atkļūdošanas būvējumiem, kas, iespējams, darbojas atšķirīgi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-320">Allows us to identify if issues are coming from Debug builds which may behave differently.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-321">**IsInstalledOnExternalStorage** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai Office ir instalēts ārējās atmiņas ierīcē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-321">**IsInstalledOnExternalStorage** - Flag indicating if Office was installed on an external storage device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-322">Ļauj mums noteikt, vai problēmas ir saistītas ar ārējās atmiņas ierīces atrašanās vietu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-322">Let's us determine if issues can be traced to an external storage location.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-323">**IsOEMInstalled** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai Office instalēja oriģinālā aprīkojuma ražotājs (OEM).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-323">**IsOEMInstalled** - Flag indicating if Office was installed by an original equipment manufacturer (OEM).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-324">Ļauj mums noteikt, vai lietojumprogramma tika instalēta, izmantojot OEM. Tas mums var palīdzēt klasificēt un noteikt problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-324">Let's us determine if the application was installed by an OEM which can help us classify and identify issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-325">**PreviousVersion** — Tā Office versija, kas bija iepriekš instalēta datorā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-325">**PreviousVersion** - The version of Office that was previously installed on the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-326">Ļauj atgriezties uz iepriekšējo versiju, ja pašreizējā versijā ir radusies problēma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-326">Allows us to roll back to a previous version if the current one has an issue.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-327">**ProcessFileName** — lietojumprogrammas faila nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-327">**ProcessFileName** - The name of the application filename.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-328">Ļauj mums noteikt tās izpildāmā procesa nosaukumu, kas ģenerē datus, jo var būt vairāki dažādu procesu failu nosaukumi, kuriem ir tās pašas programmas nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-328">Allows us to identify the name of the executable which is generating the data as there may be several different process filenames reporting as the same app name.</span></span>

#### <a name="event"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-387">Notikums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-387">Event</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-388">Notikumam raksturīga informācija, tostarp tā unikālais identifikators sesijā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-388">Event-specific information, including its unique identifier in the session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-389">Šajā kategorijā ir šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-389">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-390">**Contract** — to līgumu saraksts, kurus ievieš notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-390">**Contract** - A list of any contracts that the event is implementing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-391">Ļauj mums novērtēt, kādi dati ir daļa no atsevišķā notikuma, lai mēs to varētu efektīvi apstrādāt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-391">Allows us to evaluate what data is part of the individual event so that we can process it effectively.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-392">**CV** — vērtība, kas ļauj mums noteikt savstarpēji saistītus notikumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-392">**CV** - A value that allows us to identify events that are related to one another.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-393">Tiek izmantota diagnostikā, ļaujot mums noteikt saistīto darbību vai notikumu modeļus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-393">Used for diagnostics to allow us to identify patterns of related behavior or related events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-394">**Flags** — informācija, kas tiek izmantota, lai mainītu attiecīgā notikuma atbildi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-394">**Flags** - Information used to alter how a given event responds.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-395">Tiek izmantots nolūkā pārvaldīt veidu, kā notikums tiek apstrādāts, lai augšupielādētu datus korporācijai Microsoft.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-395">Used to manage how a given event is treated for the purposes of uploading the data to Microsoft.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-396">**Id** — unikāls notikuma identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-396">**Id** - A unique identifier for the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-397">Ļauj mums unikāli identificēt saņemtos notikumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-397">Allows us to uniquely identify the events that are being received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-398">**Level** — apzīmē notikuma veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-398">**Level** - denotes the type of event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-399">**Name** — notikuma nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-399">**Name** - The name of the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-400">Ļauj noteikt notikumu, kas tiek nosūtīts no klienta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-400">Allows to identify the event that was being sent from the client.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-401">**Rule** — tās kārtulas identifikators, kas ģenerēja datus, ja tos ģenerēja kārtula.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-401">**Rule** - An identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-402">Ļauj mums noteikt datu avotu, lai mēs varētu pārbaudīt un pārvaldīt notikuma parametrus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-402">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-403">**RuleId** — tās kārtulas identifikators, kas ģenerēja datus, ja tos ģenerēja kārtula.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-403">**RuleId** - The identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-404">Ļauj mums noteikt datu avotu, lai mēs varētu pārbaudīt un pārvaldīt notikuma parametrus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-404">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-405">**RuleInterfaces** — jebkurš interfeiss, kuru ievieš konkrēta kārtula.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-405">**RuleInterfaces** - Any interfaces that are implemented by the specific rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-406">Ļauj mums klasificēt un importēt datus atbilstoši to struktūrai, kas vienkāršo datu apstrādi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-406">Allows us to classify and import the data based on its structure which simplifies data processing.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-407">**RuleVersion** — tās kārtulas identifikators, kas ģenerēja datus, ja tos ģenerēja kārtula.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-407">**RuleVersion** - The identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-408">Ļauj mums noteikt datu avotu, lai mēs varētu pārbaudīt un pārvaldīt notikuma parametrus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-408">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-409">**SampleRate** — norāda lietotāju, kas sūta šo datu fragmentu, skaitu procentos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-409">**SampleRate** - An indication of what percentage of users are sending this piece of data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-410">Tas ļauj mums veikt datu statistisko analīzi un nodrošina to, ka ne visiem lietotājiem ir jānosūta biežāk izmantotie datu punkti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-410">This allows us to do statistical analysis of the data and for very common data points not require that to be sent by all users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-411">**SchemaVersion** — shēmas versija, kas tiek izmantota, lai ģenerētu diagnostikas datus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-411">**SchemaVersion** - The version of the schema used to generate diagnostic data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-412">Nepieciešams, lai pārvaldītu klienta sūtītos datus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-412">Required to manage data being sent from the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-413">Tādējādi laika gaitā var mainīt, kādi dati tiek sūtīti no katra klienta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-413">This allows changes over time in what data is being sent from each client.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-414">**Sequence** — skaitītājs, kas identificē secību, kādā tika ģenerēts notikums klientā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-414">**Sequence** - A counter that identifies the order that an event was generated on the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-415">Ļauj kārtot saņemtos datus, lai mēs varētu noteikt darbības, kas, iespējams, izraisīja problēmu, kas ietekmē klientus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-415">Allows the data being received to be ordered so that we can identify what steps may have led to an issue that is impacting clients.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-416">**Source** — avota kanāls, kas tika izmantots, lai augšupielādētu datus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-416">**Source** - The source pipeline that was used to upload the data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-417">Nepieciešams, lai pārraudzītu mūsu augšupielādes kanālu vispārējo darbspēju un palīdzētu noteikt problēmas saistībā ar augšupielādes kanālu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-417">Required to monitor each of our upload pipelines for overall health and to help identify issues with the upload pipeline.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-418">Tas ļauj kontrolēt atsevišķus augšupielādes kanālus, lai nodrošinātu to atbilstību prasībām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-418">This allows us to monitor individual upload pipelines to make sure they remain compliant.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-419">**Time** — laiks, kad klientā tika ģenerēts notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-419">**Time** - The time that the event was generated on the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-420">Ļauj mums sinhronizēt un pārbaudīt to notikumu secību, kas ir ģenerēti klientā, kā arī izveidot veiktspējas rādītājus lietošanas norādījumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-420">Allows us to synchronize and validate the order of events generated on the client as well as establish performance metrics for user instructions.</span></span>

#### <a name="session"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-438">Sesija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-438">Session</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-439">Informācija par procesa sesiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-439">Information about the process session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-441">**ABConfigsDelta** — izseko atšķirībai starp pašreizējiem ABConfigs datiem un iepriekšējo vērtību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-441">**ABConfigsDelta** - Tracks the difference between the current ABConfigs data and the previous value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-442">Ļauj mums izsekot jauniem mašīnā esošiem testējamiem variantiem, lai palīdzētu noteikt, vai problēma ir radusies jauna testējamā varianta dēļ.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-442">Allows us to track what new flights are on the machine to help identify if a new flight is responsible for an issue.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-445">**DisableTelemetry** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai ir iestatīta atslēga DisableTelemetry.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-445">**DisableTelemetry** - Flag indicating if the DisableTelemetry key is set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-446">Ļauj mums uzzināt, vai sesija ziņo par citiem diagnostikas datiem, kas nav EssentialServiceMetadata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-446">Allows us to know if a session was not reporting diagnostic data other than EssentialServiceMetadata.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-447">**SamplingClientIdValue** — tās atslēgas vērtība, kas tiek izmantota iztveršanas noteikšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-447">**SamplingClientIdValue** - The value of the key used to determine sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-448">Ļauj mums noteikt, kāpēc tika iztverta (vai neiztverta) sesija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-448">Allows us to determine why a session was sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-449">**SamplingDeviceIdValue** — tās atslēgas vērtība, kas tiek izmantota iztveršanas noteikšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-449">**SamplingDeviceIdValue** - The value of the key used to determine sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-450">Ļauj mums noteikt, kāpēc tika iztverta (vai neiztverta) sesija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-450">Allows us to determine why a session was sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-451">**SamplingKey** — atslēga, kas tiek izmantota, lai noteiktu, vai sesija ir iztverta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-451">**SamplingKey** - The key used to determine whether the session is sampled or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-452">Ļauj mums saprast, kā atsevišķas sesijas izvēlas savu iztveršanas statusu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-452">Allows us to understand how individual sessions are making their choice of whether they are sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-453">**SamplingMethod** — metode, kas tiek izmantota, lai noteiktu iztveršanas politiku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-453">**SamplingMethod** - The method used to determine sampling policy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-454">Ļauj mums saprast, kādi dati nāk no sesijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-454">Allows us to understand what data is coming from a session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-455">**SamplingSessionKValue** — papildu iztveršanas metadati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-455">**SamplingSessionKValue** - Advanced sampling metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-456">Izmanto, lai palīdzētu novērtēt saņemto datu statistikas nozīmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-456">Used to help evaluate statistical meaning of data that is received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-457">**SamplingSessionNValue** — papildu iztveršanas metadati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-457">**SamplingSessionNValue** - Advanced sampling metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-458">Izmanto, lai palīdzētu novērtēt saņemto datu statistikas nozīmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-458">Used to help evaluate statistical meaning of data that is received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-459">**Sequence** — unikāls skaitlisks sesijas identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-459">**Sequence** - A unique numeric identifier for the session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-460">Ļauj kārtot sesijas, lai analizētu iespējamās problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-460">Allows the ordering of sessions for analysis of the issues might have occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-461">**Start** — procesa sesijas palaišanas laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-461">**Start** - The boot time of the process session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-462">Ļauj mums noteikt sesijas sākumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-462">Allows us to establish when the session started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-463">**TelemetryPermissionLevel** — vērtība, kas norāda, kāda līmeņa diagnostikas datiem ir piekritis lietotājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-463">**TelemetryPermissionLevel** - Value indicating what level of diagnostic data the user has opted into.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-464">Ļauj mums saprast, kāda līmeņa diagnostikas datus var sagaidīt no sesijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-464">Allows us to understand what level of diagnostic data to expect from a session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-465">**TimeZoneBiasInMinutes** — starpība minūtēs starp UTC un vietējo laiku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-465">**TimeZoneBiasInMinutes** - The difference in minutes between UTC and the local time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-466">Ļauj normalizēt UTC laiku atpakaļ uz vietējo laiku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-466">Allows normalization of UTC times back to the local time.</span></span>

## <a name="data-fields-that-are-common-for-onenote-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-467">OneNote notikumiem kopīgie datu lauki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-467">Data fields that are common for OneNote events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-468">Zemāk norādītie datu lauki ir kopīgi visiem OneNote notikumiem Mac, iOS un Android operētājsistēmās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-468">The following data fields are common for all events for OneNote on Mac, iOS, and Android.</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-469">Izmantojot Diagnostikas datu skatītāju, OneNote notikumi Mac, iOS un Android operētājsistēmās tiek saukti par Activity, ReportData vai Unexpected.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-469">When using the Diagnostic Data Viewer, events for OneNote on Mac, iOS, and Android will appear to have a name of Activity, ReportData, or Unexpected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-470">Faktiskā notikuma nosaukuma meklēšanai atlasiet notikumu un apskatiet lauku EventName.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-470">To find the actual event name, select the event, and then look at the EventName field.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-471">**Activity_ActivityType** —  norāda uz šīs darbības notikuma veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-471">**Activity_ActivityType** -  Indicates the type of this activity event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-472">Darbība var būt normāla vai augstvērtīga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-472">An activity can be a normal activity or a high value activity.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-473">**Activity_AggMode** —  norāda sistēmai, kā apkopot darbības rezultātus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-473">**Activity_AggMode** -  Tells the system how to aggregate activity results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-474">Ļauj mums samazināt no lietotāja mašīnas augšupielādētās informācijas apjomu, apkopojot darbības rezultātus vienā notikumā, kas tiek periodiski nosūtīts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-474">Allows us to reduce the amount of information uploaded from a user's machine by aggregating activity results into a single event that gets sent periodically.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-475">**Count** — notikušās darbības reižu skaits, ja skaits ir no apkopotā notikuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-475">**Activity_Count** -  The number of times the activity happened if the count is from an aggregated event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-476">Ļauj mums noteikt, cik bieži darbība izdevās vai neizdevās, pamatojoties uz darbības apkopošanas režīmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-476">Allows us to determine how often an activity succeeded or failed based on the aggregation mode of the activity.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-479">**Activity_DetachedDurationInMicroseconds** — laiks, kad darbība ir dīkstāvē un faktiski neveic darbu, bet šis laiks joprojām ieskaitītas darbības kopējā laikā.  </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-479">**Activity_DetachedDurationInMicroseconds** -  The length of time an activity is idle and not doing any real work, but the time is still count towards the total activity's time.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-480">**Activity_DurationInMicroseconds** — darbības izpildei nepieciešamais laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-480">**Activity_DurationInMicroseconds** -  The length of time the activity took to execute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-481">Ļauj mums noteikt veiktspējas problēmas, kas negatīvi ietekmē lietotāju pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-481">Allows us to identify performance issues that are negatively impacting the user's experience.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-482">**Activity_Expiration** — datums skaitliskā formātā, kas norāda laiku, kad šis notikums pārtrauks sūtīšanu no klientiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-482">**Activity_Expiration** -  A date in numerical format indicates when this event will be stop sending from clients</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-483">**Activity_FailCount** — darbības neizdošanās reižu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-483">**Activity_FailCount** -  A number of times this activity has failed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-484">**Activity_Name** — īss notikuma nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-484">**Activity_Name** -  A short name of an event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-485">Ļauj noteikt notikumu, kas tiek nosūtīts no klienta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-485">Allows to identify the event that was being sent from the client.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-486">**Activity_Namespace** — notikuma nosaukumu apgabals.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-486">**Activity_Namespace** -  A namespace of an event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-487">Ļauj grupēt notikumu grupās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-487">Allows to group the event into groups.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-488">**Activity_Reason** — virkne, kas norāda uz iemeslu, kura dēļ darbība beidzas ar konkrēto rezultātu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-488">**Activity_Reason** -  A string indicating the reason causing an activity to ends with a particular result.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-489">**Activity_Result** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai darbība izdevās, neizdevās vai negaidīti neizdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-489">**Activity_Result** -  A flag indicating if the activity succeeded, failed, or unexpectedly failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-490">Ļauj mums noteikt, vai lietotāja veiktās darbības produktā ir sekmīgas vai nesekmīgas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-490">Allows us to determine if actions the user takes in the product are succeeding or failing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-491">Ļauj mums noteikt problēmas, kas ietekmē lietotāju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-491">This allows us to identify issues that are impacting the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-493">**Activity_SucceedCount** — darbības izdošanās reižu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-493">**Activity_SucceedCount** -  A number of times this activity is succeeded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-494">**ErrorCode** —  norāda kļūdas kodu, ja ir.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-494">**ErrorCode** -  Indicates an error code if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-495">**ErrorCode2** —  norāda otro kļūdas kodu, ja ir.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-495">**ErrorCode2** -  Indicates a second error code if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-496">**ErrorCode3** —  norāda trešo kļūdas kodu, ja ir.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-496">**ErrorCode3** -  Indicates a third error code if available.</span></span>
