- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-510">**Release_AppStore** — karodziņš, kas norāda uz to, vai būvējums nāk no AppStore.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-510">**Release_AppStore** -  A flag indicates whether a build is coming from an app store or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-511">**Release_Audience** — norāda konkrētās auditorijas grupas apakšauditoriju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-511">**Release_Audience** -  Identifies a sub-audience of a given audience group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-512">Ļauj mums izsekot auditorijas grupu apakškopām, lai novērtētu problēmu izplatību un noteiktu to prioritāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-512">Allows us to track subsets of audience groups to evaluate prevalence and prioritization of issues.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-513">**Release_AudienceGroup** — norāda loku, no kura nāk dati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-513">**Release_AudienceGroup** -  Identifies the ring where data is coming from.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-514">Ļauj mums pakāpeniski izlaist līdzekļus un identificēt potenciālās problēmas, pirms lielākā daļa lietotāju ir ar tām saskārušās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-514">Allows us to roll out features in a staged fashion and identify potential issues before they reach most users.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-515">**Release_Channel** — kanāls, kurā tiek izlaists produkts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-515">**Release_Channel** -  The channel that the product is being released through.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-516">Ļauj mums noteikt, vai problēma ietekmē kādu no mūsu izlaišanas kanāliem citādi nekā citus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-516">Allows us to identify if an issue is impacting one of our rollout channels differently than others.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-517">**RunningMode** — norāda, vai lietojumprogrammu palaiž lietotājs vai sistēmas process.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-517">**RunningMode** -  Indicates how the app is launched either by user or by system process.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-518">**SchemaVersion** — norāda pašreizējo telemetrijas shēmas versiju OneNote telemetrijas kanālā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-518">**SchemaVersion** -  Indicates a current telemetry schema version in OneNote's telemetry pipeline.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-519">**session_EcsETag** — indikators no testējamo variantu sistēmas, kas apzīmē mašīnai nosūtītos testējamos variantus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-519">**Session_EcsETag** -  An indicator from the flighting system that represents the flights sent to the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-520">Ļauj mums noteikt, kuri testējamie varianti, iespējams, ietekmē attiecīgo sesiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-520">Allows us to identify what flights might be impacting a given session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-521">**Session_ImpressionId** — norāda testējamo variantu kopu, kas darbojas konkrētajā sesijā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-521">**Session_ImpressionId** -  Identifies the set of flights that are running in a given session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-522">Ļauj mums noteikt, kuri konkrētie testējamie varianti darbojas sesijā, lai mēs varētu noteikt, vai testējamā versija ir tās problēmas cēlonis, kas ietekmē lietotājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-522">Allows us to identify which individual flights are running on a session so that we can determine if a flight is the source of an issue impacting users.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-523">**SessionCorrelationId** — globāli unikāls identifikators resursdatora sesijai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-523">**SessionCorrelationId** -  The globally unique identifier for the host's session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-524">**SH_ErrorCode** —  darbības neizdošanās gadījumā norāda kļūdas kodu, ja ir.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-524">**SH_ErrorCode** -  Indicates an error code if available when an activity fails.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-525">**Tag** — vesela skaitļa tags, kas nosaka atrašanās vietu kodā, kurā tiek ģenerēts telemetrijas notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-525">**Tag** -  An integer tag that identifies the location in code where the telemetry event is generated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-526">**UserInfo_IdType** — virkne, kas norāda lietotāja konta veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-526">**UserInfo_IdType** -  A string indicates the type of a user's account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-527">**UserInfo.OMSTenantId** — nomnieks, kuram ir piesaistīts lietotāja abonements.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-527">**UserInfo_OMSTenantId** -  The tenant that a user's subscription is tied to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-528">Ļauj mums klasificēt problēmas un noteikt, vai problēma ir plaši izplatīta vai izolēta konkrēta nomnieka lietotāju kopā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-528">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users or a specific tenant.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-529">**UserInfo_OtherId** — lietotāja kontus identificējošo pseidonīmu identifikatoru, kas nav primāri, saraksts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-529">**UserInfo_OtherId** -  A list of non-primary pseudonymous identifiers representing user's accounts.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-530">**UserInfo_OtherIdType** —  kontu veidu, kas nav primāri, saraksts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-530">**UserInfo_OtherIdType** -  A list of non-primary account types.</span></span>

## <a name="data-fields-that-are-common-for-outlook-mobile-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-531">Outlook mobilo notikumu kopīgie datu lauki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-531">Data fields that are common for Outlook mobile events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-532">Outlook mobilā versija apkopo kopīgos laukus katram mūsu notikumam, kas ļauj mums nodrošināt to, ka lietojumprogramma ir atjaunināta uz jaunāko versiju, darbojas atbilstošā un drošā veidā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-532">Outlook mobile collects common fields for each of our events so that we can ensure the app is up-to-date, secure, and functioning as expected.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-533">Tālāk norādītie datu lauki ir kopīgi visiem Outlook notikumiem iOS un Android operētājsistēmās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-533">The following data fields are common for all events for Outlook for iOS and Android.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-534">**aad_tenant_id** — klienta nomnieka ID, ja ir pieejams</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-534">**aad_tenant_id** - The tenant id of the customer if available</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-535">**account_cid** — identifikatora pseidonīms, kas apzīmē pašreizējo lietotāju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-535">**account_cid** - A pseudonymous identifier that represents the current user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-536">**account_domain** — konta domēna nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-536">**account_domain** - Domain name of the account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-537">**account_puid** — globāli unikāls lietotāja identifikators Microsoft lietotāja kontam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-537">**account_puid** - The globally unique user identifier for a consumer Microsoft account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-538">**account_type** — seko konta veidam, piemēram, Office 365, Google Cloud Cache, Outlook.com utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-538">**account_type** - Tracks the account type such as Office 365, Google Cloud Cache, Outlook.com, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-539">**action** — notikuma darbības nosaukums (piemēram, arhivēšana, dzēšana utt.), lai mēs spētu atklāt problēmas ar konkrētām veiktajām darbībām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-539">**action** - The event action name (such as archive, delete, etc.) so we can detect issues with specific actions taken</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-540">**ad_id** — unikālais reklāmas identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-540">**ad_id** - The unique advertising identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-541">**app_version**— instalētās lietojumprogrammas pašreizējā versija palīdz mums noteikt problēmas ar konkrētām lietojumprogrammu versijām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-541">**app_version** - Current version of the app installed to help us detect issues affecting certain app version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-542">**AppInfo.ETag** — unikāls identifikators mūsu līdzekļu laidienu pārvaldībai, kas palīdz mums atklāt problēmas, kas ietekmē konkrētu līdzekļu izlaišanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-542">**AppInfo.ETag** - A unique identifier for managing release of our features to help us detect issues affecting certain features being released</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-543">**AppInfo.Language** — pašreizējais ierīces valodas iestatījums, kas palīdz mums atklāt problēmas, kas ietekmē konkrētas valodas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-543">**AppInfo.Language** - Currently language setting of the device to help us detect issues affecting certain languages</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-544">**AppInfo.Version**— instalētās lietojumprogrammas pašreizējā versija palīdz mums noteikt problēmas ar konkrētām lietojumprogrammu versijām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-544">**AppInfo.Version** - Current version of the app installed to help us detect issues affecting certain app versions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-545">**ci** — unikāls, ierīcei specifisks identifikatora pseidonīms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-545">**ci** - a pseudonymous app-specific device unique identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-546">**cid_type** — norāda uz konta veidu, piemēram, komerciālais konts vai Outlook.com konts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-546">**cid_type** - indicates what type of account it is, such as a commercial account or Outlook.com account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-547">**cloud** — kur šajā ierīcē atrodas pastkaste, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas, kas ir raksturīgas konkrētai mākoņa pastkastei, piemēram, Office 365 vai GCC.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-547">**cloud** - Where the mailbox resides for the account on this device to help detect issues specific to a specific mailbox cloud, like Office 365 or GCC.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-548">**customer_type** — norāda klienta tipu (patērētājs, komerciālais, trešā puse utt.), kas palīdz mums atklāt problēmas ar konkrētie klientu veidiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-548">**customer_type** - Indicates the type of customer (consumer, commercial, third party, etc.) to help us detect issues affecting certain customer types</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-549">**device_category** — norāda, kāda veida ierīce tā ir (tālrunis, planšetdators utt.) un palīdz mums atklāt ierīču kategorijām raksturīgas problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-549">**device_category** - Indicates what type of device it is (phone, tablet, etc.) to help us detect device category specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-550">**DeviceInfo.Id** — unikāls ierīces identifikators, kas palīdz mums atklāt konkrētas problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-550">**DeviceInfo.Id** - A unique device identifier to help us detect device specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-551">**DeviceInfo.Make** — ierīces marka (piem., Apple, Samsung utt.) palīdz mums noteikt konkrētām ierīču markām raksturīgas problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-551">**DeviceInfo.Make** - The make of the device (i.e. Apple, Samsung, etc.) to help us detect device make specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-552">**DeviceInfo.Model** — ierīces modelis (piem., iPhone 6s) palīdz atklāt konkrētiem ierīces modeļiem raksturīgas problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-552">**DeviceInfo.Model** - The device model (i.e. iPhone 6s) to help us detect device model specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-553">**DeviceInfo.NetworkType** — tīkls, kuru ierīce pašlaik izmanto (WiFi, mobilo datu tīkls, utt.), palīdz mums atklāt konkrētiem tīkliem raksturīgas problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-553">**DeviceInfo.NetworkType** - The current device network being used (WiFi, cellular, etc.) to help us detect device network specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-554">**DeviceInfo.OsBuild** — pašreizējās ierīces operētājsistēmas būvējums palīdz mums atklāt problēmas, kas ietekmē konkrētus operētājsistēmu būvējumus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-554">**DeviceInfo.OsBuild** - The current OS build of the device to help us detect issues affecting certain OS builds</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-555">**DeviceInfo.OsName** — operētājsistēmas nosaukums (piemēram, iOS) palīdz mums atklāt problēmas, kas ietekmē konkrētas platformas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-555">**DeviceInfo.OsName** - The name of the OS (for example, iOS) to help us detect issues affecting certain platforms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-556">**DeviceInfo.OsVersion** — pašreizējās ierīces operētājsistēmas versija palīdz mums atklāt problēmas, kas ietekmē konkrētas operētājsistēmas versijas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-556">**DeviceInfo.OsVersion** - The current OS version of the device to help us detect issues affecting certain OS versions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-557">**DeviceInfo.SDKUid** — ierīces unikālais identifikators (līdzīgs DeviceInfo.Id)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-557">**DeviceInfo.SDKUid** - The device unique identifier (similar to DeviceInfo.Id)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-558">**EventInfo.InitId** — ID izmanto kā daļu no notikumu secības noteikšanas mūsu telemetrijas kanālā, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt kanāla problēmas galveno cēloni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-558">**EventInfo.InitId** - Id used as part of sequencing for event ordering through our telemetry pipeline to help us detect the root cause of a pipeline issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-559">**EventInfo.SdkVersion** — SDK versija, ko izmantojam, lai nosūtītu mūsu telemetrijas datus, lai atklātu kanāla problēmas galveno cēloni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-559">**EventInfo.SdkVersion** - The SDK version we are using to send our telemetry to help us detect the root cause of a pipeline issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-560">**EventInfo.Sequence** — secība notikumu secības noteikšanai mūsu telemetrijas kanālā, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt kanāla problēmas galveno cēloni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-560">**EventInfo.Sequence** - The sequence is for event ordering through our telemetry pipeline to help us detect the root cause of a pipeline issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-561">**EventInfo.Source** — norāda uz koda daļu, kas nosūtīja notikumu, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas galveno cēloni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-561">**EventInfo.Source** - Tells us what part of the code sent the event to help us detect the root cause of an issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-562">**EventInfo.Time** — datums un laiks, kad notikums tika pārraidīts no ierīces, lai mūsu sistēmas spētu veiksmīgi pārvaldīt ienākošos notikumus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-562">**EventInfo.Time** - The time and date the event was emitted from the device so our systems can successfully manage events coming in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-563">**eventpriority** — telemetrijas notikuma prioritāte attiecībā pret citiem notikumiem, lai mūsu sistēmas varētu veiksmīgi pārvaldīt ienākošos notikumus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-563">**eventpriority** - The priority of the telemetry event relative to other events so our systems can successfully manage events coming in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-564">**first_launch_date** — laiks, kad ierīce tika palaista pirmo reizi, palīdz mums saprast, kad sākās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-564">**first_launch_date** - The first time the app was launched so helps us understand when an issue first began</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-565">**hashed_email** — identifikatora pseidonīms, kas apzīmē pašreizējo lietotājā e-pastu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-565">**hashed_email** - A pseudonymous identifier that represents the current user email</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-566">**is_first_session** — atkļūdošanas vajadzībām izseko, vai šī ir lietojumprogrammas pirmā sesija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-566">**is_first_session** - Tracks if this is the first session of the app for debugging purposes</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-567">**origin** — darbības izcelsme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-567">**origin** - The origination of an action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-568">Piemēram, ziņojuma atzīmēšana kā lasīta var izcelties no ziņojumu saraksta vai paziņojuma par jaunu e-pasta ziņojumu. Palīdz mums atklāt problēmas, kas ir saistītas ar darbības izcelsmi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-568">For example marking a message read can originate from message list or a new mail notification, this helps us detect issues based on action origination</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-569">**PipelineInfo.AccountId** — identifikatora pseidonīms, kas apzīmē pašreizējo lietotāju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-569">**PipelineInfo.AccountId** - A pseudonymous identifier that represents the current user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-570">**PipelineInfo.ClientCountry** — pašreizējā ierīces valsts, lai noteiktu valstij vai reģionam raksturīgas problēmas un traucējumus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-570">**PipelineInfo.ClientCountry** - The current country of the device to detect country or region specific issues and outages</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-571">**PipelineInfo.ClientIp** — ierīces IP adrese, kurai ierīce ir pieslēgta, lai atkļūdotu savienojuma problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-571">**PipelineInfo.ClientIp** - The IP address the device is connected to debug connection issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-572">**PipelineInfo.IngestionTime** — laikspiedols, kad notiek šī notikuma telemetrijas uzņemšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-572">**PipelineInfo.IngestionTime** - Timestamp of when our telemetry ingestion happens for this event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-573">**Session.Id** — unikāls lietojumprogrammas sesijas identifikators, kas palīdz mums atklāt ar sesiju saistītas problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-573">**Session.Id** - A unique identifier for the app session to help identify session-related issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-574">**Session.ImpressionId** — unikāls identifikators, lai pārvaldītu mūsu līdzekļu laidienus un nodrošinātu, ka līdzekļi tiek sekmīgi izlaisti visiem lietotājiem un ierīcēm</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-574">**Session.ImpressionId** - A unique identifier for managing release of our features to ensure features are successfully released to all users and devices</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-575">**ui_mode** — norāda, vai lietotājs izmanto gaišo vai tumšo saskarnes režīmu, un palīdz mums diagnosticēt UX kļūdas tumšajā režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-575">**ui_mode** - Is the user in light or dark mode, helps us triage UX bugs with dark mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-576">**UserInfo.Language** — lietotāja valoda palīdz mums atkļūdot tulkojumu teksta problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-576">**UserInfo.Language** - The user's language to help debug translation text issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-577">**UserInfo.TimeZone** — lietotāja laika josla palīdz mums atkļūdot kalendāra problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-577">**UserInfo.TimeZone** - The user's time zone to help debug calendar issues</span></span>


<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-578">Tālāk norādītie lauki ir kopīgi visiem Outlook darbam ar iOS notikumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-578">In addition, the following fields are common for all events for Outlook for iOS.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-579">**DeviceInfo.NetworkProvider** — tīkla, kuram pieslēgta ierīce, operators (piem., Verizon)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-579">**DeviceInfo.NetworkProvider** - The network provider of the device (i.e. Verizon)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-580">**gcc_restrictions_enabled** — norāda, vai GCC ierobežojumi tika piemēroti lietojumprogrammai, lai mēs spētu nodrošināt to, ka mūsu GCC klienti izmanto mūsu lietojumprogrammu drošā veidā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-580">**gcc_restrictions_enabled** - Tells us if GCC restrictions have been applied to the app so we can ensure our GCC customers are using our app securely</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-581">**multi_window_mode** — norāda, vai iPad lietotājs izmanto vairākus logus, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas, kas saistītas ar vairāklogu lietojumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-581">**multi_window_mode** – Tells us if the user on the iPad is using multiple windows to help us detect issues related to multi-window usage.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-582">**office_session_id** — unikāls ID, kas izseko sesijai pievienotajiem Office pakalpojumiem, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt Office pakalpojumu integrēšanai Outlook, piemēram, Word, raksturīgas problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-582">**office_session_id** - A unique id tracking the session for connected Office services to help detect issues specific an Office service integration in Outlook like Word</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-583">**state** — norāda, vai lietojumprogramma bija aktīva, kad šis notikums tika nosūtīts, lai palīdzētu atklāt problēmas, kas raksturīgas aktīvajiem vai neaktīvajiem lietojumprogrammu stāvokļiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-583">**state** - Whether the app was active when this event was sent to help detect issues specific to active or inactive app states</span></span>


<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-584">Tālāk norādītie lauki ir kopīgi visiem Outlook darbam ar Android notikumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-584">In addition, the following fields are common for all events for Outlook for Android.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-585">**aad_id** — Azure Active Directory identifikatora pseidonīms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-585">**aad_id** - a pseudonymous Azure Active Directory identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-586">**DeviceInfo.NetworkCost** — norāda ierīces pašreizējā tīkla izmaksas, kas atspoguļo WiFi/mobilo datu tīkla/viesabonēšanas statusu, lai palīdzētu atklāt ierīces tīklam raksturīgas problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-586">**DeviceInfo.NetworkCost** - Indication of devices current network cost which reflects the status of WiFi/Cellular/Roaming to help detect issues specific to device network</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-587">**is_app_in_duo_split_view_mode** — informē mūs par to, ka ierīce bija Duo dalītā ekrāna režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-587">**is_app_in_duo_split_view_mode** - This will let us know that the app was in Duo split-screen mode.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-588">Šis rekvizīts ir iestatīts tikai Duo ierīcēm (tikai Android).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-588">This property is set only for Duo (Android only) devices.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-589">**is_dex_mode_enabled** — norāda, vai Samsung DeX režīms ir iespējots, lai palīdzētu noteikt problēmas, kas raksturīgas DeX režīmam Samsung ierīcēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-589">**is_dex_mode_enabled** - Whether Samsung DeX mode is enabled to help detect issues specific to DeX mode with Samsung devices</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-590">**is_sliding_drawer_enabled** — vai bīdāmās atvilktnes saskarne ir iespējota, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas ar mūsu bīdāmās atvilktnes saskarni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-590">**is_sliding_drawer_enabled** - Whether Sliding Drawer interface is enabled to help detect issues caused by our sliding drawer interface</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-591">**orientation** — ekrāna fiziskais novietojums (portrets/ainava), kas palīdz mums atklāt ierīces novietojumam raksturīgas problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-591">**orientation** - Physical orientation of the screen (portrait/landscape) to help detect issues specific to device orientation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-592">**os_arch** — ierīces operētājsistēmas arhitektūra palīdz mums atklāt ierīču operētājsistēmām raksturīgas problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-592">**os_arch** - Operating System architecture for the device to help detect issues specific to device operation systems</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-593">**process_bitness** — procesa bitu skaits (32 vai 64 biti) lietojumprogrammai palīdz mums atklāt ierīces bitu skaitam raksturīgas problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-593">**process_bitness** - Process bitness (32 or 64 bit) for the application to help detect issues specific to device bitness</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-594">**webview_kernel_version**: Chromium kodola tīmekļa skata versija ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt saderības problēmas, kas saistītas ar tīmekļa skatījuma versiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-594">**webview_kernel_version**: The Chromium kernel version of webview on the device to help us detect compatibility issues related to the version of webview.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-595">**webview_package_name**: ierīces tīmekļa skata paketes nosaukums, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt saderības problēmas, kas saistītas ar tīmekļa skatījuma versiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-595">**webview_package_name**: The package name of webview on the device to help us detect compatibility issues related to the version of webview.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-596">**webview_package_version**: ierīces tīmekļa skata paketes versija, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt saderības problēmas, kas saistītas ar tīmekļa skatījuma versiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-596">**webview_package_version**: The package version of webview on the device to help us detect compatibility issues related to the version of webview.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-605">Brīdinās Microsoft par to, vai izdevās vai radās kļūme lietotājam pievienot kontu, izmantojot vienoto pierakstīšanos (SSO).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-605">This will alert Microsoft to the success or failure of a user adding an account through single sign-on (SSO).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-608">**action_origin** — no kurienes šis notikums tika ģenerēts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-608">**action_origin** – from where this event was generated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-609">(piem., vērtības: sso_drawer, sso_add_account, sso_add_account_prompt, sso_settings, sso_oobe).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-609">(e.g., values: sso_drawer, sso_add_account, sso_add_account_prompt, sso_settings, sso_oobe).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-610">**pakalpojumu sniedzējs** — vienotās pierakstīšanās (SSO) programmatūras pakotnes identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-610">**provider** - the identifier for the provider software package for the SSO.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-611">**stāvoklis** — konta pašreizējais stāvoklis, (vērtības piemērs: NEIZDEVĀS, GAIDA, PIEVIENOTS utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-611">**state** – current state of the account, (example value: FAILED, PENDING, ADDED etc.)</span></span>
 
#### <a name="officeclicktorunupdatestatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-612">Office.ClickToRun.UpdateStatus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-612">Office.ClickToRun.UpdateStatus</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-619">**errorMessage** — papildu informācija par kļūdu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-619">**errorMessage** - Additional error information</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-620">**status** — pašreizējais atjauninājuma statuss</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-620">**status** - Current status of the update</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-621">**targetBuild** — versija, uz kuru tiek atjaunināta sistēma Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-621">**targetBuild** - Version Office is updating to</span></span>

#### <a name="officecompliancefileformatballotdisplayedonfirstboot"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-622">Office.Compliance.FileFormatBallotDisplayedOnFirstBoot</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-622">Office.Compliance.FileFormatBallotDisplayedOnFirstBoot</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-623">Norāda, vai Office faila formāta izvēles dialoglodziņš tika parādīts lietotājam pirmo/otro reizi palaižot Word, Excel PowerPoint Win32 sistēmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-623">Indicates whether the Office File Format choice dialog box was shown to the user on first/second boot of Word, Excel, PowerPoint on Win32.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-624">Seko tam, vai tiek parādīts faila formāta izvēles dialoglodziņš — notikums tiek nosūtīts pirmajā/otrajā Word, Excel vai PPT palaišanas reizē Win32 sistēmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-624">Tracks whether the FileFormat Ballot dialog box is displayed - event is sent at the first/second boot of Word, Excel or PPT Win32.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-625">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-625">The following fields are collected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-626">**CountryRegion** — lietotāja valsts/reģiona iestatījums Windows sistēmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-626">**CountryRegion** –  The users' country region setting in Windows system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-627">**FileFormatBallotBoxAppIDBootedOnce** — kurā lietojumprogrammā (Word, Excel, PPT) tika apstrādāta faila formāta izvēles dialogloga parādīšanas loģika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-627">**FileFormatBallotBoxAppIDBootedOnce** –  In which app (Word, Excel, PPT) the file format ballot display logic was processed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-628">**FileFormatBallotBoxDisplayedOnFirstBoot** — kāds ir faila formāta izvēles dialoglodziņa (parādīts/nav parādīts kā paredzēts/nav parādīts licences dēļ/nav parādīts atrašanās vietas dēļ) parādīšanas rezultāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-628">**FileFormatBallotBoxDisplayedOnFirstBoot** –  What is the display result for file format ballot (displayed/not displayed as unexpected/not displayed due to license/not displayed due to location).</span></span>

#### <a name="officecompliancefileformatballotoption"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-629">Office.Compliance.FileFormatBallotOption</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-629">Office.Compliance.FileFormatBallotOption</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-630">Seko tam, vai tiek parādīts faila formāta izvēles dialoglodziņš — notikums tiek nosūtīts pirmajā/otrajā Word, Excel vai PPT palaišanas reizē Win32 sistēmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-630">Tracks whether the FileFormat Ballot dialog box is displayed - event is sent at the first/second boot of Word, Excel or PPT Win32.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-631">Norāda, vai Office faila formāta izvēles dialoglodziņš tika parādīts pirmajā Word, Excel vai PowerPoint palaišanas reizē Win32 sistēmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-631">Indicates whether the Office File Format choice dialog box is displayed on first or second boot of Word, Excel, or PowerPoint on Win32.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-632">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-632">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-633">**FileFormatBallotSelectedOption** — nosaka faila formāta opciju (OOXML/ODF), kuru lietotājs izvēlējās faila formāta izvēles dialoglodziņā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-633">**FileFormatBallotSelectedOption** – Identifies the file format option (OOXML/ODF) that was selected by the user through the file format ballot dialog box.</span></span>


#### <a name="officecorrelationmetadatautccorrelationmetadata"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-634">Office.CorrelationMetadata.UTCCorrelationMetadata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-634">Office.CorrelationMetadata.UTCCorrelationMetadata</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-635">Nolūkā izlabot un pabeigt datus apkopo Office metadatus, izmantojot UTC, lai salīdzinātu ar līdzīgiem datiem, kas ir apkopoti, izmantojot Office telemetrijas kanālu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-635">Collects Office metadata through UTC to compare with equivalent data collected through the Office telemetry pipeline to check correctness and completeness of data.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-636">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-636">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-637">**abConfigs** — saraksts, kurā ir uzskaitīti līdzekļu ID, lai noteiktu, kādi līdzekļi ir iespējoti klientā vai kuri līdzekļi ir tukši, ja dati netiek apkopoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-637">**abConfigs** - A list of feature IDs to identify which features are enabled on the client or empty when this data is not being collected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-638">**abFlights** — "NoNL:NoFlights", ja nav iestatīti līdzekļu testējamie varianti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-638">**abFlights** - "NoNL:NoFlights" when the feature flights aren't set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-639">Pretējā gadījumā: "holdoutinfo=unknown".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-639">Otherwise "holdoutinfo=unknown".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-640">**AppSessionGuid** — tās attiecīgās lietojumprogrammas sesijas identifikators, kuras sākums ir procesa izveides laiks un kas ilgst līdz procesa beigām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-640">**AppSessionGuid** - An identifier of a particular application session starting at process creation time and persisting until process end.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-641">Tas ir formatēts kā standarta 128 bitu GUID, ko veido četras daļas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-641">It is formatted as a standard 128-bit GUID but constructed of 4 parts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-642">Šo četru daļu secība ir: (1) 32 bitu procesa ID (2) 16 bitu sesijas ID (3) 16 bitu palaišanas ID (4) 64 bitu procesa izveides laiks: UTC 100ns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-642">Those four parts in order are (1) 32-bit Process ID (2) 16-bit Session ID (3) 16 bit Boot ID (4) 64-bit Process creation time in UTC 100ns</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-643">**appVersionBuild** — programmas būvējuma versijas numurs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-643">**appVersionBuild** - The app build version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-644">**appVersionMajor** — programmas galvenās versijas numurs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-644">**appVersionMajor** - The app major version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-645">**appVersionMinor** — programmas papildversijas numurs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-645">**appVersionMinor** - The app minor version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-646">**appVersionRevision** — programmas pārskatītās versijas numurs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-646">**appVersionRevision** - The app revision version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-647">**audienceGroup** — laidiena auditorijas grupas nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-647">**audienceGroup** - The release audience group name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-648">**audienceId** — laidiena auditorijas nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-648">**audienceId** - The release audience name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-649">**channel** — Office izplatīšanas kanāls</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-649">**channel** - The channel by which Office was distributed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-650">**deviceClass** — ierīces formas faktors no operētājsistēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-650">**deviceClass** - Device form factor from the OS</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-651">**ecsETag** — procesa eksperimenta identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-651">**ecsETag** - An experiment identifier for the process</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-652">**impressionId** — GUID, kas norāda pašreizējo līdzekļu kopu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-652">**impressionId** - A guid indicating the current set of features.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-653">**languageTag** — pašreizējā Office IETF lietotāja interfeisa valodas tags</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-653">**languageTag** - The current Office UI IETF language tag</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-654">**officeUserID** — nejauši ģenerēts GUID šai Office instalācijai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-654">**officeUserID** - Randomly generated guid for this Office install</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-655">**osArchitecture** — operētājsistēmas arhitektūra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-655">**osArchitecture** - Operating system architecture</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-656">**osEnvironment** — vesels skaitlis, kas norāda operētājsistēmu (Windows, Android, iOS, Mac u.c.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-656">**osEnvironment** - An integer indicating the operating system (Windows, Android, iOS, Mac, etc.).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-657">**osVersionString** — operētājsistēmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-657">**osVersionString** - Operating system version</span></span>

#### <a name="officetargetedmessagingensurecached"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-702">Office.TargetedMessaging.EnsureCached</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-702">Office.TargetedMessaging.EnsureCached</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-703">Izseko, vai tika lejupielādēta dinamiskās pamatnes pakotne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-703">Tracks if a package for Dynamic Canvas was downloaded.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-704">Tiek uzskatīta par programmatūras konfigurāciju, jo pakotne ir sekmīgi jālejupielādē, lai iespējotu klientu atveidot pareizās iespējas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-704">Considered a software configuration because the package must be successfully downloaded to enable the client to render the right experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-705">Tas ir īpaši būtiski patērētāju abonementos, kur mēs izmantojam pamatni, lai paziņotu lietotājam par licences derīguma termiņa beigām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-705">Is especially critical in consumer subscriptions where we use canvas to communicate to the user that the license has expired.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-706">Izmanto, lai izsekotu produkta lejupielādētās un kešotās dinamiskā satura pakotnes metadatiem, kā arī to darbību rezultātiem, kam tika pakļauta pakotne: lejupielādes kļūmēm, pakotnes atvēršanas kļūmēm, konsekvences pārbaudes kļūmēm, kešatmiņas trāpījumiem, pakotnes lietojumam un lejupielādes avotiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-706">Used to track metadata of a dynamic content package downloaded and cached by the product as well as results of operations performed on the package: download failures, unpacking failures, consistency checks failures, cache hits, package usages, download sources.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-707">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-707">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-708">**Data\_CacheFolderNotCreated —** Būla karodziņš, kas norāda, vai kešatmiņas mapes izveide bija sekmīga</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-708">**Data\_CacheFolderNotCreated -** Boolean flag indicating if cache folder creation succeeded</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-709">**Data\_CdnPath — pakotnes avota adrese —**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-709">**Data\_CdnPath – source address of the package-**</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-710">**Data\_EnsureCached —** Būla karodziņš, kas norāda, vai tika kešota satura pakotne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-710">**Data\_EnsureCached -** Boolean flag indicating if content package was cached</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-711">**Data\_ExistsAlready —** Būla karodziņš, kas norāda, ka pakotne jau tika iepriekš lejupielādēta un pastāv vēl viens lejupielādes mēģinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-711">**Data\_ExistsAlready -** Boolean flag indicating that the package was already downloaded before and there was another attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-712">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailed —** avota pakotne nav pieejama avotā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-712">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailed -** source package not available in source</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-713">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailedToCreateLocalFolder —** lokālā diska problēmas, kas izraisa kļūmes direktorija izveides laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-713">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailedToCreateLocalFolder -** local disk issues causing failure in directory creation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-714">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageFailed —** karodziņš, kas norāda, vai pakotne ir lejupielādēta, bet klients nevar to nolasīt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-714">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageFailed -** flag indicating if package was downloaded, but the client can't read it</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-715">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageSuccess —** veiksmīgi mēģinājumi lasīt pakotni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-715">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageSuccess -** successful attempts to read the package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-716">**Data\_GetFileStreamSuccess —** nepastāv neviena ar disku vai konfigurāciju saistīta problēma, kas neatļauj lasīt failu plūsmu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-716">**Data\_GetFileStreamSuccess -** no disk issues nor configuration issues which doesn't let the file stream to be read</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-717">**Data\_GetRelativePathsFailed —** relatīvais ceļš nenorāda uz pieejamu atrašanās vietu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-717">**Data\_GetRelativePathsFailed -** relative path doesn't point to accessible location</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-718">**Data\_HashActualValue —** jaukšanas vērtība, kas tika iegūta no faila nosaukuma, lietojot pakotni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-718">**Data\_HashActualValue -** hash value extracted from file name when the package was used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-719">**Data\_HashCalculationFailed —** jaukšanas aprēķina kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-719">**Data\_HashCalculationFailed -** error with calculation of a hash</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-720">**Data\_HashMatchFailed —** jaukšanas neatbilstība starp pakotnes nosaukumu un kešotajām reģistra vērtībām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-720">**Data\_HashMatchFailed -** hash mismatch between the package name and registry values cached</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-721">**Data\_HashMatchSuccess —** sekmīga jaukšanas konsekvences pārbaude</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-721">**Data\_HashMatchSuccess -** hash consistency check success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-722">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestFailed —** nevar lejupielādēt pakotni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-722">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestFailed -** can't download the package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-723">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestNoData —** lejupielādētajā pakotnē nav datu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-723">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestNoData -** downloaded package contains no data</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-724">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestSuccess —** sekmīgi lejupielādēta pakotne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-724">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestSuccess -** successful download of a package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-725">**Data\_PackageExplodedSuccess —** pakotnes atvēršanas mēģinājumu statuss</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-725">**Data\_PackageExplodedSuccess -** unpacking attempts statuses</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-726">**Data\_PackageOpenFailed —** nesekmīgie pakotnes faila atvēršanas mēģinājumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-726">**Data\_PackageOpenFailed -** failed attempts to open the package file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-727">**Data\_PackageOpenSuccess —** sekmīgie pakotnes faila atvēršanas mēģinājumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-727">**Data\_PackageOpenSuccess -** successful attempts to open the package file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-728">**Data\_SuccessHashValue —** jaukšanas vērtība, kas tika iegūta no faila nosaukuma, lejupielādējot pakotni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-728">**Data\_SuccessHashValue -** hash value extracted from file name when the package was downloaded</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-729">**Data\_SuccessSource —** virsma, kam tika lejupielādēta pakotne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-729">**Data\_SuccessSource -** surface for which the package was downloaded</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiovisiosku"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-730">Office.Visio.VisioSKU</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-730">Office.Visio.VisioSKU</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-731">Nosaka, vai Visio SKU ir standarta vai profesionālā versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-731">Captures Visio SKU whether it's standard or professional.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-732">Tas ir svarīgi, lai varētu kategorizēt problēmas, kuru pamatā ir SKU.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-732">Essential to categorize issues based on SKU.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-957">**ErrorCode2** — kļūdas kods, izpildot izveidi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-957">**ErrorCode2** - Error code from executing the creation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-959">**ID** — unikālais identifikators (GUID) konteineru izveidei.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-959">**Id** - A unique identifier (GUID) for the container creation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-960">**ResetError** — kļūdas kods, mēģinot atiestatīt konteineru pēc neveiksmīgā mēģinājuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-960">**ResetError** - Error code from trying to reset the container after a failed attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-961">**ResetErrorCode1** — konteinera iestatīšanas kļūdas koda veids pēc atiestatīšanas komandas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-961">**ResetErrorCode1** - Type of Container Setup Error code after reset command.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-962">**ResetErrorCode2** — kļūdas kods, izpildot izveidi pēc atiestatīšanas komandas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-962">**ResetErrorCode2** - Error code from executing the creation after reset command.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-963">**ResetErrorCode3** — papildu kļūdas kods pēc atiestatīšanas komandas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-963">**ResetErrorCode3** - Additional error code after reset command.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-965">**WarmBoot** — identificē, vai konteiners jau bija izveidots vai nē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-965">**WarmBoot** - Identifies whether the container was already created or not.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1081">Tālāk ir norādīti šīs kategorijas datu apakštipi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1081">The following are the data subtypes in this category:</span></span>

- [<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1084">Office pieejamības konfigurācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1084">Office accessibility configuration</span></span>](#office-accessibility-configuration-subtype)

### <a name="application-feature-success-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1086">*Lietojumprogrammas līdzekļu sekmju apakštips*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1086">*Application feature success subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1087">Informācija par sekmīgu lietojumprogrammas funkcionalitāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1087">Success of application functionality.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1088">Attiecas tikai uz programmas un dokumentu atvēršanu un aizvēršanu, failu rediģēšana un failu koplietošanu (sadarbību).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1088">Limited to opening and closing of the application and documents, file editing, and file sharing (collaboration).</span></span>

#### <a name="accountaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1089">account.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1089">account.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1090">Nepieciešams, lai nodrošinātu veiksmīgu konta konfigurācijas darbību, un tiek izmantots, lai pārraudzītu konta izveides stāvokli, spēju pievienot jaunus e-pastu kontus un uzraudzītu mīkstos kontu atiestatījumus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1090">Needed to ensure account configuration is operating successfully and is used to monitor health of account creation, ability to add new email accounts, and monitor soft account resets</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1091">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1091">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1092">**account_calendar_count** — cik daudz kalendāru ir kontam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1092">**account_calendar_count** - how many calendars the account has</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1093">**action** — veicamās darbības veids, piemēram, izveidot kontu, dzēst kontu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1093">**action** - type of action performed, e.g. create_account, delete_account.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1094">**duration_seconds** — darbības ilgums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1094">**duration_seconds** - duration of the action</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1095">**entry_point** — darbības ievades punkts, kā lietotājs uzsāka darbību</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1095">**entry_point** - entry point of the action, how the user started the action</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1096">**has_hx** — nosaka, vai ierīcei ir konts, kas izmanto jaunu e-pasta sinhronizācija pakalpojumu, bet ne obligāti konts, uz kuru tika vērsta darbība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1096">**has_hx** - whether the device has an account that is using our new mail syncing service, not necessarily the account that the action was performed upon</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1097">**is_hx** — nosaka, vai konts izmantot mūsu jauno e-pastu sinhronizācijas pakalpojumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1097">**is_hx** - is the account using our new mail syncing service</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1098">**is_shared_mailbox** — vai darbība ir saistīta ar koplietotu pastkasti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1098">**is_shared_mailbox** - whether the action pertains to a shared mailbox</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1099">**number_of_accounts** — kopējais kontu skaits, attiecībā uz kuriem tiek veikta darbība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1099">**number_of_accounts** - total number of accounts that the action is performed on</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1100">**result** — darbības rezultāts, piemēram, izdevās, neizdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1100">**result** - result for the action, e.g. success, failure.</span></span>
   
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1101">**server_type** — konta servera veids, līdzīgs konta tipam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1101">**server_type** - the server type for the account, similar to account_type</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1102">**shared_type** — koplietotā konta tips (ja konts ir koplietots)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1102">**shared_type** - type of shared account (if the account is shared)</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1103">**scope** — darbības apjoms; konta dzēšanai šajā ierīcē vai visās ierīcēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1103">**scope** - the scope of the action; for delete account, this_device or all_devices</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1104">**total_calendar_accounts** — kalendāra kontu skaits lietojumprogrammā darbības veikšanas brīdī</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1104">**total_calendar_accounts** - count of calendar accounts in the app at time of action</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1105">**total_email_accounts** — e-pasta kontu skaits lietojumprogrammā darbības veikšanas brīdī</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1105">**total_email_accounts** - count of email accounts in the app at time of action</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1106">**total_file_accounts** — failu kontu skaits lietojumprogrammā darbības veikšanas brīdī</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1106">**total_file_accounts** - count of file accounts in the app at time of action</span></span>

#### <a name="accountlifecycle"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1107">account.lifecycle</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1107">account.lifecycle</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1108">Šis notikums tiek apkopots, lai nodrošinātu veiksmīgu konta konfigurācijas darbību, un tiek izmantots, lai pārraudzītu konta izveides stāvokli, spēju pievienot jaunus e-pastu kontus un uzraudzītu mīkstos kontu atiestatījumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1108">This event is collected to ensure account configuration is operating successfully and is used to monitor health of account creation, ability to add new email accounts, and monitor soft account resets.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1109">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1109">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1110">**action** — kontā veiktās darbības veids, piemēram, pievienot, dzēst vai atiestatīt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1110">**action** - The type of action performed on the account, such as add, remove, or reset</span></span>

#### <a name="addnewaccountstep"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1111">add.new.account.step</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1111">add.new.account.step</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1112">Šis pasākums ļauj mums noteikt, cik tālu lietotājs ir aizpildījis jauna konta izveides veidlapu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1112">This event lets us detect how far the user has gotten in the create new account form.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1113">Tas norāda, vai lietotājs ir pārgājis uz nākamo soli vai pārtraucis reģistrācijas procesu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1113">It indicates when the user has moved to another step or if they have dropped off.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1114">Šī informācija mums ir nepieciešama, lai noteiktu, vai visi soļi darbojas atbilstoši, un nodrošinātu veiksmīgu lietotāja konta izveidi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1114">We need this information to detect if any steps are failing and to ensure user account creation was successful.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1115">Tiek apkopots tālāk norādītais lauks:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1115">The following field is collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1116">**OTAddAccountCurrentStep** — tam var būt šādas vērtības: profile_form, redirect_mobile_check, mobile_check_success</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1116">**OTAddAccountCurrentStep** - That can have the following values: profile_form, redirect_mobile_check, mobile_check_success</span></span>

#### <a name="apperror"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1117">app.error</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1117">app.error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1118">Izseko kritiskās lietojumprogrammu kļūdas, lai mēs spētu novērst problēmas, kas var izraisīt jūsu lietojumprogrammu avārijas vai traucēt jums lasīt e-pasta ziņojumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1118">Tracks critical app errors used so that we can prevent issues that could cause your app to crash or prevent you from reading email.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1119">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1119">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1120">**clientName** — mākoņa faila, kurā notika kļūda, klienta nosaukums, ja attiecināms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1120">**clientName** - The name of the client for the cloud file where the error occurred, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1121">**cloudfile_error_type** — mākoņa failā notikušās kļūdas tips, ja attiecināms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1121">**cloudfile_error_type** - The type of error that occurred for the cloud file, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1122">**cloudfile_response_name** — mākoņa failā notikušās kļūdas atbildes nosaukums, ja attiecināms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1122">**cloudfile_response_name** - The response name for the error that occurred for the cloud file, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1123">**component_name** — lietojumprogrammas komponenta, kurā notika kļūda, nosaukums, piemēram, e-pasts vai kalendārs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1123">**component_name** - The name of the component of the app where the error occurred, such as mail or calendar.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1124">**debug_info** — informācija par mākoņa failā notikušo kļūdu, kas tiek izmantota, lai noteiktu kļūdas iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1124">**debug_info** - Information on the error that occurred for the cloud file in order to be able to determine why the error happened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1125">**error_origin_identifier** — kļūdas, kas notika melnrakstā, izcelsme, ja attiecināms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1125">**error_origin_identifier** - Origin of the error that occurred on the draft that the error occurred, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1126">**error_type** — notikušās kļūdas tips.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1126">**error_type** - The type of error that occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1127">Daži no paraugiem iekļauj saglabāt melnrakstu, sūtīt melnrakstu un mākoņa faila kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1127">Some examples include save draft, send draft, and cloud file error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1128">**exdate** — pagarinātā noteikuma datums (attiecas tikai uz atkārtotām tikšanās kļūdām) *[Šis lauks ir noņemts no pašreizējiem Office būvējumiem, bet, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1128">**exdate** - the extended rule date (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1129">**exrule** — pagarinātā noteikuma vērtību (attiecas tikai uz atkārtotām tikšanās kļūdām) *[Šis lauks ir noņemts no pašreizējiem Office būvējumiem, bet, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1129">**exrule** - the extended rule value (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1130">**has_attachments** — parāda, vai melnraksts, kurā notika kļūda, satur pielikumus, ja attiecināms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1130">**has_attachments** - Reflects if the draft the error occurred on has attachments, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1131">**is_IRM_protected** — parāda, ja melnraksts, kurā notika kļūda, ir aizsargāts ar informācijas tiesību pārvaldību, ja attiecināms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1131">**is_IRM_protected** - Reflects if the draft the error occurred on is protected by information rights management, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1132">**is_legitimate** — parāda, vai kļūdas iemesls ir programmēšanas kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1132">**is_legitimate** - Reflects if the error comes from a programming error or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1133">Programmēšanas kļūdas tiek uzskatītas par nederīgām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1133">Programming errors are considered non-legitimate.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1134">**is_local** — parāda, vai melnraksts, kurā notika kļūda, tika sinhronizēts ar serveri, ja attiecināms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1134">**is_local** - Reflects if the draft the error occurred on has synced to the server, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1135">**is_recoverable** — parāda, vai no kļūdas ir iespējams atkopties vai tā ir fatāla kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1135">**is_recoverable** - Reflects if the error can be recovered from or if it is a fatal error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1136">**rdate** — atkārtošanās noteikuma datums (attiecas tikai uz atkārtotām tikšanās kļūdām) *[Šis lauks ir noņemts no pašreizējiem Office būvējumiem, bet, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1136">**rdate** - the date of the recurrence rule (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1137">**rrule** — pats atkārtošanās noteikums (attiecas tikai uz atkārtotām tikšanās kļūdām) *[Šis lauks ir noņemts no pašreizējiem Office būvējumiem, bet, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1137">**rrule** - the recurrence rule itself (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1138">**rrule_error_message** — atkārtošanās noteikumu parsēšanas kļūdas ziņojums (attiecas tikai uz atkārtotām tikšanās kļūdām) *[Šis lauks ir noņemts no pašreizējiem Office būvējumiem, bet, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1138">**rrule_error_message** - recurrence rule parsing error message (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1139">**rrule_error_type** — atkārtošanās noteikumu parsēšanas kļūdas tips (attiecas tikai uz atkārtotām tikšanās kļūdām) *[Šis lauks ir noņemts no pašreizējiem Office būvējumiem, bet, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1139">**rrule_error_type** - recurrence rule parsing error type (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1140">**status_code** — notikušās kļūdas statusa kods.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1140">**status_code** - The status code of the error that occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1141">Palīdz mums saprast kļūdas iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1141">This helps us understand the cause of the error.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1142">Visas rakstzīmes ir arī iespējamie rekvizīti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1142">All characters are also possible properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1143">Tas palīdz mums saprast rakstzīmes melnraksta ziņojumā kļūdas rašanās brīdī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1143">This helps us understand the characters in the body of the draft message when the error occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1144">Piemēram, “a”, “b” un “c” ir iespējamie rekvizīti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1144">For example, "a", "b", "c" are possible properties.</span></span>

#### <a name="applaunchreport"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1145">app.launch.report</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1145">app.launch.report</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1146">Šis notikums ļauj mums atklāt un novērst problēmas, ja Outlook palaišana notiek lēni vai nepilnīgi, apgrūtinot mūsu lietotājiem mūsu lietojumprogrammas izmantošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1146">This event lets us detect and fix issues where Outlook is starting slowly or incompletely, making it difficult for users to use our app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1147">Tiek iekļauta informācija par konkrētiem iespējotajiem līdzekļiem un to, cik ilgu laiku aizņēma atsevišķi palaišanas posmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1147">This includes information on the specific features that were enabled and how long parts of the startup took.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1148">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1148">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1149">**is_agenda_widget_active** — norāda, vai darba kārtības logrīks ir aktīvs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1149">**is_agenda_widget_active** - Tells us if the agenda widget is active.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1150">**is_alert_available** — norāda, vai lietojumprogramma ir konfigurēta, lai atļautu brīdinājumus paziņojumos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1150">**is_alert_available** - Tell us if the app has been configured to allow alerts in notifications.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1151">**is_background_refresh_available** — norāda, vai lietojumprogramma ir konfigurēta atsvaidzināties fonā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1151">**is_background_refresh_available** - Tells if the app has been configured to be able to refresh in the background.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1152">**is_badge_available** — norāda, vai lietojumprogramma ir konfigurēta, lai atļautu žetonus paziņojumos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1152">**is_badge_available** - Tell us if the app has been configured to allow badges in notifications.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1153">**is_intune_managed** — norāda, vai lietojumprogramma ir Intune pārvaldīta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1153">**is_intune_managed** - Tell us if the app is managed by Intune.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1154">**is_registered_for_remote_notifications** — norāda, vai lietojumprogramma ir konfigurēta attālinātajiem paziņojumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1154">**is_registered_for_remote_notifications** - Tell us if the app has been registered for remote notifications.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1155">**is_sound_available** — norāda, vai lietojumprogramma ir konfigurēta, lai atļautu skaņu paziņojumos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1155">**is_sound_available** - Tell us if the app has been configured to allow sounds in notifications.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1156">**is_watch_app_installed** — norāda, vai ir instalēta Outlook lietojumprogramma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1156">**is_watch_app_installed** - Tells us if the watch Outlook app has been installed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1157">**is_watch_paired** — norāda, vai Outlook lietojumprogramma pulkstenī ir piesaistīta galvenajai Outlook lietojumprogrammai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1157">**is_watch_paired** - Tell us if the watch Outlook app is paired with the main Outlook app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1158">**launch_to_db_ready_ms** — norāda laiku, kas pagāja no Outlook lietojumprogrammas palaišanas brīža līdz datubāzes sagatavošanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1158">**launch_to_db_ready_ms** - Tell us the amount of time the Outlook app spent from launch to the database being ready.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1159">**num_calendar_accounts** — norāda kalendāra kontu skaitu lietojumprogrammā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1159">**num_calendar_accounts** - Tells us the number of calendar accounts in the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1160">**num_cloud_file_accounts** — norāda krātuves kontu skaitu lietojumprogrammā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1160">**num_cloud_file_accounts** - Tells us the number of storage accounts in the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1161">**num_hx_calendar_accounts** — norāda kalendāra kontu skaitu, kas ir pieslēgti pie mūsu jaunā sinhronizācijas pakalpojuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1161">**num_hx_calendar_accounts** - Tells us the number of calendar accounts in the app that connect to our new mail syncing service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1162">**num_hx_mail_accounts** — norāda e-pasta kontu skaitu, kas ir pieslēgti pie mūsu jaunā sinhronizācijas pakalpojuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1162">**num_hx_mail_accounts** - Tells us the number of mail accounts in the app that connect to our new mail syncing service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1163">**num_mail_accounts** — norāda e-pasta kontu skaitu lietojumprogrammā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1163">**num_mail_accounts** - Tells us the number of mail accounts in the app.</span></span>

#### <a name="calendaraction"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1164">calendar.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1164">calendar.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1165">Izmanto, lai uzraudzītu jebkādu iespējamo negatīvu ietekmi uz jūsu spēju veikt galvenās kalendāra darbības, piemēram, notikumu izveidošana vai rediģēšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1165">Used for monitoring any possible negative impact on your ability to perform core calendar actions like creating or editing events.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1166">Šis notikums var iekļaut arī rekvizītu nosaukumu sērijas un informāciju par to, vai tie ir mainījušies.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1166">The event could also include a series of property names and if they have changed or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1167">Piemēram, “title_changed”, “online_meeting_changed” un “description_changed” ir rekvizītu nosaukumi, kas palīdz mums noteikt, vai pastāv problēmas ar noteiktu rekvizītu rediģēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1167">For example, "title_changed", "online_meeting_changed", and "description_changed" are property names that are included to help us understand if there are any issues with editing certain properties.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1168">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1168">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1169">**account_sfb_enabled** — palīdz mums pārliecināties par to, ka Skype darbam ir konfigurēts pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1169">**account_sfb_enabled** - Helps us make sure that Skype for Business is configured correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1170">**action** — attiecībā pret kalendāru veiktās darbības veids.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1170">**action** - The type of action that was performed on the calendar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1171">Iekļauj tādas darbības kā atvēršana, rediģēšana, saīsņu pievienošana, atlikšana utt. Palīdz mums nodrošināt atbilstošu kalendāra darbību un stabilitāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1171">This includes things like open, editing, adding shortcut, snooze, etc. Helps us ensure our calendar experience is functioning as expected and nothing has broken</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1172">**action_result** — attiecībā pret kalendāra komponentēm veiktās darbības rezultāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1172">**action_result** - Result of the action taken on calendar components.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1173">Šeit var tikt iekļautas tādas vērtības kā sekmīga vai nesekmīga izpilde, nezināms un noilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1173">This can include values such as success, failure, unknown, and timeout.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1174">Izmanto, lai izsekotu darbību sekmīgas izpildes attiecībai un noteiktu, vai pastāv liela apjoma problēma ar kalendāra darbībām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1174">Used to track the success rate of actions and determine if there is a widespread issue with calendar actions.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1175">**attendee_busy_status** — ar darbību saistītā dalībnieka statuss brīvs/aizņemts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1175">**attendee_busy_status** - The free/busy status of the attendee that the action is related to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1176">Šī vērtība var būt brīvs, aizņemts vai nezināms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1176">This value can be free, busy, or tentative.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1177">Norāda, vai pastāv problēma ar darbībām, kas ir saistītas ar noteiktu aizņemtības statusu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1177">Helps us understand if there is an issue with actions related to a certain busy status.</span></span>
