- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1178">**availability** — pieejamības vērtība, ja vērtība brīvs/aizņemts ir mainījusies sapulces laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1178">**availability** - The availability value if the free/busy value has changed on the meeting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1179">Norāda, vai ir problēmas ar konkrētas pieejamības vērtības iestatīšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1179">Helps us understand if there are issues with setting a certain availability value.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1180">**calendar_onlinemeeting_default_provider** — satur noklusējuma tiešsaistes sapulču nodrošinātāju, izmantošanai ar servera atbalstītu tiešsaistes sapulču veidošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1180">**calendar_onlinemeeting_default_provider** - Contains the default online meeting provider for use with server-supported online meeting creation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1181">Iekļauj Skype, Skype darbam, Hangout un Teams darbam tipus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1181">This includes types of Skype, Skype for Business, Hangout, and Teams for Business.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1182">Palīdz atklāt potenciālās problēmas ar tiešsaistes sapulču veidošanu, izmantojot noteiktus nodrošinātājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1182">Helps us diagnose potential issues with creating online meetings on certain providers.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1183">**calendar_onlinemeeting_enabled** — patiess, ja kalendārs atbalsta servera atbalstītu tiešsaistes sapulču izveidošanu, balstoties uz noklusējuma sapulces nodrošinātāja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1183">**calendar_onlinemeeting_enabled** - True if the calendar supports server-supported online meeting creation based on a default online meeting provider.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1184">Norāda, vai pastāv problēmas ar kalendāriem ar iespējotām tiešsaistes sapulcēm.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1184">Helps us understand if there are any issues with online meeting enabled calendars.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1185">**calendar_type** — kalendāra tips, kurā ir norādīts notikums pēc tam, kad lietotājs ir veicis sapulces rediģēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1185">**calendar_type** - The type of calendar an event is on after the user has edited the meeting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1186">Iespējamās vērtības iekļauj primārs, sekundārs, koplietots un grupas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1186">Possible values include primary, secondary, shared, and group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1187">Norāda, vai pastāv problēmas ar noteiktu kalendāru tipu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1187">Helps us understand if there are issues with a certain calendar type.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1188">**delete_action_origin** — veiktās dzēšanas darbības izcelsme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1188">**delete_action_origin** - The origin of the delete action performed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1189">Iekļauj tādas vērtības kā navigācijas joslas rīkjosla un kapsulas rīkjosla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1189">This includes values such as navigation bar toolbar and capsule toolbar.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1190">Norāda, vai pastāv problēma ar sapulces dzēšanu no noteiktas atrašanās vietas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1190">Helps us understand if there are any issues with deleting a meeting from a certain location.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1191">**distribution_list_count** — adresātu sarakstā norādītais dalībnieku skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1191">**distribution_list_count** - Number of attendees which are on distribution lists.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1192">Palīdz mums noteikt, vai pastāv problēmas ar adresātu sarakstā esošajiem dalībniekiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1192">Helps us track if there are issues with attendees that are on distribution lists.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1193">**guest_count** — sapulces viesu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1193">**guest_count** - The number of guests on the meeting.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1194">Ļauj mums pārliecināties par to, ka viesi tiek pievienoti pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1194">Helps us make sure that the guests are being added correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1195">**is_all_day** — izmanto kopā ar “meeting_duration”, lai norādītu, vai sapulce ilgst visu dienu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1195">**is_all_day** - Used along with "meeting_duration" to specify if this is an all-day meeting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1196">Norāda, vai pastāv problēmas ar darbībām, kas tiek veiktas attiecībā uz visu dienu ilgām sapulcēm.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1196">Helps us understand if there are any issues with actions performed on all-day meetings.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1197">**is_location_permission_granted** — vai lietotājs lietojumprogrammai ir piešķīris sistēmas atrašanās vietas atļauju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1197">**is_location_permission_granted** – Whether user has granted system location permission to the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1198">Ja tiek piešķirta atrašanās vietas atļauja, lietojumprogramma var rādīt informāciju par papildu utilītu lietotāja interfeisā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1198">If location permission is granted, the app can show extra utility information in the user interface.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1199">Ja ir zināmas vai piešķirta atrašanās vietas atļauja, mēs varam uzzināt, cik bieži lietotājiem tiek rādīta informācija par papildu utilītu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1199">Knowing if location permission is granted will allow us to know how often the extra utility information is being shown to users.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1200">**is_organizer** — palīdz mums noteikt, vai organizators spēj rediģēt un veidot sapulces atbilstošā veidā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1200">**is_organizer** - Helps us understand if meetings are able to be edited and created by the organizer correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1201">**is_recurring** — norāda, vai pastāv problēma, kas ietekmē tieši regulāri notiekošās sapulces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1201">**is_recurring** - Helps us understand if there is an issue that specifically impacts recurring meetings.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1202">**launch_point** — darbības palaišanas punkts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1202">**launch_point** - The launch point of the action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1203">Var būt tādas vērtības kā logrīka galvene, logrīka kājene, visas dienas logrīks un kalendāra saīsne. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1203">Can be values such as widget header, widget footer, widget all day, and calendar shortcut.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1204">Norāda uz kontekstu, no kura tika sākta darbība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1204">Helps us understand the context that the action was started from.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1205">**location_count** — atrašanās vietu skaits, kas ir iestatītas notikuma izveidošanas un rediģēšanas brīdī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1205">**location_count** - Number of locations that are set on event create and edit.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1206">Norāda, vai pastāv problēmas ar notikumu ar noteiktu atrašanās vietu skaitu veidošanu vai rediģēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1206">Helps us understand if there are any issues with creating or editing events with a certain number of locations.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1207">**location_selection_source_type** — atrašanās vietas atlases avota tips.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1207">**location_selection_source_type** - Type of the location selection source.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1208">Var iekļaut tādas vērtības kā atrašanās vietas ieteikums, pielāgots vai esošs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1208">This can include values such as location suggestion, custom, and existing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1209">Palīdz mums atklāt jebkāda veida problēmas ar atrašanās vietas atlasi no noteikta avota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1209">Helps us diagnose any issues with selecting a location from a certain source.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1210">**location_session_id** — sapulces vietu atlasītāja ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1210">**location_session_id** - ID of the meeting location chooser session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1211">Palīdz mums atklāt problēmas ar atrašanās vietas pievienošanu sapulcei.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1211">Helps us diagnose any issues with choosing a location to add to the meeting.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1212">**location_type** — atlasītās atrašanās vietas tips.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1212">**location_type** - The type of location selected.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1213">Satur tādus tipus kā pielāgota atrašanās vieta, konferenču telpa un Bing.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1213">Contains types such as custom location, conference room, and Bing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1214">Palīdz mums izprast problēmas ar noteiktu atrašanās vietu pievienošanu sapulcēm.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1214">Helps us understand issues with adding certain location types to the meeting.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1215">**meeting_duration** — sapulces garums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1215">**meeting_duration** - The length of the meeting.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1216">Palīdz mums pārliecināties par to, ka sapulces tiek konfigurētas ar pareizajiem laikiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1216">Helps us make sure that the meetings are being configured with the correct times.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1217">**meeting_insights_type** — sapulču ieskatu tips notikuma detalizētajā informācijā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1217">**meeting_insights_type** - The type of meeting insights in the event details.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1218">Iekļauj failu un ziņojumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1218">This includes file and message.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1219">Palīdz mums noteikt parādīto sapulču ieskatu skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1219">Helps us understand the number of meeting insights that are being shown.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1220">**meeting_type** — ar darbību saistītās tiešsaistes sapulces tips.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1220">**meeting_type** - The type of online meeting associated with the action.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1221">Iekļauj Skype, Skype darbam, Hangout un Teams darbam tipus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1221">This includes types of Skype, Skype for Business, Hangout, and Teams for Business.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1222">Palīdz mums noteikt, vai tiešsaistes sapulces ir konfigurētas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1222">Helps us understand if the online meetings are configured correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1223">**origin** — kalendāra darbības izcelsme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1223">**origin** - The origin of the calendar action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1224">Iekļauj tādus tipus kā darba kārtība, kalendārs, darba kārtības logrīks utt. Palīdz mums pārliecināties par to, ka mijiedarbība ar kalendāra komponentēm darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1224">This includes types like agenda, calendar, widget agenda, etc. Helps us better ensure the interaction within the calendar components are working correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1225">**recurrence_scope** — sapulces biežuma tips, regulāras vai sērijveida sapulces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1225">**recurrence_scope** - The type of recurrence of the meeting, either occurrence or series.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1226">Palīdz noteikt, vai pastāv problēmas ar dažādu biežuma tipu sapulču rediģēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1226">Helps us understand if there are any issues with editing different meeting recurrence types.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1227">**reminder_time** — sapulces atgādinājuma laiks, ja tas ir mainīts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1227">**reminder_time** - The reminder time of the meeting if it has changed.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1228">Izmanto, lai pārliecinātos par to, ka sapulces atgādinājuma laiks ir saglabāts pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1228">Used to make sure the reminder time of the meeting is saved correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1229">**reminders_count** — atgādinājumu skaits notikumā, ja atgādinājumi ir mainīti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1229">**reminders_count** - Number of reminders on the event if the reminders have changed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1230">Palīdz mums atklāt problēmas ar vairākiem atgādinājumiem notikumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1230">Helps us diagnose any issues with multiple reminders on an event.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1231">**sensitivity** — sapulces konfidencialitātes līmenis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1231">**sensitivity** - The sensitivity of the meeting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1232">Iekļauj tipus normāla, personiska, privāta un konfidenciāla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1232">This includes types of normal, personal, private, and confidential.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1233">Palīdz mums noteikt, vai sapulces konfidencialitātes līmenis tiek konfigurēts pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1233">Helps us understand if the sensitivity of the meeting is being configured correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1234">**session_duration** — sesijas ilgums milisekundēs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1234">**session_duration** - The length that the session lasted in milliseconds.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1235">Palīdz mums noteikt, vai pastāv problēmas ar pieaugošo kalendāra darbību veikšanas laiku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1235">Helps us understand if there are issues that are increasing the amount of time needed to perform the calendar action.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1236">**shared_calendar_result** — kopīgotā kalendārā veiktās darbības rezultāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1236">**shared_calendar_result** - The result of an action performed on a shared calendar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1237">Iespējamās vērtības iekļauj labi, nav atļaujas, nezināms, lokālais īpašnieks vai īpašnieks ir grupa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1237">Possible values include ok, no permission, unknown, owner on-prem, and owner is group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1238">Palīdz mums noteikt kopīgotajos kalendāros veikto darbību uzticamību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1238">Helps us understand the reliability of actions performed on shared calendars.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1239">**time_picker_origin** — saglabāšanas darbības laika atlasītāja izcelsme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1239">**time_picker_origin** - Origin of the time picker for a save action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1240">Iekļauj tādas vērtības kā vairāk opciju un mazāk opciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1240">Includes values such as more options and fewer options.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1241">Palīdz mums noteikt, kā lietotājs pārvietojās plūsmā, lai saglabātu sapulci, un nodrošināt pareizu darbību</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1241">Helps us understand how the user navigated the flow to save the meeting and ensure that is functioning correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1242">**nosaukums** — automātiski ieteiktais nosaukums no lietojumprogrammā definētajām vērtībām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1242">**title** - The auto-suggested title from app-defined values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1243">Iekļauj tādas vērtības kā “zvans”, “pusdienas” un “Skype”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1243">This includes values such as "Call", "Lunch", and "Skype".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1244">Palīdz noteikt, vai nosaukuma automātiskā ieteikšana ir konfigurēta pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1244">Helps us understand if the title auto-suggestion is configured correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1245">**txp** — rezervācijas vai notikuma rezervācijas tips, ja ir.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1245">**txp** - The type of booking or reservation on the event, if any.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1246">Iekļauj tādus tipus kā pasākumu rezervācija, lidojumu rezervācija, automašīnu nomas rezervācija utt. Palīdz mums noteikt, vai rezervācijas/rezervēšanas kartītes darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1246">This includes types like event reservation, flight reservation, car rental reservation, etc. Helps us understand if the booking/reservation cards are performing correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1247">**upcoming_event_count** — plānoto notikumu skaits, kas tiek parādīts plānoto notikumu skatā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1247">**upcoming_event_count** - The number of upcoming events displayed in the upcoming events view.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1248">Norāda, vai pastāv problēmas ar plānoto notikumu skatu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1248">Helps us understand if there are issues with the upcoming events view.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1249">**upcoming_event_seconds_until_event** — sekunžu skaits līdz nākamā plānotā notikuma sākumam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1249">**upcoming_event_seconds_until_event** - The number of seconds until the next upcoming event starts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1250">Palīdz mums noteikt tipiskos notikumus, kas tiek parādīti plānoto notikumu skatā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1250">Helps us understand the typical events that are shown in the upcoming events view.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1251">**value** — darbībai specifiska detalizēta informācija, piemēram, aizkaves likums vai “atkārtot līdz” kategorija. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1251">**value** - Action-specific detail such as alert delay length or repeat-until category.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1252">Norāda uz kontekstu, kurā tika veikta darbība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1252">Helps us understand the context that the action was performed.</span></span> 

#### <a name="combinedsearchuse"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1253">combined.search.use</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1253">combined.search.use</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1254">Izmanto, lai noteiktu iespējamo negatīvo ietekmi uz jūsu spēju izmantot galvenās meklēšanas funkcijas, piemēram, e-pastu, kontaktpersonu vai notikumu meklēšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1254">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to perform key search functionality such as searching for mail, contacts, or events.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1255">Tālāk norādītie lauki tiek apkopoti iOS un Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1255">The following fields are collected across iOS and Android:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1256">**account_switcher_action_type** – šis darbības tips seko tam, vai lietotājs izmantoja kontu pārslēdzēju, lai pārslēgtu kontus nejauši vai apzināti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1256">**account_switcher_action_type** - This action type tracks if the user used the account switcher either in simply discovery or if they decided to switch the account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1257">**action_type** — meklēšanai veiktās darbības tips.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1257">**action_type** - The type of action that was performed for search.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1258">Nosaka, vai meklēšana tika sākta, notiek vai ir beigusies un kādas darbības notika meklēšanas laikā, piemēram, vai tika izmantots mikrofons.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1258">This identifies if a search has been started, in occurring, or ended and what actions were happening during the search, I.e. was the mic used.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1259">Kritiski svarīgs, lai nodrošinātu precīzu un lietderīgu meklēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1259">This is instrumental in ensuring accurate and helpful searches.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1260">**conversation_id** — unikāls ID katrai meklēšanas sesijai (t.i., katru reizi, kad lietotājs ievada meklēšanas lodziņu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1260">**conversation_id** - Unique ID for every search session (i.e. every time the user enters the search box)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1261">**entrance_type** — nosaka, kā lietotājs uzsāka meklēšanas pieprasījumu, piemēram, no meklēšanas cilnes, nulles vaicājuma, meklēšanas galvenes vai meklēšanas rezultāta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1261">**entrance_type** - This determines how the user started the search query, from the search tab, zero query, search heading, or search result.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1262">**has_contact_results** — norāda, vai kontaktpersonu rezultāti tiek parādīti meklēšanas vaicājumā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1262">**has_contact_results** - Simple whether contact results are shown or not in the search query</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1263">**include_deleted** — norāda, vai meklēšana rāda dzēstās opcijas meklēšanas rezultātos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1263">**include_deleted** - whether the search is showing deleted options in the search results</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1264">**is_ics_external_data** — notver, ja pievienotais notikums ir iekšējs (piemēram,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1264">**is_ics_external_data** - Captures if an added event is internal (i.e</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1265">pievienots no Outlook uz Outlook kalendāra) vai ārējs (piemēram,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1265">added in Outlook to Outlook calendar) or external (i.e</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1266">pievienots no citas e-pasta lietojumprogrammas, piemēram, no Gmail uz Outlook kalendāra).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1266">added from another email app such as Gmail to Outlook calendar).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1267">**is_network_fully_connected** — tas ir, lai iegūtu mājienu par bezsaistes meklēšanas iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1267">**is_network_fully_connected** - This is to get a hint of the reason behind the offline search.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1268">Ja tīkls ir savienots un meklēšana ir bezsaistē, iespējams, iemesls ir servera noildze.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1268">If the network is connected and the search is offline, then the reason is likely to be the server timeout</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1269">**is_offline_search** — vai meklēšanas sesija ir meklēšana bezsaistē, pamatojoties uz HX atgrieztajiem meklēšanas rezultātiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1269">**is_offline_search** - whether the search session is offline search based on search results returned by hx</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1270">**re_enter_search_tab** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, vai lietotājs ir pārslēdzis cilnes pirms meklēšanas rezultāta atlases</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1270">**re_enter_search_tab** - Boolean to indicate whether a user has switched tabs before selecting a search result</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1271">**result_selected_type** — norāda attēloto datu veidu, ar kuru mijiedarbojas lietotājs, piemēram, skatīt visas kontaktpersonas, sarunas, notikumus utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1271">**result_selected_type** - What type of data that was displayed is the user interacting with I.e. see all contact, conversations, event, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1272">**search_conversation_result_data** — satur datus par no meklēšanas rezultātiem atlasīto sarunu, tai skaitā konta tips (hx, ac, utt.), vai ziņojums atrodas mākoņa pakalpojumā un vai parādītā lapas nobīde atrodas vienā lapā ar pirmo ziņojumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1272">**search_conversation_result_data** - This contains data about the conversation selected from a search result including account type (hx, ac, etc.), whether the message is held by a cloud service, and whether the page offset shown is the same page as the first message.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1273">**search_origin** — norāda uz meklēšanas izcelsmi, piemēram, balss asistents, Cortana, ievade ar tastatūru utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1273">**search_origin** - Where did the search originate from, i.e. voice assistant, Cortana, keyboard input, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1274">**search_scope** — virkne norāda, kāda veida kontu meklēja lietotājs (piem., Exchange, Gmail utt.) vai tas bija meklējums visos kontos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1274">**search_scope** - A string indicating what type of account the user was searching in (I.e. Exchange, Gmail, etc.) or if it was in All Accounts.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1275">**search_suggestion_type**— norāda, kāds ir meklēšanas ieteikuma pamatojums, piemēram, vai tas ir pareizrakstības labojums?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1275">**search_suggestion_type** - indicates what is behind the search suggestion, I.e. is a spell correction?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1276">Balstīts vēsturē?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1276">Based on history?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1277">Automātiskā pabeigšana?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1277">Autocomplete?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1278">**search_request_reason** — norāda iemeslu, kura dēļ meklēšanas pieprasījums tika nosūtīts no lietojumprogrammas, norādot komponentu vai lietotāja darbību, kas uzsāka meklēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1278">**search_request_reason** - Indicates the reason a search request was sent from the app, in effect indicating the component or user action which invoked a search.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1279">**search_result_filter_type** — norāda, kāda veida filtrs tika piemērots meklēšanai, piem., rādīt visu vai tikai pielikumus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1279">**search_result_filter_type** - Indicates what type of filter was applied to search, show all or attachments only</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1280">Tālāk norādītie lauki tiek apkopoti Outlook Mobile iOS lietojumprogrammās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1280">The following fields are collected across iOS applications of Outlook Mobile:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1281">**action** — meklēšanai veiktās darbības tips.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1281">**action** - the type of action that was performed for search.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1282">Nosaka, vai meklēšana tika sākta, notiek vai ir beigusies un kādas darbības notika meklēšanas laikā, piemēram, vai tika izmantots mikrofons.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1282">This identifies if a search has been started, in occurring, or ended and what actions were happening during the search, I.e. was the mic used.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1283">Kritiski svarīgs, lai nodrošinātu precīzu un lietderīgu meklēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1283">This is instrumental in ensuring accurate and helpful searches.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1284">**answer_result_selected_count** — izseko, cik daudz reižu meklēšana bija “veiksmīga”, t.i., vai lietotājs atrada meklēto personu?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1284">**answer_result_selected_count** - tracks how many times the search was "successful" I.e. did the user find the person they wanted?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1285">Uzrakstīja e-pasta ziņojumu?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1285">Composed an email?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1286">Atzīmēja ziņojumu ar grāmatzīmi?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1286">Bookmarked the message?</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1287">**contact_result_in_full_list_selected_count** — izseko, cik reizes lietotājs pieprasīja “apskatīt visas kontaktpersonas” pilnā sarakstā kombinētās meklēšanas sesijas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1287">**contact_result_in_full_list_selected_count** - tracks how many times the user asked to "see all contacts" in full list was selected during the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1288">**contact_result_selected_count** — izseko, cik kontaktpersonu rezultāti tika atlasīti kombinētās meklēšanas sesijas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1288">**contact_result_selected_count** - tracks how many contact results were selected during the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1289">**conversation_result_selected_count** — izseko, cik sarunas tika atlasītas kombinētās meklēšanas sesijas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1289">**conversation_result_selected_count** - tracks how many conversations were selecting during the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1290">**mail_paging_gesture_count** — izseko, cik daudz pasta meklēšanas lapošanas žestu tika veikti kombinētajā meklēšanas sesijā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1290">**mail_paging_gesture_count** - tracks how many mail search paging gestures were performed within the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1291">**mail_requests_count** — izseko, cik daudz pasta meklēšanas pieprasījumu tika nosūtīti kombinētajā meklēšanas sesijā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1291">**mail_requests_count** - tracks how many mail search requests were sent within the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1292">**people_filter_selected_contacts_count** — tiek izsekots, cik kontaktpersonas ir atlasītas personu filtrā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1292">**people_filter_selected_contacts_count** - tracks how many contacts were selected in the people filter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1293">**search_session_ended_type** — norāda, kur beidzās meklēšana, jo tā tika atcelta vai vaicājums tika atjaunināts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1293">**search_session_ended_type** - Indicates where a search ended because it was canceled or the updated was the query</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1294">**search_suggestion_type**— norāda, kāds ir meklēšanas ieteikuma pamatojums, piemēram, vai tas ir pareizrakstības labojums?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1294">**search_suggestion_type** - indicates what is behind the search suggestion, I.e. is a spell correction?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1295">Balstīts vēsturē?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1295">Based on history?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1296">Automātiskā pabeigšana?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1296">Autocomplete?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1297">**see_all_contacts_selected_count** — izseko, cik reizes kombinētās meklēšanas sesijas laikā tika atlasīts “skatīt visas kontaktpersonas”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1297">**see_all_contacts_selected_count** - tracks how many times "see all contacts" was selected during the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1298">**subtab_type** — izseko gadījumus, kad lietotājs atlasīja rezultātu no rezultātu cilnes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1298">**subtab_type** -  tracks where the user has selected the result from which result tab</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1299">**top_mail_result_selected_count** — izseko, cik reizes lietotājs atlasa populārākos rezultātus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1299">**top_mail_result_selected_count** - tracks how many times a user selects the top results provided to them.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1300">**ui_reload_result_count** — reģistrē lietotāja interfeisa atkārtotas ielādes laiku rezultātu kopas atjaunināšanas dēļ (atbilstošā vaicājuma laikā)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1300">**ui_reload_result_count** - records the times of reloading UI because of result set update (during the corresponding query)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1301">**ui_reload_result_time** — reģistrē lietotāja interfeisa kopējo pavadīto laiku ielādes laiku rezultātu kopas atjaunināšanā (atbilstošā vaicājuma laikā)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1301">**ui_reload_result_time** - records the total time spent on reloading UI because of result set update (during the corresponding query)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1302">**ui_reload_status_count** — reģistrē lietotāja interfeisa atkārtotas ielādes laiku statusa kopas atjaunināšanas dēļ (atbilstošā vaicājuma laikā)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1302">**ui_reload_status_count** - records the times of reloading UI because of status update (during the corresponding query)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1303">**ui_reload_status_time** — reģistrē lietotāja interfeisa kopējo pavadīto laiku ielādes laiku statusa atjaunināšanā (atbilstošā vaicājuma laikā)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1303">**ui_reload_status_time** - records the total time spent on reloading UI because of status update (during the corresponding query)</span></span>

#### <a name="composemailaccessory"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1304">compose.mail.accessory</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1304">compose.mail.accessory</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1305">Šis notikums ļauj mums atklāt un novērst problēmas ar galvenajām e-pasta ziņojumu sastādīšanas darbībām, lai novērstu problēmas ar failu pievienošanu, fotoattēlu uzņemšanu un pievienošanu pielikumā vai jūsu pieejamības informācijas nosūtīšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1305">This event lets us detect and fix issues with key mail compose actions to prevent you from running into issues with attaching a file, taking a photo as an attachment, or sending your availability.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1306">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1306">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1307">**action** — norāda uz darbību, kuru bija mēģinājums veikt brīdī, kad darbība reģistrēta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1307">**action** - Tells us the action that was attempted when the action is logged.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1308">Piemēram, faila pievienošana un papildu opciju piedāvāšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1308">Some examples include attaching a file and presenting more options.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1309">**icon_name** — norāda ikonas nosaukumu, kas tiek parādīta brīdī, kad darbība tiek reģistrēta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1309">**icon_name** - Tells us the name of the icon that is being shown when the action is logged.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1310">**origin** — norāda uz darbības izcelsmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1310">**origin** – Tells us the origin of the action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1311">Iespējamās vērtības ir “quick_reply” un “full_screen”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1311">Possible values are quick_reply and full_screen.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1312">**toolbar_type** — norāda uz rīkjoslas tipu, kas ir redzams sastādīšanas lapā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1312">**toolbar_type** – Tell us the toolbar type which is presenting on compose page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1313">Iespējamās vērtība ir “compose_actions” un “formatting”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1313">Possible values are compose_actions and formatting.</span></span>


#### <a name="conversationviewaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1314">conversation.view.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1314">conversation.view.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1315">Izmanto, lai uzraudzītu iespējamo negatīvo ietekmi uz jūsu spēju skatīt un atbildēt uz e-pasta ziņojumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1315">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to view and reply to email messages</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1316">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1316">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1317">**contains_mention** — norāda, vai sarunā bija pielietots @ pieminējums, lai palīdzētu mums noteikt problēmas ar pieminējumiem e-pasta ziņojumos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1317">**contains_mention** - Tells us if the conversation had an @ mention applied to help us detect issues with email mentions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1318">**conversation_type** — norāda, kāda veida e-pasta ziņojuma skats tika renderēts, piemēram, viena ziņojuma skats vai vairāku ziņojumu skats.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1318">**conversation_type** - Tells us what type of email message view was rendered, such as a single message view or multiple message views.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1319">Palīdz atklāt ar konkrētiem ziņojumu veidiem saistītas problēmas mūsu e-pasta sarunu skatā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1319">Helps us detect issues related to a specific message type in our email conversation view.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1320">**reaction_origin** — norāda izcelsmi, no kurienes lietotājs reaģēja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1320">**reaction_origin** – Tells us origin from where the user reacted</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1321">**reaction_type** — parāda lietotāja reakcijas veidu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1321">**reaction_type** – Tells us the reaction type of the user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1322">**suggested_reply_char_count** — parāda, cik rakstzīmes ieteiktās atbildes piedāvā (ja ir), lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar ieteikumiem saistītas anomālijas un problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1322">**suggested_reply_char_count** - Tells us how many characters the suggested replies we offer (if available) to help us detect anomalies and issues related to our suggestions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1323">**suggested_reply_click_pos** — norāda, kurā pozīcijā ir norādīta ieteiktā atbilde (ja pieejama), lai mēs spētu atklāt problēmas ar konkrēto ieteikumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1323">**suggested_reply_click_pos** - Tells us which position the suggested reply (if available) is rendered so we can detect issues with a specific suggestion</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1324">**suggested_reply_type** — norāda uz ieteicamo atbildi šai darbībai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1324">**suggested_reply_type** - indicates type of suggested reply for this action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1325">Iespējamās vērtības ir “text”, “send_avail” un “create_meeting”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1325">Possible values are text, send_avail, and create_meeting.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1326">**use_default_quick_reply_mode** — norāda, vai tika izmantots ātrās noklusējuma atbildes režīms, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar ātrajām atbildēm e-pasta ziņojumos saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1326">**use_default_quick_reply_mode** - Tells us if the default quick reply mode was used to help us detect issues related to the quick reply experience for email</span></span>

#### <a name="draftaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1327">draft.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1327">draft.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1328">Izmanto, lai uzraudzītu iespējamo negatīvo ietekmi uz jūsu spēju veidot un saglabāt e-pasta ziņojumu melnrakstus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1328">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to create and save mail drafts.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1329">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1329">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1330">**action** — darbības veids, piemēram, saglabāt, atmest.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1330">**action** - the type of action, e.g. save, discard.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1331">**draft_message_id** — melnraksta ziņojuma ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1331">**draft_message_id** - message ID of the draft</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1332">**is_groups** — norāda, vai melnraksts tiek sūtīts no/uz grupas mapi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1332">**is_groups** - whether the draft is being sent to/from a group folder</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1333">**origin** — norāda melnraksta sākšanas vietu, piemēram, detalizēta ziņojuma informācija, sastādīšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1333">**origin** - where draft was initiated, e.g. message detail, compose.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1334">**smart_compose_model_version** — seko izmantojamā viedās sastādīšanas modeļa versijai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1334">**smart_compose_model_version** - tracks which version of smart compose model is being used</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1335">**suggestions_requested** — norāda pieprasīto viedo sastādīšanas ieteikumu skaitu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1335">**suggestions_requested** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions requested</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1336">**suggestions_results** — viedā sastādīšanas ieteikuma rezultāts, t.i., pieņemts, noraidīts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1336">**suggestions_results** - smart compose suggestions’ result, i.e. accepted, rejected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1337">**suggestions_requested** — norāda, cik daudz viedo sastādīšanas ieteikumu atgriezts no servera</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1337">**suggestions_returned** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions returned from server</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1338">**suggestions_requested** — norāda, cik daudz viedo sastādīšanas ieteikumu tika parādīts lietotājam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1338">**suggestions_shown** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions shown to the user</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1339">**thread_id** — sarunas, ar kuru ir saistīts melnraksts, pavediena ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1339">**thread_id** - thread ID of the conversation draft is associated with</span></span>

#### <a name="draganddrop"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1340">drag.and.drop</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1340">drag.and.drop</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1341">Šis notikums ļauj mums noteikt, vai vilkšanas un nomešanas darbība bija veiksmīga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1341">This event lets us detect if the drag and drop action was successful or not.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1342">Tiek izmantots, lai pārliecinātos par to, ka vilkšanas un nomešanas funkcija darbojas pareizi visās lietojumprogrammās, tai skaitā kā nomešanas iekš Outlook notikums un vilkšanas ārpus Outlook notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1342">It is used to ensure that drag-and-drop experiences are working correctly across applications both as a drop event into Outlook and a drag event that leaves Outlook.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1343">Ar šo datu palīdzību mēs varam pārliecināties par pilnvērtīgu darbību ar citām lietojumprogrammām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1343">With this data we are able to ensure that the end-to-end experience with other applications is working as expected.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1344">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1344">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1345">**action** — darbība būs vilkt vai nomest</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1345">**action** - Action will be either drag or drop</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1346">**location** — vilkšanas darbības gadījumā informē mūs par vietu, kur lietotājs uzsāka vilkšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1346">**location** - In case of a drag action, this will let us know from which location the user started the drag.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1347">Nomešanas darbības gadījumā informē mūs par vietu, kur lietotājs nometa vilkto failu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1347">In case of a drop action, this will let us know where the user dropped the file which was being dragged.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1348">**source** — nomešanas darbības gadījumā informē mūs par vietu, kur lietotājs uzsāka vilkšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1348">**source** – In the case of a drop action, this will let us know from which location the user started the drag.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1349">Konkrētos nomešanas gadījumos, piemēram, nomešana jaunā e-pasta ziņojumā, palīdz mums labāk atklāt problēmas ar specifiskiem avotiem, piemēram, OneDrive vai faili. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1349">This helps us better discover issues with a specific source like OneDrive or Files into a specific drop location, such as a new email.</span></span>

#### <a name="drawerevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1350">drawer.event</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1350">drawer.event</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1351">Izmanto, lai uzraudzītu iespējamo negatīvo ietekmi uz jūsu piekļūt mapēm jūsu iesūtnē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1351">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to access folders in your inbox</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1352">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1352">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1353">**add_calendar_option** — norāda no atvilktnes pievienojamā kalendāra tipu, piemēram, interesējošais kalendārs, e-pasta kalendārs, kopīgots kalendārs, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar specifiskiem kalendāru veidiem saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1353">**add_calendar_option** - Indicates the type of calendar being added from the drawer i.e. interesting calendar, mail calendar, shared calendar, to help us detect issues related to specific calendar types</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1354">**calendar_accounts_count** — norāda kalendāra kontu skaitu, kas palīdz mums atklāt problēmas ar jūsu kontu skaitu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1354">**calendar_accounts_count** - Indicates the number of calendar accounts to help us detect issues related to number of accounts you have</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1355">**calendar_apps_count** — norāda kalendāra lietojumprogrammu skaitu lietotāja ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar kalendāra lietojumprogrammām saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1355">**calendar_apps_count** - Indicates the number of calendar apps present on the user's device to help us detect issues related to calendar apps</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1356">**drawer_type** — norāda atvilktnes tipu: kalendārs, e-pasts vai nulles vaicājums, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar atvilktnes tipu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1356">**drawer_type** - Indicates the drawer type: calendar, mail or zero query to help us detect issues related to the drawer type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1357">**from_favorites** — norāda, vai darbība tika veikta no izlases, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar izlasi saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1357">**from_favorites** - Indicates if the action was taken from favorites to help us detect issues related to favorites</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1358">**group_calendar_count** — norāda uz konta kalendāru skaitu, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar grupu kalendāriem saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1358">**group_calendar_count** - Indicates the number of calendars for the account to help us detect issues related group calendars</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1359">**inbox_unread_count** — norāda nelasīto ziņojumu skaitu iesūtnē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas ar nelasīto ziņojumu skaita parādīšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1359">**inbox_unread_count** - Indicates the number of unread messages in the inbox to help us detect issues with displaying inbox unread counts.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1360">**interesting_calendar_accounts_count** — norāda kontu skaitu, kas ir piemēroti interesējošiem kalendāriem ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar interesējošiem kalendāriem saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1360">**interesting_calendar_accounts_count** - Indicates the number of accounts which are eligible for interesting calendars on the device to help us detect issues related to interesting calendars</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1361">**is_group_calendar** — norāda, vai kalendārs ir grupas kalendārs, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar grupas kalendāriem saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1361">**is_group_calendar** - Indicates if the calendar is a group calendar to help us detect issues related group calendars</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1362">**mail_folder_type** — norāda pasta mapes veidu, piemēram, iesūtne, melnraksti utt., lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar mapju tipiem saistītās problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1362">**mail_folder_type** - Indicates the mail folder type i.e. inbox, drafts, etc. to help us detect issues related to folder types.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1363">**mail_accounts_count** — norāda e-pasta kontu skaitu, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar e-pasta kontiem saistītās problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1363">**mail_accounts_count** - indicates the number of mail accounts to help us detect issues related mail accounts.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1364">**selected_group_calendar_count** — norāda UI atlasīto un aktīvo grupas kalendāru skaitu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1364">**selected_group_calendar_count** - Indicates the number of group calendars which are selected and active in the UI</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1365">**visibility_toggle** — norāda, vai lietotājs ieslēdz vai izslēdz konkrētu kalendāru, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar kalendāru rādīšanu vai slēpšanu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1365">**visibility_toggle** - indicates if the user is turning on or off a given calendar to help us detect issues related to showing or hiding calendars</span></span>

#### <a name="ipccreaterepublishinglicense"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1366">IpcCreateRepublishingLicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1366">IpcCreateRepublishingLicense</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1367">Tiek apkopots, kad lietotājs mēģina atvērt ar IRM aizsargātu dokumentu vai lietot IRM aizsardzību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1367">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1368">Tas satur informāciju, kas ir nepieciešama pareizai tādu problēmu izmeklēšanai un diagnosticēšanai, kas notiek IpcCreateRepublishingLicense API izsaukuma laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1368">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when the IpcCreateRepublishingLicense API call is made.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1369">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1369">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
