- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1613">**RMS.LicensePropertyType** — licences rekvizīta tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1613">**RMS.LicensePropertyType** - license property type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1614">**RMS.Result** — API izsaukums sekmīgs vai neizdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1614">**RMS.Result** - Success or fail of the API call</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1615">**RMS.ScenarioId** — scenārija ID, ko definē API</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1615">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario Id defined by the API</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1616">**RMS.SDKVersion** — tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma klienta versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1616">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1617">**RMS.StatusCode** — scenārija ID, ko definē API</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1617">**RMS.StatusCode** - Scenario Id defined by the API</span></span>


#### <a name="linkclickedaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1618">link.clicked.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1618">link.clicked.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1619">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai sekotu lietotāju veiksmīgai URL apskatīšanai Edge tīmekļa skatā un standarta tīmekļa scenāriju izpildei šajā tīmekļa skatā bez kļūdām. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1619">The event is used to track users' success in viewing a URL in the Edge web view and completing standard web scenarios in that web view without facing errors</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1620">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1620">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1621">**account_type** — ja Edge tīmekļa skats tika palaists no e-pasta ziņojuma vai notikuma programmā Outlook, norāda URL izcelsmes konta tipu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1621">**account_type** – if the Edge web view was launched from an email or event in Outlook, type of the account where the URL came from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1622">**action** — darbība, ko lietotājs veic programmā Outlook, no brīža, kad lietotājs pieskaras URL līdz brīdim, kad lietotājs iziet no šīs plūsmas (saite atvērta Edge tīmekļa skatā, lapas ielāde tīmekļa skatā neizdevās, veikta meklēšana tīmekļa skatā, iziešana no Edge tīmekļa skata, lai atvērtu saiti tīmekļa pārlūkprogrammā utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1622">**action** – action performed by the user inside Outlook from the moment they tap on a URL to when they exit that flow (opened the link in the Edge web view, page failed to load in the web view, performed a search in the web view, exit the Edge web view to open the link in a web browser application, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1623">**duration** — lietotāja sesijas ilgums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1623">**duration** – duration of the user session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1624">**launch_type** — ja tika palaists Edge tīmekļa skats, vai tas tika palaists no Outlook, logrīka vai operētājsistēmas komponenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1624">**launch_type** – if the Edge web view was launched, was it from Outlook, from a widget, or from an OS component</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1625">**origin** — ja lietotājs veica darbību Edge tīmekļa skatā, norāda šīs darbības izcelsmi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1625">**origin** – if the user performed an action in the Edge web view, origin of that action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1626">**referrer** — vietrāža URL, kuram pieskārās lietotājs, atrašanās vieta (e-pasta ziņojums, kalendārs, notikums, TXP kartīte, utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1626">**referrer** – the location of the URL the user tapped on (email, calendar event, TXP card, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1627">**search_scope** — norāda, vai lietotājs veica meklēšanu Edge tīmekļa skatā un šīs meklēšanas tvērumu (viss, attēli, video, utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1627">**search_scope** – if the user performed a search in the Edge web view, scope of that search (All, Images, Videos, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1628">**search_subtype** — ja lietotājs veica meklēšanu Edge tīmekļa skatā, vai šī bija sākotnējā vai precizētā meklēšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1628">**search_subtype** – if the user performed a search in the Edge web view, was it an initial search or a refined search</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1629">**session_summary_page_loaded_count** — lietotāja Edge tīmekļa skata sesijas laikā ielādēto lapu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1629">**session_summary_page_loaded_count** – number of pages loaded by the user during their session in the Edge web view</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1630">**session_summary_search_count**— lietotāja Edge tīmekļa skata sesijas laikā veikto Bing meklējumu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1630">**session_summary_search_count** - number of Bing searches performed by the user during their session in the Edge web view</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1631">**session_summary_session_id** — pašreizējās lietotāja Edge tīmekļa skata sesijas identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1631">**session_summary_session_id** – identifier for the present user session in the Edge web view</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1632">**txp** — ja Edge tīmekļa skats tika palaists no TXP kartītes, šīs kartītes notikuma tips (pusdienas, lidojums utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1632">**txp** – if the Edge web view was launched from a TXP card, event type for that card (dining, flight, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1633">**txp_component** — ja Edge tīmekļa skats tika palaists no TXP kartītes, šīs kartītes lietotāja saskarnes komponenta tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1633">**txp_component** - if the Edge web view was launched from a TXP card, UI component type for that card</span></span>


#### <a name="mailaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1634">mail.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1634">mail.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1635">Izmanto, lai uzraudzītu iespējamo negatīvo ietekmi uz jūsu spēju veikt kritiskas e-pasta darbības (piemēram, e-pasta darbība pavediena režīmā, pasta šķirošanas darbību izpilde), lai nodrošinātu mūsu lietojumprogrammas pareizu darbību ar e-pastu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1635">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to perform critical mail actions (like running mail threaded mode, ensuring mail triage actions work) to ensure our app is functioning properly for mail.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1636">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1636">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1637">**account** — konts, kas veica darbību *[Šis lauks ir dzēsts jaunākajos Office būvējumos, taču, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1637">**account** - the account which performed the action *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1638">**action** — izseko veiktās darbības veidu, piem., arhivēt, dzēst, atzīmēt kā lasītu utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1638">**action** - tracks what type of action was taking, i.e. archive, delete, mark as read, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1639">**attachment_content_type** — lejupielādētā pielikuma satura tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1639">**attachment_content_type** - the content type of the downloaded attachment</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1640">**attachment_content_type_with_count** — seko pielikumu skaitam e-pasta ziņojumā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1640">**attachment_content_type_with_count** - tracks the number of attachments in email</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1641">**attachment_download_result** — pielikuma lejupielādes darbības rezultāts (piem., izdevās/neizdevās)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1641">**attachment_download_result** - the result (i.e. success/failure) for an attachment download action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1642">**attachment_download_time** — pielikuma lejupielādes darbības laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1642">**attachment_download_time** - the time for an attachment download action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1643">**attachment_extn** — lejupielādētā pielikuma faila paplašinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1643">**attachment_extn** - the file extension of the downloaded attachment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1644">**attachment_id** — lejupielādētā pielikuma sistēmas identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1644">**attachment_id** - the system identifier for the downloaded attachment</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1645">**attachment_size** — lejupielādētā pielikuma izmērs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1645">**attachment_size** - the size of downloaded attachment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1646">**domain** — atveramā dokumenta domēns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1646">**domain** - domain of the document being opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1647">**duration** — izseko darbības ilgumam cilvēkam salasāmas virknes formātā (piem., 1 s, 4h) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1647">**duration** - tracks how long the action took as human-readable English string (e.g. 1s, 4h)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1648">**error** — ar darbību saistītās kļūdas ziņojums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1648">**error** - error message associated with the action</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1649">**event_mode** — kāda veida notikuma režīmā tas bija, grupas vai cits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1649">**event_mode** - what type of event mode it was in, groups or others.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1650">**Extension** — ar šo darbību saistītā faila paplašinājuma saite vai pielikums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1650">**Extension** - file extension of link or attachment associated with this action</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1651">**internet_message_id** — ziņojuma izsekošanas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1651">**internet_message_id** - tracking message ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1652">**is_group_escalation** — norāda, vai ziņojums par darbības veikšanu tika nosūtīts uz lietotāja pastkasti eskalācijas dēļ (abonēta grupa)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1652">**is_group_escalation** - indicates whether the message the action was taken on was sent to the user's mailbox because of an escalation (subscribed to group)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1653">**is_rule** — norāda, vai veiktā e-pasta darbība atiestata svarīgo/citu klasifikāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1653">**is_rule** - indicates if the mail action done is resetting a focused/other classification</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1654">**is_threaded_mode** — norāda, vai ziņojums bija pavediena režīmā, t.i., kā ir grupēti ziņojumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1654">**is_threaded_mode** - indicates whether the message was in threaded mode or not, i.e. how are the messages grouped</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1655">**is_unread** — norāda, vai ziņojums, saistībā ar kuru tika veikta darbība, ir nelasīts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1655">**is_unread** - indicates whether message is unread that the action was taken on</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1656">**left_swipe_setting** — norāda, kāda darbība ir iestatīta kā pavilkšana pa kreisi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1656">**left_swipe_setting** - indicates what action was a set to be the left swipe</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1657">**message_id** — servera ziņojuma ID, kas ir vērsts uz darbību, vai ar komatiem atdalīts saraksts, ja darbībā bija vairāki vienumi. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1657">**message_id** - server message id targeted for action, or comma-separated list if more than one item was in action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1658">**message_type** — norāda, kāda tipa ziņojumā tika veikta darbība\* \* — grupas vai cits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1658">**message_type** - indicates what type of message type the action was taken on\*\* - group or other</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1659">**number_selected** — vienumu skaits, ko lietotājs atlasīja ziņojumu sarakstā un veica darbību vairāku vienumu atlases režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1659">**number_selected** - the number of items the user selected on the message list and took action on during multiple selection mode.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1660">**origin** — darbības izcelsme, piem., šūnu pavilkšana, nulles vaicājums, dziļā saite, e-pasta skats, e-pastu saraksts utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1660">**origin** - source of action, i.e. cell swipe, zero-query, deep link, email view, email list, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1661">**reported_to_msft** — izvēle ziņot Microsoft par darbību pēc e-pasta ziņojuma nosūtīšanas uz mēstuļu mapi (surogātpasts) vai atkritni (pikšķerēšana).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1661">**reported_to_msft** - after sending an email to junk (spam) or trash (phishing) they can choose to report their action to Microsoft.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1662">**retry** — norāda, vai darbība tika atkārtota</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1662">**retry** - whether the action was retried</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1663">**right_swipe_setting** — norāda, kāda darbība ir iestatīta kā pavilkšana pa labi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1663">**right_swipe_setting** - indicates what action was a set to be the right swipe</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1664">**shortcut** — norāda, vai tika izmantota saīsne un, kāda saīsne tika izmantota, lai ieplānotu ziņojumu, piemēram, vēlāk, rītdien, noteiktā laikā utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1664">**shortcut** - indicates if a shortcut was used and what shortcut was used for scheduling a message i.e. later, tomorrow, choose time, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1665">**size** — ar šo darbību saistītās saites vai pielikuma izmērs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1665">**size** - size of link or attachment associated with this action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1666">**source_folder** — izseko avota mapes tipam, kad darbība norāda uz pārvietošanu no vienas mapes uz citu, piemēram, uz iesūtni, atkritni utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1666">**source_folder** - tracks source folder type when action is indicating to move from one folder to other, i.e. to inbox, trash etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1667">**source_inbox** — norāda, kurā iesūtnē notiek pasta darbība (piemēram, galvenajā, citā utt.)
state — darbības statuss, piem., izpildīta veiksmīgi vai neveiksmīgi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1667">**source_inbox** - indicates which inbox the mail action is taking place (i.e. focused, other, etc.) state - state of the action, i.e. success or point of failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1668">**target_folder** — norāda mērķa mapes tipu, pārvietojot e-pasta ziņojumus no vienas mapes uz citu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1668">**target_folder** - indicates target folder type when moving emails from one folder to other</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1669">**thread_id** — darbībai pakļautās sarunas pavediena ID vai ar komatiem atdalīts saraksts, ja darbība tika piemērota vairākiem vienumiem. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1669">**thread_id** - thread id of the conversation targeted for action, or comma-separated list if more than one item was targeted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1670">**time_taken_to_fetch_access_token** — laiks sistēmas piekļuves marķiera izgūšanai, lai atvērtu saiti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1670">**time_taken_to_fetch_access_token** - time taken to fetch a system access token to use for opening a link</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1671">**time_taken_to_fetch_drive_item** — OneDrive resursa izgūšanas laiks noklikšķinot</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1671">**time_taken_to_fetch_drive_item** - time taken to fetch a OneDrive resource when clicked</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1672">**time_taken_to_fetch_embed_viewer_resource** — iegultā skatītāja inicializācijai nepieciešamais laiks, atverot saites</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1672">**time_taken_to_fetch_embed_viewer_resource** - time taken to initialize the embedded viewer when opening links</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1673">**time_taken_to_load_embed_viewer** — iegultā skatītāja inicializācijai nepieciešamais laiks, atverot saites</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1673">**time_taken_to_load_embed_viewer** - time taken to initialize the embedded viewer when opening links</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1674">**time_taken_to_load_link** — saites ielādes darbības pabeigšanai nepieciešamais laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1674">**time_taken_to_load_link** - time a load link action takes to complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1675">**time_taken_to_tap_attachment** — laiks no ziņojuma atvēršanas brīža līdz noklikšķināšanai uz pielikuma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1675">**time_taken_to_tap_attachment** - the time between opening the message and clicking on the attachment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1676">**time_taken_to_tap_link** — laiks, kas lietotājam pagāja no ziņojuma apskatīšanas līdz noklikšķināšanai uz saites</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1676">**time_taken_to_tap_link** - time the user took between viewing message and clicking a link</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1677">**txp** — norāda, vai pastāv txp tipa vienums, kas ir saistīts ar e-pastu, kurā tika veikta darbība, piemēram, pasākuma rezervācija, lidojuma rezervācija utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1677">**txp** - indicates if there is a txp type of item associated with the mail that action was taken on, i.e. event reservation, flight reservation, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1678">**type** — caur saiti atveramā dokumenta tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1678">**type** - document type being opened via link</span></span>

#### <a name="mailcompose"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1679">mail.compose</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1679">mail.compose</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1680">Izmanto, lai uzraudzītu iespējamo negatīvo ietekmi uz jūsu spēju sastādīt un atbildēt uz e-pastiem, piemēram, problēmas ar atbildi visiem, jūsu e-pasta ziņojumu formatēšanu vai nosūtīšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1680">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to compose and reply to emails such as running into issues with reply-all, formatting your email, or sending your emails.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1681">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1681">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1682">**draft_message_id** — kā melnraksta izveidotās sarunas melnraksta ID, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar e-pastu ziņojumu melnrakstiem saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1682">**draft_message_id** - The draft id of the conversation being created as a draft to help us detect issues related to draft emails</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1683">**message_id** — ziņojuma ID sarunai, uz kuru tiek atbildēts vai no kuras tiek pārsūtīts, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar konkrētu ziņojumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1683">**message_id** - The message id of the conversation being replied to or forwarded from to help us detect issues related to a specific message</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1684">**origin** — norāda uz ziņojuma sastādīšanas izcelsmi, piemēram, atbildēt visiem, rakstīt jaunu vai ātrā atbilde.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1684">**origin** - Tells us where the compose originated from, such as from a reply all, a new compose, or quick reply.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1685">Palīdz mums atklāt problēmas, kas saistītas ar konkrētu atbildes izcelsmes tipu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1685">Helps us detect issues associated with a specific reply origin type.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1686">**is_group_escalation** — norāda, vai ziņojums ir eskalēts grupas ziņojums, lai mēs varētu atklāt ar grupām saistītas sastādīšanas problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1686">**is_group_escalation** - Whether the message is an escalated group message so we can detect compose issues related to groups.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1687">**is_link** — norāda, vai jaunizveidotais melnraksts tika izveidots no saites.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1687">**is_link** - Tells us if the new draft that was created was done from a link.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1688">Palīdz mums atklāt problēmas, kas saistītas ar no saitēm veidotajiem melnrakstiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1688">Helps us detect issues associated with drafts created from links.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1689">**is_force_touch** — norāda, vai jauns melnraksts tika izveidots no piespied darbības. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1689">**is_force_touch** - Tells us if the new draft that was created was done from a force touch action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1690">Palīdz mums atklāt problēmas, kas saistītas melnrakstiem no šīs konkrētās darbības.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1690">Helps us detect issues associated with drafts created from this specific action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1691">**is_groups** — vai notikums tika sākts no grupu telpas, lai mēs varētu atklāt ar grupām saistītās sastādīšanas problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1691">**is_groups** - Whether the event was started from the groups' space so we can detect compose issues related to groups.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1692">**source_inbox** — norāda avota iesūtni, piemēram, vai tā ir galvenā vai cita iesūtne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1692">**source_inbox** - Tells us the source inbox, such as whether it was a focused or other inbox</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1693">**thread_id** — pavedina ID sarunai, uz kuru tiek atbildēts vai no kuras tiek pārsūtīts, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar konkrētu pavedienu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1693">**thread_id** - The thread id of the conversation being replied to or forwarded from to help us detect issues related to a specific thread</span></span>

#### <a name="meetingcalltoaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1694">meeting.call.to.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1694">meeting.call.to.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1695">Izmanto, lai uzraudzīto iespējamo negatīvo ietekmi uz jūsu spēju veikt kritiskas sapulču darbības, piemēram, izveidošana, rediģēšana un atbilde uz sapulcēm.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1695">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to perform critical meeting actions like creating, editing, and responding to meetings.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1696">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1696">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1697">**event_mode** — norāda, vai šis notikums ir no grupas, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas ar grupu notikumiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1697">**event_mode** - Indicates whether this event was from a group or not to help us detect issues with group events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1698">**meeting_id** — sapulces ID, kas palīdz mums izsekot problēmām sanāksmes darbības laikā, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas ar konkrētām sapulcēm</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1698">**meeting_id** - A meeting ID that helps us track issues throughout the lifetime of a meeting to help us detect issues with specific meetings</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1699">**meeting_provider** — norāda tiešsaistes sapulces nodrošinātāju, piemēram, Teams, Skype darbam, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas ar konkrētiem sapulču nodrošinātājiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1699">**meeting_provider** - Indicates the provider for an online meeting, e.g. Teams, Skype for Business to help us detect issues with specific online meeting providers</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1700">**notify_type** — norāda atbildes tipu citu kontu tipiem, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas ar dažādiem kontu tipiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1700">**notify_type** - Indicates the response type for other account types to help us detect issues with different account types</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1701">**recurrence** — norāda, cik bieži notiek šī sapulce, piemēram, regulāri vai sērijveida, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas ar atkārtoti notiekošām sapulcēm</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1701">**recurrence** - Indicates how often this meeting occurs I.e. occurrence or series to help us detect issues with reoccurring meeting series</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1702">**response** — norāda atbildes tipu, piemēram, piekrist vai noraidīt noteiktos kontu tipos, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar atbildēm uz notikumiem saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1702">**response** - Indicates response type such as accept or decline on certain account types to help us detect issues with responding to events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1703">**response_message_length** — norāda ziņojuma garumu, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas ar sapulču atbildēm</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1703">**response_message_length** - Indicates how long the message length was to help us detect issues with meeting responses</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1704">**review_time_proposal_action_type** — norāda lietotāja atbildi uz jauna laika piedāvājumu, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas ar jauna laika piedāvāšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1704">**review_time_proposal_action_type** - Indicates a user response new time proposal to help us detect issues with proposing a new time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1705">**send_response** — norāda, vai atbilde tika nosūtīta, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas ar atbilžu uz sapulču uzaicinājumiem nosūtīšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1705">**send_response** - Indicates whether a response was sent to help us detect issues sending meeting invite responses</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1706">**txp** — norāda sapulces tipu, no kura tas tika ģenerēts, no lidojumu rezervācijām un piegādēm, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas ar šī tipa sapulcēm</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1706">**txp** - Indicates what type of meeting it was generated from flight reservations and deliveries to help us detect issues with this type of meeting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1707">**with_message_enabled** — norāda, vai lietotājs var atbildēt ar ziņojumu, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas ar atbildēšanu uz sapulču uzaicinājumiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1707">**with_message_enabled** - Indicates whether a user can response with a message to help us detect issues with responding to meeting invites</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroiddocsuifileoperationsopendocumentmeasurements"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1708">Office.Android.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenDocumentMeasurements</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1708">Office.Android.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenDocumentMeasurements</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1709">Šis notikums tiek apkopots Office lietojumprogrammām, kas darbojas uz Android platformas, un reģistrē faila atvēršanas darbības.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1709">This event is collected for Office applications running under Android platform and records when a file open operation takes place.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1710">Šis notikums palīdz nodrošināt faila atvēršanas darbības drošību, atjauninājumus un pareizu darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1710">The event helps in keeping the file open operation secure, up- to- date and performing properly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1711">Šo datu apkopošanas mērķis ir turpināt uzlabot failu atvēršanas veiktspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1711">The goal of collecting this data is to continuously improve the file open performance.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1712">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1712">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1713">**Data_AppDocsOperationDuration** — apakšslānī pavadītais laiks faila atvēršanas darbības laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1713">**Data_AppDocsOperationDuration** - The duration spent in sub- layer during a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1714">**Data_AppDuration** — lietojumprogrammā, kas veic faila atvēršanu, pavadītais laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1714">**Data_AppDuration** - The duration spent in application processing during a file open operation.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1715">**Data_AppWarmUpGain** — lietojumprogrammas startēšanas laika pieaugums, kas notiek tāpēc, ka veicam lietojumprogrammas pirmsāknēšanas daļu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1715">**Data_AppWarmUpGain** - The gain in application boot duration we get because of pre-booting a part of the application beforehand.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1716">**Data_BootDuration** — lietojumprogrammas palaišanas ilgums faila atvēršanas procesā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1716">**Data_BootDuration** - The duration of application boot in process of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1717">**Data_ClosePreviouslyOpenedMarkers** — atsevišķos failu atvēršanas scenārijos pirms pašreizējā dokumenta atvēršanas notiek iepriekš atvērtā dokumenta aizvēršana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1717">**Data_ClosePreviouslyOpenedMarkers** – In some file open scenarios, closing of a previously opened document takes place before the opening of the current document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1718">Šis laika posms starp dažām darbībām, kas šajā gadījumā notiek, tiek ierakstīts kā virknes vērtība, kuras formāts ir \<functionId>\<functionValue>\<functionId>\<functionValue>...</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1718">This time duration between some of the operations that take place in this case is captured in a string value which has the format \<functionId>\<functionValue>\<functionId>\<functionValue>...</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1719">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda uz faila piekļuves režīmu, piemēram, tikai lasāms, lasāms-rakstāms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1719">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, e.g. read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1720">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind**— uzskaitījums, kas norāda asinhronās plūsmas veidu, kas tika izmantota faila atvēršanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1720">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** - An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1721">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila dalīšanas algoritma veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1721">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - An enumeration indicating the type of chunking algorithm of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1722">**Data_Doc_EdpState** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila uzņēmuma datu aizsardzības statusu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1722">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - An enumeration indicating the enterprise data protection state of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1723">**Data_Doc_Ext** — faila paplašinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1723">**Data_Doc_Ext** - File extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1724">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** — faila servera resursdatora nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1724">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1725">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** — globāli unikāls identifikators (GUID), kas unikāli identificē servera resursdatoru.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1725">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - A Globally Unique Identifier (GUID) that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1726">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē identitāti, kas tika izmantota, lai atvērtu failu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1726">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the identity used to open a file.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1727">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda detalizēto faila atvēršanas darbības scenārija veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1727">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - An enumeration indicating the detailed scenario type of a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1728">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila atvēršanas darbības ievadizvades karodziņus, piemēram, vai fails ir kešots.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1728">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - An enumeration indicating the IO flags of a file open operation, e.g. if the file is cached or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1729">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** — vai failam ir iespējota sadarbība mākonī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1729">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** - Whether or not the cloud collaboration is enabled for the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1730">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** — vai fails tika atvērts ar inkrementālo atvēršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1730">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened via incremental open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1731">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** — vai fails atbalsta Office sadarbības pakalpojumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1731">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Whether or not a file supports Office Collaboration Service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1732">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** — vai fails tiek atvērts no bezsaistes kešatmiņas kopijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1732">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Whether or not a file is opened from an offline cached copy.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1733">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** — vai fails tika iepriekš ielādēts pirms atvēršanas darbības.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1733">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** - Whether or not the file was prefetched before open operation happened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1734">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** — vai mākonī esošajam failam ir lokālā versija un, vai tā ir sinhronizēta ar serveri.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1734">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Whether or not a cloud file exists locally and is synchronized with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1735">**Data_Doc_Location** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda uz faila atrašanās vietu, piemēram, atrodas lokāli vai mākonī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1735">**Data_Doc_Location** - An enumeration indicating where the file is located, e.g. locally or in cloud.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1736">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila tikai lasīšanas iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1736">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - An enumeration indicating the read only reason of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1737">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē faila servera resursa ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1737">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server resource id of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1738">**Data_Doc_RtcType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila izmantotā reāllaika kanāla (RTC) veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1738">**Data_Doc_RtcType** - An enumeration indicating type of real- time channel (RTC) used by the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1739">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē servera dokumenta ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1739">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server document ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1740">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda mākoņa faila servera protokolu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1740">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - An enumeration indicating the server protocol of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1741">**Data_Doc_ServerType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda mākoņa faila servera veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1741">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - An enumeration indicating the server type of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1742">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda mākoņa faila servera versiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1742">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - An enumeration indicating the server version of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1743">**Data_Doc_SessionId** — vesels skaitlis, kas pieaug par 1 ar katru faila atvēršanas darbību sesijas laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1743">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - An integer which is incremented by 1 for each file open operation in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1744">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** — virkne, kas tiek izmantota, lai savstarpēji saistītu klienta un servera žurnālus; parasti tas ir kāds ID veids.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1744">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - A string used to correlate client- side and server- side logs, typically it is a kind of ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1745">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** — dokumenta lielums baitos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1745">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - File size in bytes.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1746">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda īpašās rakstzīmes veidu faila URL adresē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1746">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - An enumeration indicating which kind of special character the file URL has.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1747">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē faila URL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1747">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the file URL.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1748">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** — norāda, vai fails tika atvērts inkrementāli, izmantojot iepriekš kešotus WRS datus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1748">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened incrementally using pre- cached WRS data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1749">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** — virkne, kas norāda, no kura pakalpojuma ir tīmekļa lietojumprogrammas atvērtās platformas interfeisa protokola (WOPI) fails.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1749">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - A string indicating which service a Web Application Open Platform Interface Protocol (WOPI) file is from.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1750">**Data_ErrorId_Code** — kļūdas kods, kas norāda uz datu vākšanas darbības kļūmi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1750">**Data_ErrorId_Code** - An error code indicating a failure in the data collection operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1751">**Data_ErrorId_Tag** — atzīme kodā, kas palīdz noteikt kļūmes punktu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1751">**Data_ErrorId_Tag** - A tag in the code to help find the point of failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1752">**Data_FileOpenFlowMarkers** — pirms faila atvēršanas procesa sākšanas notiek pirmapstrāde.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1752">**Data_FileOpenFlowMarkers** – Before the file open process begins, there is some pre-processing involved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1753">Pirmapstrādei veltītai laiks tiek ierakstīts kā virknes vērtībā, kuras formāts ir \<functionId>\<functionValue>\<functionId>\<functionValue>...</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1753">This time taken for this pre-processing is captured in a string value which has the format \<functionId>\<functionValue>\<functionId>\<functionValue>...</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1754">**Data_FirstPartyProviderApp** — ja fails, kas atvērts programmā Word, Excel vai PowerPoint vai Office lietojumprogrammās, tiek izsaukts no citas Microsoft lietojumprogrammas, šis pakalpojumu sniedzēja nosaukums tiek uztverts šeit.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1754">**Data_FirstPartyProviderApp** - If a file open on Word, Excel, or PowerPoint or Office apps is invoked from another Microsoft app, then the name of that provider app is captured here.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1755">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** — virknes vērtība, kas uzskaita atsevišķu funkciju pieprasījumā pavadīto laiku formātā ar funkcijas birku un ilgumu, kas iekļauj apakšfunkciju pieprasījumu ilgumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1755">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which includes the duration of sub- function calls.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1756">**Data_InitializationReason** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda uz faila atvēršanas veidu, piemēram, lietotāja interfeisa elements vai citas lietojumprogrammas izsaukuma rezultātā utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1756">**Data_InitializationReason** - An enumeration indicating how the file is opened, e.g. UI element, triggered by another app, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1757">**Data_Measurements** — virknes vērtība, kas uzskaita atsevišķu funkciju pieprasījumā pavadīto laiku formātā ar funkcijas atzīmi un ilgumu, kas neiekļauj apakšfunkciju pieprasījumu ilgumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1757">**Data_Measurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which excludes the duration of sub- function calls.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1758">**Data_OfficeMobileInitReason** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila atvēršanas ieejas punktu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1758">**Data_OfficeMobileInitReason** - An enumeration indicating the entry point of file open.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1759">**Data_RenderToInSpaceDuration** — ilgums starp renderēšanas beigām un silueta/kanvas animāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1759">**Data_RenderToInSpaceDuration** – The duration between render end and the silhouette/canvas animation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1760">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** — faila atvēršanas renderēšanas ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1760">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** - The duration of rendering of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1761">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements**— virknes vērtība, kas uzskaita atsevišķu funkciju pieprasījumu ilgumu formātā ar funkcija birku, sākuma laikspiedolu un ilgumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1761">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag, start timestamp and duration.</span></span> 

#### <a name="officeandroiddocsuipaywallcontrolskuchoosertoggled"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1762">Office.Android.DocsUI.PaywallControl.SkuChooserToggled</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1762">Office.Android.DocsUI.PaywallControl.SkuChooserToggled</span></span>
