<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1765">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1765">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1766">**EventDate** — notikuma laikspiedols</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1766">**EventDate** – Timestamp of the event occurrence</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1767">**SessionID** — GUID, lai savienotu notikumus pēc sesijas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1767">**SessionID** – GUID to connect events by session</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidearlytelemetryexpansionfilesavailability"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1768">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExpansionFilesAvailability</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1768">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExpansionFilesAvailability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1769">Mēs iespējojam Android pakotņu komplektu (APK) paplašināšanas failus mobilajai Office lietojumprogrammai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1769">We are enabling Android Package Kit (APK) expansion files for the Office mobile app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1770">APK paplašināšanas faili ir papildu resursu faili, kurus Android lietojumprogrammu izstrādātāji var publicēt kopā ar savu lietojumprogrammu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1770">APK Expansion files are supplementary resource files that Android app developers can publish along with their app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1771">Lai noteiktu paplašināšanas failu uzticamību, mēs reģistrējam karodziņu, kas norāda uz to, vai paplašināšanas faili ir vai nav pieejami katrā sāknēšanas reizē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1771">To understand the reliability of the expansion files, we log a flag indicating whether expansion files are available or not at every boot.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1772">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1772">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1773">**Data_ExpansionFilesAvailable** — Būla karodziņš, kas norāda vai APK izplešanās faili ir pieejami ierīcē lietojumprogrammas sāknēšanas brīdī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1773">**Data_ExpansionFilesAvailable** - A Boolean flag that indicates whether APK Expansion files are available on the device at the time of app boot.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidearlytelemetryexpansionfilesdownloader"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1774">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExpansionFilesDownloader</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1774">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExpansionFilesDownloader</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1775">Mēs iespējojam Android pakotņu komplektu (APK) paplašināšanas failus mobilajai Office lietojumprogrammai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1775">We are enabling Android Package Kit (APK) expansion files for the Office mobile app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1776">APK paplašināšanas faili ir papildu resursu faili, kurus Android lietojumprogrammu izstrādātāji var publicēt kopā ar savu lietojumprogrammu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1776">APK Expansion files are supplementary resource files, that Android app developers can publish along with their app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1777">Lai izprastu mūsu paplašināšanas faila lejupielādes mehānisma uzticamību, mēs reģistrējam karodziņu, kurš norāda, vai mēs spējam veiksmīgi lejupielādēt paplašināšanas failus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1777">To understand the reliability of our expansion file download mechanism, we are logging a flag indicating whether we are successfully able to download expansion files.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1778">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1778">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1779">**Data_DownloadSuccess** — Būla karodziņš, kas norāda, vai APK paplašināšanas failu lejupielāde ir veiksmīga katru reizi, kad mēģinām veikt lejupielādi lietojumprogrammas sāknēšanas laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1779">**Data_DownloadSuccess** - A Boolean flag that indicates whether APK Expansion files download is successful, whenever we attempt a download during app boot.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeandroidintuneintunecompliancerequest"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1780">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceRequest</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1780">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceRequest</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1781">Šis notikums tiek apkopots Office lietojumprogrammām, kas darbojas ar Android, tai skaitā Office mobilajām ierīcēm, Word, Excel, PowerPoint un OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1781">This event is collected for Office applications running on Android, including Office mobile, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and OneNote.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1782">Šis notikums norāda uz mēģinājumu pierakstīties Intune licencētā organizācijas kontā, kuram organizācijas administrators ir konfigurējis politiku piekļuvei lietojumprogrammai ar nosacījumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1782">The event indicates an attempt to sign-in to an Intune licensed organization account where the organization administrator has configured policy to enforce app conditional access.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1783">To izmanto, lai noteiktu gala lietotāju skaitu, kas mēģina izmantot lietojumprogrammas šajā politikas konfigurācijā, un šo notikumu apvieno ar citu notikumu, Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceStatus, lai pārliecinātos par to, ka konfigurētā politika tiek ievērota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1783">It is used to understand the number of end users who are attempting to use apps under this policy configuration, and is combined with another event, Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceStatus, to ensure the configured policy is enforced.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1784">Datu lauki netiek apkopoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1784">No data fields are collected.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidintuneintunecompliancestatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1785">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceStatus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1785">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceStatus</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1786">Šis notikums tiek apkopots Office lietojumprogrammām, kas darbojas ar Android, tai skaitā Office mobilajām ierīcēm, Word, Excel, PowerPoint un OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1786">This event is collected for Office applications running on Android, including Office mobile, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and OneNote.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1787">Šis notikums norāda uz mēģinājumu pierakstīties Intune licencētā organizācijas kontā, kuram organizācijas administrators ir konfigurējis politiku piekļuvei lietojumprogrammai ar nosacījumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1787">The event indicates an attempt to sign-in to an Intune licensed organization account where the organization administrator has configured policy to enforce app conditional access.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1788">Šis notikums norāda uz lietojumprogrammas, kurā lietotājs ir pierakstījies, atbilstības statusu un tiek izmantots, lai izmeklētu kļūmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1788">This event indicates the compliance status of the application to which the user has signed-in and is used to investigate failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1789">Tas tiek apvienots ar citu notikumu, Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceRequest, lai nodrošinātu konfigurētās politikas ievērošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1789">It is combined with another event, Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceRequest, to ensure the configured policy is enforced.</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1790">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1790">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1791">**Data_ComplianceStatus** — norāda uz lietojumprogrammas atbilstības status pierakstīšanās laikā, izmantojot izdošanās vai kļūmes kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1791">**Data_ComplianceStatus** - Indicates the compliance status of the application during sign-in with a success or failure error code.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1792">-1 – Nezināma kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1792">-1 – Unknown error</span></span>
  -    <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1793">0 – lietojumprogramma atbilst organizācijas politikām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1793">0 – The application is compliant with the organization policies</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1794">1 – lietojumprogramma neatbilst organizācijas politikām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1794">1 – The application is not compliant with the organization policies</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1795">2 — ar pakalpojumu saistītas kļūmes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1795">2 – Service related failures</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1796">3 — ar tīklu saistītas kļūmes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1796">3 – Network related failures</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1797">4 — lietojumprogrammai neizdevās izgūt autentifikācijas marķieri</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1797">4 – Application failed to retrieve authentication token</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1798">5 — atbilde no pakalpojuma vēl nav saņemta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1798">5 – The response has not been yet received from the service</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1799">6 — ir jāinstalē uzņēmuma portāla lietojumprogramma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1799">6 – The company portal application needs to be installed</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidodwxpssotelemetry"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1800">Office.Android.ODWXPSSO.Telemetry</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1800">Office.Android.ODWXPSSO.Telemetry</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1801">Šis notikums palīdz izprast, ar kuru citu Microsoft lietojumprogrammu ierīcē mūsu lietojumprogramma saņēma kluso pierakstīšanos, no kura ieejas punkta un tā tālāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1801">This event helps in understanding with which other Microsoft app in the device, our app got silent single sign on, from which entry point and so on.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1802">Palīdz izprast klusās pierakstīšanās kļūmes iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1802">Also helps in understanding the failure reason for not getting silent single sign on.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1803">Mēs saņemam plašāku ieskatu par to, no kuras Microsoft lietojumprogramma ierīcē mēs saņemam vienotu pierakstīšanās pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1803">We get better insights like from which Microsoft app in the device, we are getting single sign on experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1804">Rīkoties reaģējot uz kļūmēm, kad vienotā pierakstīšanās nedarbojas, kā paredzēts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1804">Act upon failures, where single sign on is not working as expected.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1805">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1805">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1806">**AccountType** — norāda konta veidu, ar kuru notiek vienotā pierakstīšanās, piemēram, personiskais Microsoft konts vai darba konts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1806">**AccountType** - Indicates the account type with which single sign on is happening, like personal Microsoft account or work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1807">**EntryPoint** — norāda ieejas punktu lietojumprogrammā, no kura tika uzsākts vienotās pierakstīšanās mēģinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1807">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where single sign on attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1808">**ErrorCode** — norāda vienotās pierakstīšanās mēģinājuma kļūdas kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1808">**ErrorCode** - Indicates the error code of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1809">**ErrorDescription** — norāda vienotās pierakstīšanās mēģinājuma kļūdas ziņojumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1809">**ErrorDescription** - Indicates the error message of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1810">**HResult**— norāda vienotās pierakstīšanās mēģinājuma rezultāta statusa kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1810">**HResult** - Indicates result status code of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1811">**ProviderPackageId** — cita Microsoft lietojumprogramma ierīcē, no kuras notiek vienotā pierakstīšanās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1811">**ProviderPackageId** - Other Microsoft app in the device from which single sign on is happening.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidphonenumbersignins"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1812">Office.Android.PhoneNumberSignIns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1812">Office.Android.PhoneNumberSignIns</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1813">Šis notikums palīdz saprast, vai lietotājs ir pierakstījies vai pierakstījies ar tālruņa numuru saistītu kontu, vai ar personisko e-astu saistītu Microsoft kontu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1813">This event helps in understanding if user signed in or signed up with phone number-based account or email based personal Microsoft account.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1814">Šis notikums palīdz noteikt lietotāju pierakstīšanos vai reģistrāciju ar mobilo tālruņa numuru saistītu personisko Microsoft kontu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1814">This event helps in knowing count of users signing in or signing up with phone number based personal Microsoft account.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1815">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1815">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1816">**EntryPoint** — norāda ieejas punktu lietojumprogrammā, no kura tika uzsākts pierakstīšanās mēģinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1816">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where sign-in attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1817">**IsEmailMissing** — vai konta profila informācijā trūkst e-pasta adreses?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1817">**IsEmailMissing** - Is email missing in the account profile information?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1818">**IsPhoneNumberMissing** — vai konta profila informācijā trūkst tālruņa numura?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1818">**IsPhoneNumberMissing** - Is phone number missing in the account profile information?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1819">**UserDecision** — norāda lietotāja veikto izvēli, piemēram, pierakstīšanās vai reģistrācija, vai pierakstīties vēlāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1819">**UserDecision** - Indicates the choice made by user like sign-in or sign-up or sign in later.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidusersignindecision"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1820">Office.Android.UserSignInDecision</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1820">Office.Android.UserSignInDecision</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1821">Šis notikums palīdz saprast, kura posmā lietotājs pārtrauc pierakstīšanās plūsmu, kāpēc pierakstīšanās neizdodas, cik daudz lietotājiem izdodas veiksmīgi pierakstīties no kura lietojumprogrammas ieejas punkta un tā tālāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1821">This event helps in understanding at which stage user is dropping in sign in flow, why sign in is failing, how many users are getting signed in successfully from which entry point in the app and so on.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1822">Šis pasākums palīdz ar pierakstīšanās piltuves datiem, kas palīdz saprast, kurā posmā rodas kļūmes lielākam lietotāju skaitam un tā tālāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1822">This event helps with sign-in funnel data, which helps in understand at which stage users are getting dropped more and so on.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1823">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1823">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1824">**AccountType** — norāda konta veidu, ar kuru notiek pierakstīšanās mēģinājums, piemēram, personiskais konts vai darba konts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1824">**AccountType** - Indicates the account type with which sign-in is attempted like personal account or work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1825">**AfterLicensingState** — norāda lietojumprogrammas licencēšanas statusu pēc pierakstīšanās pabeigšanas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1825">**AfterLicensingState** - Indicates the app licensing state after sign-in completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1826">**AllowedEditsWithoutSignIn** — norāda bezmaksas rediģējumu skaitu pirms pierakstīšanās mēģinājuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1826">**AllowedEditsWithoutSignIn** - Indicates how many free edits have lapsed before sign-in was attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1827">**BeforeLicensingState** — norāda lietojumprogrammas licencēšanas statusu pirms pierakstīšanās mēģinājuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1827">**BeforeLicensingState** - Indicates the app licensing state before sign-in attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1828">**CompletionState** — norāda pierakstīšanās pabeigšanas posmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1828">**CompletionState** - Indicates the stage of sign-in completion.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1829">**EntryPoint** — norāda ieejas punktu lietojumprogrammā, no kura tika uzsākts pierakstīšanās mēģinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1829">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where sign-in attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1830">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpAttemptCount** — norāda uz paātrinātās pierakstīšanās mēģinājumu skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1830">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpAttemptCount** - Indicates the count of accelerated sign-ups attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1831">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpQuitCount** — norāda uz atcelto paātrinātās pierakstīšanās mēģinājumu skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1831">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpQuitCount** - Indicates the count of accelerated sign-ups canceled.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1832">**HResult** — norāda pierakstīšanās darbības rezultāta statusa kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1832">**HResult** - Indicates result status code of the sign-in operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1833">**IsPhoneOnlyAuthFeatureEnabled** — vai pierakstīšanās ar tālruņa numuru ir atļauta?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1833">**IsPhoneOnlyAuthFeatureEnabled** - Is phone number-based sign-in allowed or not?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1834">**LicenseActivationHResult** — norāda licences aktivizēšanas mēģinājuma statusa kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1834">**LicenseActivationHResult** - Indicates the status code of license activation attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1835">**LicenseActivationMessageCode** — norāda licencēšanas pakalpojuma ziņojuma kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1835">**LicenseActivationMessageCode** - Indicates the message code from licensing service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1836">**NoFreeEditsTreatmentValue** — vai bezmaksas rediģēšana ir atļauta?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1836">**NoFreeEditsTreatmentValue** - Is free edits allowed or not?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1837">**SignUpAttemptCount** — norāda uz pierakstīšanās mēģinājumu skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1837">**SignUpAttemptCount** - Indicates the count of sign-ups attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1838">**StartMode** — norāda režīmu, kurā tika sākts pierakstīšanās mēģinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1838">**StartMode** - Indicates the mode in which sign-in attempt was started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1839">**UserDecision** — norāda lietotāja veikto izvēli, piemēram, pierakstīšanās vai reģistrācija, vai pierakstīties vēlāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1839">**UserDecision** - Indicates the choice made by user like sign-in or sign-up or sign in later.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompatagentupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1840">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1840">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentUpload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1841">Tiek ģenerēts klienta palaišanas laikā, ja gala lietotājs ir iespējojis Office telemetrijas informācijas paneli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1841">Generated on client startup when end user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1842">Apkopo informāciju par to, kad Office telemetrijas aģents augšupielādē datus koplietošanas mapē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1842">It collects information on when the Office Telemetry Agent has uploaded data to the share folder.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1843">Šī notikuma primārais izmantošanas veids ir uzraudzīt Office telemetrijas aģenta stāvokli, bet sekundārais izmantošanas veids ir noteikt Office telemetrijas informācijas paneļa izmantošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1843">The primary use of this event is to monitor the health of the Office Telemetry agent and the secondary use of the event is to estimate usage of the Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1844">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1844">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1845">**UploadTime** — Telemetrijas aģenta pēdējās veiksmīgās augšupielādes laikspiedols.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1845">**UploadTime** - the timestamp of the last successful upload performed by the Telemetry Agent.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompatagentscanandupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1846">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentScanAndUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1846">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentScanAndUpload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1847">Tiek apkopots tikai tad, ja lietotājs ir iespējojis Office telemetrijas informācijas paneli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1847">Only collected when end user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1848"> Tas apkopo informāciju par to, kad tiek izpildīts Office telemetrijas aģents.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1848"> It collects information on when the Office Telemetry Agent is executed.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1849"> Tiek apkopots tikai tad, ja ir iespējots Office telemetrijas informācijas panelis, un tiek izmantots, lai noteiktu Office telemetrijas aģenta darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1849">  This is only collected when Office Telemetry Dashboard is enabled and is used to determine the health of Office Telemetry agent.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1850">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1850">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1851">**Data.AgentExit** — laikspiedols, kas apzīmē sekmīgu telemetrijas aģenta iziešanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1851">**Data.AgentExit** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent exits successfully</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1852">**Data.AgentScan** — laikspiedols, kas apzīmē sekmīgu telemetrijas aģenta pabeigtu skenēšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1852">**Data.AgentScan** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent completed a scan successfully</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1853">**Data.AgentUpload** — laikspiedols, kas apzīmē sekmīgu telemetrijas aģenta pabeigtu augšupielādi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1853">**Data.AgentUpload** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent completes the upload successfully</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompattelemetrydashboardresiliencycrashlog"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1854">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.TelemetryDashboardResiliencyCrashLog</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1854">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.TelemetryDashboardResiliencyCrashLog</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1855">Tiek apkopts tikai tad, ja lietotājs (parasti administrators) ir iespējojis Office telemetrijas informācijas paneli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1855">Only collected when Office Telemetry Dashboard has been enabled by end user (most likely an admin).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1856">Tas apkopo Office pievienojumprogrammu un dokumentu avāriju gadījumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1856">It collects the occurrence of Office Add-ins and documents crashes.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1857"> Tas tiek apkopots tikai tad, ja lietotājs ir iespējojis Office telemetrijas informācijas paneli, un tiek izmantots, lai noteiktu, vai ir palielinājies pievienojumprogrammu vai dokumentu avārijas gadījumu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1857"> This is only collected when user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard and is used to determine if there is an increased occurrence of add-in or document crashes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1858">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1858">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1859">**Data.CollectionTime** — laikspiedols, kas apzīmē reģistrētu avārijas notikumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1859">**Data.CollectionTime** - Timestamp of when a crash event was logged</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappdocsappdocsdocumentoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1860">Office.AppDocs.AppDocs.DocumentOperation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1860">Office.AppDocs.AppDocs.DocumentOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1861">Šis notikums tiek apkopots Office programmām, kas darbojas Android, iOS, Universal vai Windows platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1861">This event is collected for Office applications running on Android, iOS, Universal or Windows platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1862">Notikums ieraksta brīdi, kad notiek faila darbība (izveidošana/atvēršana/saglabāšana/eksportēšana/u.c.), un šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai saprastu un noteiktu prioritāti lietotāju pieredzēm, balstoties uz informāciju par faila darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1862">The event records when a file operation (create/open/save/export/etc.) takes place and it is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on the file operation information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1863">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1863">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1864">**Data_AppIdForReportEndBeforeAppKnown** – programmas ID, kad tas nav zināms pirms darbību izsauca atskaites beigas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1864">**Data_AppIdForReportEndBeforeAppKnown** – App ID when not known before report end called on the operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1865">**Data_CanContinueFromOnBeforeOperationBegins** — stāvoklis CanContinue tiek izsaukts sākuma apdarinātājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1865">**Data_CanContinueFromOnBeforeOperationBegins** – CanContinue state, before the begin handler is invoked.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1866">**Data_DetachedDuration** — notikuma atvienošanas procesa ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1866">**Data_DetachedDuration** – The duration of detach process of an event.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1867">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda uz faila piekļuves režīmu, piemēram, tikai lasāms, lasāms-rakstāms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1867">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, e.g. read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1868">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind**— uzskaitījums, kas norāda asinhronās plūsmas veidu, kas tika izmantota faila atvēršanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1868">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1869">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila dalīšanas algoritma veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1869">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – An enumeration indicating the type of chunking algorithm of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1870">**Data_Doc_EdpState** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila uzņēmuma datu aizsardzības statusu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1870">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – An enumeration indicating the enterprise data protection state of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1871">**Data_Doc_Ext** — faila paplašinājuma pirmās 4 rakstzīmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1871">**Data_Doc_Ext** – The first 4 characters of the file extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1872">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** — faila servera resursdatora nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1872">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1873">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē servera resursdatora nosaukumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1873">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – A GUID that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1874">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId —** tādas lietotāja identitātes vienvirziena jaukšana, kas tiek izmantota atvēršanā..</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1874">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open..</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1875">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda detalizēto faila atvēršanas darbības scenārija veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1875">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – An enumeration indicating the detailed scenario type of a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1876">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila atvēršanas darbības ievadizvades karodziņus, piemēram, vai fails ir kešots.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1876">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – An enumeration indicating the IO flags of a file open operation, e.g. if the file is cached or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1877">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** — vai failam ir iespējota sadarbība mākonī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1877">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** – Whether or not the cloud collaboration is enabled for the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1878">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** — vai fails tika atvērts ar inkrementālo atvēršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1878">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – Whether or not the file was opened via incremental open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1879">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** — vai fails atbalsta Office sadarbības pakalpojumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1879">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – Whether or not a file supports Office Collaboration Service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1880">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** — vai fails tiek atvērts no bezsaistes kešatmiņas kopijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1880">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – Whether or not a file is opened from an offline cached copy.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1881">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** — vai fails tika iepriekš ielādēts pirms atvēršanas darbības.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1881">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** – Whether or not the file was prefetched before open operation happened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1882">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** — vai mākonī esošajam failam ir lokālā versija un, vai tā ir sinhronizēta ar serveri.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1882">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – Whether or not a cloud file exists locally and is synchronized with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1883">**Data_Doc_Location** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda uz faila atrašanās vietu, piemēram, atrodas lokāli vai mākonī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1883">**Data_Doc_Location** – An enumeration indicating where the file is located, e.g. locally or in cloud.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1884">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila tikai lasīšanas iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1884">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – An enumeration indicating the read only reason of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1885">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē faila servera resursa ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1885">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** – A GUID that uniquely identifies server resource id of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1886">**Data_Doc_RtcType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila izmantotā reāllaika kanāla (RTC) veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1886">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – An enumeration indicating type of real-time channel (RTC) used by the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1887">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē servera dokumenta ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1887">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** – A GUID that uniquely identifies server document ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1888">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda mākoņa faila servera protokolu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1888">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – An enumeration indicating the server protocol of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1889">**Data_Doc_ServerType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda mākoņa faila servera veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1889">**Data_Doc_ServerType** – An enumeration indicating the server type of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1890">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda mākoņa faila servera versiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1890">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – An enumeration indicating the server version of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1891">**Data_Doc_SessionId** — vesels skaitlis, kas pieaug par 1 ar katru faila atvēršanas darbību sesijas laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1891">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – An integer which is incremented by 1 for each file open operation in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1892">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** — virkne, kas tiek izmantota, lai savstarpēji saistītu klienta un servera žurnālus; parasti tas ir kāds ID veids.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1892">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – A string used to correlate client-side and server-side logs, typically it is a kind of ID.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1924">Šis notikums tiek apkopots Office programmām, kas darbojas Android, iOS, Universal vai Windows platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1924">This event is collected for Office applications running on Android, iOS, Universal or Windows platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1925">Notikums ieraksta, kad faila atvēršanas darbība notiek no ceļa, kas tika sniegts jaunāko izmantoto sarakstā, un šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāju pieredzes kļūdām, balstoties uz faila atvēršanas darbības informāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1925">The event records when a file open operation takes place from the path provided in the most recently used list and is used to understand and prioritize user-experience errors based on file open operation information.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1930">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda uz faila piekļuves režīmu, piemēram, tikai lasāms, lasāms-rakstāms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1930">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, e.g. read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1935">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** — faila servera resursdatora nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1935">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1936">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē servera resursdatora nosaukumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1936">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – A GUID that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsappdocsoperationopenfrommrubyurl"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1981">Office.Docs.AppDocs.OperationOpenFromMruByUrl</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1981">Office.Docs.AppDocs.OperationOpenFromMruByUrl</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1982">Šis notikums tiek apkopots Office programmām, kas darbojas Android, iOS, Universal vai Windows platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1982">This event is collected for Office applications running on Android, iOS, Universal or Windows platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1983">Notikums ieraksta, kad faila atvēršanas darbība notiek no URL, kas tika sniegts jaunāko izmantoto sarakstā, un šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāju pieredzē, balstoties uz faila atvēršanas darbības informāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1983">The event records when a file open operation takes place from the URL provided in the most recently used list and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-1988">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda uz faila piekļuves režīmu, piemēram, tikai lasāms, lasāms-rakstāms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-1988">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, e.g. read only, read write.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsappdocsoperationopenfromurl"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2213">Office.Docs.AppDocs.OperationOpenFromUrl</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2213">Office.Docs.AppDocs.OperationOpenFromUrl</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2214">Šis notikums tiek apkopots Office programmām, kas darbojas Android, iOS, Universal vai Windows platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2214">This event is collected for Office applications running on Android, iOS, Universal or Windows platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2215">Notikums ieraksta brīdi, kad notiek faila atvēršanas no URL darbība, un šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai saprastu un noteiktu prioritāti lietotāju pieredzēm, balstoties uz informāciju par faila atvēršanu. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2215">The event records when a file open operation takes place from a URL and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2216">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2216">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2217">**Data_AppIdForReportEndBeforeAppKnown** – programmas ID, kad tas nav zināms pirms darbību izsauca atskaites beigas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2217">**Data_AppIdForReportEndBeforeAppKnown** – App ID when not known before report end called on the operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2218">**Data_CanContinueFromOnBeforeOperationBegins** — stāvoklis CanContinue tiek izsaukts sākuma apdarinātājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2218">**Data_CanContinueFromOnBeforeOperationBegins** – CanContinue state, before the begin handler is invoked.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2219">**Data_DetachedDuration** — notikuma atvienošanas procesa ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2219">**Data_DetachedDuration** – The duration of detach process of an event.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2220">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda uz faila piekļuves režīmu, piemēram, tikai lasāms, lasāms-rakstāms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2220">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, e.g. read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2221">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind**— uzskaitījums, kas norāda asinhronās plūsmas veidu, kas tika izmantota faila atvēršanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2221">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2222">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila dalīšanas algoritma veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2222">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – An enumeration indicating the type of chunking algorithm of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2225">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** — faila servera resursdatora nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2225">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2226">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē servera resursdatora nosaukumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2226">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – A GUID that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsappledocsuxiossaveasthroughfilemenu"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2344">Office.Docs.Apple.DocsUXiOSSaveAsThroughFileMenu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2344">Office.Docs.Apple.DocsUXiOSSaveAsThroughFileMenu</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2345">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2345">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2346">Pasākumu ieraksti, veicot darbību "Saglabāt kā" un tiek izmantoti, lai izprastu un noteiktu lietotāja pieredzes prioritāti, pamatojoties uz failu darbības informāciju, piemēram, atrašanās vietas kategorijām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2346">The event records when a "Save as" operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file operation information such as location categories.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2347">Darbība "Saglabāt kā" tiek veikta katru reizi, kad lietotājs izveido jaunu failu un saglabā to pirmo reizi vai saglabā esošā faila kopiju jaunā atrašanās vietā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2347">A "Save as" operation occurs whenever a user creates a new file and saves it for the first time or saves a copy of an existing file to a new location.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2348">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2348">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2349">**Data_OriginServiceType** — sākotnējās faila atrašanās vietas abstrakta kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt. un kas nav faila faktiskā atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2349">**Data_OriginServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the original location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2350">**Data_ServiceType** — abstrakta jaunās atrašanās vietas kategorizēšana pēc saglabāšanas, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt. un kas nav faila faktiskā atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2350">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the new location of a file after the save is completed like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2355">**Data_CharactersTyped** — skaitliska vērtība, kas norāda kopējo rakstzīmju skaitu "@" pieminēšanas tekstā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2355">**Data_CharactersTyped** - A numerical value that indicates the total number of characters typed in the "@" mention text.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2357">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2357">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2358">Šis notikums ieraksta, ja lietotājs izvēlas koplietot mākoņa dokumentu, izmantojot OneDrive koplietošanas pieredzi, un tas tiek izmantots, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz dokumentu koplietošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2358">This event records when a user chooses to share a cloud document using the OneDrive sharing experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2360">**Data_ShareType** — stingri kodēta virkne, kas norāda, kāda veida kopīgošanas darbība ir pabeigta, tostarp, bet ne tikai, "Kopēt saiti", "Citas programmas", "Teams".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2360">**Data_ShareType** - A hardcoded string that indicates what kind of share operation was completed including but not limited to "Copy Link", "More apps", "Teams".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2361">**Data_ShareWebViewMode** — stingri kodēta virkne, kas norāda, kāda veida kopīgošana bija aktīva, kad kopīgošana bija pabeigta, ieskaitot ne tikai "ManageAccess", "AtMentions", "Share".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2361">**Data_ShareWebViewMode** - A hardcoded string that indicates what kind of share mode was active when the share was completed including but not limited to "ManageAccess", "AtMentions", "Share".</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2366">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2366">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2367">**Data_CoauthorCount** — skaitliska vērtība, kas apzīmē kopējo personu skaitu, kuras pašlaik rediģē to pašu dokumentu, ko lietotājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2367">**Data_CoauthorCount** - A numerical value that represents the total number of people who are currently editing the same document as the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2374">**Data_CoauthorsJoined** — līdzautoru skaits, kas pameta dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2374">**Data_CoauthorsLeft** - The number of co-authors that left the document.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuidocstagedocstagecreatenewfromtemplate"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2378">Office.DocsUI.DocStage.DocStageCreateNewFromTemplate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2378">Office.DocsUI.DocStage.DocStageCreateNewFromTemplate</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2379">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2379">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2380">Notikums ieraksta, kad tiek izveidots jauns fails, no darbības "Jauns no veidnes", un to izmanto, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzei, pamatojoties uz dokumentu izveides informāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2380">The event records when a new file is created from the "New from template" experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on document creation information.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2383">**Data_InSearch** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, vai fails tika izveidots, kad lietotājs meklēja veidni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2383">**Data_InSearch** - A Boolean that indicates whether the file was created when the user was searching for a template.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2384">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, ja cilne Sākums pašlaik ir pieejama lietotājam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2384">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the Home tab is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2385">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, ja pieredze "Ieteicams" pašlaik ir pieejama lietotājam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2385">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the "Recommended" experience is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2386">**Data_TemplateIndex** — veidnes faila skaitliskais indekss, kas tiek rādīts vizuāli lietotājam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2386">**Data_TemplateIndex** - The numerical index of the template file as it is displayed visually to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2387">**Data_TemplateType** — klasifikācija, kas palīdz atšķirt veidnes tipu, piemēram, bet ne tikai "Tiešsaistes" veidnes, "Tiešsaistes meklēšanas" veidnes, "Lokālās" veidnes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2387">**Data_TemplateType** - A classification to help distinguish the type of template like, but not limited to, "Online" templates, "Online search" templates, "Local" templates.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuifileoperationsdocsuifileopenmacrequired"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2393">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.DocsUIFileOpenMacRequired</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2393">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.DocsUIFileOpenMacRequired</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2394">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2394">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2395">Notikums ieraksta, kad notiek failu atvēršanas darbība, un tiek izmantots, lai izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz failu atvēršanas informāciju, piemēram, atrašanās vietas kategorijas "Pakalpojuma tips" un paplašinājuma pirmās četras rakstzīmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2395">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories "ServiceType" and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2396">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2396">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2397">**Data_Ext** — faila paplašinājums attiecas tikai uz pirmajiem četriem paplašinājuma simboliem vai mazāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2397">**Data_Ext** - The file extension limited to the first four characters of the extension or less.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2398">**Data_ServiceType** — faila atrašanās vietas abstrakta kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2398">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuifileoperationsopendocumentmeasurements"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2399">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenDocumentMeasurements</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2399">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenDocumentMeasurements</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2400">Šis notikums tiek apkopots Office lietojumprogrammām, kas darbojas iOS platformā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2400">This event is collected for Office applications running under iOS platform.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2401">Notikuma ieraksti brīdī, kad notiek faila atvēršanas darbība, tiek izmantoti, lai saprastu un noteiktu prioritāti lietotāju pieredzēm, balstoties uz informāciju par faila atvēršanu, it īpaši veiktspējas informāciju. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2401">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information, especially performance information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2402">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2402">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2403">**Data_AppDuration** — lietojumprogrammā, kas veic faila atvēršanu, pavadītais laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2403">**Data_AppDuration** - The duration spent in application processing during a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2404">**Data_BootDuration** — faila atvēršanas palaišanas procesa ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2404">**Data_BootDuration** - The duration of boot process of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2405">**Data_ClickOrigin** — virkne, kas norāda uz saites daļas izcelsmi brīdī, kad lietotājs noklikšķināja uz saites iOS Outlook, lai atvērtu failu Office lietojumprogrammā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2405">**Data_ClickOrigin** - A string indicating which part the link was from when user clicked a link in iOS Outlook to open a file in Office app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2406">**Data_ClickTime** — Unix diskretizācijas laiks, kad lietotājs noklikšķināja uz saites iOS Outlook, lai atvērtu failu Office lietojumprogrammā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2406">**Data_ClickTime** - The Unix epoch time when the user clicked a link in iOS Outlook to open the file in Office app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2407">**Data_ClosePreviouslyOpenedMarkers**— virknes vērtība, kas uzskaita ilgumu starp atsevišķu funkciju izsaukumiem formātā ar funkcijas ID un ilgumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2407">**Data_ClosePreviouslyOpenedMarkers** – A string value logging the time duration between some function calls, in a format with function id and duration.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2408">**Data_DetachedDuration** — notikuma atvienošanas procesa ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2408">**Data_DetachedDuration** - The duration of detach process of an event.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2409">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda uz faila piekļuves režīmu, piemēram, tikai lasāms, lasāms-rakstāms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2409">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, e.g. read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2410">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind**— uzskaitījums, kas norāda asinhronās plūsmas veidu, kas tika izmantota faila atvēršanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2410">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** - An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2411">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila dalīšanas algoritma veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2411">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - An enumeration indicating the type of chunking algorithm of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2413">**Data_Doc_Ext** — faila paplašinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2413">**Data_Doc_Ext** - File extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2414">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** — faila servera resursdatora nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2414">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2415">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē servera resursdatora nosaukumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2415">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2416">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē identitāti, kas tika izmantota, lai atvērtu failu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2416">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the identity used to open a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2417">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda detalizēto faila atvēršanas darbības scenārija veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2417">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - An enumeration indicating the detailed scenario type of a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2418">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila atvēršanas darbības ievadizvades karodziņus, piemēram, vai fails ir kešots.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2418">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - An enumeration indicating the IO flags of a file open operation, e.g. if the file is cached or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2419">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** — vai failam ir iespējota sadarbība mākonī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2419">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** - Whether or not the cloud collaboration is enabled for the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2422">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** — vai fails tiek atvērts no bezsaistes kešatmiņas kopijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2422">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Whether or not a file is opened from an offline cached copy.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2424">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** — vai mākonī esošajam failam ir lokālā versija un, vai tā ir sinhronizēta ar serveri.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2424">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Whether or not a cloud file exists locally and is synchronized with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2425">**Data_Doc_Location** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda uz faila atrašanās vietu, piemēram, atrodas lokāli vai mākonī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2425">**Data_Doc_Location** - An enumeration indicating where the file is located, e.g. locally or in cloud.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2428">**Data_Doc_RtcType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda faila izmantotā reāllaika kanāla (RTC) veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2428">**Data_Doc_RtcType** - An enumeration indicating type of real-time channel (RTC) used by the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2429">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē servera dokumenta ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2429">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server document ID.</span></span>
