- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2431">**Data_Doc_ServerType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda mākoņa faila servera veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2431">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - An enumeration indicating the server type of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2432">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda mākoņa faila servera versiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2432">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - An enumeration indicating the server version of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2433">**Data_Doc_SessionId** — vesels skaitlis, kas pieaug par 1 ar katru faila atvēršanas darbību sesijas laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2433">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - An integer which is incremented by 1 for each file open operation in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2434">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** — virkne, kas tiek izmantota, lai savstarpēji saistītu klienta un servera žurnālus; parasti tas ir kāds ID veids.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2434">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - A string used to correlate client-side and server-side logs, typically it is a kind of ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2435">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** — dokumenta lielums baitos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2435">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - File size in bytes.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2436">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda īpašās rakstzīmes veidu faila URL adresē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2436">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - An enumeration indicating which kind of special character the file URL has.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2437">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** — GUID, kas unikāli identificē faila URL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2437">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the file URL.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2438">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** — norāda, vai fails tika atvērts inkrementāli, izmantojot iepriekš kešotus WRS datus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2438">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened incrementally using pre-cached WRS data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2439">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** — virkne, kas norāda, no kura pakalpojuma ir WOPI (tīmekļa lietojumprogrammas atvērtās platformas interfeisa protokols) fails.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2439">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - A string indicating which service a WOPI (Web Application Open Platform Interface Protocol) file is from.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2440">**Data_HWModel** — iPad vai iPhone ierīces virknes vērtību uzskaites modelis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2440">**Data_HWModel** – A string value logging the model of iPad or iPhone device.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2441">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** — virknes vērtība, kas uzskaita atsevišķu funkciju pieprasījumā pavadīto laiku formātā ar funkcijas birku un ilgumu, kas iekļauj apakšfunkciju pieprasījumu ilgumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2441">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which includes the duration of sub-function calls.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2442">**Data_InitializationReason** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda uz faila atvēršanas veidu, piemēram, no lietotāja interfeisa elementa vai citas lietojumprogrammas izsaukuma rezultātā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2442">**Data_InitializationReason** - An enumeration indicating how the file is opened, e.g. from which UI element or triggered by another app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2443">**Data_IsDocumentAlreadyOpen** — norāda, vai fails jau ir atvērts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2443">**Data_IsDocumentAlreadyOpen** – Whether or not the file is already open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2444">**Data_IsInterrupted** — norāda, vai faila atvēršanas darbību pārtrauca programmas pāreja uz darbību fonā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2444">**Data_IsInterrupted** – Whether or not the file open operation was interrupted by app transitioning to background.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2445">**Data_Measurements** — virknes vērtība, kas uzskaita atsevišķu funkciju pieprasījumā pavadīto laiku formātā ar funkcijas birku un ilgumu, kas neiekļauj apakšfunkciju pieprasījumu ilgumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2445">**Data_Measurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which excludes the duration of sub-function calls.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2446">**Data_OpenInPlace** — vai fails ir jākopē Office smilškastes konteinerā, pirms lietotājs var to atvērt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2446">**Data_OpenInPlace** - Whether or not a file must be copied to the Office's sandboxed container before user can open it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2447">**Data_OpenStartTime** — Unix diskretizācijas laiks, kad tika sākta faila atvēršana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2447">**Data_OpenStartTime** - The Unix epoch time when the file open started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2448">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** — faila atvēršanas renderēšanas ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2448">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** - The duration of rendering of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2449">**Data_SourceApplication** — virkne, kas norāda avota lietojumprogrammas komplekta ID, kad faila atvēršanu uzsāk cita lietojumprogramma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2449">**Data_SourceApplication** - A string indicating the bundle ID of the source application when a file open was triggered by another app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2450">**Data_StopwatchDuration** — laiks no notikuma sākuma līdz notikuma beigām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2450">**Data_StopwatchDuration** - The duration from beginning of the event to the end of the event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2451">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements**— virknes vērtība, kas uzskaita atsevišķu funkciju pieprasījumu ilgumu formātā ar funkcija birku, sākuma laikspiedolu un ilgumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2451">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag, start timestamp and duration.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuifileoperationsopenfilewithreason"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2452">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenFileWithReason</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2452">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenFileWithReason</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2453">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2453">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2454">Notikums ieraksta, kad notiek failu atvēršana, un tiek izmantots, lai izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz failu atvēršanas informāciju, piemēram, atrašanās vietas kategorijas "Pakalpojuma tips" un no kurienes lietotājs pieprasīja atvērt failu programmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2454">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories "ServiceType" and from where within Application the user requested to open a file.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2455">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2455">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2456">**Data_IsCandidateDropboxFile** — šī ir Būla vērtība, kas tiek reģistrēta, ja, pārbaudot faila ceļu, mūsuprāt, tas var būt no mapes, kas tiek sinhronizēta ar Dropbox.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2456">**Data_IsCandidateDropboxFile** - This is a Boolean value that is logged if by inspecting the path of the file we think it might be from a folder that is sync'd by Drop Box.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2457">**Data_IsSignedIn** — neatkarīgi no tā, vai tiek pierakstīts lietotājs, kad fails ir saglabāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2457">**Data_IsSignedIn** - Whether or not a user is signed in when the file is saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2458">**Data_OpenReason** — atvērtais iemesls ir skaitliska vērtība, kas norāda, no kurienes programmā lietotājs ir atvēris failu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2458">**Data_OpenReason** - The open reason is a numerical value that indicates from where within the application a user opened a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2459">**Data_ServiceType** — sākotnējās faila atrašanās vietas abstrakta kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., un kas nav faila faktiskā atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2459">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract numerical categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuifileoperationssavetourl"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2460">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.SaveToURL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2460">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.SaveToURL</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2461">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2461">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2462">Notikums ieraksta, kad notiek darbība "saglabāt kā", un tiek izmantots, lai izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz failu darbības informāciju, piemēram, atrašanās vietas kategorijas un paplašinājuma pirmās četras rakstzīmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2462">The event records when a "save as" operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file operation information such as location categories and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2463">Darbība "Saglabāt kā" tiek veikta katru reizi, kad lietotājs izveido jaunu failu un saglabā to pirmo reizi vai saglabā esošā faila kopiju jaunā atrašanās vietā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2463">A "save as" operation occurs whenever a user creates a new file and saves it for the first time or saves a copy of an existing file to a new location.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2464">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2464">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2465">**Data_FileExtension** — pirmās četras rakstzīmes jaunā faila paplašinājumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2465">**Data_FileExtension** - The first four characters of the new file's extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2466">**Data_IsNewFileCreation** — norāda, vai saglabāšanas darbība ir paredzēta jaunam failam vai esoša faila kopijai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2466">**Data_IsNewFileCreation** - Indicates if the save operation is for a new file or a copy of an existing file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2467">**Data_IsSignedIn** — neatkarīgi no tā, vai tiek pierakstīts lietotājs, kad fails ir saglabāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2467">**Data_IsSignedIn** - Whether or not a user is signed in when the file is saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2468">**Data_SaveErrorCode** — skaitliska vērtība, kas ir iestatīta, ja ir kļūda, kas palīdz noteikt kļūdas veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2468">**Data_SaveErrorCode** - A numerical value that is set if there is an error to help identify the kind of error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2469">**Data_SaveErrorDomain** — norāda tā SaveErrorCode domēnu, ko Apple SaveErrorCode domēns definē kā "patvaļīgas virknes, kas tiek izmantotas, lai diferencētu kodu grupas".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2469">**Data_SaveErrorDomain** - Specifies the domain of the SaveErrorCode as defined by Apple SaveErrorDomains "are arbitrary strings used to differentiate groups of codes".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2470">**Data_SaveLocation** — sākotnējās faila atrašanās vietas abstrakta kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., un kas nav faila faktiskā atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2470">**Data_SaveLocation** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2471">**Data_SaveOperationType** — skaitliska vērtība, ko definē Apple NSSaveOperationType vērtību grupa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2471">**Data_SaveOperationType** - A numerical value defined by Apple's NSSaveOperationType group of values.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguicloudupsellshown"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2472">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CloudUpsellShown</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2472">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CloudUpsellShown</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2473">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2473">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2474">Šis notikums ieraksta, kad lietotājs dodas caur dokumentu papildu pārdošanai uz mākoņa plūsmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2474">This event records when a user goes through the document upsell to cloud flow.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2475">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotājam, kas saistītas ar dokumentu vienlaicīgu koprediģēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2475">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2476">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2476">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2477">**Data_FileStyle** — skaitliska vērtība, kas norāda, kādā scenārijā papildu pārdošanas pieredze tika parādīta kā no automātiskās saglabāšanas slēdža vai kopīgošanas pogas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2477">**Data_FileStyle** - A numerical value that indicates from what scenario the upsell experience was shown like from an autosave toggle or a share button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2478">**Data_FileType** — pirmās četras rakstzīmes pašreizējā faila paplašinājumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2478">**Data_FileType** - The first four characters of the current file's extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2479">**Data_InDocStage** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai papildu pārdošanas pieredze tiek parādīta dokumentu galerijā vai dokumenta logā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2479">**Data_InDocStage** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience is shown from the Document Gallery or from within a document window.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2480">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai ir atvērts pašreizējais dokuments, kurā redzama papildu pārdošanas pieredze.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2480">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** - A Boolean that indicates if the current document for which the upsell experience is being shown is also open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2481">**Data_IsDraft** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai pašreizējais fails kaut kad ir saglabāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2481">**Data_IsDraft** - A Boolean that indicates if the current file has ever been saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2482">**Data_IsSheetModal** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai papildu pārdošanas pieredze tika prezentēta modāli vai nē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2482">**Data_IsSheetModal** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience was presented modally or not.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguicloudupsellupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2483">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CloudUpsellUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2483">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CloudUpsellUpload</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2484">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2484">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2485">Šis notikums ieraksta, kad lietotājs izvēlas augšupielādēt jaunu vai lokālo failu mākonī un šīs darbības rezultātu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2485">This event records when a user chooses to upload a new or local file to the cloud and the result of that operation.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2486">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotājam, kas saistītas ar dokumentu vienlaicīgu koprediģēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2486">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2487">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2487">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2488">**Data_FileStyle** — skaitliska vērtība, kas norāda, kādā scenārijā papildu pārdošanas pieredze tika parādīta kā no automātiskās saglabāšanas slēdža vai kopīgošanas pogas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2488">**Data_FileStyle** - A numerical value that indicates from what scenario the upsell experience was shown like an autosave toggle or a share button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2489">**Data_FileType** — pirmās četras rakstzīmes pašreizējā faila paplašinājumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2489">**Data_FileType** - The first four characters of the current file's extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2490">**Data_InDocStage** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai papildu pārdošanas pieredze tiek parādīta dokumentu galerijā vai dokumenta logā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2490">**Data_InDocStage** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience is shown from the Document Gallery or from within a document window.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2491">**Data_IsDefaultServiceLocation** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, vai atlasītā atrašanās vieta, kur augšupielādēt dokumentu, ir noklusējuma atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2491">**Data_IsDefaultServiceLocation** - A Boolean value that indicates if the selected location to upload the document to is the default location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2492">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai ir atvērts pašreizējais dokuments, kurā redzama papildu pārdošanas pieredze.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2492">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** - A Boolean that indicates if the current document for which the upsell experience is being shown is also open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2493">**Data_IsDraft** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai pašreizējais fails kaut kad ir saglabāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2493">**Data_IsDraft** - A Boolean that indicates if the current file has ever been saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2494">**Data_IsSheetModal** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai papildu pārdošanas pieredze tika prezentēta modāli vai nē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2494">**Data_IsSheetModal** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience was presented modally or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2495">**Data_LocationServiceType** — sākotnējās faila atrašanās vietas abstrakta kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., un kas nav faila faktiskā atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2495">**Data_LocationServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2496">**Data_UploadAction** — cietā kodētā virkne, kas norāda, vai augšupielāde bija pārvietošanas vai kopēšanas darbība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2496">**Data_UploadAction** - A hard coded string that indicates whether the upload was a move or a copy operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2497">**Data_UploadResult** — cieta kodēta virkne, kas norāda mēģinājuma rezultātu, tostarp, bet ne tikai, "Izdevās", "UserCancelledUpload" un "PreAuthFailed".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2497">**Data_UploadResult** - A hard coded string that indicates the result of the attempt to upload including but not limited to ''Success", "UserCancelledUpload", and "PreAuthFailed".</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguicopylinkoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2498">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CopyLinkOperation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2498">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CopyLinkOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2499">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2499">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2500">Šī notikums ieraksta, kad lietotājs izvēlas kopīgot dokumentu, ģenerējot saiti uz mākoņa dokumentu, un tiek izmantots, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz dokumentu koplietošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2500">This event records when a user chooses to share a document by generating a link to a cloud document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2501">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2501">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2502">**Data_ ServiceType** — abstrakta faila atrašanās vietas kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., nevis faktiskā faila atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2502">**Data_ ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2503">**Data_LinkType** — cietā kodētā virkne, kas apraksta uzaicināšanas darbības veidu, piemēram, "ViewOnly" un "ViewAndEdit".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2503">**Data_LinkType** - A hard coded string that describes the kind of invite operation performed like "ViewOnly" and "ViewAndEdit".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2504">**Data_ShareScenario** — cieti kodēts virknes apraksts, kur programmas lietotāja interfeisā fails tiek koplietots, ieskaitot, bet ne tikai "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2504">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard-coded string description of where within the application's user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguidocsuionedriveshare"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2505">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.DocsUIOneDriveShare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2505">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.DocsUIOneDriveShare</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2506">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2506">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2507">Šis notikums ieraksta, ja lietotājs izvēlas koplietot mākoņa dokumentu, izmantojot OneDrive koplietošanas pieredzi, un tas tiek izmantots, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz dokumentu koplietošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2507">This event records when a user chooses to share a cloud document using the OneDrive sharing experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2508">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2508">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2509">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareError** — Ja koplietošanas pieredze atklāj kļūdu, tā ir skaitliska vērtība, kas palīdz noteikt kļūmes iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2509">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareError** - If the sharing experience experiences an error this is a numerical value to help identify the reason for the failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2510">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareGrantAccessResult** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, ka vieglā koplietošanas darbība ir sekmīgi pabeigta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2510">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareGrantAccessResult** - A Boolean value that when true indicates that a lightweight sharing operation successfully completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2511">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareSuccessType** — ja kopīgošanas darbība ir veiksmīgi pabeigta, šī ir skaitliska vērtība, kas tiek lietota, lai noteiktu, kāda veida koplietošanas darbība tika pabeigta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2511">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareSuccessType** - When a share operation successfully completes this is a numerical value used to determine what kind of sharing operation was completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2512">**Data_WebViewInfoResult** — ja lietotāja interfeiss nav ielādēts, šī ir skaitliska vērtība, kas palīdz identificēt kļūmes iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2512">**Data_WebViewInfoResult** - If the user interface fails to load this is a numerical value to help identify the reason for the failure.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2513">**Data_WebViewLoadTimeInMs** — skaitliska vērtība, kas ieraksta, cik daudz laika ir nepieciešams, lai tīmekļa lietotāja interfeiss tiktu ielādēts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2513">**Data_WebViewLoadTimeInMs** - A numerical value that records the amount of time it took for the web user interface to load.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguiinvitepeople"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2514">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.InvitePeople</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2514">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.InvitePeople</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2515">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2515">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2516">Šis notikums ieraksta, ja lietotājs izvēlas uzaicināt lietotājus uz mākoņa dokumentu un tiek izmantots, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz dokumentu koplietošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2516">This event records when a user chooses to invite people to a cloud document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2517">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2517">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2518">**Data_ ServiceType** — abstrakta faila atrašanās vietas kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., nevis faktiskā faila atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2518">**Data_ ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2519">**Data_InviteeCount** — kopējais kontaktpersonu skaits, kas uzaicināti uz dokumentu vienā uzaicinājuma darbībā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2519">**Data_InviteeCount** - The total number of contacts invited to a document in one invite action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2520">**Data_LinkType** — cietā kodētā virkne, kas apraksta uzaicināšanas darbības veidu, piemēram, "ViewOnly" un "ViewAndEdit".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2520">**Data_LinkType** - A hard-coded string that describes the kind of invite operation performed like "ViewOnly" and "ViewAndEdit".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2521">**Data_MessageLength** — uzaicinājuma ziņojumā nosūtīto rakstzīmju kopējais skaitlisks skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2521">**Data_MessageLength** - A numerical count of the total number of characters sent in the invite message.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2522">**Data_ShareScenario** — cieti kodēts virknes apraksts, kur programmas lietotāja interfeisā fails tiek koplietots, ieskaitot, bet ne tikai "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2522">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard coded string description of where within the application's user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguisendacopyoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2523">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.SendACopyOperation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2523">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.SendACopyOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2524">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2524">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2525">Notikums ieraksta, kad lietotājs izvēlas sūtīt dokumenta kopiju, un tiek izmantots, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, pamatojoties uz dokumentu koplietošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2525">The event records when a user chooses to send a copy of a document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2526">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2526">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2527">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, ja cilne Sākums pašlaik ir pieejama lietotājam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2527">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the Home tab is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2528">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, ja pieredze "Ieteicams" pašlaik ir pieejama lietotājam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2528">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the "Recommended" experience is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2529">**Data_OperationType** — skaitliska vērtība, kas norāda, kāda veida kopijas nosūtīšanas darbība tiek veikta, piemēram, nosūtot kopiju e-pastā vai nosūtot kopiju, izmantojot Apple kopīgošanas vadību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2529">**Data_OperationType** - A numerical value to indicate what kind of send a copy operation is taking place like sending a copy in an email or sending a copy through Apple's share control.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2530">**Data_ ServiceType** — abstrakta faila atrašanās vietas kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., nevis faktiskā faila atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2530">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2531">**Data_ShareFileType** — cietais kodētais virknes apraksts par to, kāda tipa objektu koplieto, tostarp, bet ne tikai, "Dokuments", "PDF", "Attēls".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2531">**Data_ShareFileType** - A hard coded string description of what type of object is being shared including but not limited to, "Document", "PDF", "Picture".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2532">**Data_ShareScenario** — cieti kodēts virknes apraksts, kur programmas lietotāja interfeisā fails tiek koplietots, ieskaitot, bet ne tikai "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2532">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard coded string description of where within the application's user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2533">**Data_SharingService** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, vai fails tika izveidots, kad lietotājs meklēja veidni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2533">**Data_SharingService** - A Boolean that indicates whether the file was created when the user was searching for a template.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguiupsellshare"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2534">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.UpsellShare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2534">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.UpsellShare</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2535">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2535">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2536">Šis notikums ieraksta, kad lietotājs dodas caur dokumentu papildu pārdošanai uz mākoņa plūsmu, mēģinot kopīgot dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2536">This event records when a user goes through the document upsell to cloud flow when trying to share a document.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2537">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai labāk izprastu un noteiktu prioritātes lietotāja pieredzi, kas saistīta ar dokumentu pārvietošanu uz mākoņa vietām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2537">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2538">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2538">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2539">**Data_FileOperationResult** — skaitliska vērtība, kas norāda, vai operācija bija sekmīga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2539">**Data_FileOperationResult** - A numerical value to indicate whether the operation succeeded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2540">**Data_HostedFromDocStage** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai lietotājs izmanto papildu pārdošanu, lai izveidotu mākoņa plūsmu no DocStage pieredzes vai atvērta dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2540">**Data_HostedFromDocStage** - A Boolean to indicate if a user is going through the upsell to cloud flow from the DocStage experience or from an open document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2541">**Data_isLocalCopyOn** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai, ja izmantojat, izvēlējās saglabāt lokālu dokumentu, kas tiek augšupielādēts mākoņa atrašanās vietā, vai pārvietojat esošo dokumentu uz mākoņa atrašanās vietu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2541">**Data_isLocalCopyOn** - A Boolean to indicate if the use chose to keep a local copy of the document being uploaded to a cloud location or move the existing document to a cloud location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2542">**Data_NewFileType** — faila jaunas atrašanās vietas abstrakta kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., un kas nav faila faktiskā atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2542">**Data_NewFileType** - An abstract categorization of the location of the new location of the file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2543">**Data_OriginalFileType** — abstrakta faila atrašanās vietas kategorizēšana, piemēram, "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI" utt., nevis faktiskā faila atrašanās vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2543">**Data_OriginalFileType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2544">**Data_UploadButtonPressed** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai lietotājs ir izvēlējies augšupielādēt pašreizējo dokumentu mākoņa atrašanās vietā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2544">**Data_UploadButtonPressed** - A Boolean to indicate if the user chose to upload the current document to a cloud location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2545">**Data_UploadError** — skaitliska vērtība, kas norāda, kāda veida kļūda radās, ja augšupielādes darbība neizdodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2545">**Data_UploadError** - A numerical value that indicates the kind of error that occurred if an upload operation fails.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2546">**Data_UpsellAppearsFromDelegate** — Būla vērtība, kas norāda, vai skats ir redzams koplietošanas izvēlnē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2546">**Data_UpsellAppearsFromDelegate** - A Boolean value to indicate if the view was shown from the share menu.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2700">Seko, kad tiek parādīta aptaujas uzvedne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2700">Tracks when survey prompt is shown.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2701">Tiek izmantoti, lai novērtētu aptaujas uzvednes procesa darbspēju, kā arī, lai nodrošinātu, ka, lai analizētu klientu problēmas un veselību, darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2701">Used to assess the health of the survey prompt process as well as to ensure the signal used to analyze customer issues and health is working properly.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2702">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2702">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2703">**ExpirationTimeUTC** — datums/laiks, kad aptauja beigsies</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2703">**ExpirationTimeUTC** – date/time the survey will expire</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2704">**SurveyName** — parādītās aptaujas nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2704">**SurveyName** – name of survey shown</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2705">**SurveyId** — unikāla kampaņas instance</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2705">**SurveyId** – Unique instance of a campaign</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2706">**UniqueId** — ID, lai identificētu atsevišķas telemetrijas vienības</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2706">**UniqueId** – Id to identify the individual piece of telemetry</span></span>

#### <a name="officefileiocsiccachedfilecsisavefilebasic"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2832">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiSaveFileBasic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2832">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiSaveFileBasic</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2833">Ļauj uzzināt, vai fails ir veiksmīgi saglabāts no FIO līmeņa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2833">Allows us to know if a file was successfully saved from the FIO Layer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2834">Izmanto līdzekļu darbspējas veicināšanai un pārraudzībai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2834">Used for Feature Health and monitoring.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2835">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2835">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2836">**Activity.Group —** tags, kas ļauj grupēt pārraudzības notikumu kopu, lai pārvaldītu kopējos panākumus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2836">**Activity.Group -** tag that allows a set of monitoring events to be grouped to manage overall success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2837">**Activity.IsHVA —** karodziņš, kas norāda, ka šis notikums ir svarīgs lietotāja panākumiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2837">**Activity.IsHVA -** flag to indicate that event is critical to user success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2838">**Data.AsyncOpen —** karodziņš, kas norāda, ka dokuments tika atvērts ar saturu, kas ir pieejams pēc galvenā satura atvēršanas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2838">**Data.AsyncOpen -** flag to indicate that the document was opened with content that arrived after the main body was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2839">**Data.BaseDownloadTriggered —** izmaiņu izsekošanas diagnostika, kas norāda, ka tika pieprasīta dokumenta pamata versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2839">**Data.BaseDownloadTriggered -** Change tracking diagnostic indicating that the base version of the document was requested</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2840">**Data.BlockAutoUploadReasons —** iemeslu kodi bloķētajam augšupielādes statusam (piemēram, ir izslēgta automātiskā saglabāšana, dokuments ir pārejas režīmā)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2840">**Data.BlockAutoUploadReasons -** Reason codes for blocked upload state (e.g. Autosave is turned off, the document is transitioning)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2841">**Data.BlockUploadDueToFailedSaveAsOverExisting —** augšupielāde ir bloķēta, jo mēģinot vēlreiz tā tiktu pārtraukta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2841">**Data.BlockUploadDueToFailedSaveAsOverExisting -** Upload is blocked as it would fail if retried</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2842">**Data.CacheFileId —** izveido savienojumu ar Office dokumentu kešatmiņas telemetriju, lai iespējotu analīzi saistībā ar kešatmiņas problēmu ietekmi uz lietotāju pieredzi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2842">**Data.CacheFileId -** connects to Office Document Cache telemetry to enable impact analysis of cache issues on the user experience</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2843">**Data.ChartType —** novecojis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2843">**Data.ChartType -** Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2844">**Data.CoauthStatus —** reģistrē saglabāta dokumenta sadarbības statusu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2844">**Data.CoAuthStatus -** reports collaborative status of the document on Save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2845">**Data.CoauthUpdatesContext —** reģistrē kontekstu (sapludināšana/inkrementāla atvēršana)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2845">**Data.CoauthUpdatesContext -** reports context (Merge/Incremental Open)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2846">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload —** to servera apmeklējumu skaits, kas tiek izmantoti veiktspējas un tīkla problēmu novēršanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2846">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2847">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsUpload —** to servera apmeklējumu skaits, kas tiek izmantoti veiktspējas un tīkla problēmu novēršanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2847">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsUpload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2848">**Dati.CFREnabled** — norāda, ka sesijai ir iespējota CacheFileRuntime.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2848">**Data.CFREnabled** - Indicates that CacheFileRuntime is enabled for the session.</span></span>

#### <a name="officefindtimeappfailedtostart"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2979">Office.FindTime.AppFailedToStart</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2979">Office.FindTime.AppFailedToStart</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2980">Apkopo, ja programmu nevar palaist, jo startēšanas laikā radās neparedzēta kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2980">Collected when app fails to start due to an unexpected error during startup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2981">Izmantot, lai izsekotu izņēmumiem un avārijām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2981">Used to track exceptions & crashes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2982">Palīdz pārraudzīt un atkļūdot programmas darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2982">Helps monitor & debug app health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2983">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2983">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2984">**DateTime** — notikuma reģistrēšanas laikspiedols</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2984">**DateTime** - Timestamp of when the event is logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2985">**EventName** — reģistrētā notikuma nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2985">**EventName** - The name of the event being logged</span></span>

#### <a name="officefirstrunappleactivationresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2986">Office.FirstRun.Apple.ActivationResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2986">Office.FirstRun.Apple.ActivationResult</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2987">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2987">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2988">Pasākums tiek lietots, lai pārraudzītu mūsu programmas aktivizēšanas plūsmas darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2988">The event is used to monitor the health of our application activation flow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2989">Mēs apkopojam datus, lai noskaidrotu Office 365 abonementa aktivizēšanas rezultātus kopā ar plūsmu, kas tiek lietota aktivizācijai (Pirmā palaišanas pieredze, Programmas plūsma, Iegāde utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2989">We collect data to figure out the outcome of the Office 365 subscription activation along with the flow used to activate (First Run Experience, In-App-Flow, Purchase, etc.).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2990">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2990">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2991">**Data_ActivationStatusCollectionTime** — laikspiedols</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2991">**Data_ActivationStatusCollectionTime** – A timestamp</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2992">**Data_ActivationStatusError** — aktivizācijas kļūdas kods.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2992">**Data_ActivationStatusError** – An activation error code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2993">**Data_ActivationStatusFlowType** – skaitliska vērtība, kas norāda aktivizēšanas plūsmas tipu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2993">**Data_ActivationStatusFlowType** – A numeric value indicating the type of activation flow</span></span>

#### <a name="officefirstrunappleactivationstatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2994">Office.FirstRun.Apple.ActivationStatus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2994">Office.FirstRun.Apple.ActivationStatus</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2995">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2995">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2996">Mēs apkopojam datus, lai noskaidrotu Office 365 abonementa aktivizēšanas rezultātus kopā ar plūsmu, kas tiek lietota aktivizācijai (PPP, Programmas plūsma, Iegāde utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2996">The event is used to figure out the outcome of the Office 365 subscription activation along with the flow used to activate (FRE, InApp, Purchase, etc.).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-2997">Mēs apkopojam datus, kas satur aktivizācijas tipu, plūsmas tipu (Pirmā palaišanas plūsma/DocStage/Iegāde) un Office licencēšanas pakalpojuma ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-2997">We collect data containing the Activation type, flow type (FRE/DocStage/Purchase) and Office Licensing Service ID.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3092">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3092">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3093">Pasākums tiek lietots, lai pārraudzītu mūsu programmas iegādes plūsmas darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3093">The event is used to monitor the health of our application in-app purchase flow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3094">Mēs apkopojam datus, lai izsekotu to, kā notiek programmu atjaunošanai un ar to saistītām plūsmām un kļūdām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3094">We collect data to track the attempted In-App restorations and their associated flows and errors.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3101">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3101">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3102">Šis pasākums mūs informē, ka lietotājs ir veicis pirmo palaišanas pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3102">The event lets us know a user has gone thru first run experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3103">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai noskaidrotu, vai pirmā palaišanas pieredze (PPP) bija sekmīga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3103">We use this event to figure out if the First Run-Experience (FRE) was completed successfully.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3105">**Data_FirstRunCollectionTime** — laikspiedols, kas reģistrē laiku, kad plūsma tika pabeigta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3105">**Data_FirstRunCollectionTime** - A timestamp registering the time at which the flow was completed.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeiospaywallpaywallpresented"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3112">Office.iOS.Paywall.Paywall.Presented</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3112">Office.iOS.Paywall.Paywall.Presented</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3113">Šī kritiskā lietojuma telemetrija tiek apkopota, kad lietotājam tiek parādīta Paywall vadīkla, un šo telemetriju izmanto, lai izprastu lietotāju pieredzi, veicot pirkumus programmā, un lai to optimizētu nākamajās versijās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3113">This critical usage telemetry is collected when Paywall control is shown to the user, and is used to understand the in-app purchase experience for the user and optimize the same for future versions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3114">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3114">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3115">**entryPoint** — virkne — poga/plūsma, no kuras tika parādīts Paywall.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3115">**entryPoint** - String – The Button/Flow from which Paywall was displayed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3116">Piemēram, “Premium jaunināšanas poga” vai “Pirmās palaišanas plūsma”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3116">Like “Premium Upgrade Button” or “First Run Flow”</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3117">**isFRE** — Būla — vai tiek rādīts pirmās palaišanas pieredzes lietotāja interfeiss vai standarta lietotāja interfeiss?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3117">**isFRE** - Boolean – Are we showing the First Run Experience or regular UI?</span></span>

#### <a name="officeiospaywallpaywallstats"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3118">Office.iOS.Paywall.Paywall.Stats</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3118">Office.iOS.Paywall.Paywall.Stats</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3119">Šie sesijā balstītie meta dati tiek apkopoti, kad lietotājam tiek parādīts Paywall interfeiss, un tie norāda mijiedarbības ilgumu un to, vai pirkuma veikšanas mēģinājums izdevās vai neizdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3119">This session-based metadata is collected when the Paywall UI is shown to the user, the duration of the interaction and whether a purchase was attempted and succeeded or failed.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3120">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai izprastu visas maksājuma veikšanas pieredzes lietojumu un darbspēju un veiktu atkļūdošanu, optimizētu un novērstu problēmas programmas pirkumu pieredzē nākamajās versijās. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3120">The data is used to understand the usage and health of the entire payment experience and debug, optimize and troubleshoot the in-app purchase experience in future versions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3121">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3121">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3122">**entryPoint** — virkne — poga/plūsma, no kuras tika parādīts Paywall.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3122">**entryPoint** - String – The Button/Flow from which Paywall was displayed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3123">Piemēram, “Premium jaunināšanas poga” vai “Pirmās palaišanas plūsma”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3123">Like “Premium Upgrade Button” or “First Run Flow”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3124">**isFRE** — Būla — vai tiek rādīts pirmās palaišanas pieredzes lietotāja interfeiss vai standarta lietotāja interfeiss?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3124">**isFRE** - Boolean – Are we showing the First Run Experience or regular UI?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3125">**status**— virkne — Paywall izejas statuss.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3125">**status** - String – Exit status of Paywall.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3126">Piemēram, “initiated”, “paymentDone”, “provisionFailed”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3126">Like “initiated”, “paymentDone”, “provisionFailed”</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3127">**userDuration** — datu tips Double — lietotāja Paywall veltītais laiks milisekundēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3127">**userDuration** - Double – Duration in milliseconds the user spent on Paywall</span></span>

#### <a name="officeiospaywallskuchoosermorebenefitsstats"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3128">Office.iOS.Paywall.SKUChooser.MoreBenefits.Stats</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3128">Office.iOS.Paywall.SKUChooser.MoreBenefits.Stats</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3129">Šis notikums apkopo līdzekļus un programmas, kuras lietotājs izvērš no sadaļas “Skatīt papildu priekšrocības”, un lietotāja veltītā laika ilgumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3129">This event collects the features and apps the user expands from “See More Benefits”, and the duration of time spent.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3130">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai izprastu līdzekļa “Skatīt visas priekšrocības” lietojumu un optimizētu tā lietošanas pieredzi nākamajās versijās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3130">The data is used to understand usage of the “See all benefits” feature and further optimize the experience in future versions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3131">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3131">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3132">**appsExpanded** — virkne — ar komatiem atdalītu pakalpojumu/programmu, kurām tika paplašinātas priekšrocības, saraksts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3132">**appsExpanded** - String - Comma-separated list of services/apps for which the benefits were expanded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3133">**productId** — virkne — produkta, kuram lietotājs skata papildu piedāvātās priekšrocības, App Store ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3133">**productId** - String - App Store ID of the product for which user is viewing more benefits offered</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3134">**userDuration**— datu tips Double — laika, ko lietotājs pavadīja priekšrocību ekrānā, ilgums milisekundēs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3134">**userDuration** - Double - Duration in milliseconds the user spent on the Benefits Screen.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeiospaywallskuchooserstats"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3135">Office.iOS.Paywall.SKUChooser.Stats</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3135">Office.iOS.Paywall.SKUChooser.Stats</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3136">Šī lietojuma telemetrija tiek apkopota, lai redzētu, kā lietotājs ienāca SKU izvēlē, cik daudz laika lietotājs pavadīja SKU izvēles ekrānā un kāpēc lietotājs izgāja no SKU izvēles.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3136">This usage telemetry is collected to see how the user entered the SKU Chooser, how much time the user spends on the SKU Chooser screen and why they exited the SKU Chooser.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3137">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai izprastu SKU izvēles lietojumu un optimizētu pirkumu pieredzi programmā nākamajās versijās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3137">The data is used to understand usage of the SKU chooser and optimize the in-app purchase experience in future versions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3138">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3138">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3139">**entryPoint** — virkne — poga/plūsma, no kuras tika parādīts Paywall.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3139">**entryPoint** - String – The Button/Flow from which Paywall was displayed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3140">Piemēram, “Premium jaunināšanas poga” vai “Pirmās palaišanas plūsma”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3140">Like “Premium Upgrade Button” or “First Run Flow”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3141">**exitReason** — virkne — iemesls iziešanai no SKU izvēles.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3141">**exitReason** - String – Exit reason of SKU Chooser.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3142">Piemēram, “BuyButton”, “CloseButton”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3142">Like “BuyButton”, “CloseButton</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3143">**isFRE** — Būla — vai tiek rādīts pirmās palaišanas pieredzes lietotāja interfeiss vai standarta lietotāja interfeiss?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3143">**isFRE** - Boolean – Are we showing the First Run Experience or regular UI?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3144">**userDuration** — datu tips Double — laika, ko lietotājs pavadīja SKU izvēlē, ilgums milisekundēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3144">**userDuration** - Double – Duration in milliseconds the user spent on the SKU chooser</span></span>


#### <a name="officelivepersonacardconfigurationsetaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3145">Office.LivePersonaCard.ConfigurationSetAction</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3145">Office.LivePersonaCard.ConfigurationSetAction</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3146">Mēs reģistrējam brīdi, kad lietotājs atrodas lietojumprogrammā, kas ielādē personas kartīti, sagaidot, ka lietotājs atvērs Live personas kartīti. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3146">We log when the user is in an app that loads a Persona Card in anticipation of the user opening the Live Persona Card.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3147">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai noteiktu, vai kartīte ir ielādēta pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3147">The data is used to determine whether the card loaded correctly.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3148">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3148">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3149">**Data.accountType** — norāda, vai lietotājs pieder organizācijai vai ir patērētājs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3149">**Data.accountType** - Whether the user belongs to an organization or a consumer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3150">**Data.appContextId** — nejauši ģenerēts ID, kas tiek lietots dažādu kontu identificēšanai vienā un tajā pašā lietojumprogrammā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3150">**Data.appContextId** - A randomly generated ID used to identify different accounts in the same app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3151">**Data.AppInfo.Name** — izmantojamā pakalpojuma nosaukums (profila kartīte)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3151">**Data.AppInfo.Name** - Name of the service in use (Profile card)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3152">**Data.AppInfo_Id** — resursdatora lietojumprogrammas nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3152">**Data.AppInfo_Id** - Name of the host application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3153">**Data.AppInfo_Version** — resursdatora lietojumprogrammas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3153">**Data.AppInfo_Version** - Version of the host application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3154">**Data.cardCorrelationId** — globāli unikāls identifikators personas kartītei</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3154">**Data.cardCorrelationId** - The globally unique identifier for a persona card</span></span>

#### <a name="officelivepersonacarduseractionsopenedpersonacard"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3323">Office.LivePersonaCard.UserActions.OpenedPersonaCard</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3323">Office.LivePersonaCard.UserActions.OpenedPersonaCard</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3324">Reģistrēts, kad lietotājs atver personas kartīti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3324">Logged when the user opens a Persona Card.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3325">To izmanto, lai konstatētu kritiskas anomālijas neveiksmes gadījumā, palaižot reāllaika personas kartīti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3325">It is used to observe critical anomalies in failure rates of launching the Live Persona Card.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3326">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3326">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3327">**Data.appContextId** — nejauši ģenerēts ID, kas tiek lietots dažādu kontu identificēšanai vienā un tajā pašā programmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3327">**Data.appContextId** - A randomly generated id used to identify different accounts in the same app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3329">**Data.bandwidthEstimateMbps** — efektīvo joslas platuma aprēķini Mb/s</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3329">**Data.bandwidthEstimateMbps** - Effective bandwidth estimate in Mbps</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3330">**Data.cardCorrelationId** — globāli unikāls identifikators personas kartītei</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3330">**Data.cardCorrelationId** - The globally unique identifier for a persona card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3331">**Data.cardPersonaCorrelationId** — globālais unikālais identifikators konkrētai personai, kas redzama kartītē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3331">**Data.cardPersonaCorrelationId** - The globally unique identifier for a specific persona shown in a card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3332">**Data.clientCorrelationId** — globāli unikāls identifikators programmas sesijai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3332">**Data.clientCorrelationId** - The globally unique identifier for the app's session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3333">**Data.clientType** — ierīces tips, kurā tiek palaista programma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3333">**Data.clientType** - The type of device the app is run on.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3334">**Data.eventId** — notikuma nosaukuma identifikators, piemēram, "LivePersonaCardRenderedAction"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3334">**Data.eventId** - Name identifier of the event, e.g. "LivePersonaCardRenderedAction"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3340">**Data.hostAppRing** — aplis, kurā programma tika izplatīta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3340">**Data.hostAppRing** - The ring by which the app was distributed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3343">**Data.personaCorrelationId** — globāli unikāls identifikators unikālajām personām sesijā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3343">**Data.personaCorrelationId** - A globally unique identifier for unique personas in a session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3344">**Data.properties** — katram notikumam apkopotie papildu metadati, kā aprakstīts tālāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3344">**Data.properties** - Additional metadata collected for each event as follows.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3345">*[Šis lauks ir dzēsts jaunākajos Office būvējumos, taču, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3345">*[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

    - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3346">**cardCorrelationId** — Data.appContextId dublikāts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3346">**cardCorrelationId** - Duplicate of Data.appContextId above</span></span> 
    - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3347">**cardPersonaCorrelationId** — Data.cardCorrelationId dublikāts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3347">**cardPersonaCorrelationId** - Duplicate of Data.cardCorrelationId above</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3348">**consumerCorrelationId** — Data.clientCorrelationId dublikāts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3348">**consumerCorrelationId** - Duplicate of Data.clientCorrelationId above</span></span> 
    - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3349">**networkEffectiveType** — efektīvā tīkla savienojuma tips, piemēram, "slow-2g Online", lai noteiktu, vai lietotājam ir izveidots savienojums ar internetu brīdī, kad tiek parādīta personas kartīte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3349">**networkEffectiveType** - The effective type of network connection, e.g. "slow-2g Online" to identify whether the user is connected to the internet at the time of showing the persona card</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3350">**networkType** — izmantotās ierīces tīkla savienojamības tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3350">**networkType** - The type of network connectivity of the device in use</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3351">**roundTripEstimateMs** — aprēķinātais efektīvais pašreizējā savienojuma cikls milisekundēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3351">**roundTripEstimateMs** - Estimated effective round-trip of the current connection in milliseconds</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3352">**Data.region** — tā profila kartītes aizmugursistēmas pakalpojuma ģeogrāfiskais reģions, ar kuru savienots lietotājs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3352">**Data.region** -The geographical region of the profile card backend service to which user is connected</span></span>

#### <a name="officemanageabilityclient-fetchpolicyprechecks"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3367">Office.Manageability.Client Fetch.PolicyPreChecks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3367">Office.Manageability.Client Fetch.PolicyPreChecks</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3368">Kritisko kļūdu telemetrija, lai izsekotu mākoņpakalpojuma politikas ieneses pirmspārbaudes validācijas panākumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3368">Critical telemetry to track failure\\success for cloud policy fetch precheck validation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3369">Iziešanas iemesls satur skaitītāja karti, kas attiecas uz neizdevušos pirmspārbaudes nosacījumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3369">ExitReason contains an enumerator map to the pre-check condition that failed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3370">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3370">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3371">**Data.ExitReason** — skaitītāja vērtība, kas paziņo iziešanas iemeslu, ja pirmspārbaude neizdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3371">**Data.ExitReason** - An enumerator value telling the exit reason, if the Precheck failed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3372">**Data.Log** — pielāgots žurnāla ziņojums, kas norāda pirmspārbaudes panākumus (izdošanos/neizdošanos)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3372">**Data.Log** - Custom log message indicating the precheck success or failure</span></span>

#### <a name="officemanageabilityclientfetchandapplypolicy"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3373">Office.Manageability.Client.Fetch.AndApplyPolicy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3373">Office.Manageability.Client.Fetch.AndApplyPolicy</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3376">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3376">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3377">**Data.ExitReason** — skaitītāja vērtība, kas paziņo iziešanas iemeslu, ja pirmspārbaude neizdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3377">**Data.ExitReason** - An enumerator value telling the exit reason, if the Precheck failed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3378">**Data.Log** — pielāgots žurnāla ziņojums, kas norāda pirmspārbaudes panākumus (izdošanos/neizdošanos)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3378">**Data.Log** - Custom log message indicating the precheck success or failure</span></span>

#### <a name="officeofficemobilepdfviewerpdffileopenmeasurements"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3379">Office.OfficeMobile.PdfViewer.PdfFileOpenMeasurements</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3379">Office.OfficeMobile.PdfViewer.PdfFileOpenMeasurements</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3380">Šis notikums tiek apkopots Office lietojumprogrammai darbam ar iOS un reģistrē, kad notiek faila atvēršanas darbība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3380">This event is collected for the Office app for iOS, it records when a file open operation takes place.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3381">Mēs apkopojam šos datus, lai nodrošinātu labu visu failu atvēršanas darbību veiktspēju programmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3381">We collect this data to ensure good performance for all file opens on the app.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3382">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3382">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3383">**Data_Doc_ActivationFQDN** — nodrošinātāja programmas domēna nosaukums faila aktivizēšanas scenārijam (tiek uzskaitīta tikai 1. puses programmas informācija).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3383">**Data_Doc_ActivationFQDN** - Domain name of the Provider app for a file activation scenario (only 1st party app info is being logged).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3384">**Data_Doc_CreateTelemetryReason** — telemetrijas iemesls PDF izveidei. (piemēram: izveide skenējot, izmantojot "attēls uz PDF" darbību, izmantojot "Dokuments uz PDF" darbība, utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3384">**Data_Doc_CreateTelemetryReason** – Telemetry reason for PDF creation.(eg: Create from scan, using “picture to pdf” action, using “document to pdf” action, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3385">**Data_Doc_DownloadDurationms** — PDF mākoņa faila lejupielādei nepieciešamais laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3385">**Data_Doc_DownloadDurationms** - Time to download a PDF cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3386">**Data_Doc_DownloadEndTime** — mākoņa faila lejupielādes beigu laikspiedols.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3386">**Data_Doc_DownloadEndTime** - Timestamp for end of download of a cloud file.</span></span>
