#### <a name="officeofficemobilepdfviewerpdffileoperations"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3395">Office.OfficeMobile.PdfViewer.PdfFileOperations</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3395">Office.OfficeMobile.PdfViewer.PdfFileOperations</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3396">Šis notikums tiek apkopots Office lietojumprogrammai darbam ar Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3396">The event is collected for the Office app for Android.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3397">Reģistrē, kad notiek .pdf atvēršanas, aizvēršanas vai saglabāšanas darbība, un to izmanto, lai izprastu un prioritizētu lietotāja pieredzi atbilstoši informācijai par .pdf failu darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3397">It records when a .pdf open, close, or save operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize the user experience based on .pdf file operation information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3398">Šis notikums ļauj mums nodrošināt atbilstošu .pdf atvēršanas, aizvēršanas un saglabāšanas darbību izpildi, kā arī uzlabot .pdf failu darbības veiktspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3398">The event enables us to keep the .pdf open, close and save operations performing as expected, and to improve .pdf file operation performance.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3399">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3399">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3400">**Data_Doc_FileOpSessionID**— unikāls ID dokumenta sesijai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3400">**Data_Doc_FileOpSessionID** - Unique ID for a Document Session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3401">**Data_ErrorCode** — kļūda faila atvēršanas kļūmes/ lejupielādes kļūmes / lejupielādes atcelšanas gadījumos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3401">**Data_ErrorCode** - error in case of file open failures/download failures / download canceled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3402">**Data_ErrorMessage** — atbilstošais ziņojuma par kļūdu kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3402">**Data_ErrorMessage** - relevant message-to-error code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3403">**Data_FailureReason** — atvēršanas kļūmes gadījumā, šie uzskaitījumi definē kļūmes iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3403">**Data_FailureReason** - In case of open failure, these enums define the reason for failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3404">**Data_FileGUID** — nejauši ģenerēta faila globālais identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3404">**Data_FileGUID** – Global identifier for the file which is random generated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3405">**Data_FileLocation** — faila atrašanās vieta, piemēram: lokāli, ODSP, iCloud utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3405">**Data_FileLocation** - Location where the file sits, ex: Local, ODSP, iCloud, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3406">**Data_FileOpenEntryPoint** — faila atvēršanas ievades punkts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3406">**Data_FileOpenEntryPoint** - entry point for file open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3407">**Data_FileSize** — faila, kurā notiek darbība, izmērs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3407">**Data_FileSize** - Size of the file on which the operation is happening</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3408">**Data_NetworkRequestErrorResponse** — tīkla kļūdas atbilde, kas atbilst kļūdas kodam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3408">**Data_NetworkRequestErrorResponse** – Network Error response corresponding to error code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3409">**Data_NetworkRequestStage** — kļūdu posms mākoņa PDF faila lejupielādes gadījumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3409">**Data_NetworkRequestStage** – Error stage in case of cloud pdf file download.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3410">**Data_OpenMode** — kādā režīmā tika atvērts PDF, piem.: 0: skatīšanas režīms, 2: parakstīšanās režīms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3410">**Data_OpenMode** - In which mode the PDF was opened, ex: 0: View mode, 2: Sign mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3411">**Data_PageCount** — lapu skaits PDF failā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3411">**Data_PageCount** - Count of page in the PDF File.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3412">**Data_PasswordProtected** — marķieris, kas norāda, vai parole ir aizsargāta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3412">**Data_PasswordProtected** - Marker that tell whether the file is password protected or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3413">**Data_ProviderApp** — pašreiz nodrošina pakalpojuma sniedzēja lietojumprogrammu gadījumos, kad notiek tikai faila aktivācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3413">**Data_ProviderApp** - currently providing provider app in case of file activation only</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3414">**Data_ReadOnly** — marķieris, kas norāda, vai fails ir tikai lasāms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3414">**Data_ReadOnly** - Marker that tell whether the file is read-only or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3415">**Data_Result** — veicamās darbības statuss, piemēram: patiess: izdevās, aplams: neizdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3415">**Data_Result** - The status of the operation being performed, ex: true:success, false:failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3416">**Data_Type** — faila darbības veids (atvēršana, aizvēršana vai saglabāšana)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3416">**Data_Type** - Type of file operation (open, close or save)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenoteandroidappnavigationnavigationuistatechanged-onenoteappnavigationnavigationuistatechanged-previous-name"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3436">Office.OneNote.Android.App.Navigation.NavigationUIStateChanged, OneNote.App.Navigation.NavigationUIStateChanged *(iepriekšējais nosaukums)*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3436">Office.OneNote.Android.App.Navigation.NavigationUIStateChanged, OneNote.App.Navigation.NavigationUIStateChanged *(previous name)*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3437">Šis notikums apkopo kritiskos signālus, kas tiek izmantoti, lai nodrošinātu OneNote lietotāju veiksmīgu navigāciju lietojumprogrammā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3437">This event collects the critical signal used to ensure OneNote users can successfully navigate through the app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3438">Telemetrija, kas tiek izmantota kritiskas regresijas atklāšanai OneNote lietojumprogrammā un pakalpojuma darbspējā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3438">The telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3439">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3439">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3440">**IS_SPANNED** — norāda, vai lietojumprogramma ir savienotā režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3440">**IS_SPANNED** - Indicates whether the app is in a spanned mode.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3441">Tiek īpaši uzskaitīts salokāmām ierīcēm.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3441">This is specifically logged for foldable devices.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3442">**NEW_STATE** — norāda lietojumprogrammas stāvokli uzreiz pēc navigācijas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3442">**NEW_STATE** - Indicates the applications' state right after the navigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3443">**OLD_STATE** — norāda lietojumprogrammas stāvokli tieši pirms navigācijas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3443">**OLD_STATE** - Indicates the applications' state right before the navigation</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenoteandroidlenssdkofficelenslaunched-onenotelenssdkofficelenslaunched-previous-name"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3444">Office.OneNote.Android.LensSDK.OfficeLensLaunched, OneNote.LensSDK.OfficeLensLaunched *(iepriekšējais nosaukums)*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3444">Office.OneNote.Android.LensSDK.OfficeLensLaunched, OneNote.LensSDK.OfficeLensLaunched *(previous name)*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3445">Šis notikums apkopo kritisko signālu, kas tiek izmantots, lai nodrošinātu pareizu OfficeLens palaišanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3445">This event collects the critical signal used to ensure that OfficeLens is launched correctly.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3446">Telemetrija, kas tiek izmantota kritiskas regresijas atklāšanai OneNote lietojumprogrammā un pakalpojuma darbspējā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3446">The telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3447">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3447">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3448">**CAPTURE_MODE** — norāda, kurā režīmā tika palaists OfficeLens.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3448">**CAPTURE_MODE** - Indicates which mode has OfficeLens been launched in.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3449">Iespējamie režīmi ir noklusējuma, rediģēšanas, ātrās ievietošanas vai video importēšanas režīms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3449">It could be default, edit, fast insert or video import.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3450">**ERROR_CODE** — norāda palaišanas kļūdas kodu gadījumā, ja palaišanas brīdī notika kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3450">**ERROR_CODE** - Indicates the launch error code in case there was an error while launching.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3451">**IMAGE_COUNT** — norāda uzņemto attēlu skaitu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3451">**IMAGE_COUNT** - Indicates the number of images taken</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3452">**LAUNCH_REASON** — norāda plūsmu, kurā tika palaists OfficeLens.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3452">**LAUNCH_REASON** - Indicates the flow under which OfficeLens was launched.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3453">Tas var notikt bloķēšanas ekrānā, StickyNotes kameras vai galerijas opcijās vai OneNote Canvas utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3453">It could be over the lock screen or via Camera or Gallery options in StickyNotes or via OneNote Canvas etc.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeonenoteandroidstickynotesnotecreated"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3454">Office.OneNote.Android.StickyNotes.NoteCreated</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3454">Office.OneNote.Android.StickyNotes.NoteCreated</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3455">Kritisks signāls, kas tiek lietots, lai pārraudzītu līmpiezīmju lietotāju iespēju programmā izveidot piezīmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3455">Critical signal that is used to monitor the ability of Sticky Notes users to create notes in the app.</span></span>   <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3456">Telemetrija, kas tiek izmantota kritiskas regresijas atklāšanai OneNote lietojumprogrammā un pakalpojuma darbspējā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3456">Telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3457">Ja lietotājiem neizdodas izveidot piezīmi, tā aktivizēs kritisku incidentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3457">If users can’t create a note, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3458">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3458">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3459">**IsExportable** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai šis notikums bija lietotāja darbības rezultāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3459">**IsExportable** - A flag indicating whether this event was a result of a user action or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3460">Jābūt iestatītam kā “True”, jo “NoteCreated” ir lietotāja izraisīta darbība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3460">Should be set to True as NoteCreated is a user-triggered action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3461">**NoteLocalId** — atšķirams unikāls identifikators, kas piešķirts piezīmei laikā, kad lietotājs izveido piezīmi programmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3461">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time of a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3472">**NoteLocalId** — atšķirams unikāls identifikators, kas piešķirts piezīmei laikā, kad lietotājs izveido piezīmi programmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3472">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3473">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** — versijas numurs, kurā norādīta lietotāja izmantoto līmpiezīmju versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3473">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3474">Ļauj mums noteikt, kurās produkta versijās ir radusies problēma, lai mēs varētu pareizi noteikt tās prioritāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3474">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeonenotecanvasinkinkstrokelogger"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3475">Office.OneNote.Canvas.Ink.InkStrokeLogger</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3475">Office.OneNote.Canvas.Ink.InkStrokeLogger</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3476">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai atklātu un diagnosticētu augstfrekvences kļūdu, ar ko saskaras lietotājs, izmantojot rokraksta funkciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3476">This event is used to detect and diagnose a high frequency bug that a user encounters while using Ink feature.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3477">Tas tiks izmantots, lai noteiktu atbilstošāko šīs problēmas novēršanas veidu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3477">This will be used to determine the most appropriate mode of fixing this issue.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3478">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3478">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3479">**CurrentCanvasZoomFactor** — pašreizējais kanvas tālummaiņas faktors.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3479">**CurrentCanvasZoomFactor** - Current Zoom factor of the canvas.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3480">**CurrentNotebook** — pašreiz aktīvās piezīmju grāmatiņas identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3480">**CurrentNotebook** - Identifier of the current active notebook.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3481">**CurrentPage** — pašreiz aktīvās lapas identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3481">**CurrentPage** - Identifier of the current active page</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3482">**CurrentSection** — pašreiz aktīvās sadaļas identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3482">**CurrentSection** - Identifier of the current active section.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3483">**DefaultCanvasZoomFactor** — noklusējuma kanvas tālummaiņas faktors.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3483">**DefaultCanvasZoomFactor** - Default Zoom factor of the canvas.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3484">**InkStrokeCount** — kopējais rokraksta vilkumu skaits kopš pēdējā žurnāla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3484">**InkStrokeCount** - Total count of ink strokes since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3485">**InkStrokeWithLayerInkEffect** — rokraksta vilkumu skaits ar slāņa efektu kopš pēdējā žurnāla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3485">**InkStrokeWithLayerInkEffect** - Count of ink strokes with layer ink effect since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3486">**InkStrokeWithoutPressureCount** — rokraksta vilkumu bez spiediena skaits kopš pēdējā žurnāla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3486">**InkStrokeWithoutPressureCount** - Count of Ink Strokes without Pressure since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3487">**InkStrokeWithPencilInkEffect** — rokraksta vilkumu skaits ar zīmuļa efektu kopš pēdējā žurnāla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3487">**InkStrokeWithPencilInkEffect** - Count of ink strokes with pencil ink effect since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3488">**InkStrokeWithTilt** — rokraksta vilkumu ar slīpumu skaits kopš pēdējā žurnāla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3488">**InkStrokeWithTilt** - Count of ink strokes with tilt since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3495">**IsBlank** — norāda, vai jaunā lapa ir tukša lapa vai izveidota no veidnes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3495">**IsBlank** - Indicates whether a new page is blanked page or created with a template.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3496">**IsRecentsView** — norāda, vai lapa ir izveidota no nesenajām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3496">**IsRecentsView** - Indicates whether a page is created from a recents or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3497">**NavView** — norāda, vai lapa ir izveidota no navigācijas skata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3497">**NavView** - Indicates whether a page is created from a navigation view or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3498">**NoteType** — norāda lapas veidu (ātrā piezīme, saraksts vai fotogrāfija).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3498">**NoteType** - Indicates the type (quick note, list, or photo) of a page.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3500">**RailState** — norāda uz OneNote navigācijas joslu lapas izveides brīdī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3500">**RailState** - Indicates the state of OneNote's navigation rail when creating a page.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3501">**Trigger** — norāda uz lapas izveides darbības sākuma punktu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3501">**Trigger** - Indicates an entry point where the create page action is started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3502">**TriggerInfo** — norāda papildu informāciju par trigeri.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3502">**TriggerInfo** - Indicates additional information related to the trigger.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3541">Kritiskā signāla ID, kas tiek izmantots, lai uzraudzītu OneNote lietotāju spēju atrast informāciju lapu un piezīmju grāmatiņu tūkstošos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3541">Critical signal ID used to monitor the ability of OneNote users to find information across thousands of pages and notebooks.</span></span>   <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3542">Telemetrija, kas tiek izmantota kritiskas regresijas atklāšanai OneNote lietotnē un pakalpojuma darbspējā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3542">Telemetry used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3543">Ja lietotājiem neizdodas atrast informāciju piezīmju grāmatiņās, tiks aktivizēts kritiskais incidents.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3543">If users can't find information across notebooks this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3544">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3544">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3545">**PageSearchResultCount** — norāda lapā meklēšanas režīmā atrasto meklēšanas rezultātu skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3545">**PageSearchResultCount** - Indicates the number of search's results found in a page search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3546">**PageTimeToFirstResultInMs** — norāda laiku, kas ir nepieciešams OneNote, lai atrastu pirmo atbilstošo rezultātu lapas meklēšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3546">**PageTimeToFirstResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the first match in a page search mode.</span></span>
    
-  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3547">**PageTimeToLastResultInMs** — norāda laiku, kas ir nepieciešams OneNote, lai atrastu pēdējo atbilstošo rezultātu lapas meklēšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3547">**PageTimeToLastResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the last match in a page search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3548">**PageTimeToMedianResultInMs** — norāda laiku, kas ir nepieciešams OneNote, lai atrastu visus atbilstošos rezultātus lapas meklēšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3548">**PageTimeToMedianResultInMs** - Indicates the median of time OneNote takes to find all matches in a page search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3549">**SearchResultCount** — norāda meklēšanas rezultātu skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3549">**SearchResultCount** - Indicates the number of search's results found.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3550">**TagSearchResultCount** — norāda atzīmju meklēšanas režīmā atrasto meklēšanas rezultātu skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3550">**TagSearchResultCount** - Indicates the number of search's results found in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3551">**TagTimeToFirstResultInMs** — norāda laiku, kas ir nepieciešams OneNote, lai atrastu pirmo atbilstošo rezultātu atzīmju meklēšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3551">**TagTimeToFirstResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the first match in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3552">**TagTimeToLastResultInMs** — norāda laiku, kas ir nepieciešams OneNote, lai atrastu pēdējo atbilstošo rezultātu atzīmju meklēšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3552">**TagTimeToLastResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the last match in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3553">**TagTimeToMedianResultInMs** — norāda vidējo laiku, kas ir nepieciešams OneNote, lai atrastu visus atbilstošo rezultātus atzīmju meklēšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3553">**TagTimeToMedianResultInMs** - Indicates the median of time OneNote takes to find all matches in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3554">**TimeToFirstResultInMs** — norāda laiku, kas ir nepieciešams OneNote, lai atrastu pirmo atbilstošo rezultātu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3554">**TimeToFirstResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the first match.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3555">**TimeToLastResultInMs** — norāda laiku, kas ir nepieciešams OneNote, lai atrastu pēdējo atbilstošo rezultātu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3555">**TimeToLastResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the last match.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3556">**TimeToMedianResultInMs** — norāda vidējo laiku, kas ir nepieciešams OneNote, lai atrastu visus atbilstošo rezultātus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3556">**TimeToMedianResultInMs** - Indicates the median of time OneNote takes to find all matches.</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotesigscriticalerrorencountered"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3557">Office.OneNote.SIGS.CriticalErrorEncountered</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3557">Office.OneNote.SIGS.CriticalErrorEncountered</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3558">Šis notikums uztver kritisku signālu, kas tiek izmantots signāla uzņemšanas pakalpojuma (SIGS) stāvokļa uzraudzībai, reģistrējot ikreiz, kad rodas kritiska kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3558">This event captures a critical signal that is used to monitor the health of Signal Ingestion Service (SIGS), by logging whenever a critical error is encountered.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3559">Kritiskās kļūdas var bloķēt visu SIGS, un tas palīdzēs mums novērst šādus jautājumus, tiklīdz tie būs saskārušies ar lietotājiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3559">Critical errors can block the whole of SIGS, and this will help us catch any such issues as soon as they are encountered by users.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3560">Bez šī mēs būsim atkarīgi no tā, lai lietotāji ziņotu par problēmām, ar kurām tie saskaras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3560">Without this we will be dependent on users to report the problems they are facing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3561">Šādas telemetrijas iztrūkuma dēļ šādu problēmu novēršanas laiks būs daudz lielāks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3561">Absence of such telemetry would make the turnaround time for such issues much higher.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3562">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3562">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3563">**Kļūdas _ kods** — tās problēmas kods, ar kuru saskārās lietotājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3563">**ErrorCode** - The code of the issue that was hit by the user.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeonenotestickynotesnotecreated-on-ios-onenotestickynotesnotecreated-on-android"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3564">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (iOS operētājsistēmā), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (Android operētājsistēmā)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3564">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (on iOS), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (on Android)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3565">Šis ir kritisks signāls, kas tiek lietots, lai pārraudzītu līmpiezīmju lietotāju iespēju programmā izveidot piezīmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3565">This is a critical signal that is used to monitor the ability of Sticky Notes users to create notes in the app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3566">Telemetrija, kas tiek izmantota kritiskas regresijas atklāšanai OneNote lietojumprogrammā un pakalpojuma darbspējā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3566">Telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3567">Ja lietotājiem neizdodas izveidot piezīmi, tā aktivizēs kritisku incidentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3567">If users can't create a note, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3568">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3568">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3569">**NoteLocalId** — atšķirams unikāls identifikators, kas piešķirts piezīmei laikā, kad lietotājs izveido piezīmi programmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3569">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time of a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3570">**IsExportable** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai šis notikums bija lietotāja darbības rezultāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3570">**IsExportable** - A flag indicating whether this event was a result of a user action or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3571">Jābūt iestatītam kā “True”, jo “NoteCreated” ir lietotāja izraisīta darbība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3571">Should be set to True as NoteCreated is a user-triggered action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3572">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** — versijas numurs, kurā norādīta lietotāja izmantoto līmpiezīmju versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3572">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3573">Ļauj mums noteikt, kurās produkta versijās ir radusies problēma, lai mēs varētu pareizi noteikt tās prioritāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3573">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeonenotestickynotesnoteviewed-on-ios-onenotestickynotesnoteviewed-on-android"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3574">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteViewed (iOS operētājsistēmā), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteViewed ( Android operētājsistēmā)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3574">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteViewed (on iOS), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteViewed (on Android)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3575">Šis ir kritisks signāls, kas tiek lietots, lai pārraudzītu līmpiezīmju lietotāju iespēju programmā izveidot piezīmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3575">This is a critical signal that is used to monitor the ability of Sticky Notes users to create notes in the app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3576">Telemetrija, kas tiek izmantota kritiskas regresijas atklāšanai OneNote lietojumprogrammā un pakalpojuma darbspējā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3576">Telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3577">Ja lietotājiem neizdodas izveidot piezīmi, tā aktivizēs kritisku incidentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3577">If users can't create a note, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3578">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3578">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3579">**HasImages** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai skatītajā piezīmē ir saglabāti attēli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3579">**HasImages** - A flag indicating whether the note viewed has images stored in it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3580">**IsExportable** — karodziņš, kas norāda, vai šis notikums bija lietotāja darbības rezultāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3580">**IsExportable** - A flag indicating whether this event was a result of a user action or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3581">Jābūt iestatītam kā “True”, jo “NoteViewed” ir lietotāja izraisīta darbība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3581">Should be set to True as NoteViewed is a user-triggered action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3582">**NoteLocalId** — atšķirams unikāls identifikators, kas piešķirts piezīmei laikā, kad lietotājs izveido piezīmi programmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3582">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3583">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** — versijas numurs, kurā norādīta lietotāja izmantoto līmpiezīmju versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3583">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3584">Ļauj mums noteikt, kurās produkta versijās ir radusies problēma, lai mēs varētu pareizi noteikt tās prioritāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3584">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeonenotestoragenotebooksyncresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3585">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3585">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3586">Šis notikums reģistrē piezīmju grāmatiņas sinhronizācijas rezultātu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3586">This event logs notebook sync result.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3587">Tas tiek lietots, lai, aprēķinot OneNote sinhronizācijas vērtējumu, noteiktu, cik daudz ir unikālu sinhronizācijas mērķu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3587">It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3588">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3588">The following fields are collected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3589">**CachedError_Code** — ciparu vai burtciparu kods, kas tiek lietots, lai noteiktu kešatmiņā saglabātās kļūdas raksturu un/vai to, kāpēc tā radās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3589">**CachedError_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the cached error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3590">**CachedError_Description** — kešatmiņā saglabātās kļūdas apraksts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3590">**CachedError_Description** -a description of the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3591">**CachedError_Tag** — norāda, kur kodā rodas kešatmiņā saglabātā kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3591">**CachedError_Tag** -indicate where in the code throws the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3592">**CachedError_Type** — kešatmiņā saglabātās kļūdas tips, piemēram, Win32Error u. tml.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3592">**CachedError_Type** -the type of the cached error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3593">**ExecutionTime** — laiks milisekundēs, kas bija nepieciešams, lai replicētu piezīmju grāmatiņu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3593">**ExecutionTime** -time in milliseconds taken to replicate the notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3594">**Gosid** — globālais objektu telpas ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3594">**Gosid** -global object space ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3595">**IdentityType** — identitātes tips, piemēram, Windows Live, organizācijas ID utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3595">**IdentityType** -identity type, e.g. Windows Live, Org ID, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3596">**InitialReplicationInSession** — norāda, vai šī replicēšana ir pirmā piezīmju grāmatiņas replicēšana pēc atvēršanas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3596">**InitialReplicationInSession** -is this replication the first notebook replication after open or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3597">**IsBackgroundSync** — norāda, vai tā ir fona sinhronizācija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3597">**IsBackgroundSync** -is this a background sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3598">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** — norāda, vai kešatmiņā saglabātā kļūda tiek apspiesta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3598">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** -is the cached error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3599">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** — norāda, vai kešatmiņā saglabātā kļūda ir neparedzēta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3599">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** -is the cached error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3600">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** — norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņas līmeņa sinhronizācijas kļūda tiek apspiesta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3600">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** -is the notebook level sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3601">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** — norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņas līmeņa sinhronizācijas kļūda ir neparedzēta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3601">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** -is the notebook level sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3602">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** — norāda, vai sadaļu sinhronizācijas kļūdas tiek apspiestas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3602">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** -is the section sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3603">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** — norāda, vai sadaļas sinhronizācijas kļūda bija paredzēta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3603">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** -is the section sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3604">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** — norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņas sinhronizēšana notiek, izmantojot moderno lapas satura sinhronizāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3604">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** -is the notebook sync using modern page content sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3605">**LastAttemptedSync** — laikspiedols, kad piezīmju grāmatiņu tika mēģināts sinhronizēt iepriekšējo reizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3605">**LastAttemptedSync** -timestamp when the notebook was attempted to be synced last time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3606">**LastBackgroundSync** — laikspiedols, kad notika pēdējais mēģinājums veikt sinhronizāciju fona režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3606">**LastBackgroundSync** -timestamp when the latest background sync was attempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3607">**LastNotebookViewedDate** — datums, kad piezīmju grāmatiņa pēdējoreiz tika skatīta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3607">**LastNotebookViewedDate** -the date when the notebook was last viewed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3608">**LastSuccessfulSync** — laikspiedols, kad piezīmju grāmatiņa iepriekš sekmīgi sinhronizēta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3608">**LastSuccessfulSync** -timestamp when the notebook successfully synced before</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3609">**NeedToRestartBecauseOfInconsistencies** — norāda, vai sinhronizācija ir jārestartē, jo pastāv nekonsekvences.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3609">**NeedToRestartBecauseOfInconsistencies** -does the sync need to restart because of inconsistencies or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3610">**NotebookErrorCode** — piezīmju grāmatiņas līmeņa sinhronizācijas kļūdas kods, kas saglabāts piezīmju grāmatiņas diagrammas apgabalā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3610">**NotebookErrorCode** -notebook level sync error code saved on notebook graph space</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3611">**NotebookId** — piezīmju grāmatiņas ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3611">**NotebookId** -notebook ID</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookmacdeleteaccountusage"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3701">Office.Outlook.Mac.DeleteAccountUsage</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3701">Office.Outlook.Mac.DeleteAccountUsage</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3702">Konta dzēšanas Outlook programmā rezultāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3702">Result of deleting an account in Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3703">Dati tiek uzraudzīti, lai nodrošinātu, ka kļūmju skaits nepalielinās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3703">The data is monitored to ensure we don't see any spikes in failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3704">Mēs arī analizējam datus, lai atrastu jomas, kurās nepieciešami uzlabojumi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3704">We also analyze the data to find areas of improvement.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3705">Mēs strādājam pie tā, lai uzlabotu panākumu rādītājus katrā laidienā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3705">We aim to improve this success rate with each release.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3706">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3706">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3707">**AccountType** — konfigurējamā konta veids.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3707">**AccountType** - type of account being configured</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3708">**AccountID** — konta identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3708">**AccountID** - account identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3709">**DeprovisionAccount** — norāda, vai konts ir noņemts no servera.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3709">**DeprovisionAccount** - indicates whether account is removed from server</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3710">**IsFastDelete** — norāda, vai konts ir dzēsts fona pavedienā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3710">**IsFastDelete** - indicates whether account is deleted on background thread</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationclose"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3711">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Close</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3711">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Close</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3712">Apkopo, kad ir aizvērtas PowerPoint prezentācijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3712">Collected when PowerPoint presentations are closed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3713">Tas satur informāciju, kas ir nepieciešama pareizai tādu problēmu izmeklēšanai un diagnosticēšanai, kas notiek, izmantojot aizvēršanas procesu, kas ietver lietotāja datu turpināšanu un sinhronizēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3713">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen through the close process which entail persisting and syncing the user's data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3714">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai nodrošinātu, ka aizvēršana darbojas, kā paredzēts, un lietotāju saturs tiek sekmīgi turpināts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3714">Microsoft uses this data to ensure that close is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3715">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3715">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3716">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long —** vai šim žurnāla ierakstam ir visa nepieciešamā dokumenta telemetrija (Data\_Doc\_\* lauki)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3716">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3717">Ja tā nav, kāpēc?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3717">If not, why?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3718">**Data\_AutoSaveDisabledReasons:string —** vai pastāv iepriekš noteiktu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokumentā tika atspējota automātiskā saglabāšana?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3718">**Data\_AutoSaveDisabledReasons:string -** Predefined set of values of why was autosave disabled on this document?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3719">(Sapludināšanas kļūda, saglabāšanas kļūda, grupas politika utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3719">(Merge error, Save error, Group policy etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3720">**Data\_CloseReason:long -** Kā tika veikta aizvēršana?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3720">**Data\_CloseReason:long -** How was close performed?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3721">Aizverot dokumentu?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3721">Closing document?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3722">Aizverot programmu?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3722">Closing app?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3723">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long —** neapstrādāto izņēmumu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3723">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long -** Number of unhandled exceptions</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3724">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long —** darbības atvienošanas/nedarbošanās ilgums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3724">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3725">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long —** kā šis dokuments ir atvērts (tikai lasāms | lasīšana un rakstīšana)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3725">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3726">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3726">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3727">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3727">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3728">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long —** kā dokuments ir saglabāts pakalpojumā SharePoint</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3728">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3729">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long —** dokumenta uzņēmuma datu aizsardzība statuss</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3729">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3730">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string —** dokumenta paplašinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3730">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3731">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string —** dokumenta paplašinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3731">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3732">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long —** iepriekš definētu faila formāta vērtību kopa (detalizētāka par paplašinājumu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3732">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3733">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string —** dokumentu glabāšanas vieta (SharePoint.com, live.net), pieejama tikai Office 365 domēniem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3733">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3735">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string —** unikāls lietotāja GUID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3735">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string -** Unique GUID of user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3736">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string —** tās identitātes unikālais identifikators, kas tika izmantota koplietojamo dokumentu darbībai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3736">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3737">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long —** bitmaska dažādiem ar IO saistītiem karodziņiem, kas attiecas uz dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3737">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long -** Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3738">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas attiecas uz informācijas piekļuves tiesību pārvaldības tipu, kas tiek lietots šim dokumentam (pārsūtīšana, atbildēšana, SecureReader, rediģēšana u.c.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3738">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3739">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool —** patiess, ja "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP galvene jau ir saņemta no pieprasījuma OPTIONS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3739">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool -** True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3740">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool —** vai dokuments tika atvērts inkrementāli (jauns līdzeklis, kas atver dokumentu bez vajadzības lejupielādēt visu dokumentu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3740">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool -** Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3741">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool —** vai ir dokuments atbalsta koprediģēšanu, izmantojot jauno OCS pakalpojumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3741">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool -** Is Document supports coauthoring using new OCS service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3742">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool —** pārbauda, vai dokuments tiek atvērts no lokālās kešatmiņas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3742">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool -** verifies if document is being opened from local cache</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3743">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool —** pārbauda, vai ja dokuments tiek atvērts no mapes, kas izmanto OneDrive sinhronizācijas programmu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3743">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool -** verifies if document is being opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3744">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda dokumenta glabāšanas vietu (lokālā, SharePoint, WOPI, tīkls utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3744">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long -** Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3745">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long —** iepriekš definētu detalizētākas atrašanās vietas vērtību kopa (mape Temp, lejupielāžu mape, OneDrive dokumenti, OneDrive attēli utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3745">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long -** Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3746">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long —** līdzautoru skaits dokumenta atvēršanas brīdī</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3746">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long -** Number of coauthors at the time of opening of a document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3747">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda veidu, kā dokuments ir šifrēts ar paroli (nav, parole lasīšanai, parole rediģēšanai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3747">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long -** Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)-</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3748">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc šis dokuments ir atzīmēts kā tikai lasāms (bloķēts serverī, pabeigts dokuments, aizsargāts ar paroli rediģēšanai utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3748">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why this document was marked read only (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3749">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string —** resursu identifikatora jaukšana mākonī saglabātajiem dokumentiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3749">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string -** Hash of resource identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3750">**Data_Doc_RtcType —** norāda, kā reāllaika kanāls (RTC) bija iestatīts pašreizējam failam (atspējots, neatbalstīts, pēc pieprasījuma, vienmēr ieslēgts utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3750">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3752">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kurš protokols tiek izmantots, lai sazinātos ar serveri (HTTP, Cobalt, WOPI utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3752">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long -** Predefined set of values of which protocol is used to talk to server (Http, Cobalt, WOPI etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3753">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopas servera tipam (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3753">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long -** Predefined set of values of type of server (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3754">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion:long —** pārbauda, vai servera pamatā ir Office14, Office15 vai Office 16</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3754">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion:long -** verifies if server is based off Office14, Office15 or Office 16</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3755">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long —** ģenerēts GUID, kas norāda dokumenta instanci tajā pašā procesa sesijā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3755">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long -** generated GUID that Identifies the instance of the document within the same process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3756">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext:string —** necaurspīdīga virkne, parasti GridManagerID.FarmID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3756">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext:string -** An opaque string, typically GridManagerID.FarmID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3757">Noder, lai saistītu klienta un servera žurnālu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3757">Useful for correlating client-side and server-side log</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3758">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long —** dokumenta lielums baitos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3758">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long -** Document size in bytes</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3759">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long —** bitmaska, kas norāda speciālās rakstzīmes dokumenta vietrādī URL vai ceļā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3759">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long -** Bitmask indicating special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3766">**Data\_fLifeguarded:bool —** vai dokuments kādreiz ir bijis aizsargāts (līdzeklis, lai izlabotu dokumenta kļūdas, neziņojot par to lietotājam)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3766">**Data\_fLifeguarded:bool -** Was document ever lifeguarded (feature to fix document errors by themselves without prompting user)?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3773">**Data\_OCSClosingDlgCanceled:bool —** ja augšupielāde gaida serverī OCS, kamēr lietotājs aizver dokumentu, tiek parādīts dialoglodziņš ar aicinājumu uzgaidīt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3773">**Data\_OCSClosingDlgCanceled:bool -** If upload is pending on OCS while user closes document, dialog is popped up to user to wait.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3774">Kādu opciju izvēlējās lietotājs?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3774">Which option user chose?</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationnewdocument"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3782">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.NewDocument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3782">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.NewDocument</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3783">Apkopo, kad PowerPoint izveido jaunu prezentāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3783">Collected when PowerPoint creates a new presentation.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3784"> Ietver panākumus un veiktspējas rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3784"> Includes success failure and performance metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3785">Šī informācija tiek izmantota, lai mēs varētu sekmīgi izveidot failus, nepasliktinot veiktspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3785">This information is used to ensure we can create files successfully and with no degradation in performance.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3786">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3786">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3787">**NewDocumentType** — vai jaunais dokuments ir izveidots no veidnes vai vienkārši izveidots tukšs?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3787">**NewDocumentType** – Whether new document is created from template or just created blank?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3788">**FLifeguarded** — vai dokuments ir aizsargāts (līdzeklis, kas atjauno bojāta dokumenta statusu, nepaziņojot par to lietotājam)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3788">**FLifeguarded** – Is document life guarded (feature that restores corrupt document state without prompting user)</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationopencompleteprotocol"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3789">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.OpenCompleteProtocol</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3789">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.OpenCompleteProtocol</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3790">Apkopo, kad PowerPoint atver prezentācijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3790">Collected when PowerPoint opens presentations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3791">Tas satur informāciju, kas ir nepieciešama pareizai tādu problēmu izmeklēšanai un diagnosticēšanai, kas notiek pēdējos atvēršanas procesa posmos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3791">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen through the end stages of the open process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3792">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai nodrošinātu līdzekļa pareizu darbību un neietekmētu prezentāciju atvēršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3792">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and there is no degradation to opening presentations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3793">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3793">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3794">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa pretvīrusu programmatūras skenēšanas tipam (IOAV, AMSI, nav utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3794">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod:long -** Predefined set of values of type of AntiVirus scanned (IOAV, AMSI, None etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3795">**Data\_AntiVirusScanStatus:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa pretvīrusu programmatūras skenēšanai, kas tiek veikta katram atvērtajam dokumentam (NoThreatsDetected, neizdevās, MalwareDetected utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3795">**Data\_AntiVirusScanStatus:long -** Predefined set of values of anti-virus scan that happens for every document opened (NoThreatsDetected, Failed, MalwareDetected etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3796">**Data\_CloseAndReopen:bool —** vai dokuments tika aizvērts un atkārtoti atvērts?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3796">**Data\_CloseAndReopen:bool -** Was this document closed and reopened?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3797">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long —** darbības atvienošanas/nedarbošanās ilgums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3797">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3798">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long —** kā šis dokuments ir atvērts (tikai lasāms | lasīšana un rakstīšana)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3798">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3799">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3799">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3800">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3800">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3801">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long —** kā dokuments ir saglabāts pakalpojumā SharePoint</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3801">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3802">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long —** dokumenta uzņēmuma datu aizsardzība statuss</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3802">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3803">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string —** dokumenta paplašinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3803">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3804">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string —** dokumenta paplašinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3804">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3805">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long —** iepriekš definētu faila formāta vērtību kopa (detalizētāka par paplašinājumu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3805">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3806">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string —** dokumentu glabāšanas vieta (SharePoint.com, live.net), pieejama tikai Office 365 domēniem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3806">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3807">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string —** dokumenta glabāšanas vietas jaukšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3807">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string -** Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3808">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string —** unikāls lietotāja GUID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3808">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string -** Unique GUID of user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3809">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string —** tās identitātes unikālais identifikators, kas tika izmantota koplietojamo dokumentu darbībai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3809">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3810">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long —** bitmaska dažādiem ar IO saistītiem karodziņiem, kas attiecas uz dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3810">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long -** Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3811">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas attiecas uz informācijas piekļuves tiesību pārvaldības tipu, kas tiek lietots šim dokumentam (pārsūtīšana, atbildēšana, SecureReader, rediģēšana u.c.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3811">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3812">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool —** patiess, ja "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP galvene jau ir saņemta no pieprasījuma OPTIONS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3812">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool -** True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3813">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool —** vai dokuments tika atvērts inkrementāli (jauns līdzeklis, kas atver dokumentu bez vajadzības lejupielādēt visu dokumentu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3813">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool -** Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3814">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool —** vai ir dokuments atbalsta koprediģēšanu, izmantojot jauno OCS pakalpojumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3814">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool -** Is Document supports coauthoring using new OCS service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3815">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool —** vai dokuments tiek atvērts no lokālās kešatmiņas?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3815">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool -** Is document being opened from local cache?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3816">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool —** vai dokuments tiek atvērts no mapes, kas izmanto OneDrive sinhronizācijas programmu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3816">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool -** Is document opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3817">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda dokumenta glabāšanas vietu (lokālā, SharePoint, WOPI, tīkls utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3817">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long -** Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3818">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long —** iepriekš definētu detalizētākas atrašanās vietas vērtību kopa (mape Temp, lejupielāžu mape, OneDrive dokumenti, OneDrive attēli utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3818">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long -** Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3819">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long —** līdzautoru skaits dokumenta atvēršanas brīdī</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3819">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long -** Number of coauthors at the time of opening of a document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3820">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda veidu, kā dokuments ir šifrēts ar paroli (nav, parole lasīšanai, parole rediģēšanai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3820">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long -** Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)-</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3821">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc šis dokuments ir atzīmēts kā tikai lasāms (bloķēts serverī, pabeigts dokuments, aizsargāts ar paroli rediģēšanai utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3821">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why this document was marked read only (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3822">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string —** resursu identifikatora jaukšana mākonī saglabātajiem dokumentiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3822">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string -** Hash of resource identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3823">**Data_Doc_RtcType —** norāda, kā reāllaika kanāls (RTC) bija iestatīts pašreizējam failam (atspējots, neatbalstīts, pēc pieprasījuma, vienmēr ieslēgts utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3823">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3825">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kurš protokols tiek izmantots, lai sazinātos ar serveri (HTTP, Cobalt, WOPI utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3825">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long -** Predefined set of values of which protocol is used to talk to server (Http, Cobalt, WOPI etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3826">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopas servera tipam (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3826">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long -** Predefined set of values of type of server (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3827">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion:long —** pārbauda, vai servera pamatā ir Office14, Office15 vai Office 16</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3827">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion:long -** verifies if server is based off Office14, Office15 or Office 16</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3828">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long —** ģenerēts GUID, kas norāda dokumenta instanci tajā pašā procesa sesijā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3828">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long -** generated GUID that Identifies the instance of the document within the same process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3829">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext:string —** necaurspīdīga virkne, parasti GridManagerID.FarmID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3829">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext:string -** An opaque string, typically GridManagerID.FarmID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3830">Noder, lai saistītu klienta un servera žurnālu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3830">Useful for correlating client side and server-side logs</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3831">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long —** dokumenta lielums baitos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3831">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long -** Document size in bytes</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3832">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long —** bitmaska, kas norāda speciālās rakstzīmes dokumenta vietrādī URL vai ceļā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3832">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long -** Bitmask indicating special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3838">**Data\_ExecutionCount:long —** cik reižu mēs izpildījām IncOpen protokolu pirms šī protokola (OpenComplete) izpildes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3838">**Data\_ExecutionCount:long -** How many times we executed IncOpen protocol before executing this (OpenComplete) protocol</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3845">**Data\_StopwatchDuration:long —** kopējais darbības ilgums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3845">**Data\_StopwatchDuration:long -** Total time for Activity</span></span>
