#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsave"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3849">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Save</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3849">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Save</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3850">Apkopots ikreiz, kad PowerPoint veic saglabāšanu, izmantojot modernu koda ceļu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3850">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a save using the modern code path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3851">Ietver saglabāšanas veiktspējas rādītāju rezultātu tipa panākumus un saistītos dokumenta metadatus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3851">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3852"> Saglabāšanas kļūmes var izraisīt datu zudumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3852"> Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3853">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai nodrošinātu, ka līdzeklis darbojas, kā paredzēts, un lietotāju saturs tiek sekmīgi turpināts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3853">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3854">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3854">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3855">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long —** vai šim žurnāla ierakstam ir visa nepieciešamā dokumenta telemetrija (Data\_Doc\_\* lauki)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3855">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3856">Ja tā nav, kāpēc?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3856">If not, why?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3857">**Data\_BeforeSaveEvent:long —** cik ilgā laikā tika ģenerēts dokuments pirms saglabāšanas notikuma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3857">**Data\_BeforeSaveEvent:long -** Time taken to raise Document Before Save Event</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3858">**Data\_CheckDownRevSaveTimeMS:long —** cik ilga laikā tika pārbaudīta pārskatīšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3858">**Data\_CheckDownRevSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to check revision</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3859">**Data\_CheckMacroSaveTimeMS:long —** cik ilga laikā tika saglabāts makro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3859">**Data\_CheckMacroSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to save macros</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3860">**Data\_ClearAutoSaveTimeMS:long —** cik ilgā laikā tika noņemts automātiskās saglabāšanas karodziņš</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3860">**Data\_ClearAutoSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clear AutoSave flag</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3861">**Data\_ClearDirtyFlagTimeMS:long —** cik ilgā laikā tika noņemts mainīta dokumenta karodziņš</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3861">**Data\_ClearDirtyFlagTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clear document dirty flag</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3862">**Data\_CloneDocumentTimeMS:long —** cik ilgā laikā tika klonēts dokuments pirms saglabāšanas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3862">**Data\_CloneDocumentTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clone document before starting the save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3863">**Data\_CommitTransactionTimeMS:long —** cik ilgā laikā tika izpildīta saglabāšanas darbība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3863">**Data\_CommitTransactionTimeMS:long -** Time taken to commit the save transaction</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3864">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long —** nenotverti vietējie izņēmumi darbības izpildes laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3864">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long -** Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3865">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long —** darbības atvienošanas/nedarbošanās ilgums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3865">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3866">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long —** kā šis dokuments ir atvērts (tikai lasāms | lasīšana un rakstīšana)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3866">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3867">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3867">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3868">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3868">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3869">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long —** kā dokuments ir saglabāts pakalpojumā SharePoint</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3869">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3870">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long —** dokumenta uzņēmuma datu aizsardzība statuss</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3870">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3871">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string —** dokumenta paplašinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3871">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3872">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string —** dokumenta paplašinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3872">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3873">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long —** iepriekš definētu faila formāta vērtību kopa (detalizētāka par paplašinājumu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3873">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3874">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string —** dokumentu glabāšanas vieta (SharePoint.com, live.net), pieejama tikai Office 365 domēniem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3874">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3876">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string —** unikāls lietotāja GUID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3876">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string -** Unique GUID of user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3877">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string —** tās identitātes unikālais identifikators, kas tika izmantota koplietojamo dokumentu darbībai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3877">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3878">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long —** bitmaska dažādiem ar IO saistītiem karodziņiem, kas attiecas uz dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3878">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long -** Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3879">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas attiecas uz informācijas piekļuves tiesību pārvaldības tipu, kas tiek lietots šim dokumentam (pārsūtīšana, atbildēšana, SecureReader, rediģēšana u.c.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3879">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3880">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool —** patiess, ja "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP galvene jau ir saņemta no pieprasījuma OPTIONS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3880">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool -** True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3881">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool —** vai dokuments tika atvērts inkrementāli (jauns līdzeklis, kas atver dokumentu bez vajadzības lejupielādēt visu dokumentu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3881">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool -** Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3882">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool —** vai ir dokuments atbalsta koprediģēšanu, izmantojot jauno OCS pakalpojumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3882">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool -** Is Document supports coauthoring using new OCS service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3883">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool —** pārbauda, vai dokuments tiek atvērts no lokālās kešatmiņas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3883">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool -** verifies if document being is opened from local cache</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3885">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda dokumenta glabāšanas vietu (lokālā, SharePoint, WOPI, tīkls utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3885">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long -** Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3886">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long —** iepriekš definētu detalizētākas atrašanās vietas vērtību kopa (mape Temp, lejupielāžu mape, OneDrive dokumenti, OneDrive attēli utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3886">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long -** Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3888">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda veidu, kā dokuments ir šifrēts ar paroli (nav, parole lasīšanai, parole rediģēšanai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3888">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long -** Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3889">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc šis dokuments ir atzīmēts kā tikai lasāms (bloķēts serverī, pabeigts dokuments, aizsargāts ar paroli rediģēšanai utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3889">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why this document was marked read only (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3891">**Data_Doc_RtcType —** norāda, kā reāllaika kanāls (RTC) bija iestatīts pašreizējam failam (atspējots, neatbalstīts, pēc pieprasījuma, vienmēr ieslēgts utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3891">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3893">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kurš protokols tiek izmantots, lai sazinātos ar serveri (HTTP, Cobalt, WOPI utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3893">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long -** Predefined set of values of which protocol is used to talk to server (Http, Cobalt, WOPI etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3894">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopas servera tipam (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3894">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long -** Predefined set of values of type of server (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3897">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext:string —** necaurspīdīga virkne, parasti GridManagerID.FarmID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3897">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext:string -** An opaque string, typically GridManagerID.FarmID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3898">Noder, lai saistītu klienta un servera žurnālu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3898">Useful for correlating client-side and server-side logs</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsaveas"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3935">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveAs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3935">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveAs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3936">Apkopots ikreiz, kad PowerPoint veic darbību Saglabāt kā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3936">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a Save As.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3937">Ietver saglabāšanas veiktspējas rādītāju rezultātu tipa panākumus un saistītos dokumenta metadatus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3937">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3938">Saglabāšanas kļūmes var izraisīt datu zudumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3938">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3939">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai nodrošinātu, ka līdzeklis darbojas, kā paredzēts, un lietotāju saturs tiek sekmīgi turpināts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3939">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3940">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3940">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3941">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** — vai šim žurnāla ierakstam ir visa nepieciešamā dokumenta telemetrija (Data_Doc_\* lauki)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3941">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** - Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3942">Ja nav, kāpēc?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3942">If not, why?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3943">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** — darbības izpildes laikā nenotvertie vietējie izņēmumi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3943">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** - Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3944">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** — darbības atvienošanas/nedarbošanās ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3944">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** - Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3945">**Data_DstDoc_AccessMode:long** — kā šis dokuments tika atvērts (tikai lasāms | lasīšana un rakstīšana).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3945">**Data_DstDoc_AccessMode:long** - How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3946">**Data_DstDoc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3946">**Data_DstDoc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3947">\*\*Data_DstDoc_AsyncOpenKind:long — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta jaunā mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3947">**Data_DstDoc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the new cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3948">**Data_DstDoc_ChunkingType:long** — kā dokuments ir saglabāts pakalpojumā SharePoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3948">**Data_DstDoc_ChunkingType:long** - How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3949">**Data_DstDoc_EdpState:long** — dokumenta uzņēmuma datu aizsardzība statuss.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3949">**Data_DstDoc_EdpState:long** - Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3950">**Data_DstDoc_Ext:string** — dokumenta paplašinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3950">**Data_DstDoc_Ext:string** - Document extension</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3951">**Data_DstDoc_Extension:string** — dokumenta paplašinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3951">**Data_DstDoc_Extension:string** - Document extension</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3952">**Data_DstDoc_FileFormat:long** — iepriekš definētu faila formāta vērtību kopa (detalizētāka par paplašinājumu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3952">**Data_DstDoc_FileFormat:long** - Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3953">**Data_DstDoc_Fqdn:string** — dokumentu glabāšanas vieta (SharePoint.com, live.net), pieejama tikai Office 365 domēniem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3953">**Data_DstDoc_Fqdn:string** - Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3954">**Data_DstDoc_FqdnHash:string** — dokumenta glabāšanas vietas jaukšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3954">**Data_DstDoc_FqdnHash:string** - Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3955">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityTelemetryId:string** — lietotāja unikālais GUID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3955">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityTelemetryId:string** - Unique GUID of user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3956">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityUniqueId:string** — koplietojamo dokumentu darbībai izmantotās identitātes unikālais identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3956">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityUniqueId:string** - Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3957">**Data_DstDoc_IOFlags:long** — bitmaska dažādiem ar IO saistītiem karodziņiem, kas attiecas uz dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3957">**Data_DstDoc_IOFlags:long** - Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3958">**Data_DstDoc_IrmRights:long** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas attiecas uz informācijas piekļuves tiesību pārvaldības tipu, kas tiek lietots šim dokumentam (pārsūtīšana, atbildēšana, SecureReader, rediģēšana u.c.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3958">**Data_DstDoc_IrmRights:long** - Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3959">**Data_DstDoc_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** — patiess, ja "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP galvene jau ir saņemta no pieprasījuma OPTIONS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3959">**Data_DstDoc_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** - True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3960">**Data_DstDoc_IsIncrementalOpen:bool**— vai dokuments tika atvērts inkrementāli (jauns līdzeklis, kas atver dokumentu bez vajadzības lejupielādēt visu dokumentu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3960">**Data_DstDoc_IsIncrementalOpen:bool** - Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3961">**Data_DstDoc_IsOcsSupported:bool** — vai ir dokuments atbalsta koprediģēšanu, izmantojot jauno OCS pakalpojumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3961">**Data_DstDoc_IsOcsSupported:bool** - Is Document supports coauthoring using new OCS service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3962">**Data_DstDoc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool** — pārbauda, vai dokuments tiek atvērts no lokālās kešatmiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3962">**Data_DstDoc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool** - verifies if document is being opened from local cache</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3963">**Data_DstDoc_IsSyncBacked:bool** — vai dokuments tiek atvērts no mapes, kas izmanto OneDrive sinhronizācijas programmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3963">**Data_DstDoc_IsSyncBacked:bool** - Is document opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3964">**Data_DstDoc_Location:long** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda dokumenta glabāšanas vietu (lokālā, SharePoint, WOPI, tīkls utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3964">**Data_DstDoc_Location:long** - Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3965">**Data_DstDoc_LocationDetails:long** — iepriekš definētu detalizētākas atrašanās vietas vērtību kopa (mape Temp, lejupielāžu mape, OneDrive dokumenti, OneDrive attēli utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3965">**Data_DstDoc_LocationDetails:long** - Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3966">**Data_DstDoc_NumberCoAuthors:long** — līdzautoru skaits dokumenta atvēršanas brīdī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3966">**Data_DstDoc_NumberCoAuthors:long** - Number of coauthors at the time of opening of a document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3967">**Data_DstDoc_PasswordFlags:long** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda veidu, kā dokuments ir šifrēts ar paroli (nav, parole lasīšanai, parole rediģēšanai).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3967">**Data_DstDoc_PasswordFlags:long** - Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-3968">**Data_DstDoc_ReadOnlyReasons:long** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc šis dokuments ir atzīmēts kā tikai lasāms (bloķēts serverī, pabeigts dokuments, aizsargāts ar paroli rediģēšanai utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-3968">**Data_DstDoc_ReadOnlyReasons:long** - Predefined set of values of why this document was marked read only (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit, etc.)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4036">Apkopots ikreiz, kad PowerPoint veic saglabāšanu, izmantojot mantotā koda ceļu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4036">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a save using the legacy code path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4037">Ietver saglabāšanas veiktspējas rādītāju rezultātu tipa panākumus un saistītos dokumenta metadatus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4037">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4038">Saglabāšanas kļūmes var izraisīt datu zudumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4038">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4039">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai nodrošinātu, ka līdzeklis darbojas, kā paredzēts, un lietotāju saturs tiek sekmīgi turpināts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4039">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4041">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** — vai šim žurnāla ierakstam ir visa nepieciešamā dokumenta telemetrija (Data_Doc_\* lauki)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4041">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** - Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4042">Ja nav, kāpēc?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4042">If not, why?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4043">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** — darbības izpildes laikā nenotvertie vietējie izņēmumi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4043">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** - Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4044">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** — darbības atvienošanas/nedarbošanās ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4044">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** - Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

#### <a name="officetargetedmessagingabexperimentmessagetrigger"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4244">Office.TargetedMessaging.ABExperimentMessageTrigger</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4244">Office.TargetedMessaging.ABExperimentMessageTrigger</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4245">Izseko to lietotāju skaitam, kas saņem BizBar un dinamiskās pamatnes ziņojumus no TargetedMessagingService (TMS).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4245">Tracks the number of users receiving BizBar and Dynamic Canvas messages from TargetedMessagingService (TMS).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4246">Šie dati ir būtiski, jo ļauj saprast, kādus ziņojumus saņem lietotāji un kurā virsmā. Šādi mēs varam nodrošināt, lai lietotāji nepalaistu garām nevienu ziņojumu par produkta turpmāku izmantošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4246">This data is critical to understand what messages users are getting and on what surface so that we can ensure they are not missing any messages that may be critical to their continued use of the product.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4247">Tie arī palīdz pareizi novērtēt mūsu eksperimentu un TMS kampaņu panākumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4247">Also needed to accurately measure the success of our experiments and campaigns run through TMS.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4248">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4248">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4249">**Data\_Surface** — tās virsmas nosaukums, kam ir paredzēts šis pakalpojuma piegādātais ziņojums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4249">**Data\_Surface** – Name of the surface that this service delivered message is meant for</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiosharedfeatureexperimentation"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4387">Office.Visio.Shared.FeatureExperimentation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4387">Office.Visio.Shared.FeatureExperimentation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4388">Reģistrē līdzekļu izmēģinājumus lietotājiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4388">Tracks feature flighting for users.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4389">Šis notikums palīdz mums noteikt līdzekļa izmēģinājuma izdošanos vai neveiksmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4389">This event helps us determines success or failure of feature flights.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4390">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4390">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4391">**Data\_Enable:bool**— patiess norāda, ka līdzeklis ir iespējots pašreizējam lietotājam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4391">**Data\_Enable:bool**- true indicate the feature is enabled for current user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4392">**Data\_Feature:string** — līdzekļa nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4392">**Data\_Feature:string** - name of the feature</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4393">**Data\_Flighted:bool** — patiess norāda, ka šis līdzeklis ir iespējots</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4393">**Data\_Flighted:bool** - true indicates the feature is enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4394">**Data\_Licensed:bool** — patiess norāda, ka šim līdzeklim tiek veikta licences pārbaude</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4394">**Data\_Licensed:bool** - true indicates the feature is under licensing check</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4395">**Data\_Subscriber:bool** — patiess norāda, ka lietotājam ir abonementa licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4395">**Data\_Subscriber:bool** - true indicates the user has subscription license</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiosharedrefreshsmartdiagram"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4396">Office.Visio.Shared.RefreshSmartDiagram</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4396">Office.Visio.Shared.RefreshSmartDiagram</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4397">Fiksē diagrammas atsvaidzināšanas kļūmes, kad fails tiek izveidots, izmantojot DV.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4397">Captures diagram refresh failures when file is created through DV.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4398">Tas palīdz mums atkļūdot kļūmes un problēmas ar datu atsvaidzināšanu DV shēmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4398">This helps us debug the failures and issues in data refresh in a DV diagram.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4399">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4399">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4400">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** — patiess, ja atsvaidzinātā shēma tika izveidota, izmantojot savienotāju, kura pamatā ir secības opcija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4400">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** - true if the refreshed diagram was originally created using connector based on sequence" option</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4401">**Data\_DialogError**:**string** — kļūda viedās shēmas atsvaidzināšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4401">**Data\_DialogError**:**string** - error during refreshing smart diagram</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4402">**Data\_FileError:string** — kļūdas virkne, ja pievienotais Excel fails ir nederīgs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4402">**Data\_FileError:string** - error string when connected Excel file is invalid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4403">**Data\_OverwriteSelected**:**bool** — patiess, ja lietotājs atlasīja shēmas pārrakstīšanas opciju atsvaidzināšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4403">**Data\_OverwriteSelected**:**bool** - true if user selected overwrite diagram option during refresh</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4404">**Data\_WarningShown**:**bool** — patiess, ja lietotājam tika parādīts brīdinājums datu atsvaidzināšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4404">**Data\_WarningShown**:**bool** - true if there was any warning shown to user during data refresh</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiosharedwritebacktoexcel"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4405">Office.Visio.Shared.WritebackToExcel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4405">Office.Visio.Shared.WritebackToExcel</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4406">Fiksē Excel pārrakstīšanas kļūmes, kad fails tiek izveidots, izmantojot DV.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4406">Captures Excel write back failures when file is created through DV.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4407">Tas palīdz mums atkļūdot kļūmes un problēmas ar Excel datu pārrakstīšanu DV shēmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4407">This helps us debug the failures and issues in writing back data to Excel in a DV diagram.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4408">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4408">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4409">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** — patiess nozīmē, ka savienojumi ir izveidoti, pamatojoties uz secības iestatījumiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4409">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** - true means connectors are created based on sequence settings</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4410">**Data\_DataSourceType:string** — šis aizpildītais lauks norāda, vai shēma tiek izveidota no tabulas vai pielāgota diapazona</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4410">**Data\_DataSourceType:string** - This filed indicates whether diagram is created from  "Table" or "CustomRange"</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4411">**Data\_DialogError:string** — pielāgots kļūdas tips, izveidojot viedo shēmu programmā Excel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4411">**Data\_DialogError:string** - Custom Error type while creating smart diagram through Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4412">**Data\_NoOfShapesAdded:int** — formu skaits, kas pievienotas pārrakstīšanas laikā Excel funkcionalitātē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4412">**Data\_NoOfShapesAdded:int** - Number of shapes added during writeback to Excel functionality</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4413">**Data\_NoOfShapesDeleted:int** — formu skaits, kas izdzēstas pārrakstīšanas laikā Excel funkcionalitātē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4413">**Data\_NoOfShapesDeleted:int** - Number of shapes deleted during writeback to Excel functionality</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4414">**Data\_OverwriteSelected:bool** — patiess norāda, ka lietotājs atlasīja datu pārrakstīšanas opciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4414">**Data\_OverwriteSelected:bool** - true indicate user selected overwrite data option</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4415">**Data\_SourceDataModified:bool** — patiess norāda, ka tiek mainīti avota dati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4415">**Data\_SourceDataModified:bool** - true indicates source data is modified</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4416">**Data\_WarningShown:bool** — patiess norāda, ka lietotājam tiek parādīts datu atjaunināšanas brīdinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4416">**Data\_WarningShown:bool** - true means data update warning shown to the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4417">**Data\_WarningShownBecauseOfPresenceOfFormula:bool** — patiess norāda, ka lietotājam tiek parādīts brīdinājums, jo programmā Excel ir ievietota formula</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4417">**Data\_WarningShownBecauseOfPresenceOfFormula:bool** - true indicates warning shown to the user because of presence of formula in Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4418">**Data\_WarningShownToAddNextStepID:bool** — patiess norāda, ka lietotājam tiek parādīts brīdinājums, jo programmā Excel trūkst nākamās darbības identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4418">**Data\_WarningShownToAddNextStepID:bool** - true indicates warning show to the user because next step Identifier missing in Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4419">**Data\_WarningShownToConvertToTable:bool** — patiess norāda, ka lietotājam tiek parādīts brīdinājums, lai pārvērstu Excel datus tabulas formātā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4419">**Data\_WarningShownToConvertToTable:bool** - true indicates warning shown to the user to convert Excel data to table format</span></span>


#### <a name="officewordfilenewcreatenewfile"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4420">Office.Word.FileNew.CreateNewFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4420">Office.Word.FileNew.CreateNewFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4421">Šis notikums norāda, ka ir izveidots jauns Office Word dokuments un seko šīs darbības panākumu statusam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4421">This event indicates that a new document is created in Office Word and tracks success or failure of the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4422">Notikums tiek izmantots, lai pārraudzītu jaunā dokumenta izveides pareizu darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4422">The event is used to monitor that new document creation is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4423">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4423">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4424">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4424">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4425">**Data\_DirtyState** — vai dokuments tika izveidots mainītā statusā (ar nesaglabātām izmaiņām)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4425">**Data\_DirtyState** - whether the document was created in a dirty state (with changes that need to be saved)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4426">**Data\_ErrorID** — identifikators darbības kļūmes gadījumā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4426">**Data\_ErrorID** - error identifier in case of operation failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4427">**Data\_MainPdod —** dokumenta identifikators šī procesa laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4427">**Data\_MainPdod** - The document identifier during this process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4428">**Data\_UsesCustomTemplate** — norāda, vai dokuments ir izveidots, izmantojot pielāgotu veidni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4428">**Data\_UsesCustomTemplate** - indicates whether the document was created from a custom template</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenuserinitiatedopen"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4429">Office.Word.FileOpen.UserInitiatedOpen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4429">Office.Word.FileOpen.UserInitiatedOpen</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4430">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word atver dokumentu pēc lietotāja iniciētas darbības, nevis izmantojot Office Word programmiski.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4430">This event indicates Office Word opens a document by user initiation instead of by Office Word programmatically.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4431">Tas satur arī kritiski svarīgus faila atvēršanas izpildes datus, un no lietotāja skatpunkta ir programmas startēšanas notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4431">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4432">Notikums pārrauga, vai faila atvēršana darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4432">The event monitors whether file-open is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4433">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4433">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span> 
 
<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4434">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4434">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4435">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** — norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4435">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4436">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4436">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4437">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura uzskatām, ka varēsim atvērt failu, ja tos iegūstam pirms lietotājs vēlas sākt rediģēšanu vai saglabāšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4437">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4438">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura, iespējams, varēsim atvērt failu, taču tam būs nepieciešamas būtiskas koda izmaiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4438">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4439">**Data_BytesSynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), kuram jābūt mūsu rīcībā, pirms varam sākt faila atvēršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4439">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4440">**Data_BytesUnknown**— baitu skaits dokumenta daļās, kuras neplānojam atrast.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4440">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4441">**Data_Doc_AccessMode —** dokuments ir tikai lasāms/rediģējams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4441">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4442">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4442">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4443">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType —** vienības, kas tiek izmantotas inkrementālā dokumenta atvēršanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4443">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4444">**Data_Doc_EdpState —** dokumenta elektronisko datu aizsardzības iestatījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4444">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4445">**Data_Doc_Ext —** dokumenta paplašinājums (docx/xlsb/pptx utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4445">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4446">**Data_Doc_FileFormat —** faila formāta protokola versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4446">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4447">**Data_Doc_Fqdn —** OneDrive vai SharePoint Online domēna nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4447">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4448">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash —** klientu identificējama domēna nosaukuma vienvirziena jaukšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4448">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4449">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId —** tādas lietotāja identitātes vienvirziena jaukšana, kas tiek izmantota atvēršanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4449">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4450">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario —** dokumenta atvēršanas ieraksti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4450">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4451">**Data_Doc_IOFlags —** atskaites par kešotajiem karodziņiem, kas tiek izmantoti atvēršanas pieprasījuma opciju iestatīšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4451">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4452">**Data_Doc_IrmRights —** dokumentam/lietotājam piemērotās elektronisko datu politikas atļautās darbības.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4452">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4453">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen —** karodziņš, kas norāda, ka dokuments tika atvērts inkrementāli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4453">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4454">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported —** karodziņš, kas norāda, ka dokuments tiek atbalstīts sadarbības pakalpojumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4454">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4455">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy —** karodziņš, kas norāda, ka tika atvērta dokumenta bezsaistes kopija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4455">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4456">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked —** karodziņš, kas norāda, ka datorā pastāv automātiski sinhronizēta dokumenta kopija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4456">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4457">**Data_Doc_Location —** norāda pakalpojumu, kurā atrodas dokuments (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4457">**Data_Doc_Location** - Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4458">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails —** norāda, kurā zināmajā mapē atrodas lokāli saglabātais dokuments.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4458">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** - Indicates which Known Folder provided a locally stored document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4459">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors —** citu lietotāju skaits koprediģēšanas sesijā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4459">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** - Count of the number of fellow users in a collaborative editing session</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4460">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags —** norāda lasīšanas/rakstīšanas paroles karodziņu kopu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4460">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** - Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4461">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons —** iemesli, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts tikai lasāmajā režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4461">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4462">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash —** anonimizēts dokumenta identifikators, ko izmanto problēmu noteikšanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4462">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - An anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4463">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId —** nemainīgs anonimizēts dokumenta identifikators, ko izmanto problēmu noteikšanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4463">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - An immutable anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4464">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol —** protokola versija, ko izmanto, lai sazinātos ar pakalpojumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4464">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - the protocol version used to communicate with the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4466">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion —** servera versija, kas nodrošina pakalpojumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4466">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - the server version offering the service</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4467">**Data_Doc_SessionId** — tā servera versija, kas nodrošina pakalpojumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4467">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - the server version offering the service</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4468">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext —** diagnostikas informācija no SharePoint Online pieprasījumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4468">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - Diagnostic information from SharePoint Online requests</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4469">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes —** dokumenta lieluma rādītājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4469">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - Indicator of document size</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4470">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars —** speciālo rakstzīmju rādītājs dokumenta vietrādī URL vai ceļā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4470">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - Indicator of special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4471">**Data_Doc_StreamAvailability —** norāda, vai ir pieejama/atspējota dokumenta plūsma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4471">**Data_Doc_StreamAvailability** - Indicator if document stream is available/disabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4473">**Data_UrlHash —** vienvirziena jaukšana vienkāršota dokumenta identifikatora izveidei.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4473">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - One-way hash to create a naïve document identifier</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4474">**Data.Doc.WopiServiceId —** satur unikālu WOPI pakalpojumu sniedzēja identifikatoru.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4474">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - Contains unique identifier of WOPI service provider</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4475">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** — pirmā redaktora identifikators, kas izraisīja pārdēvēšanas atspējošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4475">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** - Identifier of the first editor that caused for rename to be disabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4477">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** — vesela skaitļa vērtība, kas attēlo iemeslu, kāpēc fails tika atvērts lasīšanas/rakstīšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4477">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** - Integer value representing the reason why the file was forced into read/write mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4479">**Data_LastLoggedTag** — unikāla atzīme koda izsaukuma vietā, ko izmanto, lai noteiktu, kad neizdodas atvērt divreiz (izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4479">**Data_LastLoggedTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify when we try to fail the open twice (used for data quality diagnostics)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4480">**Data_LinkStyles** — norāda, vai ir saite ar veidņu stiliem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4480">**Data_LinkStyles** - Indicates whether we are linking to the template styles</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4481">**Data_MainPdod** — dokumenta identifikators Office Word procesā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4481">**Data_MainPdod** - The document identifier in Office Word process</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4482">**Data_Measurements** — kodēta virkne, kas satur dažādu daļu atvēršanas laika sadalījumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4482">**Data_Measurements** - Encoded string containing the time breakdown of the different parts of open.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4483">Izmanto, lai diagnosticētu atvēršanas izpildi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4483">Used to diagnose open performance.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4484">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** — kļūda, kas atspējo dokumenta pārvietošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4484">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** - Error that is disabling move for the document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4485">**Data_MoveFlightEnabled** — vai lidojuma opcija pārvietošanas līdzeklī ir iespējota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4485">**Data_MoveFlightEnabled** - Whether the flight for the move feature is enabled</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4486">**Data_OpenInitiateKind** — tāda scenārija tips, kur lietotāji sāka šo failu atvēršanas darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4486">**Data_OpenInitiateKind** – Type of the scenario where users started this file-open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4488">**Data_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag** — unikāla atzīme koda izsaukumu vietā, lai identificētu vietu kodā, kur mēs mēģināsim izlabot failu pirms tā atvēršanas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4488">**Data_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify the place in code where we attempt to fix the file before opening it</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4489">**Data_RenameDisabledReason** — kļūda, kuras dēļ tiek atspējota dokumenta pārdēvēšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4489">**Data_RenameDisabledReason** - Error that is causing for rename to be disabled for this document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4490">**Data_RenameFlightEnabled** — vai testējamā varianta opcija pārdēvēšanas līdzeklī ir iespējota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4490">**Data_RenameFlightEnabled** - Whether the flight for the rename feature is enabled</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4491">**Data_SecondaryTag** — unikāla atzīme koda izsaukšanas vietai, kas tiek izmantota, lai pievienotu papildu kļūmes datus atvēršanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4491">**Data_SecondaryTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to add additional failure data for open.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4492">**Data_TemplateFormat** — tās veidnes faila formāts, kas ir dokumenta pamatā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4492">**Data_TemplateFormat** - File format of the template that the document is based on.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4493">**Data_UsesNormal** — norāda, vai atvērtā dokumenta pamatā ir parasta veidne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4493">**Data_UsesNormal** - Indicates whether the open document is based on the normal template.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4494">**Data_VerboseMeasurements** — kodēta virkne, kas satur detalizētu dažādu daļu atvēršanas laika sadalījumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4494">**Data_VerboseMeasurements** - Encoded string containing the detailed time breakdown of the different parts of open.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4495">Tiek izmantota, lai mērītu veiktspēju, kas iespējota tikai iekšējiem apļiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4495">Used to measure performance, only enabled for internal rings.</span></span> 



#### <a name="officewordfilesaveactcmdgosubsaveas"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4496">Office.Word.FileSave.ActCmdGosubSaveAs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4496">Office.Word.FileSave.ActCmdGosubSaveAs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4497">Šis notikums norāda, ka lietotājs saglabā izmaiņas jaunā dokumentā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4497">This event indicates that a user is saving their changes to a new document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4498">Notikums pārrauga jauna dokumenta saglabāšanas pareizu darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4498">The event monitors whether saving to a new document is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4499">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4499">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfilesavesaveassavefile"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4608">Office.Word.FileSave.SaveAsSaveFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4608">Office.Word.FileSave.SaveAsSaveFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4609">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word saglabā dokumentu jaunā dokumentā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4609">This event indicates Office Word saves a document into a new document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4610">Tādējādi Microsoft var noteikt darbības “saglabāt kā” kļūdas, kam ir būtiska nozīme, lai novērstu dokumenta datu zudumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4610">It allows Microsoft to detect errors in save-as which is important to avoid document data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4611">Notikums pārrauga, vai dokumenta saglabāšana darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4611">The event monitors whether save-as is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4612">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4612">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4613">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4613">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4614">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** — norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4614">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4615">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4615">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4616">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** — norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā mērķa dokumentam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4616">**Data_AddDocTelemResDst** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event for the destination document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4617">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4617">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4618">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** — norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā avota dokumentam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4618">**Data_AddDocTelemResSrc** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event for the source document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4619">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4619">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4620">**Data_detachedDuration** — cik ilgi darbība bija atdalīta no pavediena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4620">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4621">**Data_Doc_AccessMode —** dokuments ir tikai lasāms/rediģējams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4621">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4622">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4622">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordworddocumentdirtyflagchanged"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4733">Office.Word.Word.DocumentDirtyFlagChanged</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4733">Office.Word.Word.DocumentDirtyFlagChanged</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4734">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word rediģē dokumentu, kas dokumenta iekšējo stāvokli padara "netīru".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4734">This event indicates Office Word edits a document which changes the document internal state into "dirty".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4735">Tas ļauj Microsoft novērtēt dokumenta rediģēšanas līdzekļa darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4735">It allows Microsoft to evaluate the feature health of edit-document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4736">Notikums ir lietotāja veikto rediģējumu periodiskais kontrolziņojums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4736">The event is a heartbeat of user edits.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4737">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4737">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4738">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4738">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4739">**Data\_CollectionTime —** notikuma laikspiedols</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4739">**Data\_CollectionTime-** Timestamp of the event</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4740">**Data\_DocumentLocation —** dokumenta atrašanās vietas tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4740">**Data\_DocumentLocation-** type of the document location</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4741">**Data\_DocumentLocationDetails —** dokumenta atrašanās vietas apakštips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4741">**Data\_DocumentLocationDetails-** Sub-type of the document location</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4742">**Data\_FAlwaysSaveEnabled —** norāda, vai ir iespējota iespēja vienmēr saglabāt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4742">**Data\_FAlwaysSaveEnabled-** Indicates whether always-save was enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4743">**Data\_FirstEditTime —** pirmās rediģēšanas laikspiedols</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4743">**Data\_FirstEditTime-** Timestamp of first edit</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4744">**Data\_NumberCoAuthors —** līdzautoru skaits, kuri sesijā rediģē dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4744">**Data\_NumberCoAuthors-** Number of coauthors editing the document during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4745">**Data\_NumberOfTimesDocumentDirtied —** dokumentā veikto rediģējumu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4745">**Data\_NumberOfTimesDocumentDirtied-** Number of edits made to the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4746">**Data\_Pdod —** dokumenta identifikators Office Word procesā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4746">**Data\_Pdod-** Document identifier in Office Word process</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4747">**Data\_UrlHash —** dokumenta ceļa jaukšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4747">**Data\_UrlHash-** Hash of the document path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4748">**Data\_ViewKind —** Word skata tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4748">**Data\_ViewKind-** Type of Word view</span></span>
