<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4775">Tiek apkopots, kad lietotājs mēģina atvērt ar IRM aizsargātu dokumentu vai lietot IRM aizsardzību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4775">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4776">Tas satur informāciju, kas ir nepieciešama pareizai tādu problēmu izmeklēšanai un diagnosticēšanai, kas notiek licenču parsēšanas darbības laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4776">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when parsing licenses operation is performed.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4777">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4777">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4778">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** — klienta hierarhija, kas norāda, ka lietojumprogramma darbojas ražošanas vidē vai izstrādātāja vidē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4778">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4779">**AppInfo.Name** — lietojumprogrammas nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4779">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4780">**AppInfo.Version** — lietojumprogrammas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4780">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4781">**iKey** — reģistrētāja servera ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4781">**iKey** - Logger server Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4782">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** — scenārija ID, ko nodrošina lietojumprogramma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4782">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** - Scenario Id provided by the application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4783">**RMS.Duration** — kopējais laiks darbības veikšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4783">**RMS.Duration** - Total time for the operation to complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4784">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** — kopējais patērētais laiks mīnus ārējās operācijas, piemēram, tīkla latentums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4784">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** - Total time minus external operations consumed, such as network latency.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4785">**RMS.ErrorCode** — atgrieztais kļūdas kods, ja tāds ir, no darbības</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4785">**RMS.ErrorCode** - The error code returned if any from the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4786">**RMS.HttpCall** — norāda, vai ir HTTP operācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4786">**RMS.HttpCall** - indicate if there is HTTP operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4787">**RMS.LicenseFormat** — licences formāts: XrML vai JSON</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4787">**RMS.LicenseFormat** - The license Format: Xrml or Json</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4788">**RMS.Result** — darbība sekmīga vai neizdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4788">**RMS.Result** - Success or fail of the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4789">**RMS.ScenarioId** — scenārija ID, ko definē tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma klients</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4789">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario Id defined by Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4790">**RMS.SDKVersion** — tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma klienta versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4790">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4791">**RMS.ServerType** — tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma servera tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4791">**RMS.ServerType** - The type of Rights Management Service Server</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4792">**RMS.StatusCode** — darbības rezultāta statusa kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4792">**RMS.StatusCode** - Status code of the operation result</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4793">**RMS.VerifyCertChainDuration** — laiks, lai verificētu sertifikātu ķēdi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4793">**RMS.VerifyCertChainDuration** - Duration time to verify certificate chain</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4794">**RMS.VerifySignatureDuration** — laiks, lai verificētu parakstu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4794">**RMS.VerifySignatureDuration** - Duration time to verify signature</span></span>

#### <a name="readconversation"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4795">read.conversation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4795">read.conversation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4796">Izmanto, lai uzraudzītu iespējamo negatīvu ietekmi uz e-pasta ziņojumu renderēšanas darbspēju un veiktspēju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4796">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on the health and performance of rendering an email message</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4797">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4797">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4798">**above_40fps** — virs 40 kadriem sekundē renderēto kadru skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4798">**above_40fps** - count of frames rendered above 40fps</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4799">**above_50fps** — virs 50 kadriem sekundē renderēto kadru skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4799">**above_50fps** - count of frames rendered above 50fps</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4800">**above_55fps** — virs 55 kadriem sekundē renderēto kadru skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4800">**above_55fps** - count of frames rendered above 55fps</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4801">**adal_id** — konta aktīvās direktorijas autentifikācijas ID, unikāls identifikators Microsoft autentifikācijas sistēmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4801">**adal_id** - the account's active directory authentication ID, a unique identifier in the Microsoft authentication system</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4802">**component_name** — tā komponenta/skata nosaukums, kas ir aktīvs filtrēšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4802">**component_name** - the name of the component/view which is active during the filtering</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4803">**event_mode** — vieta lietojumprogrammā, kuru lietotājs ir ievadījis sarunā (grupas vai cits)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4803">**event_mode** - the place in the app that the user entered the conversation (groups or other)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4804">**internet_message_id** — izsekošanas ID jaunākajam ziņojumam sarunā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4804">**internet_message_id** - a tracking ID for the most recent message in the conversation</span></span>
      
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4805">**orientation** — ekrāna orientācija (portrets vai ainava) notikuma laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4805">**orientation** - the screen orientation at the time of the even (portrait or landscape)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4806">**recent_message_id** — sarunā jaunāka ziņojuma ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4806">**recent_message_id** - the ID of the most recent message in the conversation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4807">**suggested_reply_state** — šai sarunai ieteikto atbilžu stāvoklis (nav pieejams, pieejams, parādīts, izmantots vai atmests)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4807">**suggested_reply_state** - the state of suggested replies for this conversation (unavailable, available, shown, used, or discarded)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4808">**suggested_reply_types** — norāda šai sarunai ieteikto/izmantoto atbilžu tipu un skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4808">**suggested_reply_types** - indicates type and count of suggested reply shown/used for this conversation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4809">Tā ir vārdnīca.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4809">It’s a dictionary.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4810">Piemēram, {text: 2, send_avail: 1}.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4810">For example {text: 2, send_avail: 1}.</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4811">**total_count** — kopējais komponenta attēloto kadru skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4811">**total_count** - total frames displayed by the component</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4812">**view_duration** — kopējais laiks, ko komponenta skatīšanai veltīja lietotājs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4812">**view_duration** - how long the component was viewed by the user</span></span>

#### <a name="saveattempt"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4813">save.attempt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4813">save.attempt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4814">Ļauj mums noteikt problēmu, kuru iemesls ir lietotāju mēģinājumi saglabāt failu, ietekmi, izvērtējot ietekmēto sesiju skaitu un nosakot, vai šīm sesijām ir kopīgas pazīmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4814">Allows us to identify the impact of issues caused by users attempting to save a file by evaluating the number of sessions impacted and if there are common features of those sessions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4815">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4815">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4816">**file_type** — faila tips, ko lietotājs mēģināja saglabāt (piemēram,. doc)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4816">**file_type** - The type of file the user tried to save (such as .doc)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4817">**origin** — norāda faila saglabāšanas mēģinājuma izcelsmi (piemēram, no e-pasta), ļaujot mums noteikt ar failu saglabāšanu konkrētajā vietā lietojumprogrammā saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4817">**origin** - Where the file save attempt originated from (such as from an email) so we can detect issues associated with saving a file from a specific place in the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4818">**token_type** — faila saglabāšanai veiktās konta autentifikācijas marķiera veids, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar faila saglabāšanu saistītās autentifikācijas problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4818">**token_type** - the type of token used to authenticate the account in order to save the file to help us detect authentication issues associated with saving a file</span></span>

#### <a name="searchsubtabselected"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4819">search.subtab.selected</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4819">search.subtab.selected</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4820">Pasākums apkopo izcelsmes punktus, lai atrastu iemeslu, kāpēc tika atlasīta meklēšanas apakšcilne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4820">The event collects origin points for the reason a search sub_tab was selected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4821">Apakšcilnes atrodas zem primārās lietojumprogrammas meklēšanas joslas, lai filtrētu datus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4821">The sub tabs sit under the primary app search bar to filter data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4822">Šis notikums mums ļauj izsekot vienuma veida atzīmes (viss, pasts, kontakti un kalendārs), ko lietotāji izmanto meklēšanas laikā, lai mēs varētu nodrošināt atbilstošu meklēšanas filtru mehānismu darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4822">This event lets us track the entity type pills (all, mail, contacts and calendar) that users are using when they do their searches so we can ensure the search filter mechanisms are working properly.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4823">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4823">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4824">**properties_general** — vispārīgi rekvizīti, kurus apkopo visi Aria notikumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4824">**properties_general** -The general properties that all Aria event is collecting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4825">**selected_reason** — tipa atzīmes atlases iemesls, kas var būt viena no šekojošajām vērtībām (glifs ir ikona): tap_on_header, tap_on_see_all, enter_search_mode, mail_glyph, calendar_glyph.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4825">**selected_reason** - The cause of the type pill getting selected, which could be one of the following values (glyph being an icon): tap_on_header, tap_on_see_all, enter_search_mode, mail_glyph, calendar_glyph.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4826">**subtab_type** — tipa atzīme, kas tika atlasīta un varētu būt viena no šīm četrām vērtībām: viss, pasts, kontaktpersona, notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4826">**subtab_type** - The type pill that got selected, which could be one of these four values: all, mail, contact, event.</span></span>

#### <a name="sendmessage"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4827">send.message</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4827">send.message</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4828">Izmanto, lai uzraudzītu iespējamo negatīvo ietekmi uz e-pasta ziņojumu sūtīšanas veiktspēju un darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4828">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on the performance and health of sending email messages.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4829">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4829">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4830">**account** — izseko kontam, kas veica darbību</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4830">**account** - tracks the account which performed the action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4831">**compose_duration** — izseko kopējam laikam, ko lietotājs veltīja ziņojuma sastādīšanai, tai skaitā vairākas melnrakstu sesijas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4831">**compose_duration** - tracks the total time user took to compose the message including multiple drafts session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4832">**draft_message_id** — izseko nosūtāmā ziņojuma sastādīšanas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4832">**draft_message_id** - tracks the compose message ID of the message being sent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4833">**event_mode** — izseko notikuma režīmam, ja attiecināms uz ziņojumu (“grupas” vai “cits”)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4833">**event_mode** - tracks the event mode if applicable to the message, ("groups" or "other")</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4834">**has_attachment** — norāda, vai ziņojumam ir pielikumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4834">**has_attachment** - indicates whether message has any attachments</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4835">**has_mip_label** — norāda, vai ziņojums tika apzīmogots ar MIP etiķeti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4835">**has_mip_label** - indicates whether a MIP label was stamped on the message or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4836">**is_group_escalation** — norāda, vai šis ir grupas eskalēts ziņojums; “eskalēts ziņojums” ir ziņojums, kas nosūtīts uz lietotāja pastkasti eskalācijas dēļ (abonējis grupu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4836">**is_group_escalation** - is this a group escalated message, "escalated message" is a message that was sent to the user's mailbox because of an escalation (subscribed to group)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4837">**is_groups** — izseko, vai nosūtītais ziņojums ir grupas ziņojums vai nav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4837">**is_groups** - track whether message sent is a groups message or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4838">**key_stroke_count** — seko taustiņsitienu skaitam nosūtāmajā ziņojumā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4838">**key_stroke_count** - tracks the keystrokes count for the message that is being sent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4839">**message_id** — izseko ziņojuma ID, uz kuru tiek atbildēts/kas tiek pārsūtīts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4839">**message_id** - tracks the message ID being replied/forwarded</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4840">**origin** — norāda, kur tika sākta sastādīšana, piemēram, jauns, atbilde, ātrā atbilde utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4840">**origin** - indicates where compose was initiated, i.e. new, reply, quick reply etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4841">**send_draft_origin** — norāda, kur tika sākta sūtīšana, piemēram, rakstīt vai ātrā atbilde utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4841">**send_draft_origin** - indicates where send was initiated, i.e. compose or quick reply</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4842">**smart_compose_model_version** — seko izmantojamā viedās sastādīšanas modeļa versijai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4842">**smart_compose_model_version** - tracks which version of smart compose model is being used</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4843">**source_inbox** — norāda avota iesūtnes tipu atsauces ziņojumam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4843">**source_inbox** - indicates source inbox type for reference message,</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4844">**suggested_reply_state** — fiksē ieteiktās atbildes šim nosūtītajam e-pasta ziņojumam stāvokli, piem., nav pieejams, pieejams, parādīts, izmantots vai atmests.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4844">**suggested_reply_state** - capturing suggested reply state i.e., unavailable, available, shown, used, discarded for this sent mail</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4845">**suggested_reply_types** — norāda šim e-pasta ziņojumam ieteikto/izmantoto atbilžu tipu un skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4845">**suggested_reply_types** - indicates type and count of suggested reply shown/used for this sent email.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4846">Tā ir vārdnīca.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4846">It’s a dictionary.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4847">Piemēram, {text: 2, send_avail: 1}.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4847">For example {text: 2,  send_avail: 1}.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4848">**suggestions_requested** — norāda pieprasīto viedo sastādīšanas ieteikumu skaitu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4848">**suggestions_requested** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions requested</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4849">**suggestions_results** — viedā sastādīšanas ieteikuma rezultāts, t.i.,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4849">**suggestions_results** - smart compose suggestions’ result, i.e</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4850">pieņemts, noraidīts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4850">accepted, rejected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4851">**suggestions_requested** — norāda, cik daudz viedo sastādīšanas ieteikumu atgriezts no servera</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4851">**suggestions_returned** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions returned from server</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4852">**suggestions_requested** — norāda, cik daudz viedo sastādīšanas ieteikumu tika parādīts lietotājam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4852">**suggestions_shown** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions shown to the user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4853">**thread_id** — norāda sarunas, uz kuru tiek atbildēts/kas tiek pārsūtīta, pavediena ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4853">**thread_id** - indicates thread ID of the conversation being replied/forwarded</span></span>

#### <a name="session"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4854">session</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4854">session</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4855">Ļauj mums atklāt un novērst situācijas, kurās mēs pārmērīgi izmantojam jūsu ierīces akumulatoru, kā arī palīdz mums noteikt šādu situāciju iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4855">Allows us to detect and fix situations where we are using up too much of your device's battery and helps us identify what could be the cause.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4856">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4856">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4857">**battery_level** — norāda jūsu ierīces akumulatora uzlādes līmeni, lai palīdzētu mums noteikt, vai mūsu lietojumprogramma negatīvi ietekmē jūsu ierīces akumulatora uzlādes līmeni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4857">**battery_level** - tells us the battery level on the device to help us detect when our app is causing a negative impact on your device's battery level</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4858">**has_hx** — norāda, vai konts izmanto jauno sinhronizācijas pakalpojumu, lai palīdzētu noteikt mūsu sinhronizācijas pakalpojuma radītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4858">**has_hx** - Tells us the account is using our new sync service to help us detect issues caused by our sync service</span></span>

#### <a name="settingsaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4859">settings.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4859">settings.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4860">Šis notikums apkopo iestatījumu konfigurācijas informāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4860">This event collects the configuration information in settings.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4861">Šie dati ļauj noteikt situācijas, kad ir iespējami negatīva ietekme uz lietotāja spēju konfigurēt lietojumprogrammas iestatījumus, piemēram, paziņojumu iestatījumu, primāro pasta kontu un e-pasta paraksta konfigurēšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4861">The data allows us to detect situations where there is possible negative impact on the users’ ability configure app settings, such as notification settings, primary mail account, and configuring the email signature.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4862">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4862">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4863">**account_order_changed** — ļauj pārbaudīt, vai jūs mainījāt savu kontu secību, lai nodrošinātu pareizu šīs konfigurācijas darbību</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4863">**account_order_changed** - To check if you changed the order of your accounts to make sure this configuration works properly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4864">**action** — iespējamās iestatījumos veicamās darbības, piemēram, konta dzēšana, palīdz mums atklāt problēmas un izvairīties no negatīvas ietekmes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4864">**action** - possible actions taken in settings, such as deleting an account to help us diagnose issues and ensure no negative impact</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4865">**auth_type** — konta izmantotais autentifikācijas tips, lai mēs varētu saprast, kuru aizmugursistēmas slāni mēs izmantojam problēmu diagnostikai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4865">**auth_type** - The authentication type being used by the account, so we understand which backend sync layer we are using to help us diagnose issues</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4866">**changed_folder** — reģistrē, vai mape ir mainīta, lai palīdzētu mums diagnosticēt problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4866">**changed_folder** - Capturing whether a folder was changed to help us diagnose issues.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4867">**delete_scope** — konta dzēšanas laikā norāda, vai jūs dzēšat kontu tikai šajā ierīcē vai visās ierīcēs ar Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4867">**delete_scope** - During an account deletion, whether you deleted the account from this device or from all devices with Outlook.</span></span>  

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4868">**enabled_state** — norāda, vai jūsu automātiskās atbildes, kontaktpersonu saglabāšanas un ārējo attēlu saglabāšanas iestatījumi ir konfigurēti pareizi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4868">**enabled_state** - Whether your auto reply, save contacts, and block external images settings are configured correctly</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4871">**server_type** — līdzīgs auth_type, norāda jūsu konta veidu labākai problēmas noteikšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4871">**server_type** - Similar to auth_type, it tells us which type of account you have to help us diagnose issues better.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4872">Piemēri: Office365, Gmail, Outlook</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4872">Examples: Office365, Gmail, Outlook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4873">**setting_properties** — izseko rekvizīta saistību ar iestatīšanas darbību saskaņā ar tālāk norādīto:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4873">**setting_properties** - Tracks properties relation to setting action detailed below:</span></span> 
   - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4874">**alternate_app_icon_setting** — atlasītā alternatīvā programmas ikona (gaiša, tumša)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4874">**alternate_app_icon_setting** - the selected alternate app icon (light, dark)</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4875">**auth_type** — norāda aizmugursistēmas autentifikācijas tipu, ļaujot mums noskaidrot, vai pastāv problēma ar konkrēto konta veidu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4875">**auth_type** - indicates the back-end authentication type allowing us to know if there is an issue with a particular account type</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4876">**badge_count_state** — norāda, kāda veida žetonu skaitīšanu pieprasīja lietotājs, piemēram, nav žetonu, tikai iesūtnei utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4876">**badge_count_state** - indicates what type of badge count the user has asked for I.e. no badges, focused inbox only, etc.</span></span>

   - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4878">**delete_scope** — seko, vai šī darbība bija saistīta ar dzēšanu tikai šajā ierīcē vai visās ierīcēs, ja attiecināms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4878">**delete_scope** - tracks whether this action was related to deleting someone just on this device or on all devices, if applicable.</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4879">**enabled_state** — norāda, vai ir iespējots ar darbību saistītais stāvoklis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4879">**enabled_state** - whether state related to the action is enabled</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4880">**in_app_language** — atlasītā programmas valoda, virknes tips (noklusējums, en-US, fa, ru utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4880">**in_app_language** - the selected in-app language, string type (default, en-US, fa, ru etc.)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4881">**notification_action_setting** — norāda detalizētu informāciju par ar šo darbību saistīto paziņojumu iestatījumiem, ja attiecināms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4881">**notification_action_setting** - indicates the details of, if applicable, notification action settings related to this action</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4882">**notification_action** — norāda, ko lietotājs mēģināja izdarīt, piemēram, atzīmēt ar karodziņu, dzēst, arhivēt; ļauj mums noteikt, kādu ziņojuma darbību lietotājs vēlējās veikt ar paziņojumu, un, vai šī darbība izdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4882">**notification_action** - indicates what the user was trying to do, I.e. flag, delete, archive, it allows us to determine what message action the user wanted to perform on the notification and if the action failed or not.</span></span> 
    - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4883">**notification_action_number** — norāda, kurš darbības numurs (divas no trim darbībām ir iespējams pielāgot) tika piešķirts paziņojuma darbībai, piemēram, pirmā darbība, otrā darbība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4883">**notification_action_number** - indicates which action number (two of three actions are customizable) was assigned a notification action, i.e. action one, action two.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4884">Ļauj mums noteikt, vai pastāv problēmas ar konkrēto darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4884">This allows us to determine if there is a problem with a particular action.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4885">**notification_state** — norāda, kāda veida žetonu skaitīšanu pieprasīja lietotājs, piemēram, nav žetonu, tikai iesūtnei utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4885">**notification_state** - indicates what type of badge count the user has asked for i.e. no badges, focused inbox only, etc.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4886">**server_type** — norāda aizmugursistēmas autentifikācijas tipu, ļaujot mums noskaidrot, vai pastāv problēma ar konkrēto servera veidu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4886">**server_type** - indicates the back-end server type allowing us to know if there is an issue with a particular server type</span></span>

   - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4888">**swipe_setting** — norāda uz ar šo darbību saistītās pavilkšanas iestatījumu detalizētu informāciju, ja attiecināms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4888">**swipe_setting** - indicates the details of, if applicable, swipe settings related to this action</span></span>
     - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4889">**swipe_action** — norāda, ko lietotājs mēģināja izdarīt, piemēram, atzīmēt ar karodziņu, dzēst, arhivēt; ļauj mums noteikt, kādu darbību lietotājs vēlējās veikt, un, vai darbība izdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4889">**swipe_action** - indicates what the user was trying to do, i.e. flag, delete, archive, it allows us to determine what action the user wanted and if the action failed or not.</span></span> 
     - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4890">**swipe_direction** — norāda, kādā virzienā lietotājs iestatīja pavilkšanu, t.i., no kreisās uz labo vai no labās uz kreiso pusi. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4890">**swipe_direction** - indicates which way the user set up the swipe to be, i.e. left to right or right to left.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4891">Ļauj mums noteikt, vai pastāv problēmas ar konkrētu pavilkšanas virzienu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4891">This allows us to determine if there is a problem with a particular swipe direction.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4892">**ui_mode_setting** — atlasītais UI režīms (tumšs, gaišs, sistēmas noklusējuma, zems akumulatora uzlādes līmenis utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4892">**ui_mode_setting** - the selected UI mode (dark, light, system default, low battery etc.)</span></span>

#### <a name="sidebaraction"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4897">sidebar.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4897">sidebar.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4898">Ļauj mums noteikt situācijas, kad ir iespējami negatīva ietekme uz jūsu iespēju konfigurēt lietojumprogrammas iestatījumus, piemēram, paziņojumu iestatījumus, primāro pasta kontu un e-pasta paraksta konfigurēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4898">Allows us to detect situations where there is possible negative impact on your ability configure your app settings, such as your notification settings, your primary mail account, and configuring your mail signature.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4899">Outlook Mobile datu lauki, kas šim notikumam ir kopīgi iOS un Android:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4899">Data fields that are common for Outlook Mobile for this event on iOS and Android:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4900">**Account** — izseko ar notikumu saistītajam kontam un tā datiem; šajos datos izsekotās vērtības ir norādītas vispārīgajā lauka dokumentācijā *[Šis lauks ir dzēsts jaunākajos Office būvējumos, taču, iespējams, joprojām tiek rādīts vecākos būvējumos.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4900">**Account** - tracks the account and its data associated with the event, values tracked in this data are in the common om field documentation *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4901">**action** — izseko sānu joslas darbības tipam, piemēram, noraidīts, atlasīta palīdzības poga, pasta sānu josla utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4901">**action** - tracks the type of side bar action occurred, i.e. dismissed, help button selected, mail side bar, etc.,</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4902">**from_favorites** — izseko, vai darbība ir izcēlusies no izlasē esoša vienuma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4902">**from_favorites** - tracks if the action is coming from an item in favorites</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4903">**mail_folder_type** — norāda mapes veidu, kas tika atlasīts sānu joslas darbības laikā, ja attiecināms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4903">**mail_folder_type** - what type of folder was selected during the side bar action, if any.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4904">**sidebar_type** — izseko ar šo notikumu saistītās sānu joslas tipu, piemēram, e-pasts vai kalendārs, lai palīdzētu mums nodrošināt pareizu navigācijas no izlases iestatījuma darbību</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4904">**sidebar_type** - tracks the type of side bar associated with this event, i.e. mail or calendar to helps us ensure the navigation from the favorites setting works properly</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4905">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4905">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4906">**account_type** — norāda konta autentifikācijas tipu, piemēram, Gmail, Outlook utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4906">**account_type** - indicates what authentication type the account is i.e. Gmail, outlook, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4907">**account_has_groups** — palīdz mums pārliecināties par to, vai grupas ir konfigurētas pareizi, ja kontam tādas ir</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4907">**account_has_groups** - Helps us make sure if the account has groups, they are configured correctly</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4908">**calendar_accounts_count** — jūsu kalendāra kontu skaits, lai palīdzētu mums pārliecināties par to, ka jūsu kalendāra konti ir konfigurēti pareizi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4908">**calendar_accounts_count** - Number of calendar accounts you have to help us make sure your calendar accounts are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4909">**calendar_apps_count** — jūsu kalendāra lietojumprogrammu skaits, lai palīdzētu mums pārliecināties par to, ka jūs interesējošās kalendāra lietojumprogrammas ir konfigurētas pareizi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4909">**calendar_apps_count** - Number of calendar apps you have to help us make sure your interesting calendar apps are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4910">**calendar_type** — jūsu kalendāra tips (primārais kalendārs, grupas kalendārs utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4910">**calendar_type** - The type of calendar you have (Primary calendar, Group calendar, etc.)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4911">**has_favorite_folders** — palīdz mums pārliecināties par to, ka izlases mapes ir konfigurētas pareizi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4911">**has_favorite_folders** - Helps us make sure favorite folders are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4912">**has_favorite_people** — palīdz mums pārliecināties par to, ka izlases personas/kontaktpersonas ir konfigurētas pareizi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4912">**has_favorite_people** - Helps us make sure favorite people/contacts are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4913">**has_group_calendar** — palīdz mums pārliecināties par to, ka jūsu grupu kalendāri ir konfigurēti pareizi, ja tādi ir</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4913">**has_group_calendar** - Helps us make sure if you have group calendars, they are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4914">**has_group_calendar_account** — palīdz mums pārliecināties par to, ka jūsu grupu kalendāri ir konfigurēti pareizi, ja tādi ir</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4914">**has_group_calendar_account** - Helps us make sure if you have group calendars, they are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4915">**has_group_toggled** — ja jūs pārslēdzāt grupu kalendārus, palīdz mums pārliecināties par to, ka šis iestatījums ir konfigurēts pareizi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4915">**has_group_toggled** - Helps us make sure if you have toggled group calendars, this setting is configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4916">**interesting_calendars_accounts_count** — jūsu interesējošo kalendāra kontu skaits, kas palīdz mums pārliecināties par to, ka jūsu interesējošo kalendāru konti ir konfigurēti pareizi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4916">**interesting_calendars_accounts_count** - Number of interesting calendar accounts you have to help us make sure your interesting calendar accounts are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4917">**mail_accounts_count** — kopējais e-pasta kontu skaits sānu joslā, lai pārliecinātos par pareizu konfigurāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4917">**mail_accounts_count** - The total number of mail accounts in the sidebar to make sure this is configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4918">**mail_folder_type** — mapes tips, kuru lietotājs nospieda, lai pārliecinātos, ka tā ir konfigurēta pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4918">**mail_folder_type** - The type of folder the user tapped on to make sure it's configured correctly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4919">Var iekļaut dzēsto ziņojumu mapi, mēstuļu mapi vai nosūtīto ziņojumu mapi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4919">This could include Deleted folder, Spam, or your Sent folder.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4920">**mail_inbox_unread_count** — palīdz mums pārliecināties par to, ka nelasīto ziņojumu skaits tiek ir konfigurēts un tiek parādīts pareizi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4920">**mail_inbox_unread_count** - Helps us ensure the unread count is displayed and configured accurately</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4921">**mail_subfolder_depth** — palīdz mums nodrošināt sekmīgu lietotāja e-pasta apakšmapju konfigurācijas parādīšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4921">**mail_subfolder_depth** - Helps us ensure we can successfully display a user's mail subfolder configurations</span></span>

#### <a name="storeop"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4922">StoreOp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4922">StoreOp</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4923">Tiek apkopots, kad lietotājs mēģina atvērt ar IRM aizsargātu dokumentu vai lietot IRM aizsardzību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4923">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4924">Tas satur informāciju, kas ir nepieciešama pareizai tādu problēmu izmeklēšanai un diagnosticēšanai, kas notiek tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma licences saglabāšanas darbības laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4924">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when Rights Management Service license store operation is performed.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4925">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4925">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4926">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** — klienta hierarhija, kas norāda, ka lietojumprogramma darbojas ražošanas vidē vai izstrādātāja vidē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4926">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4927">**AppInfo.Name** — lietojumprogrammas nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4927">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4928">**AppInfo.Version** — lietojumprogrammas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4928">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4929">**iKey** — pieteikšanās pakalpojuma servera ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4929">**iKey** - Logging service server Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4930">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** — scenārija ID, ko nodrošina lietojumprogramma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4930">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** - Scenario Id provided by the application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4931">**RMS.ContentId** — satura ID lietotāja licencē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4931">**RMS.ContentId** - Content Id in End User License</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4932">**RMS.Duration** — kopējais laiks API izsaukuma veikšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4932">**RMS.Duration** - Total time for API call to complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4933">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** — kopējais patērētais laiks mīnus ārējās operācijas, piemēram, tīkla latentums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4933">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** - Total time minus external operations consumed, such as network latency.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4934">**RMS.ErrorCode** — atgrieztais kļūdas kods, ja tāds ir, no darbības</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4934">**RMS.ErrorCode** - The error code returned if any from the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4935">**RMS.HttpCall** — norāda, vai ir HTTP operācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4935">**RMS.HttpCall** - indicate if there is HTTP operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4936">**RMS.LicenseFormat** — licences formāts: XrML vai JSON</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4936">**RMS.LicenseFormat** - The license Format: Xrml or Json</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4937">**RMS.OperationName** — darbības nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4937">**RMS.OperationName** - Operation name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4938">**RMS.Result** — darbība sekmīga vai neizdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4938">**RMS.Result** - Success or fail of the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4939">**RMS.ScenarioId** — scenārija ID, ko definē tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma klients</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4939">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario Id defined by Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4940">**RMS.SDKVersion** — tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma klienta versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4940">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4941">**RMS.ServerType** — tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma servera tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4941">**RMS.ServerType** - The type of Rights Management Service Server</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4942">**RMS.StatusCode** — darbības rezultāta statusa kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4942">**RMS.StatusCode** - Status code of the operation result</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4943">**RMS.Url** — tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma servera vietrādis URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4943">**RMS.Url** - The URL of Rights Management Service Server</span></span>

#### <a name="watchappv2"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4944">watchAppV2</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4944">watchAppV2</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4945">Šis notikums ļauj mums atklāt un novērst iespējamās problēmas ar jūsu Apple Watch, piemēram, ziņojumu saņemšana vai atbildēšana uz e-pasta ziņojumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4945">This event allows us to detect and fix possible issues with capabilities on your Apple Watch such as receiving notifications and responding to emails.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4946">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4946">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4947">**app_action** — norāda uz darbībām, kuras lietotājs veica Apple Watch, piemēram, “archive_message”, kas palīdz mums atklāt ar konkrētu darbību saistītas problēmas, piemēram, veiksmīga ziņojumu arhivēšana ar Apple Watch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4947">**app_action** - Tells us the types of action the user took on the Apple watch, such as "archive_message" to help us detect issues related to a specific action such as being unable to successfully archive messages on the Apple Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4948">**is_watch_app_installed** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir instalējis mūsu Apple Watch lietojumprogrammu savā ierīcē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4948">**is_watch_app_installed** - Tells us if the user has installed our Apple Watch app on their device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4949">**is_complication_enabled** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir pievienojis Outlook savam Apple Watch ekrānam, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar Apple Watch ekrāniem saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4949">**is_complication_enabled** - Tells us if the user has added Outlook to their Apple Watch screen to help us detect issues related to Apple Watch screens</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4950">**watch_os** — norāda instalēto Apple Watch operētājsistēmas versiju, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar konkrētām Apple Watch operētājsistēmas versiju saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4950">**watch_os** - Tells us the OS version of the Apple Watch they have installed to help us detect issues related to specific OS versions of the Apple Watch</span></span>


### <a name="application-status-and-boot-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4951">*Lietojumprogrammas statuss un palaišanas apakštips*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4951">*Application status and boot subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4952">Nosaka, vai ir notikuši konkrēti līdzekļu notikumi, piemēram, startēšana vai apturēšana, un vai līdzeklis darbojas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4952">Determination if specific feature events have occurred, such as start or stop, and if feature is running.</span></span>

#### <a name="appstartup"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4953">app.startup</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4953">app.startup</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4954">Šis notikums ļauj mums atklāt un novērst problēmas, ja Outlook palaišana notiek lēni vai nepilnīgi, apgrūtinot mūsu lietotājiem mūsu lietojumprogrammas izmantošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4954">This event lets us detect and fix issues where Outlook is starting slowly or incompletely, making it difficult for users to use our app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4955">Tiek iekļauta informācija par konkrētiem iespējotajiem līdzekļiem un to, cik ilgu laiku aizņēma atsevišķi palaišanas posmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4955">This includes information on the specific features that were enabled and how long parts of the startup took.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4956">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4956">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4957">**attach_base_context_millis** — norāda laiku starp bāzes konteksta palaišanu un OnCreate() palaišanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4957">**attach_base_context_millis** - time between the base Context starting and onCreate() starting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4958">**device_ram_in_mb** — ierīcē pieejamā RAM atmiņa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4958">**device_ram_in_mb** - the RAM available on the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4959">**has_company_portal** — norāda, vai ir instalēta uzņēmuma portāla lietojumprogramma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4959">**has_company_portal** - whether the company portal app is installed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4960">**hx_okhttp_mode** — norāda, vai jaunā e-pasta sinhronizēšanas pakalpojuma komponents izmanto OKHttp, lai nosūtītu un saņemtu HTTP-balstītus tīkla pieprasījumus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4960">**hx_okhttp_mode** - whether the new email syncing service component is using OKHttp for sending and receiving HTTP-based network requests</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4961">**initial_activity_name** — Android darbība, kas palaida lietojumprogrammu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4961">**initial_activity_name** - the Android Activity which launched the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4962">**manufacturer** — ierīces ražotājs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4962">**manufacturer** - the device manufacturer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4963">**model** — ierīces modelis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4963">**model** - the device model</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4964">**on_create_millis** — metodē onCreate() pavadītais laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4964">**on_create_millis** - time taken in the onCreate() method</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4965">**on_resume_millis** — metodē onResume() pavadītais laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4965">**on_resume_millis** - time taken in the onResume() method</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4966">**time_until_attach** — laiks starp klases ielādi un bāzes konteksta palaišanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4966">**time_until_attach** - time between the class loading and the base Context starting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4967">**total_millis** — kopējais laiks no klases ielādes sākuma līdz Android darbības atsākšanas pabeigšanas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4967">**total_millis** - total time from class loading start to Android Activity resume completion</span></span>

#### <a name="boottime"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4968">boot.time</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4968">boot.time</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4969">Šis notikums ļauj mums noteikt, kad notiek kritiskas lietojumprogrammas kļūdas, kas izraisa jūsu lietojumprogrammas avāriju vai nopietnas problēmas, kuru rezultātā jūs redzat tukšas rindas jūsu iesūtnē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4969">This event lets us detect when critical app errors occurred that would cause your app to crash or experience serious issues like causing you to see empty rows in your inbox.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4970">Šis notikums apkopo informāciju, kas ļauj mums kategorizēt un klasificēt problēmas, lai noteiktu problēmu ietekmes pakāpi uz klientiem. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4970">This event collects information that allows us to categorize and classify issues to help prioritize the impact of issues on customers.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4971">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4971">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4972">**black_list_reason** — norāda, vai pastāv iemesls šo datu atmešanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4972">**black_list_reason** - Tells us if there is a reason why we should disregard this data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4973">Daži piemēri iekļauj palaišanu attālinātā paziņojuma dēļ un fona ieneses dēļ.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4973">Some examples include launching due to a remote notification and launching due to a background fetch.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4974">**step_premain** — norāda laiku, kas bija nepieciešams, lai Outlook no brīža, kad lietotājs pieskaras ikonai, pārietu uz step0_main, kas ir “galvenā” šajā dokumentā definētā darbība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4974">**step_premain** – Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the user tapping the icon to step0_main the “main” step defined in this document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4975">**step0_main** — norāda laiku, kas bija nepieciešams Outlook sasniegtu galveno “darbību”, kas ir Apple definēta darbība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4975">**step0_main** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to get to the "main" step, which is a step defined by Apple.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4976">**step1_appWillFinishLaunching** — norāda mums laiku, kas bija nepieciešams Outlook, lai pārietu no “galvenās” darbības līdz “appWillFinishLaunching” darbībai, kas ir Apple definēta darbība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4976">**step1_appWillFinishLaunching** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the "main" step to the "appWillFinishLaunching" step, which is a step defined by Apple.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4977">**step2_appDidFinishLaunching** — norāda mums laiku, kas bija nepieciešams Outlook, lai pārietu no “appWillFinishLaunching” darbības līdz ““appDidFinishLaunching” darbībai, kas ir Apple definēta darbība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4977">**step2_appDidFinishLaunching** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the "appWillFinishLaunching" step to the "appDidFinishLaunching" step, which is a step defined by Apple.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4978">**step3_engineStarted** — norāda mums laiku, ka bija nepieciešams Outlook, lai pārietu no “appDidFinishLaunching” darbības līdz lietojumprogrammas dzinēja palaišanas, kas veic datu uzglabāšanu un sinhronizēšanu. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4978">**step3_engineStarted** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the "appDidFinishLaunching" step to starting the engine of the app, which handles storing and syncing data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4979">**step4_runLoopFirstIdle** — norāda mums laiku, kas bija nepieciešams Outlook, lai pārietu no “engineStarted” darbības līdz brīdim, kad vairs nav jāveic papildu darbi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4979">**step4_runLoopFirstIdle** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the "engineStarted" step to having no additional work to complete.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4980">**total_time** — norāda kopējo laiku, kas bija nepieciešams Outlook, lai pabeigtu sāknēšanas procesu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4980">**total_time** - Tells us the total amount of time it has taken for Outlook to complete the boot process.</span></span>

#### <a name="dnslookupop"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4981">DnsLookupOp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4981">DnsLookupOp</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4982">Tiek apkopots, kad lietotājs mēģina atvērt ar IRM aizsargātu dokumentu vai lietot IRM aizsardzību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4982">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4983">Tas satur informāciju, kas ir nepieciešama pareizai tādu problēmu izmeklēšanai un diagnosticēšanai, kas notiek DNS informācijas uzmeklēšanas darbības laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4983">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when DNS information lookup operation is performed.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4984">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4984">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4985">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** — klienta hierarhija, kas norāda, ka lietojumprogramma darbojas ražošanas vidē vai izstrādātāja vidē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4985">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4986">**AppInfo.Name** — lietojumprogrammas nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4986">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4987">**AppInfo.Version** — lietojumprogrammas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4987">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4988">**iKey** — pieteikšanās pakalpojuma servera ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4988">**iKey** - Logging service server Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4989">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** — scenārija ID, ko nodrošina lietojumprogramma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4989">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** - Scenario Id provided by the application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4990">**RMS.Duration** — kopējais laiks darbības veikšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4990">**RMS.Duration** - Total time for the operation to complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4991">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** — kopējais patērētais laiks mīnus ārējās operācijas, piemēram, tīkla latentums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4991">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** - Total time minus external operations consumed, such as network latency.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4992">**RMS.ErrorCode** — atgrieztais kļūdas kods, ja tāds ir, no darbības</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4992">**RMS.ErrorCode** - The error code returned if any from the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4993">**RMS.HttpCall** — norāda, vai pastāv HTTP operācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4993">**RMS.HttpCall** - indicate if there is http operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4994">**RMS.LicenseFormat** — licences formāts: XrML vai JSON</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4994">**RMS.LicenseFormat** - The license Format: Xrml or Json</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4995">**RMS.NoOfDomainsSearched** — meklēto domēnu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4995">**RMS.NoOfDomainsSearched** - The number of domains searched</span></span>    

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4996">**RMS.NoOfDomainsSkipped** — izlaisto domēnu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4996">**RMS.NoOfDomainsSkipped** - The number of domains skipped</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4997">**RMS.Result** — darbība sekmīga vai neizdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4997">**RMS.Result** - Success or fail of the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4998">**RMS.ScenarioId** — scenārija ID, ko definē tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma klients</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4998">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario Id defined by Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-4999">**RMS.SDKVersion** — tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma klienta versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-4999">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5000">**RMS.ServerType** — tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma servera tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5000">**RMS.ServerType** - The type of Rights Management Service Server</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5001">**RMS.StatusCode** — darbības rezultāta statusa kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5001">**RMS.StatusCode** - Status code of the operation result</span></span>

#### <a name="firstvisible"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5002">first.visible</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5002">first.visible</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5003">Šis notikums ļauj mums atklāt pirmo reizi, kad lietotājs ar nodomu palaiž lietojumprogrammu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5003">This event lets us detect the first time the app is launched intentionally by the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5004">Šis notikums ir nepieciešams, lai nodrošinātu lietojumprogrammas veiksmīgu darbību oriģinālā aprīkojuma ražotāja (OEM) būvējumos. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5004">This event is required to ensure that the app is successfully working in Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM) builds.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5005">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5005">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5006">**is_oem** — izsekošanas lauks, kas norāda uz to, vai lietojumprogramma darbojas OEM variantā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5006">**is_oem** - a field tracking that indicates whether the application is running on an OEM variant</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5007">**is_system_install** — izsekošanas lauks, kas izseko iepriekš instalēta rekvizītu failu esamību, kas norāda, ka šī instalācija ir OEM</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5007">**is_system_install** - a field tracking the presence of a pre-installed property file that should indicate that this install is OEM</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidoffice16bootlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5086">Office.Android.AndroidOffice16BootLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5086">Office.Android.AndroidOffice16BootLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5087">Ir būtiski svarīgs, lai fiksētu lietojumprogrammas veiktspējas rādītāju attiecībā uz lietojumprogrammas atbildes laiku no sāknēšanas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5087">Critical to capture for app performance metric with respect to the response time of the app from the boot.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5088">Microsoft to izmanto, lai apkopotu laiku, kas ir nepieciešams lietojumprogrammai, lai atbildētu, kā arī, lai noteiktu scenārijus, kas varat ietekmēt sāknēšanas laiku Word, Excel vai PowerPoint lietojumprogrammās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5088">Microsoft uses this to collect the time taken for the app to be responsive and also detect scenarios that may impact boot time in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5089">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5089">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5090">**AppLaunchResponsiveTimeInMilliSec** — lietojumprogrammas sāknēšanas atbildes laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5090">**AppLaunchResponsiveTimeInMilliSec** - App launch responsive time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5091">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** — būla, kas norāda, vai lietotne tika aizturēta sāknēšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5091">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** - Boolean to indicate if app was suspended during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5092">**CollectionTime** — notikuma laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5092">**CollectionTime** - Time of event</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5098">Ieraksta informāciju par neparedzētu Office izslēgšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5098">Records information about unexpected shutdowns of Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5099">Tas ļauj mums noteikt produkta avārijas vai, ja tas pārstāj reaģēt, un atrisināt šīs problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5099">This allows us to identify crashes or hangs in the product so that they can be addressed.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5106">**Data\_AppURL —** pievienojumprogrammas URL; reģistrē pilnu URL krātuves pievienojumprogrammām un URL domēnu pievienojumprogrammām, kas nav krātuves pievienojumprogrammas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5106">**Data\_AppURL -** URL of the Add in; Logs full URL for Store Add-ins and URL domain for non-store Add-ins</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5232">**Office.Visio.FileCharacteristicsVisio —** tver faila rekvizītus Visio C2R un Dev16 failu startēšanas laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5232">**Office.Visio.FileCharacteristicsVisio -** Captures file properties at the time of file boot for Visio C2R and Dev16.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5233">Šis notikums palīdz mums kategorizēt un atkļūdot kļūdas saistībā ar dokumentu rekvizītiem, kas savukārt ļauj ātrāk atrast problēmu cēloņus un tos novērst.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5233">This event helps us to categorize and debug errors about document properties, which in turn enables us root cause issues faster and fix it for customer satisfaction.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5234">**Office.Visio.Shared.BootStats —** šis notikums apkopo Visio Win32 lietojumprogrammas startēšanas laiku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5234">**Office.Visio.Shared.BootStats -** This event collects boot time for Visio Win32 app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5235">Tas apkopo dažādus laukus saistībā ar dažādu komponentu startēšanu, piemēram, lentes ielādes laiku un programmas inicializācijas laiku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5235">It collects various fields for boot of various components like Ribbon load time, App Initialization time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5236">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai noteiktu Visio startēšanas izpildi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5236">This event is used to measure Boot perf for Visio.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5237">**Office.Visio.Shared.FileOpen —** šis notikums apkopo failu atvēršanas statistiku programmā Visio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5237">**Office.Visio.Shared.FileOpen -** This event collects File open stats for Visio.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5238">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai pārraudzītu failu sekmīgas/nesekmīgas atvēršanas skaitu, un kartē to ar dažiem rekvizītiem, piemēram, faila lielumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5238">This event is used to monitor file open Success/ Fail rates and maps it with few properties of like file size.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5239">Faila rekvizīti sniedz mums iespēju ātrāk atkļūdot problēmas un uzzināt to cēloņus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5239">File properties enable us debug and root cause issues faster.</span></span>
