#### <a name="officeextensibilitysandboxodpactivationhanging"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5257">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHanging</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5257">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHanging</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5258">Apkopo gadījumus, kad Office programmas palaišana aizņem neparedzēti daudz laika (> 5 sek.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5258">Collects when an Office add-in takes unexpectedly long to launch (>5 sec).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5259">Izmanto, lai atklātu un novērstu problēmas ar Office pievienojumprogrammu palaišanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5259">Used to detect and fix problems with Office add-ins launching.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5260">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5260">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5261">**AppId** — lietojumprogrammas ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5261">**AppId** - ID of the App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5262">**AppInfo** — dati par pievienojumprogrammas veidu (uzdevumrūts vai UILess, vai iegulšanas utt.) un nodrošinātāja veidu (omen, SharePoint, filesystem utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5262">**AppInfo** - data regarding the type of add-in (task pane or UILess or in content etc.) and the provider type (omen, SharePoint, filesystem etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5263">**AppInstanceId** — lietojumprogrammas instances ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5263">**AppInstanceId** - ID of the app instance</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5264">**AssetId** — lietojumprogrammas līdzekļa ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5264">**AssetId** - asset ID of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5265">**IsPreload** — norāda, vai pievienojumprogramma tiek sākotnēji ielādēta fonā, lai uzlabotu aktivizēšanas veiktspēju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5265">**IsPreload** – indicates if the add-in is being preloaded in background for improving activation performance</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5266">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** — aktivēto pievienojumprogrammu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5266">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** - counter of add-ins activated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5267">**RemoterType** — norāda pievienojumprogrammas aktivēšanai izmantotā attālinātāja veidu (uzticams, neuzticams, Win32webView, uzticams UDF utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5267">**RemoterType** - specifies the type of remoter (Trusted, untrusted, Win32webView, Trusted UDF etc.) used to activate the add-in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5268">**StoreType** — lietojumprogrammas izcelsme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5268">**StoreType** - origin of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5269">**TimeForAuth** — autentifikācijai iztērētais laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5269">**TimeForAuth** - time spent on auth</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5270">**TimeForSandbox** — smilškastei iztērētais laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5270">**TimeForSandbox** - time spent on the sandbox</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5271">**TimeForServerCall** — saziņai ar serveri iztērētais laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5271">**TimeForServerCall** - time spent on the server call</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5272">**TotalTime** — iztērētais laiks kopā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5272">**TotalTime** - total time spent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5273">**UsesSharedRuntime** — norāda, vai programma izmanto sharedRuntime.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5273">**UsesSharedRuntime** - indicates if the app uses sharedRuntime or not.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeofficemobileappactivationlaunch"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5274">Office.OfficeMobile.AppActivation.Launch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5274">Office.OfficeMobile.AppActivation.Launch</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5275">Šis notikums identificē pirmās reizes un turpmākās aktivizācijas, izmantojot ārējos trigerus, kas aktivizē programmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5275">This event identifies first time and subsequent activations through external triggers that activate the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5276">Programmu aktivizācija ielādē noteiktas atkarības, kas ir atbildīgas par programmas nevainojamu darbību, un šis notikums ierakstīs, ja tā tiek ielādēta sekmīgi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5276">App activation loads certain dependencies that are responsible for making the app run smoothly and this event will record if it loaded successfully.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5277">Tajā būs arī reģistrēts aktivizēšanas un programmu nolūka avots, kas bija atbildīgs par programmas aktivizēšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5277">It will also record the source of activation and app intent that was responsible for activating the app</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5278">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5278">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5279">**Darbības nosaukums** — vesela skaitļa vērtību kartēšana uz darbības/līdzekļa nosaukumu, kas tiek izsaukts no aktivizācijas punkta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5279">**ActionName** - Integer value mapping to the name of the action/feature which is invoked from the activation point.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5280">**ActivationType** — vesela skaitļa vērtību kartēšana uz aktivizēšanas avotu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5280">**ActivationType** - Integer value mapping to the source of activation</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5281">**IsActionTriggered** — Būla vērtība, kas nosaka, vai darbība tika palaista pēc sekmīgas programmas aktivizēšanas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5281">**IsActionTriggered** - Boolean value determining whether the action got triggered after the successful activation of the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5282">**IsFirstRun** — Būla vērtība, kas nosaka, vai tā bija pirmā programmas izpilde vai turpmākā izpilde.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5282">**IsFirstRun** - Boolean value determining whether it was the first run of the app or a subsequent run.</span></span>
 

#### <a name="officeofficemobilefrefirstrunsetup"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5283">Office.OfficeMobile.FRE.FirstRunSetup</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5283">Office.OfficeMobile.FRE.FirstRunSetup</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5284">Pirmā programmas palaišanas reize pēc instalēšanas aktivizēs šo periodiskā kontrolziņojuma notikumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5284">The first run of the app after installation will trigger this heartbeat event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5285">Tas palīdzēs identificēt programmas iepriekšējo versiju instalācijas un automātiskos atjauninājumus, kā arī ļaus mums identificēt automātisko atjauninājumu kļūdas, tai skaitā bibliotēku ielādes un paplašinājumu/valodas pakotņu lejupielāžu kļūmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5285">It will help identify installs and auto upgrades from older versions of the app and enable us to identify errors in auto-upgrades, including library loads and expansion/language package download failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5286">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5286">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5287">**IsFlightAssigned** — Būla vērtība, kas nosaka, vai lietotājs piedalījās iepriekš piešķirtā lidojuma grupā, kas var aktivizēt noteiktas pieredzes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5287">**IsFlightAssigned** - Boolean value determining if the user was part of any preassigned flight group which can trigger exposure to certain experiences.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5288">**IsFRELoadSuccessful** — vesels skaitlis, kas norāda rezultātu stāvokli</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5288">**IsFRELoadSuccessful** - integer mentioning the result state</span></span>

#### <a name="onenoteappappbootcomplete-previous-name-officeonenoteandroidappappbootcomplete-officeandroidearlytelemetryappbootcomplete"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5289">OneNote.App.AppBootComplete *(iepriekšējais nosaukums)*, Office.OneNote.Android.App.AppBootComplete, Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.AppBootComplete</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5289">OneNote.App.AppBootComplete *(previous name)*, Office.OneNote.Android.App.AppBootComplete, Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.AppBootComplete</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5290">Kritiskais signāls, kas tiek lietots, lai nodrošinātu, ka jaunie lietotāji (Microsoft konts) var sekmīgi palaist un lietot OneNote pirmo reizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5290">The critical signal used to ensure new consumer users (Microsoft Account) can successfully launch and use OneNote for the first time.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5291">Tek izmantota kritiskas regresijas atklāšanai OneNote lietojumprogrammā un pakalpojuma darbspējā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5291">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5292">Ja lietotājiem pirmo reizi neizdodas palaist lietojumprogrammu, tiks aktivizēts kritiskais incidents.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5292">If users can't launch the app for the first time, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5293">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5293">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5294">**ACTIVITY_BOOT_TIME_IN_MS** — aktivitātes izveides pabeigšanai veltītais laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5294">**ACTIVITY_BOOT_TIME_IN_MS** - Time taken to complete Activity creation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5295">**ACTIVITY_NAME** — aktivitātes, kas tiek atvērta pēc sāknēšanas, nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5295">**ACTIVITY_NAME** - Name of the Activity opened when booted</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5296">**ANY_DIALOG_SHOWN** — norāda, vai sāknēšanas laikā tiek rādīts dialoglodziņš</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5296">**ANY_DIALOG_SHOWN** - Indicates if any dialog is shown during boot time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5297">**APP_SUSPEND_DURING_EVENT** — norāda, vai sāknēšana bija paredzēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5297">**APP_SUSPEND_DURING_EVENT** - Indicates if the boot was preempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5298">**APP_THREAD_CREATION_WAIT_TIME_TIME_FOR_APP_THREAD_CREATION** — laiks, kas tika veltīts lietojumprogrammas pavedienu izveidošanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5298">**APP_THREAD_CREATION_WAIT_TIME_TIME_FOR_APP_THREAD_CREATION** - Time taken to create Application threads</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5299">**AVAILABLE_MEMORY_IN_MB** — ierīces kopējā pieejamā atmiņa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5299">**AVAILABLE_MEMORY_IN_MB** - Total memory available in device</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5300">**AVG_SNAPSHOT_POPULATION_TIME** — vidējais laiks, kas veltīts piezīmju grāmatiņas struktūru ienešanai, izmantojot lietojumprogrammu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5300">**AVG_SNAPSHOT_POPULATION_TIME** - Avg. time taken to fetch notebook structures while using the App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5301">**BOOT_END_AT_VIEW** — aktivitātes nosaukuma apakškategorija (skata nosaukums)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5301">**BOOT_END_AT_VIEW** - Sub-category of Activity name (Name of the View)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5302">**BOOT_SNAPSHOTS** — detalizēta informācija par piezīmju grāmatiņas struktūru ienešanu lietojumprogrammā izmantotajam kontam(-iem)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5302">**BOOT_SNAPSHOTS** - Detail of notebook structure fetches for the account(s) used in App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5303">**COREAPP_STARTUP_ACCOUNT_SETUP_STARTUP_ACCOUNT_SETUP** — SSO pieredzes pārbaudei un iniciēšanai nepieciešamais laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5303">**COREAPP_STARTUP_ACCOUNT_SETUP_STARTUP_ACCOUNT_SETUP** - Time taken to check and initiate SSO experience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5304">**CRASH_INTERACTION_DURING_BOOT> 0** — norāda, vai lietojumprogramma avarēja pēdējās sesijas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5304">**CRASH_INTERACTION_DURING_BOOT> 0** - To indicate if the App crashed during last session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5305">**DALVIK_HEAP_LIMIT_IN_MB** — novecojis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5305">**DALVIK_HEAP_LIMIT_IN_MB** - Obsolete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5306">**DELAY_LOAD_STICKY_NOTES** — norāda, vai piezīmju lapiņas ir aizkavētas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5306">**DELAY_LOAD_STICKY_NOTES** - Indicates if the Sticky Notes with delay or not</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5371">Apkopots ikreiz, kad PowerPoint atver failu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5371">Collected whenever PowerPoint opens a file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5372">Satur informāciju par sekmīgām darbībām, kļūmes informāciju, izpildes metriku un pamatinformāciju par failu, tostarp faila formāta tipu un dokumenta metadatus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5372">Contains success information, failure details, performance metrics, and basic details about the file including file format type and document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5373">Šī informācija ir nepieciešama, lai PowerPoint varētu sekmīgi atvērt failus, nepasliktinot izpildi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5373">This information is necessary to ensure PowerPoint can open files successfully with no degradation in performance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5374">Tā ļauj mums diagnosticēt atklātās problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5374">It allows us to diagnose any problems we discover.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5375">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5375">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5376">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult —** vai šim žurnāla ierakstam ir visa nepieciešamā dokumenta telemetrija (Data\_Doc\_\* lauki)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5376">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5377">**Data\_AddDocumentToMruList —** metodes AddDocumentToMruList izpildes laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5377">**Data\_AddDocumentToMruList -** Method AddDocumentToMruList execution duration</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5379">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa pretvīrusu programmatūras skenēšanas tipam (IOAV, AMSI, nav utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5379">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod -** Predefined set of values of type of anti-virus scanned (IOAV, AMSI, None etc.)</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointpptdesktopbootime"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5547">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Desktop.Bootime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5547">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Desktop.Bootime</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5548">Apkopo, kā tiek startēts PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5548">Collecting how PowerPoint is booted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5549">Iekļauta PowerPoint startēšana aizsargātā skatā, asistētas lasīšanas režīmā, no makro, drukāšana, jauns un tukšs dokuments, dokumenta atkopšana, no automatizācijas un, ja tas ir “Click-to-Run”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5549">It includes boot PowerPoint in protected view, in assisted reading mode, from Macro, print, new and blank document, document recovery, from automation and if it is click- to-run.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5550">Tas apkopo arī PowerPoint startēšanas laiku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5550">It also collects how long it takes PowerPoint to boot.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5551">Šie dati ir kritiski svarīgi, lai nodrošinātu PowerPoint sekmīgu startēšanu no dažādiem režīmiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5551">This data is critical to guarantee PowerPoint performs well when booted from different modes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5552">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai fiksētu ilgu startēšanas laiku, atverot PowerPoint no dažādiem režīmiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5552">Microsoft uses this data to catch long booting time when opening PowerPoint from different modes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5553">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5553">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5554">**AssistedReading —** asistētas lasīšanas režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5554">**AssistedReading -** in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5555">**Automation —** no automatizācijas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5555">**Automation -** from automation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5556">**Benchmark —** palaist izpildes kritēriju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5556">**Benchmark -** run performance benchmark</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5557">**Blank —** tukšs dokuments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5557">**Blank -** blank document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5558">**BootTime —** sesijas startēšanas laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5558">**BootTime -** session boot time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5559">**Embedding —** dokumenta iegulšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5559">**Embedding -** embedding document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5560">**IsC2R —** ir “Click-to-Run”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5560">**IsC2R -** is click-to-run</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5561">**IsNew —** jauns dokuments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5561">**IsNew -** new document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5562">**IsOpen —** ir atvērts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5562">**IsOpen -** is open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5563">**Macro1 —** palaist makro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5563">**Macro1 -** run Macro</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5564">**Macro2 —** palaist makro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5564">**Macro2 -** run Macro</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5565">**NonStandardSpaceInCmdLine** — komandrindā ir nestandarta atstarpe</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5565">**NonStandardSpaceInCmdLine** – there is non-standard space in command line</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5566">**Print —** drukāt dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5566">**Print -** print document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5567">**PrintDialog —** drukāt dokumentu ar dialoglodziņu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5567">**PrintDialog -** print document with dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5568">**PrintPrinter —** drukāt dokumentu ar printeri</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5568">**PrintPrinter -** print document with printer</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5569">**ProtectedView —** aizsargātā skatā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5569">**ProtectedView -** in protected view</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5570">**Regserver —** reģistrēt PowerPoint kā COM serveri</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5570">**Regserver -** Register PowerPoint as a COM server</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5571">**Restore —** atjaunot dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5571">**Restore -** restore document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5572">**Show —** rādīt dokumentu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5572">**Show -** show document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5573">**Time —** sesijas laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5573">**Time -** session time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5574">**UnprotectedView —** neaizsargātā skatā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5574">**UnprotectedView -** in unprotected view</span></span>

#### <a name="officesessionidproviderofficeprocesssessionstart"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5620">Office.SessionIdProvider.OfficeProcessSessionStart</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5620">Office.SessionIdProvider.OfficeProcessSessionStart</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5621">Attiecas uz visām Office Windows lietojumprogrammām: win32 un UWP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5621">Applicable to all the Office windows-based applications: win32 and UWP</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5623">**OfficeProcessSessionStart** nosūta pamatinformāciju jaunas Office sesijas sākumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5623">**OfficeProcessSessionStart** sends basic information upon the start of a new Office session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5624">To izmanto, lai saskaitītu unikālās sesijas, kas redzamas konkrētajā ierīcē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5624">This is used to count the number of unique sessions seen on a given device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5625">Tas tiek izmantots kā periodiska kontrolziņojuma notikums, lai pārliecinātos, vai lietojumprogramma darbojas ierīcē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5625">This is used as a heartbeat event to ensure that the application is running on a device or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5626">Turklāt to var izmantot kā kritiski svarīgu signālu par kopējo lietojumprogrammu uzticamību</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5626">In addition, it serves as a critical signal for overall application reliability</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5627">**AppSessionGuid** — tās attiecīgās lietojumprogrammas sesijas identifikators, kuras sākums ir procesa izveides laiks un kas ilgst līdz procesa beigām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5627">**AppSessionGuid** - An identifier of a particular application session starting at process creation time and persisting until process end.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5628">Tas ir formatēts kā standarta 128 bitu GUID, ko veido četras daļas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5628">It is formatted as a standard 128-bit GUID but constructed of 4 parts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5629">Šo četru daļu secība ir: (1) 32 bitu procesa ID (2) 16 bitu sesijas ID (3) 16 bitu palaišanas ID (4) 64 bitu procesa izveides laiks: UTC 100ns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5629">Those four parts in order are (1) 32 bit Process ID (2) 16 bit Session ID (3) 16 bit Boot ID (4) 64 bit Process creation time in UTC 100ns</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5630">**processSessionId** — nejauši ģenerēts GUID, lai noteiktu programmas sesiju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5630">**processSessionId** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5631">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** — konstanta Būla vērtība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5631">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** - Constant boolean value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5632">Vienmēr patiess.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5632">Always true.</span></span>

#### <a name="officesystemsessionhandoff"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5633">Office.System.SessionHandoff</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5633">Office.System.SessionHandoff</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5634">Norāda, ka pašreizējā Office sesija ir nodošanas sesija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5634">Indicates that the current Office session is a handoff session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5635">Tas nozīmē, ka darbs ar lietotāja pieprasījumu, lai atvērtu dokumentu, tiek pārsūtīts uz jau darbojošos instanci tajā pašā programmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5635">This means that handling of a user's request to open a document is being handed off to an already running instance of the same application.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5636">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5636">The following fields are collected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5637">**ParentSessionId** — tās sesijas ID, kas veiks lietotāju pieprasījuma apstrādi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5637">**ParentSessionId** - The ID of the session that will be taking over handling of the users' request.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5647">**SessionID** — nejauši ģenerēts GUID, lai noteiktu programmas sesiju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5647">**SessionID** - Randomly generated GUID to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5657">**childSessionID** — nejauši ģenerēts GUID, lai noteiktu programmas sesiju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5657">**childSessionID** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5664">**Data_AppBootTime** — programmas sāknēšanas ilgums milisekundēs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5664">**Data_AppBootTime** - Duration taken for app to boot, in milliseconds.</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopencmdfilemrupriv"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5670">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenCmdFileMruPriv</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5670">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenCmdFileMruPriv</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5671">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word atver dokumentu no pēdējo lietoto dokumentu saraksta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5671">This event indicates Office Word opens a document from the Most Recent Used (MRU) list.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5672">Tas satur arī kritiski svarīgus faila atvēršanas izpildes datus, un no lietotāja skatpunkta ir programmas startēšanas notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5672">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5673">Notikums pārrauga, vai faila atvēršana no pēdējo lietoto dokumentu saraksta darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5673">The event monitors whether fileopen-from-MRU is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5674">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5674">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5675">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5675">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5676">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** — norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5676">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5677">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5677">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5678">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura uzskatām, ka varēsim atvērt failu, ja tos iegūstam pirms lietotājs vēlas sākt rediģēšanu vai saglabāšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5678">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5679">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura, iespējams, varēsim atvērt failu, taču tam būs nepieciešamas būtiskas koda izmaiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5679">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5680">**Data_BytesSynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), kuram jābūt mūsu rīcībā, pirms varam sākt faila atvēršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5680">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5681">**Data_BytesUnknown**— baitu skaits dokumenta daļās, kuras neplānojam atrast.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5681">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5682">**Data_detachedDuration** — cik ilgi darbība bija atdalīta no pavediena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5682">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5683">**Data_Doc_AccessMode —** dokuments ir tikai lasāms/rediģējams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5683">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read-only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5684">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5684">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5685">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5685">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenffileopenxstzcore"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5737">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenFFileOpenXstzCore</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5737">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenFFileOpenXstzCore</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5738">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word atver dokumentu, uz kura lietotājs veic dubultklikšķi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5738">This event indicates Office Word opens a document who is double clicked by a user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5739">Tas satur arī kritiski svarīgus faila atvēršanas izpildes datus, un no lietotāja skatpunkta ir programmas startēšanas notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5739">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5740">Notikums pārrauga, vai faila atvēršana ar dubultklikšķi darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5740">The event monitors whether file-openfrom-file-double-click is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5741">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5741">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5742">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5742">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5743">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** — norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5743">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5744">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5744">Used for data quality diagnostics</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5745">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura uzskatām, ka varēsim atvērt failu, ja tos iegūstam pirms lietotājs vēlas sākt rediģēšanu vai saglabāšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5745">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5746">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura, iespējams, varēsim atvērt failu, taču tam būs nepieciešamas būtiskas koda izmaiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5746">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5747">**Data_BytesSynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), kuram jābūt mūsu rīcībā, pirms varam sākt faila atvēršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5747">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5748">**Data_BytesUnknown**— baitu skaits dokumenta daļās, kuras neplānojam atrast.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5748">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5749">**Data_detachedDuration** — cik ilgi darbība bija atdalīta no pavediena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5749">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5750">**Data_Doc_AccessMode —** dokuments ir tikai lasāms/rediģējams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5750">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read-only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5751">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5751">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5752">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5752">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5753">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType —** vienības, kas tiek izmantotas inkrementālā dokumenta atvēršanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5753">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5754">**Data_Doc_EdpState —** dokumenta elektronisko datu aizsardzības iestatījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5754">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5755">**Data_Doc_Ext —** dokumenta paplašinājums (docx/xlsb/pptx utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5755">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5756">**Data_Doc_FileFormat —** faila formāta protokola versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5756">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5757">**Data_Doc_Fqdn —** OneDrive vai SharePoint Online domēna nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5757">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenifrinitargs"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5804">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenIfrInitArgs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5804">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenIfrInitArgs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5805">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word atver dokumentu, izmantojot COM aktivizēšanu vai komandrindu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5805">This event indicates Office Word opens a document via COM activation or command line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5806">Tas satur arī kritiski svarīgus faila atvēršanas izpildes datus, un no lietotāja skatpunkta ir programmas startēšanas notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5806">It also contains critical file open performance data, and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5807">Notikums pārrauga, vai faila atvēršana no komandrindas darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5807">The event monitors whether file-open-from-command-line is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5808">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5808">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5809">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5809">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5810">**Data\_AddDocTelemRes —** norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5810">**Data\_AddDocTelemRes -** Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5811">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5811">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5812">**Data\_BytesAsynchronous —** baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura uzskatām, ka varēsim atvērt failu, ja tos iegūstam pirms lietotājs vēlas sākt rediģēšanu vai saglabāšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5812">**Data\_BytesAsynchronous -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5813">**Data\_BytesAsynchronousWithWork —** baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura, iespējams, varēsim atvērt failu, taču tam būs nepieciešamas būtiskas koda izmaiņas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5813">**Data\_BytesAsynchronousWithWork -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5814">**Data\_BytesSynchronous —** baitu skaits (saspiests), kuram jābūt mūsu rīcībā, pirms varam sākt faila atvēršanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5814">**Data\_BytesSynchronous -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5815">**Data\_BytesUnknown —** baitu skaits dokumenta daļās, kuras neplānojam atrast.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5815">**Data\_BytesUnknown -** Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5816">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode —** dokuments ir tikai lasāms/rediģējams</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5816">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode -** Document is read only/editable</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5817">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons —** iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5817">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5818">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5818">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5819">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType —** vienības, kas tiek izmantotas inkrementālā dokumenta atvēršanā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5819">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType -** Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5820">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState —** dokumenta elektronisko datu aizsardzības iestatījums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5820">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState -** Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5821">**Data\_Doc\_Ext —** dokumentu paplašinājums (docx/xlsb/pptx utt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5821">**Data\_Doc\_Ext -** Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5822">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat —** faila formāta protokola versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5822">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat -** File format protocol version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5823">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn —** OneDrive vai SharePoint Online domēna nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5823">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn -** OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5824">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash —** klientu identificējama domēna nosaukuma vienvirziena jaukšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5824">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash -** One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5825">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags —** atskaites par kešotajiem karodziņiem, kas tiek izmantoti pieprasījuma opciju iestatīšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5825">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags -** Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5826">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId —** tādas lietotāja identitātes vienvirziena jaukšana, kas tiek izmantota atvēršanā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5826">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId -** A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5827">**Data\_Doc\_InitializationScenario —** dokumenta atvēršanas ieraksti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5827">**Data\_Doc\_InitializationScenario -** Records how the document was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5828">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights —** dokumentam/lietotājam piemērotās elektronisko datu politikas atļautās darbības</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5828">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights -** Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5829">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen —** karodziņš, kas norāda, ka dokuments ir atvērts inkrementāli</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5829">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen -** Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenloadfile"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5870">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenLoadFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5870">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenLoadFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5871">Šis notikums norāda, ka Office Word atver dokumentu, izmantojot atvēršanas dialoglodziņu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5871">This event indicates Office Word opens a document via Open dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5872">Tas satur arī kritiski svarīgus faila atvēršanas izpildes datus, un no lietotāja skatpunkta ir programmas startēšanas notikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5872">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5873">Notikums pārrauga, vai faila atvēršana no atvēršanas dialoglodziņa darbojas pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5873">The event monitors whether file-open-from-the-open-filedialog is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5874">To izmanto arī, lai aprēķinātu mēneša aktīvos lietotājus/ierīces un mākoņpakalpojumu uzticamības rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5874">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5875">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5875">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5876">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** — norāda, vai mēs varam pareizi aizpildīt citas ar dokumentu telemetriju saistītās vērtības šajā notikumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5876">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5877">Izmanto datu kvalitātes diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5877">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5878">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura uzskatām, ka varēsim atvērt failu, ja tos iegūstam pirms lietotājs vēlas sākt rediģēšanu vai saglabāšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5878">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5879">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** — baitu skaits (saspiests), bez kura, iespējams, varēsim atvērt failu, taču tam būs nepieciešamas būtiskas koda izmaiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5879">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5880">**Data_BytesSynchronous** — baitu skaits (saspiests), kuram jābūt mūsu rīcībā, pirms varam sākt faila atvēršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5880">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5881">**Data_BytesUnknown**— baitu skaits dokumenta daļās, kuras neplānojam atrast.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5881">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5882">**Data_detachedDuration** — cik ilgi darbība bija atdalīta no pavediena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5882">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5883">**Data_Doc_AccessMode —** dokuments ir tikai lasāms/rediģējams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5883">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5884">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** — iepriekš definētu vērtību kopa, kas norāda, kāpēc dokuments ir atvērts pieejamā lasīšanas režīmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5884">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5885">\*\*Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind — \*\* norāda, vai tika atvērta mākoņa dokumenta kešotā versijā un kura asinhronā atsvaidzināšanas loģika tika izmantota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5885">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5886">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType —** vienības, kas tiek izmantotas inkrementālā dokumenta atvēršanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5886">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5887">**Data_Doc_EdpState —** dokumenta elektronisko datu aizsardzības iestatījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5887">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5888">**Data_Doc_Ext —** dokumenta paplašinājums (docx/xlsb/pptx utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5888">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5889">**Data_Doc_FileFormat —** faila formāta protokola versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5889">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5890">**Data_Doc_Fqdn —** OneDrive vai SharePoint Online domēna nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5890">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5891">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash —** klientu identificējama domēna nosaukuma vienvirziena jaukšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5891">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5892">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId —** tādas lietotāja identitātes vienvirziena jaukšana, kas tiek izmantota atvēršanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5892">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5893">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario —** dokumenta atvēršanas ieraksti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5893">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5894">**Data_Doc_IOFlags —** atskaites par kešotajiem karodziņiem, kas tiek izmantoti atvēršanas pieprasījuma opciju iestatīšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5894">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5895">**Data_Doc_IrmRights —** dokumentam/lietotājam piemērotās elektronisko datu politikas atļautās darbības.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5895">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5896">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen —** karodziņš, kas norāda, ka dokuments tika atvērts inkrementāli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5896">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5897">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported —** karodziņš, kas norāda, ka dokuments tiek atbalstīts sadarbības pakalpojumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5897">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5898">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy —** karodziņš, kas norāda, ka tika atvērta dokumenta bezsaistes kopija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5898">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5899">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked —** karodziņš, kas norāda, ka datorā pastāv automātiski sinhronizēta dokumenta kopija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5899">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5943">**iKey** — reģistrētāja servera ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5943">**iKey** - Logger server Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5944">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** — scenārija ID, ko nodrošina lietojumprogramma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5944">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** - Scenario Id provided by the application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-5951">**RMS.ScenarioId** — scenārija ID, ko definē tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma klients</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-5951">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario Id defined by Rights Management Service Client</span></span>
