### <a name="privacy-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6043">*Konfidencialitātes apakštips*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6043">*Privacy subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6044">Office konfidencialitātes iestatījumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6044">Office privacy settings</span></span> 

#### <a name="officeintelligentserviceprivacyconsentprivacyevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6045">Office.IntelligentService.PrivacyConsent.PrivacyEvent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6045">Office.IntelligentService.PrivacyConsent.PrivacyEvent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6046">Šis notikums apzīmē lietotāja vai sistēmas iniciētu darbību, kas ir daļa no Office lietotāju pieredzes ar konfidencialitāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6046">This event represents a user or system initiated action that is part of the privacy User experience for Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6047">Tas tiek aktivizēts konfidencialitātes dialogos Pirmā palaišana, dialogā Konta konfidencialitāte un konfidencialitātes paziņojumos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6047">It is triggered on the privacy First Run dialogs, Account Privacy dialog, and privacy notifications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6048">Notikums tiek izmantots, lai izprastu šādus faktorus: lietotāju piekrišana Office konfidencialitātes iestatījumiem, lietotāju veiktas Office konfidencialitātes iestatījumu izmaiņas un Office konfidencialitātes iestatījumu atjaunināšana lietotāju sesijās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6048">The event is used to understand the following: users consenting to Office privacy settings, users changing Office privacy settings, and Office privacy settings getting updated in user sessions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6049">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6049">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6050">**Data_ActionId —** lietotāja darbība konfidencialitātes dialogā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6050">**Data_ActionId -** User action in a privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6051">**Data_ControllerConnectedServicesState —** lietotāju politikas iestatījums papildu savienotajām pieredzēm pēc izvēles</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6051">**Data_ControllerConnectedServicesState -** User policy setting for additional optional connected experiences</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6052">**Data_DownloadedContentServiceGroupState —** lietotāja iestatījums lejupielādētajam saturam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6052">**Data_DownloadedContentServiceGroupState -** User setting for downloaded content</span></span> 
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6053">**Data_ForwardLinkId —** saite uz konfidencialitātes dokumentiem saistībā ar lietotāja scenāriju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6053">**Data_ForwardLinkId -** Link to privacy documentation for the user scenario</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6054">**Data_HRESULT —** kļūdu ieraksts mijiedarbības laikā ar konfidencialitātes dialogu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6054">**Data_HRESULT -** Record of errors during interaction with a privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6055">**Data_IsEnterpriseUser —** lietotāja licences kategorija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6055">**Data_IsEnterpriseUser -** User license category</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6056">**Data_OfficeServiceConnectionState —** lietotāja iestatījums savienotajiem pakalpojumiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6056">**Data_OfficeServiceConnectionState -** User setting for connected services</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6057">**Data_RecordRegistry —** uzņēmumu konfidencialitātes dialoga rādīšanas ieraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6057">**Data_RecordRegistry -** Record of showing the enterprise privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6058">**Data_Scenario —** pirmās palaišanas scenārijs saistībā ar lietotāja licenci un kategoriju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6058">**Data_Scenario -** First run scenario based on the user license and category</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6059">**Data_SeenInsidersDialog —** Insider programmas dalībnieku dialoga rādīšanas ieraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6059">**Data_SeenInsidersDialog -** Record of showing the Insiders privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6060">**Data_SendTelemetryOption —** lietotāja iestatījums telemetrijai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6060">**Data_SendTelemetryOption -** User setting for telemetry</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6061">**Data_SendTelemetryOptionPolicy —** lietotāja politikas iestatījums telemetrijai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6061">**Data_SendTelemetryOptionPolicy -** User policy setting for telemetry</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6062">**Data_UserCategory —** lietotāja konta veids</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6062">**Data_UserCategory -** User account type</span></span>  

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6063">**Data_UserCCSDisabled —** lietotāja iestatīta ignorēšana papildu savienotajām pieredzēm pēc izvēles</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6063">**Data_UserCCSDisabled -** User override for additional optional connected experiences</span></span>

   - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6064">**Data_UserContentServiceGroupState —** lietotāja iestatījums satura analīzei</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6064">**Data_UserContentServiceGroupState -** User setting for analyzing content</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6065">**Data_WillShowDialogs —** reižu skaits, kad lietotājam bijusi nepieciešamība skatīt konfidencialitātes dialogus Pirmā palaišana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6065">**Data_WillShowDialogs -** Record of user needing to see privacy First Run dialogs</span></span>



## <a name="product-and-service-performance-data-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6066">Produktu un pakalpojumu izpildes datu notikumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6066">Product and service performance data events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6067">Tālāk ir norādīti šīs kategorijas datu apakštipi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6067">The following are the data subtypes in this category:</span></span>
- [<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6068">Neparedzēts lietojumprogrammas darbības pārtraukums (avārijas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6068">Unexpected application exit (crash)</span></span>](#unexpected-application-exit-crash-subtype)
- [<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6069">Lietojumprogrammas līdzekļu novērtējums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6069">Application feature performance </span></span>](#application-feature-performance-subtype)
- [<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6070">Lietojumprogrammas darbības kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6070">Application activity error</span></span>](#application-activity-error-subtype)

### <a name="unexpected-application-exit-crash-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6071">*Neparedzēts lietojumprogrammas darbības pārtraukums (avārijas) apakštips*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6071">*Unexpected application exit (crash) subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6072">Neparedzēts lietojumprogrammas darbības pārtraukums un programmas statuss brīdī, kad tas notika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6072">Unexpected application exits and the state of the application when that happens.</span></span>

#### <a name="appstartupreason"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6073">app.startup.reason</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6073">app.startup.reason</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6074">Šis notikums ļauj mums atklāt un novērst problēmas, kuru dēļ notika Outlook avārija sāknēšanas laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6074">This event lets us detect and fix issues where Outlook crashed during app start up.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6075">Šis notikums iekļauj informāciju par avārijas iemeslu, lai mēs spētu novērst problēmu pēc iespējas ātrāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6075">This event includes information on why the crash happened so we can fix the issue quickly.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6076">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6076">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6077">**app_background_time** — laiks, ko pēdējās sesijas laikā lietojumprogramma pavadīja fonā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6077">**app_background_time** - duration of how long app was in background last session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6078">**startup_reason_type** — norāda, kāpēc lietojumprogramma tiek sāknētā, kā arī norāda, vai iemesls ir piespiedu iziešana vai cits iemesls.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6078">**startup_reason_type** - indicates why the app is starting up, this will indicate if it was due to force quit, or other reason.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6079">**watch_status_info** — uzskaita tālāk noradīto informāciju, ja attiecināms.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6079">**watch_status_info** - keeps track of the following information, if applicable.</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6080">**is_watch_app_installed** — nosaka, vai lietotājs ir instalējis pulksteņa lietojumprogrammu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6080">**is_watch_app_installed** - determines if the user has the Watch app installed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6081">**is_watch_paired** — nosaka, vai iOS ierīce ir savienota ar pulksteni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6081">**is_watch_paired** - determines if iOS device is paired to a watch</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6082">**is_watch_supported_and_active** — norāda, vai pulkstenis sesijas laikā nodrošina atbalstu un ir aktīvs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6082">**is_watch_supported_and_active** - indicates whether a watch is supportive and active during the session</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6083">Tālāk norādītie lauki tiek apkopoti tikai Outlook Mobile darbam ar iOS:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6083">The following fields are collected for only Outlook Mobile for iOS:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6084">**clean_exit_reason** — vārdu virkne, kas norāda, vai ir iemesls lietojumprogrammas apturēšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6084">**clean_exit_reason** - A string of words indicating why if there was a reason for the app stop</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6085">**is_agenda_user** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir nesen atvēris dienas kārtību, kas norāda, vai notiek ierakstīšana diskā sāknēšanas laikā </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6085">**is_agenda_user** - Indicates if the user has opened the agenda recently which indicates if we are writing disk on the startup</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6086">**is_watch_supported_and_active** — norāda, vai pulkstenis sesijas laikā nodrošina atbalstu un ir aktīvs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6086">**is_watch_supported_and_active** - indicates whether a watch is supportive and active during the session</span></span>


#### <a name="applicationcrash"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6087">application.crash</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6087">application.crash</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6088">Izmanto, lai uzraudzītu kritiskas lietojumprogrammu avārijas, un palīdz mums apkopot informāciju par to, kāpēc notika lietojumprogrammas avārija un kā to novērst.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6088">Used for monitoring critical app crashes and helps us collect information on why the app has crashed and how to prevent it.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6089">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6089">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6090">**android.hardware.**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6090">**android.hardware.**</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6091">— (piem., android.hardware.bluetooth) Android platformas sniegtās aparatūras konfigurācijas vērtības</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6091">- (e.g. android.hardware.bluetooth) Hardware configuration values provided by the Android platform</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6092">**android.software.**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6092">**android.software.**</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6093">— (e.g. android.software.device_admin) Android platformas sniegtās programmatūras konfigurācijas vērtības</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6093">- (e.g. android.software.device_admin) Software configuration values provided by the Android platform</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6094">**android_version** — ierīces Android versijas nosaukums, kas norādīts android.os.Build.VERSION#RELEASE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6094">**android_version** - Device android version name as indicated by android.os.Build.VERSION#RELEASE</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6095">**application_package_name** — lietojumprogrammas pakotnes nosaukums, kas norādīts android.content.Context#getPackageName()</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6095">**application_package_name** - Application package name as indicated by android.content.Context#getPackageName()</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6096">**application_stack_trace** — avārijas izsekošanas steks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6096">**application_stack_trace** - the stack trace of the crash</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6097">**application_version_code** — Outlook lietojumprogrammas noteiktais lietojumprogrammas versijas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6097">**application_version_code** - Application version code defined by the Outlook app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6098">**application_version_name** — Outlook lietojumprogrammas noteiktais lietojumprogrammas versijas nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6098">**application_version_name** - Application version name defined by the Outlook app</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6099">**com.**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6099">**com.**</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6100">(piem., com.google.android.feature.FASTPASS_BUILD, com.amazon.feature.PRELOAD, com.samsung.android.bio.face) Android platformas nodrošinātās ražotājam specifiskas konfigurācijas vērtības</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6100">(e.g. com.google.android.feature.FASTPASS_BUILD, com.amazon.feature.PRELOAD, com.samsung.android.bio.face) Manufacturer specific configuration values provided by the Android platform</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6101">**crash_report_sdk** — SDK avārijas žurnāla nosūtīšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6101">**crash_report_sdk** - SDK to send crash logs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6102">Hockey vai AppCenter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6102">Either Hockey or AppCenter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6103">**crash_type** — crash_type tipi būs Java, vietējs, nekritisks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6103">**crash_type** - crash_type will have java, native, non-fatal as types.</span></span>

     - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6104">Java — ja avārija ir ierakstīta lietojumslānī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6104">java - if crash recorded on application Layer.</span></span>

     - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6105">Vietējs — ja avārija ir ierakstīta programmas lietojumslānī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6105">native - if crash recorded on native layer within the app.</span></span> 

     - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6106">Nekritisks — avārijas tiek ierakstītas jebkura līdzekļa atkļūdošanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6106">non-fatal - crashes being recorded to debug any feature.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6107">Programmas avārija nenotiks, bet tā augšupielādēs nekritiskos avārijas žurnālus, lai palīdzētu līdzekļa atkļūdošanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6107">Application won’t crash but it will upload non-fatal crash logs to help in debugging a feature.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6108">**device_brand** — ierīces zīmols (ražotājs vai operators), ko norāda android.os.Build#BRAND</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6108">**device_brand** - Device brand (manufacturer or carrier) as indicated by android.os.Build#BRAND</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6109">**device_ID** — ierīces unikālais ID (IMEI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6109">**device_ID** - Device unique ID (IMEI)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6110">**device_manufacturer** — ierīces ražotājs, ko norāda android.os.Build#MANUFACTURER</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6110">**device_manufacturer** - Device manufacturer as indicated by android.os.Build#MANUFACTURER</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6111">**device_model** — ierīces modelis, ko norāda android.os.Build#MODEL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6111">**device_model** - Device model as indicated by android.os.Build#MODEL</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6112">**device_name** — ierīces nosaukums, ko norāda android.os.Build#DEVICE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6112">**device_name** - Device name as indicated by android.os.Build#DEVICE</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6113">**device_total_memory** — kopējā ierīces atmiņas apjoma novērtējums, pamatojoties uz filesystem datiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6113">**device_total_memory** - Estimation of the total device memory size based on filesystem stats.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6114">**glEsVersion** — OpenGL iegulto sistēmu versijas atslēga</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6114">**glEsVersion** - OpenGL Embedded Systems version key</span></span>


#### <a name="crashevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6115">crash.event</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6115">crash.event</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6116">Palīdz mums atklāt un novērst situācijas, kurās notiek kritiskas lietojumprogrammas avārijas, un palīdz mums apkopot informāciju par lietojumprogrammas avārijas iemesliem un kā tos novērst.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6116">Allows us to detect and fix situations where critical app crashes have occurred and helps us collect information on why the app has crashed and how to prevent it.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6117">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6117">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6118">**crashTime** — avārijas datums un laiks, kas palīdz mūsu izmeklēšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6118">**crashTime** - Date and time the crash occurred to help with investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6119">**crash_time_from_start** — pagājušais laiks no programmas sākuma līdz avāriju rašanās brīdim, lai palīdzētu veikt izmeklēšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6119">**crash_time_from_start** – The elapsed time from app start to the crash occurred, to help with investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6120">**exceptionName** — izņēmuma, kas izraisīja avāriju, nosaukums, lai palīdzētu mūsu izmeklēšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6120">**exceptionName** - The name of the exception that triggered the crash to help with investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6121">**exception_reason** — izņēmuma, kas izraisīja avāriju, nosaukums, lai palīdzētu mūsu izmeklēšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6121">**exception_reason** – The reason of the exception that triggered the crash to help with investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6122">**hasHx** — norāda, vai konts izmanto jauno sinhronizācijas pakalpojumu, lai palīdzētu noteikt mūsu sinhronizācijas pakalpojuma radītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6122">**hasHx** - Tells us the account is using our new sync service to help us detect issues caused by our sync service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6123">**incidentIdentifier** — unikāls ID avārijas ziņojumam, kas palīdz mums atklāt atbilstošo problēmu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6123">**incidentIdentifier** - A unique ID for the crash report so we can find the corresponding issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6124">**isAppKill** — palīdz mums noteikt, vai lietojumprogramma ierīcē tika apturēta vai aizvērta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6124">**isAppKill** - Helps us understand if that app was killed or close on the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6125">**is_crashloop** — palīdz mums saprast, vai avārija varētu būt avārijas cilpa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6125">**is_crashloop** – Helps us understand if the crash could likely be a crash loop.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6126">**reportKey** — unikāls lietojumprogrammas instalēšanas ID ierīcē problēmu izmeklēšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6126">**reportKey** - A unique ID for the application installation om the device for issue investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6127">**signal** — signāls, kas izraisīja avāriju, lai sniegtu mums papildu informāciju šīs avārijas izmeklēšanā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6127">**signal** - A signal that caused the crash to give us more details to investigate this crash</span></span>


#### <a name="error"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6128">Error</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6128">Error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6129">Ļauj mums noteikt problēmas, ar kurām saskaras mobilās lietojumprogrammas, kad tās mēģina izgūt konfidencialitātes iestatījumus no servera.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6129">Allows us to understand the issues that mobile apps are facing when attempting to fetch privacy settings from the server.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6130">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6130">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6131">**correlationId** — unikāls identifikators pakalpojuma savienojumam, kas radīja kļūdu, ļauj mums diagnosticēt iespējamos kļūdas iemeslus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6131">**correlationId** - a unique identifier for a service connection that resulted in an error, allowing us to diagnose what might have gone wrong</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6132">**errorCode** — identificē atbilstošo kļūdas kodu, kas saņemts no pakalpojuma un kuru var izmantot problēmas diagnosticēšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6132">**errorCode** - identifies the relevant error code received from the service that could be used to diagnose the problem</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6133">**exceptionType** — kļūdas tips, ar kuru saskārās bibliotēka iestatījuma ieneses laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6133">**exceptionType** - type of error that the library encountered when fetching the setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6134">**message** — identificē no pakalpojuma saņemto kļūdas ziņojumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6134">**message** - identifies the error message received from the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6135">**roamingSettingType** — nosaka atrašanās vietu, no kuras tika veikts mēģinājums nolasīt iestatījumus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6135">**roamingSettingType** - identifies the location from which we attempt to read settings</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6136">**settingId** — iestatījums, kuru mēģināja ienest</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6136">**settingId** - the setting that was attempted to be fetched</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappdomainunhandledexceptionhandlerfailed"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6137">Office.AppDomain.UnhandledExceptionHandlerFailed</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6137">Office.AppDomain.UnhandledExceptionHandlerFailed</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6138">Apkopo informāciju par neapstrādātiem izņēmumiem, izmantojot programmu Data Streamer.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6138">Collects information for any unhandled exceptions using the Data Streamer App.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6139">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai pārraudzītu programmas darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6139">This data is used to monitor the health of the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6140">Šo notikumu ģenerē Microsoft Data Streamer Excel pievienojumprogrammai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6140">This event is generated by Microsoft Data Streamer for Excel Add-in.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6141">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6141">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6142">**Exception** — izņēmuma izsaukuma steks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6142">**Exception** - Call stack for the Exception</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6143">**Event Name** — notikuma nosaukums ir notikuma kategorija un notikuma etiķete.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6143">**Event Name** - Event Name is the Event Category and Event Label.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappleidentitydomainname"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6144">Office.Apple.IdentityDomainName</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6144">Office.Apple.IdentityDomainName</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6145">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6145">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6146">Pasākums tiek lietots, lai pārraudzītu mūsu sistēmas darbspēju, kā arī noteiktu domēna lietotāju neveiksmes iemeslus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6146">The event is used to monitor the health of our system as well as investigating causes of failures by certain domain users.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6147">Mēs apkopojam domēnu, ko izmanto mūsu lietotāji autentificēšanas laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6147">We collect the domain used by our users when they authenticate.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6148">Šie dati tiek izmantoti, lai palīdzētu noteikt un novērst problēmas, kas var neradīt pārāk lielu iespaidu plašākā līmenī, bet ir ļoti iespaidīgas noteiktiem lietotāju domēniem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6148">We use this data to help identify and fix those issues that might not seem too impactful at a broader level, but that turn out to be very impactful to a certain domain of users.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6149">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6149">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6150">**Data_Domain** — autentifikācijai izmantotais domēns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6150">**Data_Domain** - the domain used for authentication</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6151">**Data_IdentityProvider** — autentifikācijas identitātes nodrošinātāja nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6151">**Data_IdentityProvider** - The authentication identity provider name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6152">(piem., LiveId vai ADAL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6152">(i.e. LiveId or ADAL)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6153">**Data_IdentityProviderEnum** — autentifikācijas identitātes nodrošinātāja nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6153">**Data_IdentityProviderEnum** - The authentication identity provider code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6154">(Skaitlis)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6154">(A number)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeapplesystemhealthappexitmacandios"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6155">Office.Apple.SystemHealthAppExitMacAndiOS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6155">Office.Apple.SystemHealthAppExitMacAndiOS</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6156">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6156">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6157">Pasākums tiek lietots, lai pārraudzītu mūsu Office programmu darbspēju, kā arī noteiktu kļūmju iemeslus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6157">The event is used to monitor the health of our Office applications as well as for investigating causes of failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6158">Mēs apkopojam datus katras programmas iziešanas laikā, lai noteiktu, vai no programmas ir iziets bez aizķeršanās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6158">We collect data on each application exit to determine whether an application exited gracefully.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6159">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6159">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6160">**Data_AffectedProcessSessionID** — sesijas identifikators, kas veic programmas iziešanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6160">**Data_AffectedProcessSessionID** - The identifier for the session that experience the application exit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6161">**Data_AffectedSessionBuildNumber** — tās programmas sekundārā versija, kurā tika novērota programmas iziešana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6161">**Data_AffectedSessionBuildNumber** - The minor version of the application in which an application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6162">**Data_AffectedSessionDuration** — sesijas ilgums no sākuma līdz beigām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6162">**Data_AffectedSessionDuration** - The length of the session from start to exit</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6163">**Data_AffectedSessionIDSMatch** — telemetrijas darbspējas rādītājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6163">**Data_AffectedSessionIDSMatch** - An indicator of telemetry health.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6164">**Data_AffectedSessionMERPSessionID** — telemetrijas darbspējas rādītājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6164">**Data_AffectedSessionMERPSessionID** - An indicator of telemetry health.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6165">**Data_AffectedSessionOSLocale** — tās operētājsistēmas lokalizācija, ar kuru tika novērota programmas iziešana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6165">**Data_AffectedSessionOSLocale** - The Locale of the OS under which the application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6166">**Data_AffectedSessionOSVersion** — tās operētājsistēmas lokalizācija, ar kuru tika novērota programmas iziešana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6166">**Data_AffectedSessionOSVersion** - The OS version under which the application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6167">**Data_AffectedSessionResidentMemoryOnCrash** — rezidenta atmiņas apjoms, kas tika patērēts, kad tika veikta lietojumprogrammas iziešana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6167">**Data_AffectedSessionResidentMemoryOnCrash** - The amount of resident memory that was consumed when the application exit occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6168">**Data_AffectedSessionStackHash** — identifikators, kas aprakstīs konkrētās kļūdas trāpījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6168">**Data_AffectedSessionStackHash** - An identifier that will denote the specific error being hit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6169">**Data_AffectedSessionStartTime** — laiks, kad sesija sākās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6169">**Data_AffectedSessionStartTime** - The time at which the session started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6170">**Data_AffectedSessionUAEType** — novērotais programmas iziešanas veids (ja tas bija ar aizķeršanos iziešanas gadījumā, šis kods apzīmēs novērotās kļūdas tipu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6170">**Data_AffectedSessionUAEType** - The type of application exit observed (if it was an ungraceful exit, this code will denote the type of error observed)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6171">**Data_AffectedSessionBuildNumber** — programmas galvenā versija, kurā tika novērota programmas iziešana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6171">**Data_AffectedSessionVersion** - The major version of the application in which an application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6172">**Data_AffectedSessionResidentMemoryOnCrash** — virtuālās atmiņas apjoms, kas tika patērēts, kad notika programmas iziešana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6172">**Data_AffectedSessionVirtualMemoryOnCrash** - The amount of virtual memory that was consumed when the application exit occurred.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6173">**Data_ExitWasGraceful** — vai programmas iziešana bija bez aizķeršanās vai ar aizķeršanos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6173">**Data_ExitWasGraceful** - Whether the application Exit was graceful or ungraceful.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilitycomaddinunhandledexception"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6174">Office.Extensibility.COMAddinUnhandledException</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6174">Office.Extensibility.COMAddinUnhandledException</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6175">Šis notikums tiek ģenerēts, kad Office lietotāju versijā notiek COM pievienojumprogrammas avārija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6175">Event generated when COM Add-in crashes on a consumer version of Office applications.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6176">Izmantošana: izmanto, lai izskaitļotu globālu, ar konkrētu uzņēmumu nesaistītu Microsoft 365 programmas lieluzņēmumiem pievienojumprogrammas ieviešanu, kas tālāk tiek izmantota ar tādiem rīkiem kā Readiness Toolkit.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6176">Usage: this is used to compute a global, non-enterprise-specific Microsoft 365 Apps for enterprise "adoption" for an add-in which is then used by tools like the Readiness Toolkit.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6177">Ļauj lieluzņēmumu versijas klientiem pārbaudīt, vai pievienojumprogrammas, kuras viņi ieviesa savās organizācijās, ir saderīgas ar jaunākajām Microsoft 365 programmām lieluzņēmumiem, un atbilstoši plānot atjauninājumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6177">This allows enterprise customers to validate if the add-ins they have deployed in their organizations are compatible with the latest versions of Microsoft 365 Apps for enterprise and plan their upgrades accordingly.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6178">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6178">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6179">**ScopeId** — pašreizējā pavediena tvērums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6179">**ScopeId** – the current thread scope</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6180">**Method** — Office metode, kurā radās izņēmums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6180">**Method** – Office method where exception occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6181">**Interface** — Office interfeiss, kurā radās izņēmums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6181">**Interface** – Office interface where exception occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6182">**AddinId** — pievienojumprogrammas klases ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6182">**AddinId** – the add-in Class Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6183">**AddinProgId** — novecojis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6183">**AddinProgId** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6184">**AddinFriendlyName** — novecojis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6184">**AddinFriendlyName** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6185">**AddinTimeDateStamp** — pievienojumprogrammas laikspiedols no DLL metadatiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6185">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – the add-in timestamp from the DLL metadata</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6186">**AddinVersion** — novecojis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6186">**AddinVersion** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6187">**AddinFileName** — novecojis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6187">**AddinFileName** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6188">**VSTOAddIn** — vai pievienojumprogramma ir VSTO</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6188">**VSTOAddIn** – whether add-in is VSTO</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6189">**AddinConnectFlag** — pašreizējās ielādes darbība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6189">**AddinConnectFlag** – current load behavior</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6190">**LoadAttempts** — pievienojumprogrammas ielādes mēģinājumu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6190">**LoadAttempts** – number of attempts to load add-in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6195">**ScopeId** — pašreizējā pavediena tvērums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6195">**ScopeId** – the current thread scope</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6198">**AddinId** — pievienojumprogrammas klases ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6198">**AddinId** – the add-in Class Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6199">**AddinProgId** — novecojis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6199">**AddinProgId** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6200">**AddinFriendlyName** — novecojis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6200">**AddinFriendlyName** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6201">**AddinTimeDateStamp** — pievienojumprogrammas laikspiedols no DLL metadatiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6201">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – the add-in timestamp from the DLL metadata</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilitysandboxodpactivationheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6207">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHeartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6207">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHeartbeat</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6208">Office pievienojumprogrammas darbojas smilškastē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6208">Office Add-ins run in a sandbox.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6209">Notikums periodiski apkopo informāciju par aktivācijām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6209">This event collects heartbeat information on activations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6210">Kad notiek pievienojumprogrammas avārija, notikums apkopo ar mūsu smilškasti saistītās avārijas iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6210">When an add-in crashes, this event collects why it crashed in the case it's related to our sandbox.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6211">Izmanto gadījumos, kad klienti aktualizē problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6211">Used to investigate when customers escalate issues.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6212">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6212">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6213">**AppId** — lietojumprogrammas ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6213">**AppId** - ID of the App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6214">**AppInfo** — dati par pievienojumprogrammas veidu (uzdevumrūts vai UILess, vai iegulšanas utt.) un nodrošinātāja veidu (omen, SharePoint, filesystem utt.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6214">**AppInfo** - Data regarding the type of add-in (task pane or UILess or in content etc.) and the provider type (omen, SharePoint, filesystem etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6215">**AppInstanceId** — lietojumprogrammas instances ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6215">**AppInstanceId** - ID of the app instance</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6216">**AssetId** — lietojumprogrammas līdzekļa ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6216">**AssetId** - Asset ID of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6217">**ErrorCodeime** — iztērētais laiks kopā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6217">**ErrorCode** - Total time spent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6218">**IsAugmentationScenario**— norāda uz to, vai pieauguma cilpa ir atbildīga par Office Solutions struktūras vadības inicializēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6218">**IsAugmentationScenario** – indicates if the augmentation loop is responsible for initializing the Office Solutions Framework control</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6219">**IsDebug** - norāda, vai sesija ir atkļūdošanas sesija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6219">**IsDebug** - indicates if session is a debug session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6220">**IsPreload** — norāda, vai pievienojumprogramma tiek sākotnēji ielādēta fonā, lai uzlabotu aktivizēšanas veiktspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6220">**IsPreload** – indicates if the add-in is being preloaded in background for improving activation perf.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6221">**IsWdagContainer** — norāda, vai pievienojumprogrammas aktivācija tiek veikta Windows Defender Application Guard konteinerī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6221">**IsWdagContainer** – indicates if the add-in activation is being taken place in a Windows Defender Application Guard container.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6222">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** — aktivēto pievienojumprogrammu skaitītājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6222">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** - Counter of add-ins activated</span></span>
