- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6757">**Data_SessionVersion** — programmas galvenā versija, kurā tika novērota iziešana no programmas ar aizķeršanos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6757">**Data_SessionVersion** - The major version of the application in which an ungraceful application exit was observed.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeapplewhatsnewerrorandwarning"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6758">Office.Apple.WhatsNewErrorAndWarning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6758">Office.Apple.WhatsNewErrorAndWarning</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6759">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6759">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6760">Pasākums tiek lietots, lai pārraudzītu, kas ir jaunā līdzekļa darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6760">The event is used to monitor the health of the What's New feature.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6761">Šis notikums norāda, ka, parsējot jaunumu saturu, radās kļūda/brīdinājums, norādot uz potenciālām satura autorēšanas problēmām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6761">This event denotes that an error/warning occurred while parsing What's New content, pointing to potential content authoring issues.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6762">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6762">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6763">**Data_ContentKey** — rādītājs uz satura sadaļu, kas visticamāk izraisīja kļūdu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6763">**Data_ContentKey** - A pointer to the section of the content that is likely to have caused the error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6764">**Data_ErrorCode** — novērotais kļūdas kods (ja pieejams)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6764">**Data_ErrorCode** - The observed error code (if available)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6765">**Data_ErrorDescription** — kļūdas apraksts (ja pieejams)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6765">**Data_ErrorDescription** - A description of the error (if available)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6766">**Data_EventID** — mēs apkopojam virkni, kas norāda novērotās kļūdas tipu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6766">**Data_EventID** - We collect a string representing the type of error observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6767">**Data_IncludesHTMLTag** — vai saturā ir bagātināts html</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6767">**Data_IncludesHTMLTag** - Whether the content contains rich html</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6768">**Data_IncludesItemsTag** — vai saturā ir vienumu hierarhija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6768">**Data_IncludesItemsTag** - Whether the content contains a hierarchy of items</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6769">**Data_LengthOfRawData** — satura lielums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6769">**Data_LengthOfRawData** - The size of the content</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6770">**Data_RequestURL** — vietrādis URL, no kura saturs tika lejupielādēts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6770">**Data_RequestURL** - The URL from which the content was downloaded</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6771">**Data_ServerLanguageTag** — valoda, kurā bija saturs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6771">**Data_ServerLanguageTag** - The language the content was in.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6772">**Data_StatusCode** — kļūdas statuss (ja pieejams)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6772">**Data_StatusCode** - The status of the error (if available)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilityrichapimethodinvocation"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6773">Office.Extensibility.RichApiMethodInvocation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6773">Office.Extensibility.RichApiMethodInvocation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6774">Šis notikums aktivizējas, kad klients izmanto Office pievienojumprogrammu un sazinās ar Rich API pakalpojuma sniegšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6774">When customer uses an Office Add-in and calls Rich API for providing service, this event will be triggered.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6775">Izmanto, lai izmērītu pakalpojuma uzticamību, veiktspēju un lietojumu Rich API metodes izsaukšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6775">Used to measure the service reliability, performance and usage for Rich API method invocation.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6776">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6776">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6777">**API** — pilns API nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6777">**Api** - Full name of the API</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6778">**DispFlag** — bitu karodziņš, kas apraksta metodes izsaukuma tipu (piem., 0x1 = METHOD, 0x2 = PROPERTYGET, 0x4 = PROPERTYPUT, 0x8 = PROPERTYPUTREF).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6778">**DispFlag** - A bit flag describing the type of method call (Ex: 0x1 = METHOD, 0x2 = PROPERTYGET, 0x4 = PROPERTYPUT, 0x8 = PROPERTYPUTREF)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6779">**DispId** — izsauktās metodes izsūtīšanas identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6779">**DispId** - Dispatch ID for the method being called</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6780">**HResult** — metodes izsaukšanas HResult.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6780">**HResult** - HResult for the method call</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6781">**Latency** — izsaukuma latentums mikrosekundēs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6781">**Latency** - Latency for the call, in microseconds</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6782">**ReqId** — pakešu pieprasījuma GUID, pie kura pieder šī metode.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6782">**ReqId** - GUID for the batch request that this method belongs to</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6783">**TypeId** — interfeisa GUID, uz kura šī metode tiek izsaukta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6783">**TypeId** - GUID for the interface on which this method being called</span></span>

#### <a name="officeiospaywallfailedscreenretrybuttontap"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6784">Office.iOS.Paywall.FailedScreen.RetryButtonTap</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6784">Office.iOS.Paywall.FailedScreen.RetryButtonTap</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6785">Šī lietojuma telemetrija tiek apkopota, lai noteiktu, kad neizdodas pirkuma/nodrošināšanas/aktivizēšanas darbība un lietotājs pieskaras pogai “Mēģināt vēlreiz”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6785">This usage telemetry is collected to know when the Purchase/Provisioning/Activation failed, and the user tapped the “Retry” button.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6786">Izmanto, lai veiktu pirkšanas kļūdu scenāriju, kas izraisa atkārtošanu, problēmu novēršanu un uzlabotu procesa uzticamību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6786">Used to troubleshoot purchase error scenarios that lead to retry and improve process reliability.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6787">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6787">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6788">**failureReason** — virkne — norāda kļūmi, kuru lietotājs mēģina atkārtot vēlreiz.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6788">**failureReason** - String – Indicates what the failure was the user is retrying.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6789">Piemēram, “provisioningFailed”, “purchaseFailed”, “activationFailed”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6789">Like “provisioningFailed”, “purchaseFailed”, “activationFailed”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6790">**productid**— virkne — produkta, kuram lietotājs mēģina vēlreiz nesekmīgo pieprasījumu, App Store ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6790">**productid** - String – App Store ID of the product for which user is retrying the failed request</span></span>


#### <a name="officemanageabilityserviceapplypolicy"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6791">Office.Manageability.Service.ApplyPolicy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6791">Office.Manageability.Service.ApplyPolicy</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6792">Kritiski svarīgi telemetrijas dati, lai izsekotu kļūmi\\Sekmīgi lietoti mākoņa politikas iestatījumi reģistrā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6792">Critical telemetry to track failure\\Success of applying cloud policy settings to registry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6793">LastError norāda, kāpēc un kur neizdevās politikas lietošana reģistrā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6793">LastError tells why and where the Application of policy in registry failed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6794">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6794">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6795">**Data.ApplyLogMsg** — izņēmuma ziņojums politikas lietošanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6795">**Data.ApplyLogMsg** - The exception msg if any while policy was being applied</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6796">**Data.Cid** — dinamiski ģenerēts korelācijas identifikators, kas nosūtīts uz pakalpojumu, kad tika veikts pakalpojuma izsaukums, lai ienestu mākoņa politiku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6796">**Data.Cid** - dynamically generated correlation identifier sent to the service when the service call was made to fetch the cloud policy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6797">Tiek izmantots, lai korelētu, kurš izsaukums izraisīja problēmu, lietojot politikas mākonī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6797">Used to correlate which call caused an issue while applying the policies on the cloud.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6798">**Data.Last Error** — viena no piecām virknes vērtībām (skaitītājiem), kas reģistrē, kurš politikas lietojums posms tika izpildīts, kad radās izņēmums </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6798">**Data.Last Error** - One of five string values (enumerators) to log which stage of policy application was being executed when the exception occurred</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenoteandroidsyncprovisioningerror"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6799">Office.OneNote.Android.Sync.ProvisioningError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6799">Office.OneNote.Android.Sync.ProvisioningError</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6800">Kritiskais signāls, kas tiek izmantots, ka pēc lietotāja pierakstīšanās OneNote Android lietojumprogrammā, tiek atbilstoši nodrošinātas piezīmju grāmatiņas, lai tām būtu vienkārši piekļūt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6800">The critical signal used to ensure that after a user signs-into a OneNote Android App, notebooks are properly provisioned so that they can be easily accessed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6801">Tek izmantota kritiskas regresijas atklāšanai OneNote lietojumprogrammā un pakalpojuma darbspējā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6801">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6802">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6802">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6803">**AppSuspendedDuringEvent** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai lietojumprogramma tika aizturēta nodrošināšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6803">**AppSuspendedDuringEvent**: Returns boolean to indicate if app was suspended during provisioning</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6804">**ErrorCode** — atgriež par nodrošināšanas kļūmi atbildīgās kļūdas kodu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6804">**ErrorCode** – Returns the error code responsible for failure of provisioning</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6805">**NetworkConnection** — izmantotās ierīces tīkla savienojamības tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6805">**NetworkConnection**: The type of network connectivity of the device in use</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6806">**NetworkDataExchange** — reģistrē nodrošināšanas laikā apmainīto baitu skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6806">**NetworkDataExchange** - Records the number of bytes exchanged during provisioning.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6807">**ServerType** — atgriež tā servera tipu, kas piedāvā pakalpojumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6807">**ServerType**: Returns the type of the server offering the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6808">**TimeTakenInMilliSeconds** — norāda nodrošināšanas pabeigšanai nepieciešamo laiku milisekundēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6808">**TimeTakenInMilliSeconds**: Returns time taken to complete provisioning in millisecond</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6810">Kritiskais signāls tiek izmantots izsekošanai, kad mēs izlemjam parādīt lietotājam drošās sāknēšanas dialoglodziņu nākamajā sāknēšanas reizē, jo sāknēšanas laikā regulāri notiek vairākas avārijas. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6810">The critical signal used to track when we decide to show user a safe boot dialog on next boot because we have been crashing on boot multiple times continuously.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6811">Tek izmantota kritiskas regresijas atklāšanai OneNote lietojumprogrammā un pakalpojuma darbspējā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6811">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6812">Ja lietotāji redz šo drošās sāknēšanas dialoglodziņu, tad mums ir kritiska sāknēšanas avārijas kļūda un šī informācija palīdzēs mums noteikt, cik daudz lietotāju saskaras ar šo problēmu un cik daudz lietotāju atkārtoti sāknē šo programmu, lai faktiski ieraudzītu drošās sāknēšanas dialoglodziņu un cik daudz lietotāju neatgriežas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6812">If users are seeing the safe boot dialog then we have a critical boot crash bug and this info will help us know how many users are facing this issue and how many users boot the app again to actually see the safe boot dialog vs how many don’t return.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6813">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6813">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6814">Nav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6814">None</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookdesktopbootperfmetrics"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6815">Office.Outlook.Desktop.BootPerfMetrics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6815">Office.Outlook.Desktop.BootPerfMetrics</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6819">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6819">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6820">**AddinElapsedTotal** — kopējais laiks, lai ielādētu pievienojumprogrammas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6820">**AddinElapsedTotal** - Total time spent for loading add-ins</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6821">**CredPromptCount** — parādīto akreditācijas datu uzvedņu skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6821">**CredPromptCount** – Number of credential prompts shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6822">**ElapsedTotal** — kopējais startēšanas laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6822">**ElapsedTotal** - Total time spent for boot</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6823">**IsLoggingEnabled** — vai ir iespējota reģistrēšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6823">**IsLoggingEnabled** - Is logging enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6824">**ShowChooseProfileDlg** — vai bija redzams dialoglodziņš Profila izvēle</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6824">**ShowChooseProfileDlg** – Whether the Choose Profile Dialog was shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6825">**ShowFirstRunDlg** — vai Outlook tiek palaista pirmo reizi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6825">**ShowFirstRunDlg** - is outlook launched for the first time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6826">**ShowIMAPSrchfldWarningDlg** — brīdinājumi, ja ir IMAP konts ar ANSI PST</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6826">**ShowIMAPSrchfldWarningDlg** - Warnings in case we have an IMAP account with an ANSI PST</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6827">**ShowNeedSupportDlg** — startēšanas kļūme aktivizēja atbalsta dialoglodziņu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6827">**ShowNeedSupportDlg** - Boot failure triggered support dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6828">**ShowSafeModeDlg** — vai sesija ir atvērta drošajā režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6828">**ShowSafeModeDlg** - is the session opened in safe mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6829">**ShowScanPstDlg** — krātuves labošanas pārbaude parādīja kļūdas ziņojumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6829">**ShowScanPstDlg** - Store repair check displayed error message</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6835">**MacOLKBootPerfDuration** — kopējais sāknēšanas laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6835">**MacOLKBootPerfDuration** - total time spent booting</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookmacperformanceunresponsive"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6837">Office.Outlook.Mac.PerformanceUnresponsive</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6837">Office.Outlook.Mac.PerformanceUnresponsive</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6838">Izmanto, lai identificētu problēmas Outlook, kas ietekmē lietotāju un var izpausties kā pasliktināta veiktspēja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6838">Used to identify user impacting issues in Outlook that may manifest as degraded performance.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6839">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6839">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6840">**Duration** — pasliktinātās veiktspējas ilgums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6840">**Duration** - time elapsed of degraded performance</span></span>

#### <a name="officeperformanceboot"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6842">Office.Performance.Boot</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6842">Office.Performance.Boot</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6843">Tiek apkopots, palaižot Office programmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6843">Collected when an Office application is booted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6844">Ietver informāciju par to, vai palaišana tika sākta, atverot failu vai palaižot no sākuma izvēlnes, vai tā bija pirmā programmas palaišana, cik daudz atmiņas programma izmanto un vai lietotājam tika rādīts bloķēšanas UI.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6844">Includes whether the boot was initiated by opening a file or launching via the Start menu, whether this was the first boot of the application, how much memory the application is using, and whether there was any blocking UI shown to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6845">Tiek izmantots, lai noteiktu, cik ātri Office programmas tiek palaistas un cik daudz atmiņas tās izmanto, kad tiek startētas, lai nodrošinātu pieņemamu lietotāja pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6845">Used to measure how fast Office applications boot and how much memory they use when they start, to ensure there is an acceptable user experience.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6846">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6846">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6847">**ActivationKind** — vai programma tika startēta, palaižot no sākuma izvēlnes, atverot failu vai izmantojot OLE automatizāciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6847">**ActivationKind** - Whether the application was started by launching from the Start menu, by opening a file, or through OLE Automation.</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6848">**BootToStart** — vai lietotājs ir izvēlējies sākuma ekrāna parādīšanu lietojumprogrammas startēšanas laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6848">**BootToStart** - Whether the user has chosen to show the start screen when this application starts.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6849">**ColdBoot** — norāda, vai tā ir pirmā reize, kad Office programma tiek palaista pēc sistēmas restartēšanas, vai programmas binārs bija jāielādē no diska.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6849">**ColdBoot** - Whether is first time Office application runs after a system restart or application binary had to be loaded from disk.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6850">**DeviceModel** — ierīces modelis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6850">**DeviceModel** - The model of the device.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6851">**DocLocation** —  dokumenta atvēršanas brīdī norāda uz dokumenta izcelsmes pakalpojumu (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint, u. tml.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6851">**DocLocation** -  When opening a document, indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint, etc.).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6852">**DurationUntilMso20Initialization** — laiks milisekundēs no brīža, kad tika inicializēts Office process, līdz mso20win32client ielādei.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6852">**DurationUntilMso20Initialization** - The duration in microseconds it took between when the Office process was initialized and mso20win32client.dll was loaded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6853">**Iegulšana** — neatkarīgi no tā, vai programma tika atvērta objektu saistīšanai un iegulšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6853">**Embedding** – Whether the app was opened for OLE embedding.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6854">**FirstBoot** — vai šī bija pirmā programmas palaišana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6854">**FirstBoot** - Whether this was a first boot of the application.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6855">**InitializationDuration** — laiks milisekundēs, kas bija nepieciešams, lai vispirms inicializētu Office procesu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6855">**InitializationDuration** - The duration in microseconds it took to first initialize the Office process.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6856">**InterruptionMessageId** — vai palaišanu pārtrauca dialogs, pieprasot lietotāja ievadi, kā arī šī dialoga ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6856">**InterruptionMessageId** - If the boot was interrupted by a dialog asking for user input, the ID of the dialog.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6857">**LegacyDuration** — laiks, kas bija nepieciešams darbības izpildei, tiek mērīts, izmantojot dažādus sākuma un beigu punktus nekā Activity.Duration.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6857">**LegacyDuration** - The length of time the activity took to execute, measured using different starting and ending points than Activity.Duration.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6858">**OpenAsNew** — vai programma tika startēta, atverot esošu dokumentu kā jaunu veidni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6858">**OpenAsNew** – Whether the app was started by opening an existing document as the template for a new one.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6859">**TotalWorkingSetMB** — atmiņas apjoms megabaitos procesa darba kopā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6859">**TotalWorkingSetMB** - The amount of memory in megabytes in the process's working set.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6860">**VirtualSetMB** — atmiņas apjoms megabaitos procesa virtuālajā kopā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6860">**VirtualSetMB** - The amount of memory in megabytes in the process's virtual set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6861">(Tikai MacOS/iOS)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6861">(MacOS / iOS only)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6862">**WorkingSetPeakMB** — vislielākais atmiņas apjoms megabaitos, kas līdz šim ir bijis procesa darba kopā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6862">**WorkingSetPeakMB** - The largest amount of memory in megabytes that was ever in the process's working set so far.</span></span>


#### <a name="officepowerpointpptandroidrehearseview"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6863">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6863">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6864">Šis notikums norāda, ka lietotājs pārtrauca mēģinājuma sesiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6864">This event is denoting that user has stopped the rehearsal session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6865">Apvienojot ar Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView.StartSession, šis būs pirmais indikators jebkādām avārijām vai kļūdām, ar kurām saskaras lietotājs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6865">In combination with Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView.StartSession this will be the first indicator of any crashes or errors that user faces.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6866">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6866">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6867">**ConnectionCreationTime** — laiks, kas nepieciešams, lai izveidotu pakalpojuma puses savienojumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6867">**ConnectionCreationTime** - time taken to create service side connections.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6868">**CountDownAlertTime** — laiks, kuram tika parādīs atpakaļskaitīšanas brīdinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6868">**CountDownAlertTime** – Time for which countdown alert was displayed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6869">**CountdownInitTime —** laiks starp slaidrādes ielādes pabeigšanu un atpakaļskaitīšanas sākšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6869">**CountdownInitTime–** Time between slideshow load completed and countdown started.</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointrehearsalsessionmetrics"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6909">Office.PowerPoint.Rehearsal.SessionMetrics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6909">Office.PowerPoint.Rehearsal.SessionMetrics</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6910">Notikums tiek aktivizēts, kad Prezentēšanas trenera runas sesija tiek apturēta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6910">Event triggered when the speech session is stopped for Presenter Coach.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6911">Šis notikums palīdz mums fiksēt dažas Prezentēšanas trenera izmēģinājuma sesijas metrikas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6911">This event helps us in capturing some metrics for a rehearsal session in Presenter Coach.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6912">Tas palīdzēs šim līdzeklim saglābt augstu pakalpojuma kvalitātes līmeni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6912">It will help in maintaining a high quality of service for this feature.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6913">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6913">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6914">**ActualRehearseBootTimeInMs** — šis ir faktiskais laiks, kas nepieciešams, lai izveidotu savienojumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6914">**ActualRehearseBootTimeInMs** – This is the actual time taken for the connections to be created.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6915">**AdaptationTextSize** — šis ir teksta lielums, kas ir nosūtīts pakalpojumam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6915">**AdaptationTextSize** – This is the size of the text that is send to service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6916">**AuthDurationInMs** — autentifikācijai nepieciešamais laiks milisekundēs (autentifikācijas marķiera atsvaidzināšana).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6916">**AuthDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds for authentication (refresh the auth token).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6917">**AuthError** — apraksta notikušo autentifikācijas kļūdu (ja notika).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6917">**AuthError** – This describes the authentication error that occurred (if at all).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6918">**AvgFragmentLatencyInMs** — šis ir vidējais laiks, kas nepieciešams balss ziņojumu nosūtīšanai tiklā no sūtītāja adresātam un atpakaļ.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6918">**AvgFragmentLatencyInMs** – This is the average round-trip time for network speech messages.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6919">**ConnectDurationInMs** — šis ir laiks milisekundēs, kas nepieciešams sesijas savienojuma izveides pabeigšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6919">**ConnectDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds for the session to complete the connection.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6920">**FirstAudioDelayInMs** — šis ir laiks milisekundēs, kas ir nepieciešams pirmo audio datu saņemšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6920">**FirstAudioDelayInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds for the first audio data to be received.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6921">**FRetriedOnOpenConnection** — šis ir Būla, kas norāda, vai atkārtota instalēšana notiek atvērtam savienojumam vai ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6921">**FRetriedOnOpenConnection** – This is a Boolean which indicates whether retry happen for openconnection or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6922">**InitMediaCaptureLayerDurationInMs** — šis ir laiks milisekundēs, kas ir nepieciešams multivides/audio tveršanas slāņa inicializācijai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6922">**InitMediaCaptureLayerDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to initialize the media/audio capture layer.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6923">**LocallyDroppedMessageCount** — šis ir lokāli nomesto ziņojumu kopējais skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6923">**LocallyDroppedMessageCount** – This is the total number of messages dropped locally.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6924">**NumReconnectAttemptsDuringSession** — tas norāda, cik reizes tika veikts mēģinājums atkārtoti izveidot savienojumu ar runas pakalpojumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6924">**NumReconnectAttemptsDuringSession** – This indicates how many times the attempt was made to reconnect to speechservice.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6925">**NumTriesDuringEachReconnectAttempt** — šis ir masīvs, kas norāda, cik daudz mēģinājumu tika veikti katras atkārtotas savienošanas mēģinājuma laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6925">**NumTriesDuringEachReconnectAttempt** – This is an array that indicates number of tries that were done during each reconnect attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6926">**OpenFrontDoorConnectionDurationInMs** — šis ir laiks milisekundēs, kas ir nepieciešams, lai atvērtu savienojumu ar pakalpojumu FrontDoor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6926">**OpenFrontDoorConnectionDurationInMs** – This is the time in milliseconds taken to open the connection to the FrontDoor service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6927">**SendAdaptationTextDurationInMs** — šis ir laiks milisekundēs, kas ir nepieciešams, lai pakalpojumam nosūtītu adaptācijas tekstu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6927">**SendAdaptationTextDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to send the adaptation text to the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6928">**ServiceDroppedMessageCount** — šis ir pakalpojuma nomesto ziņojumu kopējais skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6928">**ServiceDroppedMessageCount** – This is the total number of messages dropped by the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6929">**SessionDurationInMs** — šis ir visu seansu laika ilgums, kad lietotājs noklikšķināja sākt līdz kad lietotājs noklikšķināja apturēt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6929">**SessionDurationInMs** – This is the time duration of entire session from when user clicked start to when user clicked stop.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6930">**SessionId** — šis ir runas FrontDoor sesijas ID. Mēs to varam izmantot, lai atkļūdotu pakalpojumu darbības žurnālus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6930">**SessionId** – This is the speech frontdoor session id. We can use this to debug service logs.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6931">**SpeechClientResultEventsWithTimestamps** — šis kļūdu kodu masīvs, kas ir saņemts kopā ar laikspiedoliem, kas var palīdzēt veikt atkļūdošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6931">**SpeechClientResultEventsWithTimestamps** – This is an array of error codes received along with the timestamps which can help in debugging.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6932">**SpeechHResultsWithTimestamps** — šis kļūdu kodu masīvs, kas ir saņemts kopā ar laikspiedoliem, kas var palīdzēt veikt atkļūdošanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6932">**SpeechHResultsWithTimestamps** – This is an array of error codes received along with the timestamps which can help in debugging.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6933">**StartSpeechCaptureDurationInMs** — šis ir laiks milisekundēs, kas ir nepieciešams, lai sāktu runas tveršanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6933">**StartSpeechCaptureDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to start speech capture.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6934">**StartSpeechServiceDurationInMs** — šis ir laika masīvs, kas nepieciešams, lai sāktu runas sesiju katru reizi, kad tiek izveidots savienojums, tostarp arī pirmās runas sesijas sākuma ilgumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6934">**StartSpeechServiceDurationInMs** – This is an array of time taken to start speech session every time there is reconnect, including first start speech session duration also.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6935">**TotalMessageCount** — šis ir kopējais pakalpojumam nosūtīto audio ziņojumu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6935">**TotalMessageCount** – This is the total number of audio messages sent to the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-6936">**WebSocketConnectDurationInMs** — šis ir laiks milisekundēs, kas nepieciešams, lai pabeigtu tīmekļa ligzdas savienojuma izveidi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-6936">**WebSocketConnectDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to complete the web socket connection.</span></span>
