#### <a name="onenoteappsafebootdialogactiontaken-officeonenoteandroidsafebootdialogactiontaken-officeandroidearlytelemetrysafebootdialogactiontaken"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7012">OneNote.App.SafeBootDialogActionTaken, Office.OneNote.Android.SafeBootDialogActionTaken, Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.SafeBootDialogActionTaken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7012">OneNote.App.SafeBootDialogActionTaken, Office.OneNote.Android.SafeBootDialogActionTaken, Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.SafeBootDialogActionTaken</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7013">Kritiskais signāls, kas tiek izmantots, lai sekotu lietotāju reakcijai uz drošas sāknēšanas dialoglodziņu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7013">The critical signal used to track user response when he/she sees a safe boot dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7014">Drošas sāknēšanas dialoglodziņš tiek parādīts, kad mums atkārtoti neizdodas palaist programmu. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7014">Safe boot dialog is shown when we were unable to launch repeatedly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7015">Lietotāja izvēle veikt drošo sāknēšanu tiek izmantota kā atļauja, lai dzēstu programmas datus un veiksmīgi palaistu programmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7015">User choice to safe boot is used as permission to clear app data to launch successfully.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7016">Tek izmantota kritiskas regresijas atklāšanai OneNote lietojumprogrammā un pakalpojuma darbspējā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7016">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7017">Lietotājs to redz, kad saskaras ar kritisku sāknēšanas avārijas kļūdu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7017">User sees when they encounter critical boot crash bug.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7018">Šī informācija palīdzēs mums noteikt, vai avārijas iemesls ir atrisināts un vai lietotājs var veiksmīgi palaist programmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7018">This info will help track if they crash cause has been resolved and user can launch the app successfully or not.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7019">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7019">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7020">**DIALOG_ACTION** — norāda, kuru dialoglodziņu noklikšķināja lietotājs – pozitīvas vai negatīvas atbildes poga</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7020">**DIALOG_ACTION** - Which dialog button did the user click on – Positive button or negative button</span></span>


#### <a name="onenotesyncprovisioningcompleted-previous-name-officeonenoteandroidsyncprovisioningcompleted"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7021">OneNote.Sync.ProvisioningCompleted *(iepriekšējais nosaukums)*, Office.OneNote.Android.Sync.ProvisioningCompleted</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7021">OneNote.Sync.ProvisioningCompleted *(previous name)*, Office.OneNote.Android.Sync.ProvisioningCompleted</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7022">Kritiskais signāls, kas tiek izmantots, ka pēc lietotāja pierakstīšanās OneNote Android lietojumprogrammā, tiek atbilstoši nodrošinātas piezīmju grāmatiņas, lai tām būtu vienkārši piekļūt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7022">The critical signal used to ensure that after a user signs-into a OneNote Android App, notebooks are properly provisioned so that they can be easily accessed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7023">Tek izmantota kritiskas regresijas atklāšanai OneNote lietojumprogrammā un pakalpojuma darbspējā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7023">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7024">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7024">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7025">**AppSuspendedDuringEvent** — Būla izteiksme, kas norāda, vai lietojumprogramma tika aizturēta nodrošināšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7025">**AppSuspendedDuringEvent** - Returns Boolean to indicate if app was suspended during provisioning</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7026">**NetworkConnection** — izmantotās ierīces tīkla savienojamības tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7026">**NetworkConnection** - The type of network connectivity of the device in use</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7027">**NetworkDataExchange** — reģistrē nodrošināšanas laikā apmainīto baitu skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7027">**NetworkDataExchange** - Records the number of bytes exchanged during provisioning.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7028">**ServerType** — atgriež tā servera tipu, kas piedāvā pakalpojumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7028">**ServerType** - Returns the type of the server offering the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7029">**TimeTakenInMilliSeconds** — norāda nodrošināšanas pabeigšanai nepieciešamo laiku milisekundēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7029">**TimeTakenInMilliSeconds** - Returns time taken to complete provisioning in millisecond</span></span>

#### <a name="onenotesyncprovisioningstarted-previous-name-officeonenoteandroidsyncprovisioningstarted"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7030">OneNote.Sync.ProvisioningStarted *(iepriekšējais nosaukums)*, Office.OneNote.Android.Sync.ProvisioningStarted</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7030">OneNote.Sync.ProvisioningStarted *(previous name)*, Office.OneNote.Android.Sync.ProvisioningStarted</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7031">Kritiskais signāls, kas tiek izmantots, ka pēc lietotāja pierakstīšanās OneNote Android lietojumprogrammā, tiek atbilstoši nodrošinātas piezīmju grāmatiņas, lai tām būtu vienkārši piekļūt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7031">The critical signal used to ensure that after a user signs into a OneNote Android App, notebooks are properly provisioned so that they can be easily accessed.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7032">Tek izmantota kritiskas regresijas atklāšanai OneNote lietojumprogrammā un pakalpojuma darbspējā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7032">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7033">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7033">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7034">**NetworkConnection** — izmantotās ierīces tīkla savienojamības tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7034">**NetworkConnection** - The type of network connectivity of the device in use</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7035">**ServerType** — atgriež tā servera tipu, kas piedāvā pakalpojumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7035">**ServerType** - Returns the type of the server offering the service</span></span>

#### <a name="perfevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7036">perf.event</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7036">perf.event</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7037">Izmanto, lai uzraudzītu iespējamo negatīvo ietekmi uz dažādu lietojumprogrammas daļu ielādes veiktspēju, piemēram, lai nodrošinātu to, ka pirmajā lietojumprogrammas atvēršanas reizē jūsu iesūtne tiktu ielādēta tik ātri, cik iespējams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7037">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on performance of loading different parts of the app, for example to ensure when you first open the app, your inbox loads as quickly as possible.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7038">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7038">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7039">**app_start_show_message_list** — nozīmē to, ka notika lietojumprogrammas sāknēšanas veiktspējas problēma, kuras rezultātā jūsu iesūtnes ziņojumu saraksta ielādei bija nepieciešams ilgs laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7039">**app_start_show_message_list** - that means there was a performance issue with the app start-up causing your inbox message list to take a long time to load</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7040">**event_type** — norāda, kāda veida veiktspējas notikums izraisīja veiktspējas problēmu, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt problēmas, kas saistītas ar konkrētu tipu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7040">**event_type** - tells us the type of performance event that caused a performance issue to help us detect issues related to a specific type.</span></span>   

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7041">**extra_params** — izstrādātājs šeit var pievienot papildu parametrus, lai sniegtu mums vairāk informācijas par šīs veiktspējas problēmas iemesliem, piemēram, kad šī darbība sākās un beidzās utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7041">**extra_params** - A developer can add additional parameters here to help give us more details about what could be causing this performance issue, i.e. when did this action start and end, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7042">**profiling_summary** — nodrošina informāciju par uzdevumu grupu, uzdevumu skaitu un vidējo šo grupu ilgumu, lai palīdzētu mums izprast potenciālo regresiju konkrētos apgabalos programmas ielādes laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7042">**profiling_summary** - provides information about the group of tasks, the number of tasks and the average time for those groups to help understand potential regressions in specific areas when loading the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7043">**total_time_elapsed** — norāda veiktspējas notikuma ilgumu, lai palīdzētu mums noteikt veiktspējas problēmas nozīmīgumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7043">**total_time_elapsed** - Tells us how long the performance event took to help us understand the severity of the performance issue</span></span>

#### <a name="performancerecord"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7044">performance.record</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7044">performance.record</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7045">Šis notikums apkopo lietojumprogrammas veiktspējas rādītājus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7045">This event collects performance metrics of the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7046">Tas ļauj mums noteikt un novērst situācijas, kad lietojumprogrammas atmiņas izmantošana un procesora izmantošana kļūst kritiski augsta vai ir citas veiktspējas problēmas, kas var izraisīt jūsu ierīces darbības palēnināšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7046">This allows us to detect and fix situations where the app memory usage and CPU usage becomes critically high or has other performance issues which could cause your device to slow down.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7047">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7047">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7048">**app_exit_metric** — informējiet mūs par dažādu veiktspējas tipu priekšplāna un fona lietojumprogrammu veiktspējas tipiem, kad lietojumprogramma negaidīti tiek aizvērta, lai mums būtu pieejama salīdzināma informācija negatīvās ietekmes uz veiktspēju noteikšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7048">**app_exit_metric** - Tell us the metrics about counts of different performance types of foreground and background app exits, to help us understand app exits unexpectedly with negative performance reasons.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7049">**average_suspended_memory** — parāda vidējo atmiņas apjomu, ko programma izmanto, kad tas ir aizturēts, tāpēc mums ir kaut kas, kas ir jāsalīdzina, lai mums būtu pieejama salīdzināma informācija negatīvās ietekmes uz veiktspēju noteikšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7049">**average_suspended_memory** - Tells us the average amount of memory in use by the app when it’s suspended so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7050">**category** — norāda, vai lietojumprogramma konkrētajā laikā ir priekšplānā vai fonā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7050">**category** - Tells us if the app is in the foreground or background at the time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7051">Iespējamās vērtības iekļauj priekšplānu un fonu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7051">Possible values include foreground and background.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7052">**cpu_usage** — norāda, kādu daļu procesora procentu izteiksmē izmantoja lietojumprogramma, lai mums būtu pieejama salīdzināma informācija negatīvās ietekmes uz veiktspēju noteikšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7052">**cpu_usage** - Tells us how much CPU was used by the app so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7053">**cumulative_CPU_time** — parāda kopējo centrālā procesora lielumu, kas tiek izmantots, lai noteiktu laika ilgumu, lai mums būtu pieejama salīdzināma informācija negatīvās ietekmes uz veiktspēju noteikšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7053">**cumulative_CPU_time** - Tells us the total amount of CPU the app used with the measurement of duration of time, so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7054">**cumulative_GPU_time** — parāda, cik daudz GPU laika tiek izmantots, lai iegūtu salīdzinājumu, kas palīdzēs mums izprast negatīvo akumulatora darbības ilgumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7054">**cumulative_GPU_time** - Tells us the total amount of GPU time used by the app, so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative battery life impact.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7055">**is_watch_app_installed** — norāda, vai lietotājs pašlaik izmanto Apple Watch un vai tas ir instalēts, lai palīdzētu mums izprast pulksteņa radīto negatīvo ietekmi uz veiktspēju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7055">**is_watch_app_installed** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is installed to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7056">**is_watch_paired** — norāda, vai lietotājs pašlaik izmanto Apple Watch un vai tas ir savienots ar ierīci, lai palīdzētu mums noteikt Apple Watch radīto negatīvo ietekmi uz veiktspēju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7056">**is_watch_paired** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is paired with the device to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7057">**is_watch_supported_and_active** — norāda, vai lietotājs pašlaik izmanto Apple Watch un vai tas ir aktīvs, lai palīdzētu mums izprast pulksteņa radīto negatīvo ietekmi uz veiktspēju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7057">**is_watch_supported_and_active** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is active to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7058">**memoAry_used_percentage** — norāda, kādu daļu atmiņas procentu izteiksmē izmantoja lietojumprogramma, lai mums būtu pieejama salīdzināma informācija negatīvās ietekmes uz veiktspēju noteikšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7058">**memoAry_used_percentage** - Tells us what percentage of memory was used by the app so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7059">**memory_used** — norāda, cik daudz atmiņas izmantoja lietojumprogramma, lai mums būtu pieejama salīdzināma informācija negatīvās ietekmes uz veiktspēju noteikšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7059">**memory_used** - Tells us how much memory was used by the app so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7060">**memory_used** — norāda lielāko programmas izmantoto atmiņu, lai mums būtu pieejama salīdzināma informācija negatīvās ietekmes uz veiktspēju noteikšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7060">**peak_memory_usage** - Tells us the largest amount of memory used by the app so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7061">**scroll_hitch_time_ratio** — norāda laika attiecību, kas pavadīts, saskaroties ar ķibelēm, vienlaikus ritinot uz UI, lai palīdzētu mums izprast negatīvo UI veiktspējas ietekmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7061">**scroll_hitch_time_ratio** - Tells us the ratio of the time spent hitching while scrolling on UI, to help us understand the negative UI performance impact.</span></span>


### <a name="application-activity-error-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7062">*Lietojumprogrammas darbības kļūdas apakštips*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7062">*Application activity error subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7063">Līdzekļa funkcionalitātes vai lietošanas iespēju kļūdas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7063">Errors in functionality of a feature or user experience.</span></span>

#### <a name="assertion"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7064">assertion</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7064">assertion</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7065">Šis notikums ļauj mums noteikt, kad notiek kritiskas lietojumprogrammas kļūdas, kas izraisa jūsu lietojumprogrammas avāriju vai nopietnas problēmas, kuru rezultātā jūs redzat tukšas rindas jūsu iesūtnē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7065">This event lets us detect when critical app errors occurred that would cause your app to crash or experience serious issues like causing you to see empty rows in your inbox.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7066">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7066">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7067">**count** — kopējais ar kļūdu saistīto vienumu skaits, piemēram, kalendāru ar kļūdām skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7067">**count** - Total number of items associated with the error; for example, number of calendars that have errors</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7068">**has_hx** — norāda, vai konts izmanto jauno sinhronizācijas pakalpojumu, lai palīdzētu noteikt mūsu sinhronizācijas pakalpojuma radītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7068">**has_hx** - Tells us the account is using our new sync service to help us detect issues caused by our sync service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7069">**host_name** — ar kļūdu saistītā pakalpojuma resursdatora nosaukums, kas ļauj mums noteikt ar konkrēto resursdatoru saistītās kļūdas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7069">**host_name** - the name of the service host that was involved in the error to help us detect issues related to a specific host</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7070">**host_name** — ar kļūdu saistītā resursdatora tips, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar konkrētu resursdatora tipu saistītās problēmas </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7070">**host_type** - the type of host that was involved in the error to help us detect issues related to a specific host type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7071">**message** — pielāgots ziņojums novērtējumam, kas tiek izmantots problēmas diagnosticēšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7071">**message** - custom message for the assertion that is used to diagnose the issue</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7072">**origin** — kļūdas izcelsme kodā, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar konkrēto koda daļu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7072">**origin** - the origin of the error in the code to help us detect issues related to a certain part of the code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7073">**stacktrace** — izsekošanas steks, kurā notika novērtējums, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar konkrētu koda daļu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7073">**stacktrace** - the stack trace where the assertion occurred to help us detect issues related to a certain part of the code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7074">**type** — notikušās novērtējuma kļūdas tips, piemēram, null_folder_name, compose_selected_null_account, kas palīdz mums noteikt ar konkrētu koda daļu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7074">**type** - the type of assertion error that occurred, e.g. null_folder_name, compose_selected_null_account, to help us detect issues related to a certain part of the code</span></span>

#### <a name="editcontacterror"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7075">edit.contact.error</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7075">edit.contact.error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7076">Ļauj mums noteikt un novērst situācijas, kad kļūdas notiek tad, kad mēģināt apskatīt vai rediģēt kontaktpersonas mūsu lietojumprogrammā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7076">Allows us to detect and fix situations where errors were caused when you're trying to view or edit contacts through our app.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7077">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7077">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7078">**errorType** — notikušās kļūdas tips, kas palīdz mums diagnosticēt problēmu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7078">**errorType** - the type of error that occurred to help us diagnose the issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7079">**field** — kontaktpersonas lauks, ko lietotājs mēģināja rediģēt, kas palīdz mums diagnosticēt problēmu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7079">**field** - The contact field that the user was trying to edit to help us diagnose the issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7080">**version** — mūsu izmantotā kontaktpersonas kartītes pakalpojuma versija, kas palīdz mums diagnosticēt problēmu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7080">**version** - The version of the contact card service we are using to help us diagnose the issue</span></span>

#### <a name="errorreport"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7081">error.report</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7081">error.report</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7082">Šis notikums ļauj mums noteikt, kad notika kritiskās lietojumprogrammas kļūdas, lai mēs varētu novērst problēmas, kas izraisa jūsu lietojumprogrammas avārijas vai neļauj jums lasīt e-pasta ziņojumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7082">This event lets us detect when critical app errors occurred so that we can prevent issues that could cause your app to crash or prevent you from reading email.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7083">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7083">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7084">**client-request-id** — klienta pieprasītais identifikators pieprasījumam, kas izraisīja kļūdu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7084">**client-request-id** - the client request identifier for the request which caused the error</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7085">**date** — pieprasījuma, kas izraisīja kļūdu, laikspiedols</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7085">**date** - the datestamp of the request which caused the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7086">**error** — kļūdas tips, piemēram, get_mailbox_location_failed</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7086">**error** - the type of error, e.g. get_mailbox_location_failed</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7087">**error_body** — kļūdas ziņojuma pamatteksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7087">**error_body** - the body of the error message</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7088">**is_x_mailbox_anchor_set** — norāda, vai pieprasījumā tika iestatīts rekvizīts X-AnchorMailbox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7088">**is_x_mailbox_anchor_set** - whether the X-AnchorMailbox property was set on the request</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7089">**reason** — norāda kļūdas iemeslu, piemēram, kļūdas ziņojums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7089">**reason** - the reason for the error, i.e. an error message</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7090">**request-id** — servera pieprasījuma identifikators pieprasījumam, kas izraisīja kļūdu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7090">**request-id** - the server request identifier for the request which caused the error</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7091">**source** — kļūdas avots OM infrastruktūrā, parasti viens no 'BE' vai 'FE'</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7091">**source** - the source of the error within the OM infrastructure, typically one of 'BE' or 'FE'</span></span>


#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriversofthang"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7092">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverSoftHang</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7092">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverSoftHang</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7093">Palīdz Microsoft nošķirt videokartes draivera nereaģēšanas gadījumus no īsākiem gadījumiem, lai vieglāk pieņemtu lēmumus par to, kuriem videokartes draiveriem, iespējams, ir radušās problēmas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7093">Helps Microsoft separate long video card driver hangs from short ones, which in turn helps make decisions about which video card drivers may be having problems.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7094">Lietotāja videokartes draiveris izraisīja situāciju, kurā Office pārtrauca reaģēt, taču šīs situācijas ietekme vēl nav zināma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7094">The user's video card driver has caused Office to hang, but the impact of the hang is not known yet</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7095">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7095">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7096">**Data\_InDeviceCall** — metode izsauca videokarti, kas izraisīja reaģēšanas pārtraukumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7096">**Data\_InDeviceCall** - The method called on the video card that produced the hang</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7097">**Data\_Timeout** — cik ilgi nereaģēja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7097">**Data\_Timeout** - How long the hang lasted</span></span>

  #### <a name="officeandroidadalsigninuiprompts"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7098">Office.Android.ADALSignInUIPrompts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7098">Office.Android.ADALSignInUIPrompts</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7099">Šīs notikums norāda, ka lietotājs saņēma pierakstīšanās uzvedni skolas vai darba kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7099">This event denotes that sign-in prompt came to the user, for school or work account.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7100">Šis notikums palīdz saprast mūsu lietojumprogrammu pierakstīšanās stāvokļa darbspēju un atbilstoši rīkoties, kad pamanām neparedzētas pierakstīšanās uzvednes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7100">This event helps in understanding the health of signed in state of our apps and take appropriate actions, when we notice unexpected sign-in re-prompts.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7101">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7101">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7102">**LastLoginDelta** — laika delta no pēdējās sekmīgās pieteikšanās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7102">**LastLoginDelta** - The time delta from last successful login.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7103">**PreviousIdentityCredProviderState** — norāda konta stāvokli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7103">**PreviousIdentityCredProviderState** - Indicates the state of the account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7104">**PreviousIdentityState** — norāda konta stāvokli, piemēram, sesijas laiks beidzies.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7104">**PreviousIdentityState** - Indicates state of the account, like session expired.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7105">**SignInResultCode** — norāda pierakstīšanās uzvednes beigu rezultātā kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7105">**SignInResultCode** - Indicates the result code of sign-in prompt end.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7106">**UseCache**— norāda, vai mēs ar uzvednes palīdzību likām lietotājam ievadīt paroli atkārtoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7106">**UseCache** - Indicates if we force prompted the user to provide the password again.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7107">**UserType** — norāda, vai tas ir esošs konts vai jauns konts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7107">**UserType** - Indicates whether it is existing account or new account</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidappdocsfileoperationends"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7108">Office.Android.AndroidAppDocsFileOperationEnds</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7108">Office.Android.AndroidAppDocsFileOperationEnds</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7109">Kritiskie dokumenti tikai Android (AppDocs) telemetrijas dati faila jauns/atvērt/saglabāt kā beigu darbībām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7109">Critical Docs Android Only (AppDocs) telemetry data for File New/Open/SaveAs end operations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7110">Uzskaita šo AppDocs neveiksmīgo darbību kļūdu kodus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7110">This captures error codes for failures of these AppDocsOperations.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7111">Microsoft to izmanto, lai noteiktu kļūmes dažādās failu darbībā un precīzo slāni, kurā radās Word, Excel vai PowerPoint lietojumprogrammu kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7111">Microsoft uses this to identify failures in various file operation and the exact layer at which the failure has occurred in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7112">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7112">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7113">**AccessMode** — faila piekļuves režīma uzskaitījuma vērtība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7113">**AccessMode** - enumeration value for the access mode for the file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7114">Vērtības — nav, ReadOnly, ReadOnlyUpgradable, ReadWrite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7114">Values- None, ReadOnly, ReadOnlyUpgradable, ReadWrite</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7115">**BlockingUIShown** — būla, kas norāda, vai jebkurā vietā plūsmā tika parādīts bloķēšanas lietotāja interfeiss.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7115">**BlockingUIShown** - Boolean to indicate if blocking UI was shown in the flow anywhere.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7116">**ContentUriAuthority** — satura URL no SAF iestādes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7116">**ContentUriAuthority** - the authority of the content URL from SAF</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7117">**Correlation** — GUID ar darbību saistītajam sasaistes ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7117">**Correlation** - GUID for the correlation Id related to the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7118">**DocId** — AppDocs ģenerētais dokumenta ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7118">**DocId** - the document ID generated by AppDocs</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7119">**DocInstanceId** — AppDocs ģenerētā dokumenta instances ID, kas ir ietverta darbības instancē dokumentā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7119">**DocInstanceId** - DocInstanceId the document instance ID generated by AppDocs that is scoped to an operation instance on a document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7120">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** — būla, kas norāda, vai dokuments ir aizsargāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7120">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** - Boolean to indicate if document is protected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7121">**DocUserId** — lietotāja ID no MS autentifikācijas slāņa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7121">**DocUserId** - user ID from the MS auth layer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7122">**DocUserIdProvider** — uzskaitījums, kas apzīmē lietotāja ID nodrošinātāju, 0 = nezināms, 1 = LiveId, 2 = OrgId, 3 = SSPI, 4 = ADAL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7122">**DocUserIdProvider** - enumeration that represents the user ID provider, 0 = Unkown, 1 = LiveId, 2 = OrgId, 3 = SSPI, 4 = ADAL</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7123">**DurationInMs** — faila darbības beigšanās laiks milisekundēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7123">**DurationInMs** - time in millisecond for the file operation to end</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7124">**EndReason** — uzskaitījuma vērtība, kas apzīmē beigu iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7124">**EndReason** - enumeration value for the end reason.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7125">Vērtības — nav, izdevās, neizdevās, atcelt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7125">Values - None, Success, Failure, Cancel</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7126">**ErrorCode** — faila darbības kļūdas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7126">**ErrorCode** - error code for the file operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7127">**Extension** — faila, kas tiek atvērts, paplašinājums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7127">**Extension** - extension of the file being opened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7128">**FileSourceLocation** — faila atrašanās vietas uzskaitījuma vērtība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7128">**FileSourceLocation** - enumeration value for file location.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7129">Iespējamās vērtības: nav, lokāls, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, lietojumprogramma, SharePoint, UnknownServer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7129">Possible values: None, Local, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, UnknownServer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7130">**FILETIME** — notikuma laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7130">**FILETIME** - Time of the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7131">**FirstBCSClientError_Info** — kļūdas koda informācija, kas saistīta ar failu konvertēšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7131">**FirstBCSClientError_Info** - Error code information related to file conversions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7132">**HttpStatusCode** — http atbildes kods tīmekļa pakalpojuma pieprasījumam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7132">**HttpStatusCode** - http response code for web service request</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7133">**InitalizationReason** — faila atvēršanas ieejas punkts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7133">**InitalizationReason** - entry point for file open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7134">**K2FileIOHresult** — Hresult kods faila atvēršanas darbības beigām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7134">**K2FileIOHresult** - Hresult code for File open operation end</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7135">**LastBCSClientError_TagId** — pēdējā BCS (binārā konvertēšanas pakalpojums) klienta kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7135">**LastBCSClientError_TagId** - last error of BCS (binary conversion service) client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7136">**OfficeWebServiceApiStatusFlag** — statusa karodziņš tīmekļa pakalpojuma pieprasījumam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7136">**OfficeWebServiceApiStatusFlag** - status flag for the web service request</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7137">**OpEndEventId** — atzīme, kas norāda, kur faktiski beidzās darbība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7137">**OpEndEventId** - tag that represents where the operation actually ended</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7138">**OpFlags** — dokumenta darbību param. karodziņi, ko izmanto AppDocs slānis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7138">**OpFlags** - Document operation param flags used by AppDocs layer.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7139">**OpSeqNum** — skaitlis, kas norāda ar failu darbību saistīto pieprasījumu secību AppDocs slānī</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7139">**OpSeqNum** - A number that represents the sequencing of file operation related calls in AppDocs layer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7140">**OpType** — darbības veida uzskaitījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7140">**OpType** - operation type enumeration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7141">Vērtības: "nav", "CreateDocument", "OpenDocument", "CopyDocument", "CloseDocument", "SaveDocument", "OpenVersion", "CloseVersion"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7141">Values: "None", "CreateDocument", "OpenDocument", "CopyDocument", "CloseDocument", "SaveDocument", "OpenVersion", "CloseVersion"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7142">**PreFetchState** — uzskaitījums jaunu failu izveides darbību vedņu iepriekšējās ieneses stāvoklim.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7142">**PreFetchState** - enumeration for prefetch state of templates for new file create operations.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7143">**ProviderApp** — tās lietojumprogrammas pakotnes nosaukums, no kuras tiek atvērts fails</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7143">**ProviderApp** - the package name of the app from which file is opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7144">**ScopeInstanceId** — tvēruma instances ID, kas tiek lietots datu konteksta pievienošanai darbībām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7144">**ScopeInstanceId** - Scope Instance ID used to join data context to activities</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7145">**Size** — faila lielums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7145">**Size** - file size</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7146">**State** — faila stāvokļa uzskaitījuma vērtība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7146">**State** - enumeration value for the state of the file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7147">Vērtības: nav, notiek izveide, izveidots, neizdevās izveidot, atvēršana, atvērts, atvēršana neizdevās, notiek kopēšana, kopēšana neizdevās, notiek aizvēršana, aizvērts, aizvēršana neizdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7147">Values: None, Creating, Created, CreateFailed, Opening, Opened, OpenFailed, Copying, Copied, CopyFailed, Closing, Closed, CloseFail</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7148">**TemplateName** — binārais dokumenta veidnes no veidņu pakalpojuma nosaukums, piemēram, TF10002009.dotx</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7148">**TemplateName** - the binary template name of the document template from the template service, e.g. TF10002009.dotx</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7149">**UriScheme** — URL shēma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7149">**UriScheme** - scheme of the URL</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidautherror"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7150">Office.Android.AndroidAuthError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7150">Office.Android.AndroidAuthError</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7151">Šis notikums apzīmē pamata autentifikācijas kļūmes klusās marķiera atsvaidzināšanas laikā, pakalpojuma pierakstīšanās lapas ielādes laikā un tā tālāk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7151">This event denotes core authentication failures during silent token refresh, loading sign in page from service and so on.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7152">Šis notikums palīdz saprast mūsu lietojumprogrammu pierakstīšanās stāvokļa darbspēju, veiktos pierakstīšanās mēģinājumus, un atbilstoši rīkoties, kad pamanām neparedzētas kļūmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7152">This event helps in understanding the health of signed in state of our apps, sign in attempts that are made, and take appropriate actions, when we notice unexpected failures.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7153">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7153">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7154">**ADALErrorCode** — norāda kļūdas kodu, vienlaikus parādot pierakstīšanās uzvedni vai kluso marķiera ieneses mēģinājumu darba kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7154">**ADALErrorCode** - Indicates error code while showing sign-in prompt or silent token fetch attempt for work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7155">**ADALErrorCode** — norāda neapstrādāto kļūdas kodu, vienlaikus parādot pierakstīšanās uzvedni vai kluso marķiera ieneses mēģinājumu darba kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7155">**ADALRawErrorCode** - Indicates raw error code while showing sign-in prompt or silent token fetch attempt for work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7156">**ErrorGroup** — norāda konta veidu, piemēram, personiskais vai darba konts vai lokālo darba kontu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7156">**ErrorGroup** - Indicates the type of account like personal account or work account or on-premise work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7157">**IDCRLErrorCode** — norāda kļūdas kodu, vienlaikus parādot pierakstīšanās uzvedni personiskajam kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7157">**IDCRLErrorCode** - Indicates error code while showing sign-in prompt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7158">**IDCRLRawErrorCode** — norāda neapstrādātu kļūdas kodu, vienlaikus parādot pierakstīšanās uzvedni personiskajam kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7158">**IDCRLRawErrorCode** - Indicates raw error code while showing sign-in prompt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7159">**LiveOAuthErrorCode** — norāda kļūdas kodu personiskā konta klusā marķiera atsvaidzināšanas mēģinājuma laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7159">**LiveOAuthErrorCode** - Indicates error code during silent token refresh attempt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7160">**LiveOAuthRawErrorCode** — norāda neapstrādātu kļūdas kodu personiskā konta klusā marķiera atsvaidzināšanas mēģinājuma laikā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7160">**LiveOAuthRawErrorCode** - Indicates raw error code during silent token refresh attempt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7161">**NTLMErrorCode** — norāda kļūdas kodu, vienlaikus parādot pierakstīšanās uzvedni lokālajam kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7161">**NTLMErrorCode** - Indicates error code while showing sign-in prompt for on-premise work account.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidfileasyncsavestatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7162">Office.Android.AndroidFileAsyncSaveStatus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7162">Office.Android.AndroidFileAsyncSaveStatus</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidofficeactivationlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7234">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeActivationLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7234">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeActivationLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7235">Kritiski svarīgi dati, lai apkopotu pilnvērtīgu faila atvēršanas laiku visām faila atvēršanām Windows, Excel, PowerPoint lietojumprogrammās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7235">Critical data to collect end-to-end file open time for all file opens in Windows, Excel, PowerPoint apps.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7236">Microsoft to izmanto, lai noskaidrotu mūsu lietojumprogrammu failu atvēršanas metriku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7236">This is used by Microsoft to find out the metric for file open performance of our apps</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7237">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7237">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7238">**AppBootingOccured** — būla, lai pārbaudītu, vai lietojumprogrammas sāknēšana ir pabeigta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7238">**AppBootingOccured** - Boolean to check if app boot is complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7239">**ApplicationBootTime** — lietojumprogrammas sāknēšanas specifiskajai fāzei nepieciešamais laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7239">**ApplicationBootTime** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7240">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** — būla, lai pārbaudītu, vai lietojumprogramma tika aizturēta sāknēšanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7240">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** - Boolean to check if app was suspended during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7241">**BlockingUIShownDuringFileOpen** — būla, lai norādītu, vai faila atvēršanas darbības laikā bija bloķēšanas dialogs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7241">**BlockingUIShownDuringFileOpen** - Boolean to indicate if there was any blocking dialog during the file open operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7242">**CachedInfoAvailable** — būla, lai meklētu kešatmiņā saglabātu faila atvēršanai specifisku informāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7242">**CachedInfoAvailable** - Boolean to look for cached info specific to file open operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7243">**DocumentRecoveryInvoked** — būla, kas norāda, vai bija atgūšanu gaidošs dokuments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7243">**DocumentRecoveryInvoked** - Boolean to indicate if there was a document pending for recovery</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidappdocsfileoperationends"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7261">Office.Android.AppDocsFileOperationEnds</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7261">Office.Android.AppDocsFileOperationEnds</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7262">Kritiskie dokumenti tikai Android (AppDocs) telemetrijas dati faila jauns/atvērt/saglabāt kā beigu darbībām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7262">Critical Docs Android Only (AppDocs) telemetry data for File New/Open/SaveAs end operations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7263">Uzskaita šo AppDocs neveiksmīgo darbību kļūdu kodus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7263">This captures error codes for failures of these AppDocsOperations.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7264">Microsoft to izmanto, lai noteiktu kļūmes dažādās failu darbībā un precīzo slāni, kurā radās Word, Excel vai PowerPoint lietojumprogrammu kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7264">Microsoft uses this to identify failures in various file operation and the exact layer at which the failure has occurred in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7266">**AccessMode** — faila piekļuves režīma uzskaitījuma vērtība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7266">**AccessMode** - enumeration value for the access mode for the file.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7267">Vērtības: nav, ReadOnly, ReadOnlyUpgradable, ReadWrite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7267">Values: None, ReadOnly, ReadOnlyUpgradable, ReadWrite</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7268">**BlockingUIShown** — būla, kas norāda, vai jebkurā vietā plūsmā tika parādīts bloķēšanas lietotāja interfeiss.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7268">**BlockingUIShown** - Boolean to indicate if blocking UI was shown in the flow anywhere.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7269">**ContentUriAuthority** — satura URL no SAF iestādes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7269">**ContentUriAuthority** - the authority of the content URL from SAF</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7270">**Correlation** — GUID ar darbību saistītajam sasaistes ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7270">**Correlation** - GUID for the correlation ID related to the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7271">**DocId** — AppDocs ģenerētais dokumenta ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7271">**DocId** - the document id generated by AppDocs</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7272">**DocInstanceId** — AppDocs ģenerētā dokumenta instances ID, kas ir ietverta darbības instancē dokumentā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7272">**DocInstanceId** - DocInstanceId the document instance ID generated by AppDocs that is scoped to an operation instance on a document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7273">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** — būla, kas norāda, vai dokuments ir aizsargāts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7273">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** - Boolean to indicate if document is protected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7274">**DocUserId** — lietotāja ID no MS autentifikācijas slāņa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7274">**DocUserId** - user ID from the MS auth layer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7275">**DocUserIdProvider** — uzskaitījums, kas apzīmē lietotāja ID nodrošinātāju, 0 = nezināms, 1 = LiveId, 2 = OrgId, 3 = SSPI, 4 = ADAL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7275">**DocUserIdProvider** - enumeration that represents the user id provider, 0 = Unkown, 1 = LiveId , 2 = OrgId, 3 = SSPI, 4 = ADAL</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7276">**DurationInMs** — faila darbības pabeigšanas laiks milisekundēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7276">**DurationInMs** - time in milliseconds for the file operation to end</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7277">**EndReason** — uzskaitījuma vērtība, kas apzīmē beigu iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7277">**EndReason** - enumeration value for the end reason.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7278">Vērtības: nav, izdevās, neizdevās, atcelt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7278">Values: None, Success, Failure, Cancel</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7279">**ErrorCode** — faila darbības kļūdas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7279">**ErrorCode** - error code for the file operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7280">**Paplašinājums** — pirmās četras paplašinājuma rakstzīmes failam, kas tiek atvērts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7280">**Extension** - first four characters of the extension of the file being opened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7281">**FileSourceLocation** — faila atrašanās vietas uzskaitījuma vērtība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7281">**FileSourceLocation** - enumeration value for file location.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7282">Iespējamās vērtības: nav, lokāls, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, lietojumprogramma, SharePoint, UnknownServer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7282">Possible values: None, Local, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, UnknownServer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7283">**FILETIME** — notikuma laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7283">**FILETIME** - Time of the event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7285">**HttpStatusCode** — HTTP atbildes kods tīmekļa pakalpojuma pieprasījumam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7285">**HttpStatusCode** - HTTP response code for web service request</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7286">**InitalizationReason** — faila atvēršanas ieejas punkts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7286">**InitalizationReason** - entry point for file open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7287">**K2FileIOHresult** — Hresult kods faila atvēršanas darbības beigām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7287">**K2FileIOHresult** - Hresult code for File open operation end</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7288">**LastBCSClientError_TagId** — pēdējā BCS (binārā konvertēšanas pakalpojums) klienta kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7288">**LastBCSClientError_TagId** - last error of BCS (binary conversion service) client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7289">**OfficeWebServiceApiStatusFlag** — statusa karodziņš tīmekļa pakalpojuma pieprasījumam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7289">**OfficeWebServiceApiStatusFlag** - status flag for the web service request</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7290">**OpEndEventId** — atzīme, kas norāda, kur faktiski beidzās darbība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7290">**OpEndEventId** - tag that represents where the operation actually ended</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7291">**OpFlags** — dokumenta darbību param. karodziņi, ko izmanto AppDocs slānis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7291">**OpFlags** - Document operation param flags used by AppDocs layer.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7292">**OpSeqNum** — skaitlis, kas norāda ar failu darbību saistīto pieprasījumu secību AppDocs slānī</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7292">**OpSeqNum** - A number that represents the sequencing of file operation related calls in AppDocs layer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7293">**OpType** — darbības veida uzskaitījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7293">**OpType** - operation type enumeration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7294">Vērtības: "nav", "CreateDocument", "OpenDocument", "CopyDocument", "CloseDocument", "SaveDocument", "OpenVersion", "CloseVersion"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7294">Values: "None", "CreateDocument", "OpenDocument", "CopyDocument", "CloseDocument", "SaveDocument", "OpenVersion", "CloseVersion"</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidauthaceerrors"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7303">Office.Android.AuthACEErrors</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7303">Office.Android.AuthACEErrors</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7304">Šis notikums izmanto Microsoft kontu (MSA), lai noteiktu, kurš lietotājs mēģina pierakstīties programmā un kura telemetrija tiek aktivizēta šajā diskusijā kā daļa no nesekmīga mēģinājuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7304">This event uses the Microsoft Account (MSA) to determine which user is attempting to sign-in to the app and during that which telemetry in discussion is getting triggered as part of an unsuccessful attempt.</span></span>  

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7305">Šis pasākums palīdz veikt MSA pierakstīšanās kļūdu izplatīšanas analīzi, kas palīdz izprast neveiksmīgas MSA pierakstīšanās plūsmas beigu iemeslus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7305">This event helps with MSA sign-in error distribution analysis, which helps in understanding reasons behind unsuccessful MSA sign-in flow end.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7306">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7306">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7307">**ExceptionsName** — norāda izņēmuma klases ar izņēmuma tagiem, kas parādās pierakstīšanās ar Microsoft kontu plūsmas laikā. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7307">**ExceptionsName** - indicates exception classes with regard to exception tags that occur during Microsoft account sign-in flow.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7308">**ExceptionsTag** — norāda, kuri ieplūstošie izņēmumi savienojumā notiek MSA pierakstīšanās plūsmā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7308">**ExceptionsTag** - indicates which inflow exceptions present in union are occurring for MSA-sign in flow.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7309">**IDCRLACEErrorCode** — norāda kļūdas, kas notiek MSA pierakstīšanās plūsmas laikā, kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7309">**IDCRLACEErrorCode** - Gives error code occurring during MSA sign-in flow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7310">Dažādi kļūdu kodi ir norādīti %SRCROOT%\identity\coreapi\public\IdentityData.h</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7310">Different error codes mentioned at %SRCROOT%\identity\coreapi\public\IdentityData.h</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7311">**IDCRLAuthenticationStatusErrorCode** — norāda kļūdu kodus autentifikācijas rezultāta, kas tiek saņemts no Microsoft konta (MSA), statusam “nederīgs”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7311">**IDCRLAuthenticationStatusErrorCode** - Indicates error codes for invalid status of Authentication result coming from Microsoft Account (MSA).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7312">**IDCRLUserInteractionMissingError** — norāda, vai pierakstīšanās ar Microsoft kontu (MSA) plūsma tika aktivizēta ar karodziņu showUI atzīmētu kā nepatiesu, kas izraisīja aktivizēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7312">**IDCRLUserInteractionMissingError** - Indicates if Microsoft Account (MSA) sign-in flow invoked with showUI flag as false causing the hit.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeandroidbcserrors"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7313">Office.Android.BCS.Errors</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7313">Office.Android.BCS.Errors</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7314">Binārās konversijas kļūdu telemetrija PDF drukāšanai un koplietošanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7314">Binary conversion Errors telemetry for Print and Share as PDF.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7315">Microsoft to izmanto, lai identificētu kļūmes punktus BCS konversijas laikā Word, Excel vai PowerPoint lietojumprogrammās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7315">Microsoft uses this to identify failure points during BCS conversions in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7316">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7316">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7317">**DocumentFileSize** — faila lielums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7317">**DocumentFileSize** - File size.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7318">**FileExtension** — faila paplašinājuma pirmās četras rakstzīmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7318">**FileExtension** - First four characters of the extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7319">**IsFileDirty** — būla, kas norāda, vai failā ir nesaglabātas izmaiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7319">**IsFileDirty** - Boolean to indicate if there were unsaved changes in the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7320">**Location** — faila atrašanās vietas uzskaitījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7320">**Location** - File location enumeration.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7321">Vērtības: OneDrive, SharePoint, Dropbox, citi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7321">Values: OneDrive, SharePoint, Dropbox, Others</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7322">**PDFConversionError** — atzīme, pie kuras rodas PDF konvertēšanas kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7322">**PDFConversionError** - Tag at which error occurs for PDF conversion</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7323">**PdfConversionErrorCode** — PDF konvertēšanas kļūdas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7323">**PdfConversionErrorCode** - PDF conversion error code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7324">**PdfConversionHRStatus** — PDF konvertēšanas statusa kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7324">**PdfConversionHRStatus** - PDF conversion status code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7325">**PdfConversionResult** — PDF konvertēšanas rezultāta uzskaitījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7325">**PdfConversionResult** - PDF Conversion result enumeration.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7326">Vērtības: “izdevās”, “neizdevās” un “atcelts”</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7326">Values: "Success", "Failed" and "Canceled"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7327">**PdfFileSize** — PDF faila lielums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7327">**PdfFileSize** - Size of the PDF</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidclientsideiap"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7328">Office.Android.ClientSideIAP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7328">Office.Android.ClientSideIAP</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7329">Kritisko kļūdu telemetrija datu bāzu kļūmei, pārlūkojot failus un pievienojot vietas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7329">Critical Error telemetry for Database Failure while file browsing and adds places.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7330">Microsoft to izmanto, lai identificētu datu bāzu problēmas lietojumprogrammās, kas var traucēt lietotājam pievienot vietas vai pārlūkot tās lietojumprogrammās, izmantojot Word, Excel vai PowerPoint lietojumprogrammas. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7330">Microsoft uses this to identify DB corruption issues in the apps which might hinder user to add places or browse through them from within the app in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>
