- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7332">**ClientTransactionId** — GUID, kas tiek nodots DSC specifiskam izpirkšanas pieprasījumam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7332">**ClientTransactionId** - GUID passed to DSC for a specific Redemption request.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7333">**CollectionTime** — abonementa iegādes pabeigšanas laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7333">**CollectionTime** - time of subscription purchase completion</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7334">**CountryCode** — klienta valsts kods, kas tiek nosūtīts DSC klienta izpirkšanas pieprasījumam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7334">**CountryCode** - Client country code which is sent to DSC for client redemption request</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7335">**GoPremiumEntryPoint** — pirkuma aktivizēšanas ieejas punkts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7335">**GoPremiumEntryPoint** - entry point for triggering purchase</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7336">**IsActivateExistingSubscription** — būla, kas norāda, vai bija iepriekš esošs abonements, kas tika aktivizēts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7336">**IsActivateExistingSubscription** - Boolean to indicate if there was an existing subscription which was activated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7337">**IsErrorRetriable** — būla, kas norāda, vai izpirkšanu var atkārtot</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7337">**IsErrorRetriable** - Boolean to indicate if redemption can be retried</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7338">**IsPreviousPurchase** — būla, kas norāda, vai aktivācija notika ar iepriekšējo abonementu iegādi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7338">**IsPreviousPurchase** - Boolean to indicate if activation occurred with a previous purchase of subscription</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7339">**IsProvisioningTriggeredByRetry** — būla, kas norāda, vai tika iesaistīts atkārtots mēģinājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7339">**IsProvisioningTriggeredByRetry** - Boolean to indicate if retry was involved</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7340">**LanguageCode** — klienta valodas kods, kas tiek nosūtīts DSC klienta izpirkšanas pieprasījumam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7340">**LanguageCode** - Client language code which is sent to DSC for client redemption request</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7341">**ProductIdentifier** — SKU, kuru klients mēģina iegādāties, nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7341">**ProductIdentifier** - SKU name which the client is trying to purchase</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7342">**ProvisioningHttpStatusCode** — nodrošināšanas http statusa kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7342">**ProvisioningHttpStatusCode** - Provisioning http status code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7343">**ProvisioningStatusCode** — nodrošināšanas statusa kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7343">**ProvisioningStatusCode** - Provisioning status code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7344">**PurchaseOrderId** — pirkšanas pasūtījuma identifikators no Google/Samsung veikala</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7344">**PurchaseOrderId** - Purchase order identifier from Google/Samsung store</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7345">**RedemptionTaskHR** — HResult abonementa izpirkšanas uzdevumam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7345">**RedemptionTaskHR** - HResult for redemption task of subscription</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7346">**SubscriptionProvisioningSucceeded** — būla veiksmīgam abonementa nodrošināšanas rezultātam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7346">**SubscriptionProvisioningSucceeded** - Boolean for subscription provisioning result success</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7347">**SubscriptionPurchaseHR**— Hresult abonementa iegādes uzdevumam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7347">**SubscriptionPurchaseHR** - Hresult for subscription purchase task</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7348">**SubscriptionType** — abonementa veida vai SKU uzskaitījums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7348">**SubscriptionType** - enumeration for subscription type or SKUs.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7349">**TCID** — noklikšķināšana uz ikonas uzsāk abonementa plūsmu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7349">**TCID** - Icon click the triggers the subscription flow</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroiddbfailurecause"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7350">Office.Android.DBFailureCause</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7350">Office.Android.DBFailureCause</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7351">Kritisko kļūdu telemetrija datu bāzu kļūmei, pārlūkojot failus un pievienojot vietas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7351">Critical Error telemetry for Database Failure while file browsing and adds places.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7352">Microsoft to izmanto, lai identificētu datu bāzu problēmas lietojumprogrammās, kas var traucēt lietotājam pievienot vietas vai pārlūkot tās lietojumprogrammās, izmantojot Word, Excel vai PowerPoint lietojumprogrammas. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7352">Microsoft uses this to identify DB corruption issues in the apps which might hinder user to add places or browse through them from within the app in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7353">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7353">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7354">**ErrorAt** — atzīmes vērtība: informācija par vietu, kurā notika kļūme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7354">**ErrorAt** - Tag Value: Information about the place where the Failure happened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7355">**ExceptionErrorMessage** — izvērsts kļūdas ziņojums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7355">**ExceptionErrorMessage** - verbose error message</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidearlytelemetryexpansionfileserrors"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7356">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExpansionFilesErrors</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7356">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExpansionFilesErrors</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7357">Android paplašināšanas failu komplekta (APK) paplašināšanas faili Office mobilajai lietojumprogrammai ir papildu resursu faili, kurus Android lietojumprogrammu izstrādātāji var publicēt kopā ar savu lietojumprogrammu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7357">Android Package Kit (APK) expansion files for the Office mobile app are supplementary resource files that Android app developers can publish along with their app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7358">Lai padarītu mūsu paplašināšanas failu lejupielādes mehānismu par uzticamāku, mēs reģistrējam kļūdu iemeslus, kas rodas lejupielādējot paplašināšanas failus vai lasot lejupielādētos paplašināšanas failus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7358">To make our Expansion files download mechanism more reliable, we are logging the cause of errors that occur either in downloading the expansion files or while reading the downloaded expansion files.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7359">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7359">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7360">**Data_ClassName** — teksts, kas norāda avota koda faila nosaukumu, kurā ir kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7360">**Data_ClassName** - Text representing the source code file name where there is an error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7361">**Data_ErrorMessage** — teksts, kas norāda neveiksmīgo darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7361">**Data_ErrorMessage** - Text representing the operation that has failed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7362">**Data_ExceptionMessage** — neobligāts teksta lauks, kas norāda izņēmuma iemeslu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7362">**Data_ExceptionMessage** - An optional text field representing the cause of the exception.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7363">**Data_ExceptionType** — neobligāts teksta lauks, kas norāda izņēmumu, kas tiek izmests avota koda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7363">**Data_ExceptionType** - An optional text field representing the name of the exception thrown from source code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7364">**Data_MethodName** — teksts, kas norāda metodes nosaukumu avota kodā, kurā ir kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7364">**Data_MethodName** - Text representing the method name in source code where there is an error.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidearlytelemetryextractionerror"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7365">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExtractionError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7365">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExtractionError</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7366">Lai samazinātu Office Android programmu lielumu, mēs izmantojam gala pakotnes resursu saspiešanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7366">To reduce the size of Office Android apps, we apply compression to the resources in the final package.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7367">Izpildes laikā šie resursi tiek izvilkti pirms izmantošanas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7367">At run time, we first extract these resources before using them.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7368">Dažreiz izvilkšanas laikā var notikt neparedzētas kļūdas, kas izraisa programmas avarēšanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7368">Sometimes there are unexpected errors while performing extractions, which leads to app crashes.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7369">Ar šī notikuma palīdzību mēs apkopojam ar izvilkšanu saistītu diagnostikas informāciju, piemēram, izvelkamā resursa nosaukums, izvilkšanas ceļš, pieejamā brīvā vieta krātuvē utt. Šie dati tiek apkopoti tikai izvilkšanas kļūdu gadījumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7369">Through this event we are collecting some diagnostic information related to extraction, like name of the resource being extracted, path where its extracted etc., free disk space available etc. This data is collected only when there are extraction errors.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7370">Mēs izmantojam šos datus, lai izprastu izvilkšanas kļūdu iemeslus un lai uzlabotu mūsu programmu lietošanas pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7370">We use this data to understand the cause of extraction failures, and to improve the user experience of our apps.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7371">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7371">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7372">**Data_ArchiveName** — izvelkamā resursa nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7372">**Data_ArchiveName** - Name of the resource that is being extracted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7373">**Data_ArchivePath** — ceļš uz resursa īslaicīgās kešošanas vietu. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7373">**Data_ArchivePath** - Path where the resource is temporarily cached.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7374">**Data_ArchiveSizeKB** — izvelkamā resursa lielums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7374">**Data_ArchiveSizeKB** - Size of the resource that is being extracted.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7375">**Data_ClassName** — faila nosaukums avota kodā, kur notika kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7375">**Data_ClassName** - File name in source code where the error is encountered.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7376">**Data_ErrorDetail** — teksts, kas sniedz vairāk informācijas par kļūdas iemeslu, piemēram, kļūdas kods utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7376">**Data_ErrorDetail** - Text describing more details about the cause of the error, like the error code etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7377">**Data_ErrorMessage** — teksts, kas apraksta izvilkšanas laikā notikušās kļūdas tipu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7377">**Data_ErrorMessage** - Text describing the type of error encountered during extraction.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7378">**Data_ExtractionDestinationPath** — ceļš uz vietu, kur resurss tiks saglabāts pēc izvilkšanas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7378">**Data_ExtractionDestinationPath** - Path where the resource is to be saved after extraction.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7379">**Data_FreeDiskSpaceMB** — ierīcē pieejamās brīvās vietas apjoms megabaitos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7379">**Data_FreeDiskSpaceMB** - The amount of free disk space available on the device measured in Mega Bytes.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7380">**Data_ItemToExtract** — izvelkamā resursa nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7380">**Data_ItemToExtract** - Name of the resource that is being extracted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7381">**Data_MethodName** — metodes nosaukums avota kodā, kur notika kļūda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7381">**Data_MethodName** - Method name in source code where the error is encountered.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeandroidearlytelemetryregistryerrors"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7382">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.RegistryErrors</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7382">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.RegistryErrors</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7383">Šis notikums fiksē jebkuras kļūdas, kas radās piekļūstot Android reģistram.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7383">This event captures any errors faced during Android registry access.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7384">Šis notikums palīdz mums izprast lietotāju kļūdas un padarīt reģistra līdzekli jaudīgāku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7384">This event data helps us in understanding the user errors and making the registry feature more robust.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7385">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7385">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7386">**App** — programmas process, kas sūta notikumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7386">**App** – The application process sending the event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7387">**AppVersionLong** — programmas versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7387">**AppVersionLong** – The application version.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7388">**Data_StackTrace** — kļūdas izsekošanas steks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7388">**Data_StackTrace** – The stacktrace of the error.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidearlytelemetrysharedlibraryloadersearchandloadlibraryerror"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7389">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.SharedLibraryLoadersearchAndloadLibraryError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7389">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.SharedLibraryLoadersearchAndloadLibraryError</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7390">Mēs reģistrējam šo notikumu gadījumā, ja ir rodas kļūdas, ielādējot koplietojamās bibliotēkas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7390">We log this event in case there are errors while loading shared libraries.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7391">Bibliotēkas ielādes kļūdas var notikt divu iemeslu dēļ: 1) instalētais APK nav saderīgs ar ierīci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7391">There can be library loading errors for two reasons 1) Installed Apk is incompatible with the device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7392">2) bibliotēka, ko mēģinām ielādēt var būt bojāta kļūdu, kas rodas izvēršanas kļūdu rezultātā, kuru iemesls ir vietas trūkums diskā vai atmiņas trūkums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7392">2) The library that we are trying to load may be corrupt, because of errors in extracting it due to low disk space, or low memory.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7393">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7393">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7394">**Data_ExceptionMessage** — izņēmuma ziņojums, kuru parāda Android API System.loadlibrary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7394">**Data_ExceptionMessage** - Exception message thrown by Android API System.loadlibrary</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7395">**Data_FreeSpaceInMB** — ierīcē pieejamā brīvā vieta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7395">**Data_FreeSpaceInMB** - Free space available on device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7396">**Data_nickName** — bibliotēkas, kuru neizdevās ielādēt, nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7396">**Data_nickName** - Name of the library which couldn't be loaded.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidintuneintunejavacopyfailedattempts"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7397">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneJavaCopyFailedAttempts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7397">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneJavaCopyFailedAttempts</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7398">Kritisko kļūdu telemetriju, lai izsekotu neveiksmēm atsevišķiem Intune API; šī telemetrija tiek reģistrēta gadījumos, kad notiek kļūdas Intune aizsargāto mākoņa dokumentu lokālo kopiju saglabāšanā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7398">Critical Error telemetry to track failures for individual Intune APIs; This telemetry gets logged in case of errors to save local copy of Intune protected Cloud documents.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7399">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai identificētu kļūdas, kas rodas Intune reģistrēšanas laikā lietojumprogrammā un pēc tās pēc pierakstīšanās lietojumprogrammā ar darba kontu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7399">Microsoft uses this data to identify errors during and after Intune enrollment within the app, post signing into the app with a work account</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7400">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7400">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidlicenseactivationfailure"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7492">Office.Android.LicenseActivationFailure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7492">Office.Android.LicenseActivationFailure</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7493">Kritisko kļūdu telemetrija, kas tiek izmantota Office 365 kontu Word, Excel vai PowerPoint lietojumprogrammās licencēšanas aktivizēšanas kļūmju izsekošanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7493">Critical Error telemetry to track failures to activate licenses for Office 365 accounts in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7494">Microsoft to izmanto, lai analizētu iegādāto Office 365 licenču aktivizēšanas kļūmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7494">Microsoft uses this to analyze failures to activate a purchased Office 365 license.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7495">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7495">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7496">**EntryPoint** — ieejas punkta uzskaitījums licenču aktivizēšanas plūsmas aktivizēšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7496">**EntryPoint** - Entrypoint enumeration for triggering the license activation flow</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7497">**HResult** — kļūmes kļūdas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7497">**HResult** - error code for the failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7498">**IsGallatin** — būla, kas tiek izmantota, lai pārbaudītu, vai tas ir Gallatin konts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7498">**IsGallatin** - Boolean to check if it is a Gallatin account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7499">**MessageCode**— uzskaitījums, kas norāda aktivizēšanas kļūmes punktu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7499">**MessageCode** - enumeration to indicate the point of failure for activation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7500">**PreviousEntryPoint** — ieejas punkta uzskaitījums licenču aktivizēšanas plūsmas aktivizēšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7500">**PreviousEntryPoint** - Entrypoint enumeration for triggering the license activation flow</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7501">**StateAfterActivation** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda lietojumprogrammas licencēšanas stāvokli pirms aktivizēšanas plūsmas sākuma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7501">**StateAfterActivation** - enumeration to indicate licensing state of the app before the activation flow started</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7502">**StateBeforeActivation** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda lietojumprogrammas licencēšanas stāvokli pirms aktivizēšanas plūsmas sākuma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7502">**StateBeforeActivation** - enumeration to indicate licensing state of the app before the activation flow started</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7503">**UserAccountType** — uzskaitījums, kas norāda, vai konts ir personiskais vai uzņēmuma konts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7503">**UserAccountType** - enumeration to indicate whether personal account or enterprise account.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidmsasigninuiprompts"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7504">Office.Android.MSASignInUIPrompts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7504">Office.Android.MSASignInUIPrompts</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7505">Šīs notikums norāda, ka lietotājs saņēma pierakstīšanās uzvedni personiskajam kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7505">This event denotes that sign-in prompt came to the user, for personal account.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7506">Šis notikums palīdz saprast mūsu lietojumprogrammu pierakstīšanās stāvokļa darbspēju un atbilstoši rīkoties, kad pamanām neparedzētas pierakstīšanās uzvednes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7506">This event helps in understanding the health of signed in state of our apps and take appropriate actions, when we notice unexpected sign-in re-prompts.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7507">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7507">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7508">**ExternalCacheRefreshError** — marķiera atsvaidzināšanas mēģinājuma pirms pierakstīšanās uzvednes parādīšanas kļūdas kods.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7508">**ExternalCacheRefreshError** - Error code of token refresh attempt, before showing sign-in prompt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7509">**LastLoginDelta** — laika delta no pēdējās sekmīgās pieteikšanās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7509">**LastLoginDelta** - The time delta from last successful login.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7510">**MSAserverUAID** — korelācijas ID ar pakalpojuma telemetrijas datiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7510">**MSAserverUAID** - Correlation id with service telemetry data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7511">**PreviousIdentityState** — norāda konta stāvokli, piemēram, sesijas laiks beidzies.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7511">**PreviousIdentityState** - Indicates state of the account, like session expired.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7512">**SignInResultCode** — norāda pierakstīšanās uzvednes beigu rezultātā kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7512">**SignInResultCode** - Indicates the result code of sign-in prompt end.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7513">**UseCache**— norāda, vai mēs ar uzvednes palīdzību likām lietotājam ievadīt paroli atkārtoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7513">**UseCache** - Indicates if we force prompted the user to provide the password again.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7514">**UserType** — norāda, vai tas ir esošs konts vai jauns konts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7514">**UserType** - Indicates whether it is existing account or new account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7515">**WasIdentitySignedOut** — norāda, vai konts bija izrakstīšanās stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7515">**WasIdentitySignedOut** - Indicates if account was in signed out state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7520">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7520">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7521">**Data_DigitalRiverID** — Digital River produkta ID, kas kartē uz šo Office produkta SKY</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7521">**Data_DigitalRiverID** - Digital River product Id that maps to this Office product SKY</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7522">**Data_Error** — virkne, kas norāda aktivizācijas kļūdas kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7522">**Data_Error** - A string representing an activation error code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7523">**Data_ProductKey** — produkta atslēga, ko bija mēģināts aktivizēt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7523">**Data_ProductKey** - Product key that was attempted to be activated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7524">**Data_ProductKeyHash** — aktivizēta kodētā produkta atslēga</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7524">**Data_ProductKeyHash** - An encoded product key being activated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7526">Šo notikumu apkopo Office programmām, kas darbojas Apple platformās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7526">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7527">Pasākums apkopo kļūdas kodu, kas tiek atgriezts, periodiski pārbaudot abonementa licences derīgumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7527">The event collects the error code returned while periodically checking the validity of a subscription license.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7528">Kļūdas kods var nozīmēt servera nepieejamību, kā arī licenču derīguma beigu datumu, datoru skaita ierobežojumu, uaparatūras ID utt.  Šis notikums tiek lietots, lai pārraudzītu Office licencēšanas pakalpojuma darbspēju, kā arī izmeklētu problēmas, kas saistītas ar abonementu datoru pārvaldību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7528">The error code can signify server unavailability but also license expiration, machine count limit, invalid hardware ID, etc.  This event is used to monitor the health of the Office Licensing Service but also to investigate issues related to subscription machine management.</span></span>

#### <a name="officegraphicsarcexceptions"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7544">Office.Graphics.ARCExceptions</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7544">Office.Graphics.ARCExceptions</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7545">Šī izņēmuma uzrādītā informācija ir svarīga, lai izvērtētu kopējo grafikas steka darbspēju, kā arī identificētu tās koda daļas, kur kļūmes radās ar lielu intensitāti, lai noteiktu izmeklēšanas prioritātes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7545">This exception reporting information is important for assessing the overall health of the graphics stack, as well as identifying parts of the code where failures are occurring at high frequency, in order to prioritize investigation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7546">Šī izņēmuma uzrādītā informācija ir svarīga, lai izvērtētu kopējo grafikas steka darbspēju, kā arī identificētu tās koda daļas, kur kļūmes radās ar lielu intensitāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7546">This exception reporting information is important for assessing the overall health of the graphics stack, as well as identifying parts of the code where failures are occurring at high frequency.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7547">Tas palīdz inženierim noteikt, kuras atveidošanas kļūmes ietekmē lielāko daļu lietotāju, lai mēs varētu noteikt prioritātes mūsu ieguldījumiem, vēršot tos uz tādu problēmu novēršanu, kas lietotājiem sniegs vislielāko ieguvumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7547">This helps an engineer to determine which rendering failures are impacting the most users, enabling us to prioritize our investigations toward fixing issues that will have the greatest user benefit.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7548">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7548">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7549">**Data\_HResult** — kļūmes atgrieztais kļūdas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7549">**Data\_HResult** - The error code returned from failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7550">**Data\_TagCount** — katras radušās kļūmes skaits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7550">**Data\_TagCount** - The count of each failure that occurred</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookdesktopndbcorruptionresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7564">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NdbCorruptionResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7564">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NdbCorruptionResult</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7565">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NdbCorruptionResult un Office.Outlook.Desktop.NDBCorruptStore.Warning tiek apkopoti, kad mēs konstatējam bojājumu lietotāja PST/OST.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7565">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NdbCorruptionResult and Office.Outlook.Desktop.NDBCorruptStore.Warning are collected when we detect corruption in a user's PST/OST.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7566">Kad mēs konstatējam bojājumu, korporācija Microsoft apkopo informāciju par datu bāzes formātu, vietu, kur bojājums tika konstatēts, un nelielu kontekstinformāciju par bojājumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7566">When we detect corruption, Microsoft collects the format of the database, the place where detected it, and a small amount of context about the corruption.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7567">OST/PST bojājums neļauj lietotājiem piekļūt saviem e-pasta ziņojumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7567">OST/PST corruption prevents users from accessing their emails.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7568">Mēs aktīvi pārraugām šos datus, lai konstatētu nepareizu darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7568">We actively monitor this data for anomalous activity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7569">Mēs strādājam pie tā, lai izpētītu un diagnosticētu problēmas un ierobežotu klientu datu zudumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7569">We aim to investigate and diagnose issues to limit loss of customer data.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7570">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7570">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7571">**0 —** procesa nosaukums, kas ziņoja par bojājumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7571">**0 -** The Process name which reported corruption</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7572">**1 —** Būla virkne, kas norāda, vai lietotājs izvēlas jaunu failu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7572">**1 -** Bool indicating if the user chooses new file or not</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7573">**2 —** citu procesu skaits, kuros ir atvērta datu bāze</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7573">**2 -** the number of other processes which have the database open</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookdesktopndbcorruptstorewarning"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7574">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NDBCorruptStore.Warning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7574">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NDBCorruptStore.Warning</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7575">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NdbCorruptionResult un Office.Outlook.Desktop.NDBCorruptStore.Warning tiek apkopoti, kad mēs konstatējam bojājumu lietotāja PST/OST.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7575">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NdbCorruptionResult and Office.Outlook.Desktop.NDBCorruptStore.Warning are collected when we detect corruption in a user's PST/OST.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7576">Kad mēs konstatējam bojājumu, korporācija Microsoft apkopo informāciju par datu bāzes formātu, vietu, kur bojājums tika konstatēts, un nelielu kontekstinformāciju par bojājumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7576">When we detect corruption, Microsoft collects the format of the database, the place where detected it, and a small amount of context about the corruption.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7577">OST/PST bojājums neļauj lietotājiem piekļūt saviem e-pasta ziņojumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7577">OST/PST corruption prevents users from accessing their emails.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7578">Mēs aktīvi pārraugām šos datus, lai konstatētu nepareizu darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7578">We actively monitor this data for anomalous activity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7579">Mēs strādājam pie tā, lai izpētītu un diagnosticētu problēmas un ierobežotu klientu datu zudumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7579">We aim to investigate and diagnose issues to limit loss of customer data.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7580">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7580">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7581">**CollectionTime** — apkopošanas laiks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7581">**CollectionTime** - collection time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7582">**Context** — bojātas krātuves konteksts, kur tika konstatēts bojājums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7582">**Context** - Corrupt Store Context, where corruption was detected</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7583">**CreatedWithVersion** — (neobligāts) lauks ar krātuves versiju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7583">**CreatedWithVersion** – (Optional) field with version of store</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7587">**PstVersion** — MSPST32.DLL versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7587">**PstVersion** - Version of the MSPST32.DLL</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7588">**Version** — krātuves faila formāta versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7588">**Version** - Version of store file format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7705">Tiek apkopots, kad lietotājs mēģina atvērt ar IRM aizsargātu dokumentu vai lietot IRM aizsardzību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7705">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7706">Tas satur informāciju, kas ir nepieciešama pareizai tādu problēmu izmeklēšanai un diagnosticēšanai, kas notiek, kad neizdodas lietotāja sertifikātu atjaunošana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7706">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when failed to renew user certificates.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7707">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7707">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7718">**RMS.SDKVersion** — tiesību pārvaldības pakalpojuma klienta versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7718">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

#### <a name="saveerror"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7719">save.error</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7719">save.error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7720">Ļauj mums atklāt un novērst situācijas, kad kļūda notiek brīdī, kad mēģinājāt saglabāt failu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7720">Allows us to detect and fix situations where there was an error when you attempted to save a file.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7721">Izseko kļūdām, kuru cēlonis ir failu saglabāšanas kļūmes, iekļaujot aprakstošos kļūdu ziņojumus, kas mums palīdz atrisināt problēmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7721">It tracks errors caused by failures to save a file, including a descriptive error message to help us resolve the issue.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7722">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7722">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7723">**error** — notikušās kļūdas tips, kas palīdz mums atklāt un atrisināt problēmas, kas ir saistītas ar konkrētu kļūdas tipu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7723">**error** - The type of error that happened to help us detect and resolve issues related to a specific error type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7724">**file_type** — faila tips, ko lietotājs mēģināja saglabāt (piemēram,. doc)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7724">**file_type** - The type of file the user tried to save (such as .doc)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7725">**origin** — norāda faila saglabāšanas mēģinājuma izcelsmi (piemēram, no e-pasta), ļaujot mums noteikt ar failu saglabāšanu konkrētajā vietā lietojumprogrammā saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7725">**origin** - Where the file save attempt originated from (such as from an email) so we can detect issues associated with saving a file from a specific place in the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7726">**token_type** — faila saglabāšanai veiktās konta autentifikācijas marķiera veids, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar faila saglabāšanu saistītās autentifikācijas problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7726">**token_type** - the type of token used to authenticate the account in order to save the file to help us detect authentication issues associated with saving a file</span></span>


## <a name="device-connectivity-and-configuration-data-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7727">Ierīču savienojamības un konfigurācijas datu notikumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7727">Device connectivity and configuration data events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7728">Tālāk ir norādīti šīs kategorijas datu apakštipi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7728">The following are the data subtypes in this category:</span></span>

- [<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7729">Ierīču savienojamība un konfigurācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7729">Device connectivity and configuration</span></span>](#device-connectivity-and-configuration-subtype)


### <a name="device-connectivity-and-configuration-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7730">*Ierīču savienojamības un konfigurācijas apakštips*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7730">*Device connectivity and configuration subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7731">Tīkla savienojuma statuss un ierīces iestatījumi, piemēram, atmiņas iestatījumi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7731">Network connection state and device settings, such as memory.</span></span>

#### <a name="applicationdidreceivememorywarning"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7732">application.did.receive.memory.warning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7732">application.did.receive.memory.warning</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7733">Šis notikums tiek sūtīts, kad Apple norāda uz to, ka lietojumprogrammā sāk pietrūkt atmiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7733">This event is sent when Apple tells us that the application is running out of memory.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7734">Tas norāda mums uz to, ka mērs jūsu ierīcē radījām atmiņas pārvaldības problēmu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7734">It tells us that we have introduced an issue with memory management on your device.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7735">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7735">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7736">**current_memory_used** — norāda uz lietojumprogrammas izmantotās atmiņas apjomu brīdī, kad lietojumprogrammā beidzās atmiņa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7736">**current_memory_used** - Tells us the amount of memory used by the application at the point the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7737">**current_memory_used_percentage** — norāda uz lietojumprogrammas izmantotās atmiņas daudzumu procentu izteiksmē no kopējā pieejamā atmiņas apjoma brīdī, kad lietojumprogrammā beidzās atmiņa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7737">**current_memory_used_percentage** - Tell us the percentage of memory used by the application out of the total memory available at the point the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7738">**currentVC** — norāda, kurš skats tika rādīts brīdī, kad lietojumprogrammā beidzās atmiņa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7738">**currentVC** - Tells us the view that is currently showing when the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7739">**has_hx** — norāda, vai konts izmanto jauno sinhronizācijas pakalpojumu, lai palīdzētu noteikt mūsu sinhronizācijas pakalpojuma radītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7739">**has_hx** - Tells us the account is using our new sync service to help us detect issues caused by our sync service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7740">**is_watch_app_installed** — norāda, vai lietotājs pašlaik izmanto Apple Watch un vai tas ir instalēts, lai palīdzētu mums izprast pulksteņa radīto negatīvo ietekmi uz veiktspēju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7740">**is_watch_app_installed** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is installed to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7741">**is_watch_paired** — norāda, vai lietotājs pašlaik izmanto Apple Watch un vai tas ir savienots ar ierīci, lai palīdzētu mums noteikt Apple Watch radīto negatīvo ietekmi uz veiktspēju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7741">**is_watch_paired** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is paired with the device to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7742">**is_watch_supported_and_active** — norāda, vai lietotājs pašlaik izmanto Apple Watch un vai tas ir aktīvs, lai palīdzētu mums izprast pulksteņa radīto negatīvo ietekmi uz veiktspēju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7742">**is_watch_supported_and_active** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is active to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7743">**rn_initialized** — norāda, vai brīdī, kad lietojumprogrammā beidzās atmiņa, tika inicializēts vietējais reaģēšanas modulis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7743">**rn_initialized** - Tell us if React Native has been initialized at the point the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7744">**running_time** — norāda uz laiku, ko lietojumprogrammai pavadīja darbībā brīdī, kad lietojumprogrammā beidzās atmiņa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7744">**running_time** - Tell us the amount of time that app has spent running at the time the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

#### <a name="conversationmemoryleak"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7745">conversation.memory.leak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7745">conversation.memory.leak</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7746">Ļauj mums noteikt situācijas, kurās mūsu e-pasta sarunas skata dēļ tiek izmantots lielāks jūsu ierīces atmiņas apjoms nekā paredzēts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7746">Allows us to detect situations where our email conversation view is causing us to use up more memory on your device that expected.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7747">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7747">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7748">Lauki vai pievienotie dati netiek apkopoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7748">No fields or added data are collected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7749">Ja atmiņas noplūde ir saistīta ar sarunas pavedienu, tiek apkopoti tikai žurnāli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7749">Only logs are collected if there is a memory leak related to a conversation thread.</span></span>

#### <a name="coredatacorruption"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7750">core.data.corruption</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7750">core.data.corruption</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7751">Ļauj mums noteikt situācijas, kad mēs nevaram jums parādīt jūsu e-pastu vai kalendāru, jo krātuve jūsu ierīcē, kurā mēs glabājam jūsu e-pastu, ir bojāta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7751">Allows us to detect situations where we cannot show you your email or calendar because where we store your email on your device has become corrupted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7752">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7752">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7753">**errorSource** — norāda, vai kļūdas izcēlās no saglabāšanas vai izveidošanas darbības</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7753">**errorSource** - indicates whether it came from a save or create action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7754">**sqlError** — skaitlisks kļūdas kods, kas norādīts https://www.sqlite.org/c3ref/c_abort.html</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7754">**sqlError** - numerical error code listed at https://www.sqlite.org/c3ref/c_abort.html</span></span>

#### <a name="coredatacorruptionuserreset"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7755">core.data.corruption.user.reset</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7755">core.data.corruption.user.reset</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7756">Ļauj mums noteikt situācijas, kad jūs dzēsāt vai atiestatījāt savu kontu mūsu lietotnē, kā iemesls bija e-pasta datu, kurus mēs saglabājām jūsu ierīcē, bojājumi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7756">Allows us to detect situations where you have deleted or reset your account in our app and it was caused by a corruption in email data we've stored on your device.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7757">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7757">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7758">**errorSource** — norāda, kur ir noticis bojājums, vai saglabāšanas vai izveidošanas laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7758">**errorSource** - dictates where the corruption occurred whether during save or create</span></span>

#### <a name="coredatadiagnostics"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7759">core.data.diagnostics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7759">core.data.diagnostics</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7760">Ļauj mums noteikt un novērst situācijas, kad mūsu e-pasta glabātuve izmanto pārāk lielu jūsu ierīces krātuves vietas apjomu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7760">Allows us to detect and fix situations where our email storage is using up too much of your device storage space</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7761">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7761">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7762">**db_size_megabytes** — izseko pamatdatu datubāzes izmēram, kas ir noapaļots līdz tuvākajiem 25 megabaitiem, ar maksimālo megabaitu 500</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7762">**db_size_megabytes** - tracks the size of the core data database rounded to the nearest 25 megabytes and with a maximum megabyte of 500</span></span>

#### <a name="generalpropertieslog"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7763">general.properties.log</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7763">general.properties.log</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7764">Šis notikums apkopo informāciju, kas ļauj mums kategorizēt un klasificēt Outlook lietojumprogrammas problēmas, kas ir saistītas ar pieejamības un ierīces iestatījumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7764">This event collects information that allows us to categorize and classify issues within the Outlook app that are related to accessibility and device settings.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7765">Šī kategorizācija ir nepieciešama, lai noteiktu problēmu ietekmes uz klientiem līmeni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7765">This categorization is necessary to prioritize the impact of issues on customers.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7766">Tālāk norādītie lauki tiek apkopoti tikai iOS:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7766">The following fields are collected for iOS only:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7767">**bold_text** — norāda, vai ierīcei ir ieslēgts treknraksta teksts, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt treknraksta tekstu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7767">**bold_text** - Tells us if the device has bold text turned on to help us detect issues related to bold text</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7768">**closed_captioning** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis slēptos titrus savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar slēptajiem titriem saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7768">**closed_captioning** - Tells us if the user has turned on closed captioning on their device to help us detect issues related to closed captioning</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7769">**darker_system_colors** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis tumšākas sistēmas krāsas savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums noteikt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7769">**darker_system_colors** - Tells us if the user has turned on darkening of system colors on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7770">**gray_scale** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis pelēktoņu sistēmas krāsas savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums noteikt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7770">**gray_scale** - Tells us if the user has turned on gray scale on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7771">**guided_access** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis piekļuvi ar ceļvedi savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums noteikt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7771">**guided_access** - Tells us if the user has turned on guided access on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7772">**invert_colors** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis krāsu inversijas iestatījumu savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7772">**invert_colors** - Tells us if the user has turned on the setting to invert colors on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7773">**mono_audio** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis mono skaņas iestatījumu savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7773">**mono_audio** - Tells us if the user has turned on the setting for mono audio on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7774">**reduce_motion** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis kustības samazināšanas iestatījumu savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7774">**reduce_motion** - Tells us if the user has turned on the setting for reducing motion on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7775">**reduce_transparency** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis caurspīdības samazināšanas iestatījumu savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7775">**reduce_transparency** - Tells us if the user has turned on the setting to reduce transparency on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7776">**speak_screen** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis mono skaņas iestatījumu savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7776">**speak_screen** - Tells us if the user has turned on the setting for mono audio on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7777">**speak_selection** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis runas atlases iestatījumu savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7777">**speak_selection** - Tells us if the user has turned on the setting for Speak Selection on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7778">**switch_control** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis Switch Control iestatījumu savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7778">**switch_control** - Tells us if the user has turned on the setting for Switch Control on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7779">**voice_over** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis VoiceOver iestatījumu savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7779">**voice_over** - Tells us if the user has turned on the setting for voiceover on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7780">Tālāk norādītie lauki tiek apkopoti tikai Android:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7780">The following fields are collected for Android only:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7781">**braille** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis Braila raksta iestatījumu savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7781">**braille** - Tells us if the user has turned on the setting to invert colors on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7782">**caption** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis slēptos titrus savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar slēptajiem titriem saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7782">**caption** - Tells us if the user has turned on closed captioning on their device to help us detect issues related to closed captioning</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7783">**color_inversion** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis krāsu inversijas iestatījumu savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7783">**color_inversion** - Tells us if the user has turned on the setting to invert colors on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7784">**high_contrast** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis augsta kontrasta iestatījumu savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7784">**high_contrast** - Tells us if the user has turned on the setting for high contrast on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7785">**large_text** — norāda, vai ierīcē ir ieslēgts lielizmēra teksta iestatījums, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7785">**large_text** - Tells us if the device has large text setting turned on to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7787">**supported_abis** — norāda, kāda veida lietojumprogrammu binārās saskarnes (ABI) tiek atbalstītas ierīces platformā, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7787">**supported_abis** - Tells us what kind of application binary interfaces (ABIs) are supported by the device platform to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7788">**switch_access** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis Switch Access iestatījumu savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7788">**switch_access** - Tells us if the user has turned on the setting for Switch Access on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7789">**talkback** — norāda, vai lietotājs ir ieslēdzis TalkBack iestatījumu savā ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt ar šo iestatījumu saistītās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7789">**talkback** - Tells us if the user has turned on the setting for talkback on their device to help us detect issues related to this setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7790">**webview_kernel_version**: Chromium kodola tīmekļa skata versija ierīcē, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt saderības problēmas, kas saistītas ar tīmekļa skatījuma versiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7790">**webview_kernel_version**: The Chromium kernel version of webview on the device to help us detect compatibility issues related to the version of webview.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7791">**webview_package_name**: ierīces tīmekļa skata paketes nosaukums, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt saderības problēmas, kas saistītas ar tīmekļa skatījuma versiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7791">**webview_package_name**: The package name of webview on the device to help us detect compatibility issues related to the version of webview.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7792">**webview_package_version**: ierīces tīmekļa skata paketes versija, lai palīdzētu mums atklāt saderības problēmas, kas saistītas ar tīmekļa skatījuma versiju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7792">**webview_package_version**: The package version of webview on the device to help us detect compatibility issues related to the version of webview.</span></span>

#### <a name="lowstoragewarning"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7793">low.storage.warning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7793">low.storage.warning</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7794">Ir nepieciešams, lai uzraudzītu, vai mūsu lietojumprogramma pēkšņi neaizņem lielāko daļu jūsu ierīces krātuves palielināta atmiņas izmantošanas apjoma dēļ, norādot brīdi, kurā ierīcei trūkst krātuves apjoma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7794">This is needed to monitor if our app suddenly takes up most of your device storage due to high memory usage by indicating when the device is low on storage</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7796">**free_bytes** — ierīcē pieejamās brīvās krātuves vietas apjoms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7796">**free_bytes** - the amount of free storage space available on the device</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspaceairspacelocalblocklistdriverupdated"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7797">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistDriverUpdated</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7797">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistDriverUpdated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7798">Lietotājs atjaunināja videokartes draiveri, kas iepriekš izraisīja Office avārijas, un tas vairs netiek izmantots atveidošanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7798">User has updated a video card driver that was previously causing Office crashes and thus no longer being used to render.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7799">Informē Microsoft, ka lietotājiem, kuriem bija pasliktināts atveidošanas stāvoklis, atkal ir ieteicamais atveidošanas stāvoklis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7799">Informs Microsoft that users who were once in a sub-optimal rendering state are once again in the recommended rendering state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7800">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7800">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7801">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** — bloķētā draivera versija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7801">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** - Version of the driver that was blocklisted.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7802">**Data\_DeviceId** — bloķētās videokartes ierīces identifikators.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7802">**Data\_DeviceId** -identifier of the video card device that was blocklisted.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7803">**Data\_UpdatedDriverVersion** — atjauninātā draivera versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7803">**Data\_UpdatedDriverVersion** - Version of the updated driver</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspaceairspacelocalblocklistinfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7804">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7804">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistInfo</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7805">Detalizēta informācija par lietotāja videokartes draiveri, kas izraisīja vairākas nesenas Office lietojumprogrammu avārijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7805">Details on the user's video card driver that has caused multiple recent crashes of Office applications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7806">Office neizmantos šo videokarti šajā Office sesijā (tā vietā izmantojot programmatūras atveidošanu), līdz draiveris būs atjaunināts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7806">Office will not use this video card in this Office session (using software rendering instead) until the driver is updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7807">Informē Microsoft par videokartes draiveri, kas rada problēmas sistēmā Office, lai identificētu tendences un analizētu šādu draiveru ietekmi uz lietotāju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7807">Informs Microsoft of video card drivers that are causing problems in Office so trends can be identified and the user of impact of such drivers can be analyzed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7808">Informējiet Microsoft, cik lietotāju ir šādā pasliktinātā stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7808">Tell Microsoft how many users are in this sub-optimal state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7809">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7809">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7810">**Data\_AllAppsBlocked** — vai visas Office lietojumprogrammas ir bloķētas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7810">**Data\_AllAppsBlocked** - Whether all Office apps are blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7811">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** — bloķētās videokartes ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7811">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** - identifier of the video card device that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7812">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** — bloķētā draivera versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7812">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** - Version of the driver that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7813">**Data\_CrashHistory** — virkne, kas attēlo videokartes draivera izraisītās avārijas, lai veiktu analīzi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7813">**Data\_CrashHistory** - A string that represents the history of video card driver caused crashes for analysis</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7814">**Data\_SecsBetweenCrashes** — cik bieži avarē draivera karte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7814">**Data\_SecsBetweenCrashes** - How frequently driver card crashes are occurring</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspaceairspacewincompisenabled"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7815">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceWinCompIsEnabled</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7815">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceWinCompIsEnabled</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7816">Vai tiek izmantota jaunākā Office zema līmeņa atveidošanas platforma, kuras pamatā ir Windows salikums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7816">Whether the latest Office low-level rendering platform based on Windows Composition is being used.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7817">Norit jaunākās Office zema līmeņa atveidošanas platformas izstrāde un piegāde klientiem, kas ļauj Microsoft redzēt, cik daudz lietotāju ir katrā versijā, lai nodrošinātu, ka platforma darbojas bez kļūdām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7817">As the latest Office low-level rendering platform is developed and begins to be released to customers, this allows Microsoft to see how many users are on each version to ensure the platform remains bug-free.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7818">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7818">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7819">**Data\_WinCompEnabled** — vai tiek izmantota Windows salikuma aizmugursistēma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7819">**Data\_WinCompEnabled** -Whether the Windows Composition-based backend is in use</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriverhangdetectorblocklistapp"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7820">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorBlocklistApp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7820">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorBlocklistApp</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7821">Lietotāja videokarte ir noteikta kā iemesls, kas izraisa ilgus vai neatkopjamus reaģēšanas pārtraukumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7821">User's video card has been detected as causing long or unrecoverable hangs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7822">Office neizmantos šo videokarti šajā Office sesijā (tā vietā izmantojot programmatūras atveidošanu), līdz draiveris būs atjaunināts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7822">Office will not use this video card in this Office session (using software rendering instead) until the driver is updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7823">Informē Microsoft par videokartes draiveri, kas rada problēmas sistēmā Office, lai identificētu tendences un analizētu šādu draiveru ietekmi uz lietotāju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7823">Informs Microsoft of video card drivers that are causing problems in Office so trends can be identified and the user of impact of such drivers can be analyzed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7824">Palīdz arī informēt, cik lietotāju ir šādā pasliktinātā stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7824">Also helps in informing how many users are in this sub-optimal state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7825">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7825">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7826">**Data\_AppName** — kurā programmā videokartes draiveris pārtrauca reaģēt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7826">**Data\_AppName** - Which app has encountered video card driver hangs</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriverhangdetectorregistrywrite"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7827">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorRegistryWrite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7827">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorRegistryWrite</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7828">Office konstatēja, ka lietotāja videokartes draiveris izraisīja reaģēšanas pārtraukumu, kas ir jāanalizē nākamajā Office lietojumprogrammas startēšanas reizē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7828">Office has identified that the user's video card driver has caused a hang that should be analyzed at the next Office application boot.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7829">Izmanto, lai noteiktu, vai cits videokartes draiveris vai adapteris nodrošina labāku lietotāja pieredzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7829">Used to determine whether using a different video card driver or adapter would offer a better user experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7830">Shēmu izpildes laikā Microsoft var veikt pielāgojumus, lai Office pieredzi saglabātu iespējami netraucētu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7830">As patterns occur, Microsoft may make adjustments to keep the Office experience as smooth as possible.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7831">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7831">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7832">**Data\_HangDetected** — vai tika konstatēts reaģēšanas pārtraukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7832">**Data\_HangDetected** - Whether a hang was detected</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7833">**Data\_InDeviceCall** — kādu videokartes atveidošanas izsaukumu veica Office, kad tā pārtrauca reaģēt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7833">**Data\_InDeviceCall** - Which video card rendering call Office was in when the hang occurred</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7834">**Data\_Timeout** — cik ilgi nereaģēja, ja notika atkopšanās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7834">**Data\_Timeout** - How long the hang lasted, if it recovered</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7835">**Data\_UnrecoverableCommand** — vai reaģēšanas pārtraukumu šajā videokartes atveidošanas komandā parasti iespējams atkopt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7835">**Data\_UnrecoverableCommand** - Whether the hang in this video card rendering command is typically recoverable.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7842">**Data.AllAppsBlocked** — vai visas Office lietojumprogrammas ir bloķētas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7842">**Data.AllAppsBlocked** - Whether all Office apps are blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7844">**Data.BlockedDriverVersion** — bloķētā draivera versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7844">**Data.BlockedDriverVersion** - Version of the driver that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7845">**Data.CrashHistory System.String** — virkne, kas attēlo videokartes draivera izraisītās avārijas, lai veiktu analīzi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7845">**Data.CrashHistory System.String** - A string that represents the history of video card driver caused crashes for analysis</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7846">**Data.SecsBetweenCrashes** — cik bieži avarē draivera karte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7846">**Data.SecsBetweenCrashes** - How frequently driver card crashes are occurring</span></span>
