#### <a name="officegraphicsspritememcorrupt"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7854">Office.Graphics.SpriteMemCorrupt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7854">Office.Graphics.SpriteMemCorrupt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7855">Uzrāda visas kļūdas, kas konstatētas Sprite atmiņas uzskaites telemetrijā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7855">Reports any errors detected in the sprite memory accounting telemetry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7856">Kritiski svarīgi, lai novērtētu grafikas atmiņas lietojuma telemetrijas darbspēju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7856">Critical for assessing health of the graphics memory usage telemetry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7857">Šī informācija ir nepieciešama, lai validētu mūsu SpriteMem telemetrijas datu pareizību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7857">This information is needed to validate the correctness of our SpriteMem telemetry.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7858">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7858">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7859">**Data\_CurrentSpriteMem** — kopējais atmiņas apjoms, kas tiek aktīvi piešķirta, lai noturētu Sprite objektus (attēlus), radot ekrāna saturu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7859">**Data\_CurrentSpriteMem** - Total amount of memory that is actively allocated to hold sprites (images) that result in screen content.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7860">**Data\_Function** — funkcijas nosaukums, kas mēģina atbrīvot Sprite atmiņu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7860">**Data\_Function** - The name of the function that is attempting to release sprite memory.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7861">**Data\_SpriteMemToRemove** — atmiņas apjoms, kas jānoņem no Sprite sadalījuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7861">**Data\_SpriteMemToRemove** - Amount of memory to be removed from sprite allocation.</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointpptsharednointernetconnectivity"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7862">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Shared.NoInternetConnectivity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7862">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Shared.NoInternetConnectivity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7863">Apkopo katru reizi, kad PowerPoint konstatē, ka nav interneta savienojuma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7863">Collected whenever PowerPoint detects there is no internet connectivity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7864">Microsoft izmanto šos datus, lai iegūtu diagnostikas informāciju par lietotāja interneta savienojumu un izprastu, kā tas ietekmē savienojumu ar Office pakalpojumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7864">Microsoft uses this data to get diagnostic information about the user's internet connection to be able to understand how that impacts connectivity to Office services.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7865">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7865">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7866">**Data\_IsNexusDetected:bool** – redzams, vai ir interneta savienojuma statuss, izsaucot Nexus pakalpojumu (patiesa vērtība) vai izsaucot standarta tīmekļa pakalpojuma API (aplama vērtība)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7866">**Data\_IsNexusDetected:bool** - shows whether we got the Internet connectivity status when calling Nexus service (value true) or when calling generic web service API call (value false)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerofficesvcmgrprofile"></a><span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7867">Office.ServiceabilityManager.OfficeSvcMgrProfile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7867">Office.ServiceabilityManager.OfficeSvcMgrProfile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7868">Notikums sākas brīdi, kad tiek sāknēts Office Serviceability Manager, un ir kritiski svarīgs, lai sniegtu ieskatu saistībā ar izvietošanas statusu, lietojumprogrammu un pievienojumprogrammu avārijām klienta nomniekā, ļaujot mums ģenerēt ieskatus, lai IT administrators spētu pārliecināti veidot atjauninājumus sava uzņēmumam datoriem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7868">This event is triggered when Office Serviceability Manager starts, and is critical for providing accurate insights related to Deployment Status and Application and Add-in crashes within customer's tenant by allowing us to generate insights for the IT Admin to be able to confidently roll out updates for their enterprise machines.</span></span>  

<span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7869">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7869">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7870">**DeviceIdJoinToken** — tiek izmantots, lai savienotu telemetrijas datus darbspējas un izvietošanas statusa ar citiem funkcionāliem datiem, kas tiek iegūti no pakalpojumu konveijera.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7870">**DeviceIdJoinToken** - used to join Telemetry data from Health and Deployment Status with other Functional Data which is collected via the Services pipeline.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="3ff28-7871">**TenantAssociationKeyStamped** — būlas karodziņš, kas tiek izmantots, lai noteiktu Office ekosistēmā pārvaldīto ierīču skaitu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3ff28-7871">**TenantAssociationKeyStamped** - a Boolean flag used to determine the number of Managed devices in the Office eco-system.</span></span>
